Comment: Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to score by a neck.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 600M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, unable to maintain position on turn, wider from 550M, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 900M, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide on turn, commenced move after passing 550M, made contact turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.

Began smartly from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, positioned 3 wide just ahead of midfield from 900M, carried wide after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Quickly into stride, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 3 wide from 900M, weakened turning in, emptied early in straight.
Rolled forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, drifted away 300M to score.
Pushed forward, 1 out 1 back, closed off strongly for 2nd.
In front of midfield, 2-3 wide, ran no well for 3rd.
Slow away, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, just held ground in straight.
At back, 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, bumped 800M, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, emptied 200M.
Pushed early, 2 wide at back, checked 1400M, bumped 800M, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 4-5 wide, ran on fairly.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 500M.
Ridden from widest barrier, raced in handy position, responded solidly in the straight, quickened near 200M to score.
Urged for some distance to race in box seat, passing 400M became unbalanced when crowded for room, responded nicely in the straight.
Sent forward, settled behind leaders, made ground passing 300M, finished well.
Raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, worked home well.
Ridden along after start then steadied to obtain cover passing 900M, settled towards rear, in the early part of straight was held up, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, near 350M became unbalanced when crowded for room, worked home one-paced.
Broke well, raced behind leaders, passing 800M lost left hind plate, near 750M travelled keenly and checked away from heels, one-paced in the straight, blood in trachea.
Crowded at start, then crowded again passing 900M, wide rounding the Home Turn, gave ground near 150M.
Ridden for some distance to race outside the lead, lay out rounding the Home Turn, gave ground near 200M.
Took lead with nice early speed, lay out in middle stages, made the Home Turn awkwardly, faded out passing 200M.
Began awkwardly and then lost ground, raced at tail, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly and race at rear, placed pressure but no response.

Raced in midfield, between runners, 4.5L from lead after first section. Moved wider, checked on cornering, before balancing & closing strongly. Assumed lead passing furlong mark before continuing on well in closing stages.

Not fast away, maintained rail position, improved to midfield after start. Pushed out away from rail on corner, sprinted up to assume lead at 275m before being joined & headed at the 200m. Fought strongly to hold second.

Bumped & lost ground at start, raced keenly when being steadied to race at tail. Continued a clear last on cornering, shifted wider when over 6L off lead, closed very fast in final 300m to finish close up third.

Shifted across behind runners after start, settling third from last, 3 wide with cover in early stages. Continued wide with cover, moved within 4L of lead on straightening, finished well in final section to be close behind.
Steadied after start, shifted across to race midfield on rail after first section. Moved away from the rail on cornering before finishing off evenly in last section to not be far behind.
Ridden forward after start before settling outside leader by the 1200m. Moved up to assume lead on cornering before being headed at the 275m & weakening a few lengths thereafter.
Began fast, steadied to midfield away from rail. Forced wider on cornering by runner-up, unbalanced on straightening before finishing off only fairly in final 350m.
Raced on leaders back throughout early & middle stages. Held up on straightening & continued in restricted room before failing to finish off in final 150m once clear.

Not bustled at start, allowed to drift back worse than midfield away from rail in early stages. Moved very wide approaching the corner before failing to make any further headway into margin in final section.

Shifted across behind runners after start & raced near the rear. Made some ground on cornering, entering last section 3.5L from lead on rail. Limited room 300m to 200m, before yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Shifted across after start to race worse than midfield, over 6L from lead after first section. Came under hard riding approaching the 550m mark before yielding a further 3L in straight. Well beaten.

Strode forward from wide gate, raced prominently until steadying to 1,1 passing the 1200m. Moved within a length of the lead entering final section before weakening badly final 250m. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Touch slow to begin, mustered speed after start to drive through and assume lead approaching 1200m. Headed in the lead on straightening before yielding significant ground in the last section to be well beaten.

Strode to midfield after start, left three wide without cover from the 1200m. Began yielding ground approaching bend, inconvenienced on cornering before giving significant ground in final section. Well beaten.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved closer after passing 800M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.

Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight near 250M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Quickly into stride, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer after passing 650M, wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began smartly from gate 1, showed good speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L behind the lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, slightly taken back near 950M, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 to 4 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly near 750M, no cover on turn, very wide into straight, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Away well, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Prominent, sat behind lead on outside rail, cruised home to win very comfortably by 3L.
Travelled in behind midfield, stand-side, ran home nicely for 2nd but was no match.
Crowded after start, settled midfield on centre-track, ran on well to take 3rd.
Jumped only fairly, on stand-side, closed off strongly inside final 300M.
Raced handy, on stand-side, kept on going to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, along the outside rail, ran on to the line.
Pushed, took led and sat on the outside rail, found no extra at 100M.
In worse than midfield, stand-side, ran on to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, on centre-track, remained in touch until 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, stand-side, remained one-paced.
In worse than midfield, on centre-tack, didn't save ground.
Slow to jump, at tail stand-side, shifted centre-track after 500M, did not threaten.
In midfield, stand-side, emptied passing 400M.
Sat in front of midfield, 1 off the outside rail, dropped off from 400M.(Blood in trachea and See Incident Report)
Settled in last few and waited with, switched out for a run entering home straight, quickened well to take charge over 100 metres out.
Taken back from a wide gate settling over 3L back in 5th off the rail, came to challenge under pressure after straightening, ran on steadily but not able to match pace of the winner.
Taken well back from the widest gate, commenced move 3-wide turning for home, ran on under pressure to grab 3rd over 100 metres out.
Disputed lead, gained narrow advantage briefly early in straight, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside the final 200 metres.
Set the pace on the rail, narrowly headed early in straight, swamped for a placing inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly settling one out one back, in similar position entering home straight, kept on until finding no extra 250 metres out.
Niggled along in last few, hampered and dropped further back 900 metres out, trailed the field rounding home bend and into the straight, produced some late impression closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled one back in 4th or 3rd on the rail, gradually weakened shortly after straightening.
Away well to be tracking leader along the 2-path, cruised to the lead 300M, quickened clear inside 200 under confident riding, won unextended.

Jumped on terms from inside gate, settled ahead of midfield 3-4Ls away, held up for clear running early straight, responded well from 300M, got up for 2nd inside 100M but unable to catch the easy winner.
Up with early pace, tracked leaders from 950M, couldn't quicken as well as the winner in straight, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Pressed forward, crossed to the lead 950M, driven out 350M, soon headed by the easy winner, faded to 4th towards the line.
Caught wide from draw 12 down the back straight, slotted into a 3-wide spot in midfield 850M, kept on evenly in the straight, not pace to challenge leaders.
Began fairly and crowded for room at start, recovered to sit behind midfield, 5Ls to make up top of straight but gave limited response only, never reach contention.
Chased leaders 3-wide without cover, outpaced by rivals on straightening, out of contention 300M.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover early stages, settled down 3rd from last 6Ls behind, failed to quicken in straight, never threatened.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover early stages, raced at the back 8-9Ls behind leader, still plenty to do turning for home, ran past beaten rivals only.
Settled just ahead of midfield, in touch turning for home but couldn't go on passing 400M, weakened towards the line.
Behind midfield on settling, 5Ls to make up top of straight, couldn't' find much when asked, never involved.

From wide draw steadied to obtain cover early stages, took up 2nd last spot, raced greenly early and middle stages, couldn't go on turning for home, eased over final 200M when no chance. (Jockey : raced greenly in straight and lay out.)

Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, kept on very well in straight but always held, lost 2nd close home.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, led by half length turning in, kept on well early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, bumped near 500M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on one pace.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled keenly after passing 900M, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, inconvenienced near 300M, ran on one pace thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, bumped near 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, wider from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, lost position turning in, crowded near 400M, failed to make any progress thereafter, finished last.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Fast into stride, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.

Shifted out at start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half length behind the leader on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off well without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly without threatening.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, no clear running until 250M, made some progress thereafter.
Away well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, kept on well to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, just ahead of midfield, wider from 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1-1/2L behind the leader, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Slightly slow out, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear, 3 lengths or so back, hard ridden from 400M, finished off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, raced 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, no clear running until final 150M, made good progress thereafter to take a place without threatening.
Clean jump, raced prominently near to the stands rail, peaked 300M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 14, positioned a length or so back, 2 away from the stands rail, not enough room near 300M, raced tight 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned a length or so back in the middle of the track, made some progress after passing 400M, no extra final 200M.

Crowded shortly after start and unbalanced, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden from 350M, showed some response, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced prominently nearer to the middle of the track, showed limited response after passing 400M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M, only showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently in the middle of the track, took brief lead 350M, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, detached from the main group early, moved a bit closer in the middle stages but still 5 lengths back at 400M, kept on evenly to the line.
Clean jump, raced prominently on the stands rail, hard ridden from 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Away well from the middle draw, raced prominently on the middle track, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands rail, peaked 400M, weakened thereafter.
Pushed early, settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to secure box seat, pace good, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, pace good, held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, pace good, made minor ground 250M.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, weakened 200M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, lack room 4-2, ran on fairly.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, pace good, emptied in straight.
At back, trapped 3 wide, pace good, no progress.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, pace good, never improved.
Slow away, never traveled at rear.
Checked start, never competitive.
Niggled to take lead with nice early speed, responded solidly when asked for effort, finished strongly to score.
Raced outside the leader on rail, battled well in the concluding stages, missed by Neck.
Ridden along, raced in handy position, improved passing 350M, finished solidly.
Crowded at start, raced in handy position in middle of track, came home solidly.
Settled behind midfield, gained nice ground passing 300M, finished nicely, rider questioned.
Raced behind the leaders, placed pressure passing 500M, worked home one-paced.
Fractious in barrier and dislodged its rider, settled midfield, one-paced when under pressure, must Stalls test.
Urged along to share lead, gave ground near 200M.
Settled behind leaders, asked for effort passing 450M, weakened passing 200M.
Fractious in barrier and dislodged its rider, raced midfield on rail, gave ground passing 200M, must trial.
Settled midfield in middle of track, limited response when asked for effort.
Hard ridden to settle midfield, weakened near 200M, roar.
Began only fairly, raced detached in the early stages, no response when placed pressure.
Began awkwardly and raced greenly, no response.
Strode forward from wide gate before racing in second away from rail. Moved up to assume the lead passing the 350m mark before continuing on thereafter to hold narrow margin on the line.
Began well, shared early lead before racing leaders back from the 1100m. Shifted into clear running approaching the 300m, improved to second at the 200m & continued strongly late to just miss.

Not fast into stride before improving to midfield away from rail. Moved wider on straightening, entered last section under 3L from lead, improved strongly to second inside the 150m before finishing a close up third on line.

Shifted across after start & raced a clear last after 100m. Continued rearward, over 6.5L from lead on straightening before moving wider & making up many lengths in the final 350m to be close behind. Sharply improved.
Shifted behind runners to race on the rail before improving to midfield approaching the 1000m. Shifted out passing the 400m before making solid late ground in the final furlong to not be far behind.

Raced in midfield between runners before racing keenly between the 800m & 600m. Held up on straightening & near the 300m before shifting into clear running & making up a few lengths thereafter. Not beaten far.

Shifted across after the start & raced towards the rear in the early & middle stages. Momentarily held up on straightening before getting into clear running & finishing well in the final 300m. Not beaten far.
Not the fastest away, improved after start to race midfield on the rail. Shifted out after straightening, held up near the 175m before finishing off ok in late stages.
Shifted behind runners after start, settling second from last on the rail. Stayed close to the inside rail on cornering, held up from the 250m to the 200m before holding midfield position thereafter.

Strode to midfield but was left wide without cover in early & middle stages. Moved wider on straightening when just under 4L from lead before peaking on effort passing the 250m & offering no more in the last furlong.

Strode forward after start before being crossed and getting good position in 4th away from rail. Moved up within a length of the lead at the 350m before peaking shortly after & giving 5 lengths in last 250m.

Steadied to obtain cover after 100m before racing very keenly throughout the early & middle stages. Continued with only 2 runners behind entering the last section, over 5L from lead, before weakening a further length late.
Improved after the start to assume the lead near the 1100m. Headed on the outside passing the 350m & yielded ground in the final 250m. Well beaten.

Refused to settle when being steadied after start before being bumped & racing very wide near the rear from the 1100m. Continued wide passage into bend before entering final section in last. Never improved & was well beaten.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 600M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well, positioned 1 out 1 back, carried wider after passing 600M, same margin behind the leader turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, just outpaced by the winner.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 700M, angled out after passing 600M, kept on well in straight but outpaced by the first two.
Away well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 to 3 wide, 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well, no threat to the first few.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, angled out 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Slightly slow out, showed no early speed, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with them, raced 6 lengths behind the leader, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight, finished last.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, stayed neck to neck to the line, edged ahead to win by a short-head.
Niggled along, raced in box-seat, ran on gamely in a duel battle, finished 2nd, a short-head behind.
Awkward start, raced in midfield, 2 wide, continued nicely for 3rd but was no match to first two.
Crowded start, settled at rear along the rail, swung widest, made ground and ran on nicely.
Raced in behind midfield, wide but with cover, ran on well to the finish.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly late.
Bumped start, settled midfield, wide but with cover, remained one paced.
Sent forward, took rail and led, weakened gradually from 200M out.
Taken back, at rear 2 wide, ran on but saved no ground.
Rolled forward, raced outside the lead, in touch until weakened at 250M.
Lost ground at start, recovered in behind midfield, along the rail, showed nothing.
Slow to jump, settled midfield along the rail, faded out from 200M.
Eased back, travelled wide but with cover, not competitive. (See Incident Report)
Prominent, but trapped wide and without cover, finished tailed out in straight. Must trial.(Mucus in trachea)
Settled in midfield near the rail, in similar position turning in, ran on well between runners inside the 200 metres and hit the front close to home.

Crowded at start losing ground, settled in last few before racing keenly just worse than midfield, obtained clear passage shortly after straightening, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
Began well settling one out one back, improved 3-wide around home bend to hit the front into straight, kept on until overhauled inside final 100 metres.

Broke well from a wide gate settling wide without cover in forward of midfield, improved 4-wide rounding home bend to join the leaders turning for home, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden to share the lead from a wide gate, amongst the leaders rounding home bend and into straight, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate, taken back to 6th within 3L of the pace, in similar position turning in, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Taken well back from the widest gate travelling wide, came under pressure rounding home bend and went the widest turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish. (Blood in trachea)
Chased the leaders to home straight, gradually weakened under pressure.
Jostled at start, remained in rear to home straight, made some late impression closing stages.
Hampered at start, settled wide in rear of midfield from a wide gate, drifted wider turning in, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, always at the back despite niggling along, made no show. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly and quickly picked up to share the lead on the rail, headed upon straightening and folded up quickly. (Lame)
Settled down in midfield 2-wide, 3Ls off leader top of straight, quickened well to lead near 150M, kept on momentum to the line.
Bumped and crowded for room at the start, raced near the rear 6-7Ls back, in a difficult position turning in and unable to obtain clear running until 150M, closed off well to go 2nd near line.

Positively ridden, crossed to track leader, steadied 350M when commencing a run down the fence, shifted out to find clear running, closed off reasonably well to claim 3rd in a blanket finish for minor placings.
Not hurried after the jump, held up behind mid-division, got steadied 900M, made stealthy progress between horses over final 300M to go 4th in blanket finish for the minor placings.
Held up behind midfield, shifted out to improve nearing 500M, stayed on to claim 5th in a blanket finish for the minor placings.

Settled down ahead of midfield, wide no cover from 1000M, urged along 500M, quickened up to join leaders near 200M, battled on to line, narrowly missed out on podium in blanket finish for minor placings.
Restrained behind leaders, commenced to travel keenly 1100M, checked 950M, responded well early straight to challenge for the lead 200M, one paced final stages.
Settled 3-wide, 4Ls off the pace in midfield, pushed along 600M, kept on steadily under pressure in straight, always held by leaders.
Pressed forward to lead as expected, driven 350M but couldn't shake off rivals, headed by pursuers 200M, weakened towards the line.
Began well from draw 1, restrained to race in midfield, no clear run early straight, couldn't go on from 300M. (Bled 2nd time.)
Dropped back to the rear from wide draw, 5Ls to make up 400M, failed to pick up when switched to outside on straightening. Never in the picture.

Crowded for room at start, recovered to race outside the leader, couldn't find extra when pushed along 500M, dropped away from 200M. (Jockey : off the bridle 900M, failed to finish off in the straight / Unacceptable Performance.)
Caught wide early stages, taken back to near last 6Ls off the pace, commenced to travel keenly 750M, failed to finish off on straightening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail, slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began smartly from gate 10, raced in 3rd, 4 lengths or so back, moved closer in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always held by the winner.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back turning in, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 300M, found daylight 200M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide turning, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out abruptly at start and bumped, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider near 900M, no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Bumped start, taken back to race 3 wide with no cover at rear, sent forward after passing 1100M, took the lead near 850M, 2 wide turning, headed near 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 850M, retook the lead turning in, peaked early in straight, headed and weakened from 250M.
Taken back from barrier 12, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 800M, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to score, impressive debut.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well after turning in, just unable to hold off the impressive winner final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Slightly slow out, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, just behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made good progress early in straight, raced tight near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress early in straight, raced tight near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, one pace thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found cover near 850M, commenced move after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 850M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover in the middle stages, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score by a head.
Commenced well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 200M, kept on very well but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, headed near 200M, stayed on well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight, no threat to the first few.
Clean jump, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, closed off well to score.
Eased to sit in midfield trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, on heels 250M, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Slow away, raced keenly at back, 2-4 wide, made ground 200M.
Pushed early, trapped wide, then eased back for cover, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, checked 250M, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, bumped 250M, emptied 200M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Failed to muster, took rail at rear, suited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, no progress.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort passing 300M, quickened passing 200M to score.
Settled midfield on rail, niggled near 700M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, made up some nice late ground.
Settled behind leaders, placed pressure near 400M, wide on straightening, responded nicely in the straight.
Stumbled on jumping, raced in front of midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, responded well in the straight.
Settled in handy position on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, fought hard and gained some ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 400M, made up some late ground.
Taken back at start, raced at rear on rail, one-paced in the straight.
After the 1400M was left racing wide and without cover in handy position, widest on straightening, one-paced.
Sent forward and took lead passing 1300M, weakened passing 200M.
Raced midfield, tried to improve passing 700M, limited response in the straight.
Crowded on jumping, settled behind midfield, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, approaching the winning post on the first occasion became badly unbalanced and bumped rail, raced at tail, no failed to run on.

Steadied approaching the first bend before drifting back to race midfield. Moved wider & improved quickly at the 400m before cornering the widest. Sprinted quickly in straight, assumed lead at the 100m & drew away. Easy win.

Ridden forward after start, assumed lead, crossed to rail by the 900m. Raced two lengths clear on cornering & continued to hold lead until being passed inside the last 100m. Held second closing stages.

Improved to midfield after first turn when racing 4 wide without cover in middle stages. Continued to cover extra ground approaching the corner, improved to 3rd at the 225m & battled on strongly in last furlong.

Bumped & lost some ground at start before settling worse than midfield on rail. Travelled strongly before being momentarily held up near 400m, cornered rearward before finishing off strongly in last 250m to be just behind third.

Steadied from widest gate to race second last away from rail. Moved wider entering the final section when nearly 7 lengths from lead, before making good late headway in final 200m to not be far behind.

Hampered after start before shifting back to last. Continued at the rear, 7 lengths from lead entering last section. Moved the widest runner after straightening & made solid late ground from rearward position. Not beaten far.
Began fast before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 900m. Three lengths from lead entering the final section before yielding a further 2 lengths in the straight. No threat.
Began well, crossed after start before racing in midfield between runners. Came under pressure approaching the 400m before yielding a further length in straight. Never threatened.
Hampered slightly after start, shifted back to third from last. Over 5 lengths from lead entering the final section & made no further improvement in the straight.
Pushed to midfield, racing wide, before being left wide without after improving to 4th by the 800m. Momentarily shared second placing on straightening before weakening out in final 250m. Well beaten.

Crossed after first bend, held midfield position on rail throughout early & middle stages. Continued on inside on cornering, awkwardly placed nearing the 200m but had limited response thereafter. Well beaten.
Improved after the start, moving to second, away from rail by the 850m. Niggled along before straightening & gave significant ground in the straight to be long last.
Out in line, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, wider on turn, finished off very strongly to score.

Moderately away, raced 3w behind midfield early, travelled keenly 1050M, 4w with no cover after entering the back straight, sent forward after passing 800M, 3w turning, took the lead 200M, kept on well but headed 50M, finished 2nd.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide at rear, wider from 800M, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 550M, finished off well without threatening.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider after entering the back straight, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, found rail near 500M, moved closer along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, took the lead 1100M, challenged by rival turning in, headed near 350M, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, peaked on turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to quicken under pressure in straight, eased final 100M.
Away with them, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Settled to race outside the lead, sprinted home nicely, scored unchallenged.
Taken back, at rear 2 wide, saved ground and closed off strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, continued run on the inside, continued on fairly for 3rd.
Rolled forward into the lead, on rail, headed passing 250M, one paced.
Travelled in midfield, wide and without cover throughout, ran on to the line.
Slotted in to be in midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot.
Raced at the rear, along the rail, improved slightly only.
Rolled forward and sat in box-seat, was one paced in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Eased, raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, did not quicken in the straight.
Settled just off the pace off the rail, travelled one back in 2nd 2-wide down back straight, hit the front over 400 metres out, ridden out.
Settled in 6th in midfield 2-wide, became 9th coming onto home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, ran home well inside final the final 200 metres.
Taken back from a wide gate to last few for cover, made rapid progress out wide down back straight, given reminders 400 metres out, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled about 3L off the pace in 4th 2-wide, became 5th leaving the Rock, came under pressure entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Pressed forward from the widest gate for rails run, ceded advantage to settle just off the pace in 3rd coming onto first bend, remained similar turning for home, kept on steadily without threatening.

Settled well behind, commenced move from the Rock to reach midfield 3-wide just over 4L off the pace at home bend, shifted wider making final bend, fought on steadily down the centre of the straight and without threatening.
Broke well from the one gate settling some 4L off the pace in 5th on the rail, in similar position in 6th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Settled just worse than midfield, shuffled backward under pressure rounding home bend, very wide entering home straight, made up some late ground.
Slightly slow out settling well behind, made steady progress out wide from the 800 metres reaching rear of midfield 4-wide rounding home bend, wider entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Settled in midfield on the rail, shuffled back to last few going up the Rock, one of the last entering straight but saved ground turning in, made no further impression.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning for home, never seen with a chance. (Questioned for disappointing performance).
Moderate start, took up running passing the winning post the first time, led until headed over 400 metres out, dropped out.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, hit the line strongly on straightening, got up close home.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, switched wide nearing 400M, quickened up well to lead passing 200M, caught by fast finishing winner close home.
Jumped best, restrained to track leaders, driven near 300M, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to take lead, led at even pace, driven out 350M, caught inside 200M, no extra late but held on to 4th.
Not hurried early stages, took up a position behind midfield, niggled along 500M, stayed on moderately.
Began fairly, ended up racing near the rear 6Ls back, took a while to pick up in straight, did best work late.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, bumped 200M, ran on mildly.
Outside leader, couldn't go on turning into straight, laboured home final 200M.
Dropped back from wide draw, soon detached in last, still 7Ls to make up 400M, failed to pick up.
Steadied early stages from wide draw, held up 3-wide behind midfield, wide into straight, failed to run on.
Began well from draw 1, chased leaders along the fence, kept on same pace turning in, steadied 150M, weakened towards the line.
Bustled along after the start, settled down midfield 3Ls back, saved ground on inside, driven along 400M out, soon outpaced.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide turning in, finished off very strongly, just narrowly beaten.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 200M, finished off well to make frame. (Lame left hind leg next day morning.)
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 450M, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, just behind midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Away well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader, kept on well to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, saved ground throughout, still 8 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, positioned 7 lengths back on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 150M, soon weakened.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide with no cover at rear early, 2 wide from 800M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Away well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly early, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few late.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.

Jumped well, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, slightly taken back after passing 1000M, positioned 3w with cover, 1-2Ls back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide from 800M, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, ran home one paced.
Stumbled at start, raced prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, weakened turning in, emptied early in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led at good pace, made all.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, held up 4-2, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Slow away, trapped 3-5 wide at rear, pace good, dashed well 250M.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, blocked most straight, just held ground.
Eased to sit just behind the pace, 2 wide, no dash.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, pace good, blocked most straight, dashed well to the line.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, pace good, weakened 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped wide, improved 1100M to sit outside the leader, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, made early move 700M, emptied 300M.
At back, never progressed.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, never improved.
Never competitive.
Settled in front of midfield, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 200M to score.
Taken back at start, settled towards rear, widest on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Began very awkwardly, settled at tail, quickened passing 200M, rider questioned.
Settled in box seat, passing 900M lost ground when awkwardly placed, asked for effort on straightening, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, battled hard in the straight, made some late ground in the straight.
Travelled midfield, placed pressure passing 450M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 200M.
Urged for some distance to take lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Slow to begin, raced at rear on rail, placed pressure in the straight but limited response.
Began awkwardly and lost ground when crowded, limited response in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, limited response when asked for effort.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, raced greenly in the straight.
Pushed to send forward, raced outside the lead, faded out passing 250M.
Jumped sharply, wide and without cover throughout in handy position, in the straight gave ground, blood trachea.
Not fast away, settled third from last in early & middle stages. Moved the second widest on cornering before finishing powerfully to strike the lead inside the last 100m. Easy late.

Ridden hard to hold midfield position between runners after start. Moved three wide, with cover at the 1000m. Sprinted quickly to assume the lead at the 175m before being headed soon after. Held second, well clear of third.

Ridden forward to assume the lead after 250m. Joined & shared the lead near the 850m before regaining shortly after. Headed near the 200m before digging deep late to regain third placing. Well behind first two.

A touch slow to begin, shifted across behind runners before improving to race in midfield on rail. Niggled along from the 500m before shifting out at the 300m & finishing off ok thereafter. No match for first two.

Shifted to midfield when racing 4 wide in early stages before improving position to share the lead by the 850m. Regained the lead momentarily near the 200m before peaking shortly after due to wide passage.
Raced in midfield before improving position in second section when racing three wide without cover. Cornered less than 2L from lead but could offer no more in final 250m after tough trip.
Raced in midfield away from rail before easing three wide with cover from half-way. Moved the widest runner on cornering when 4 lengths from lead & could only maintain that margin in final section.

Steadied after start & taken back to race a clear last after first section. Hard ridden from the 550m when a long way from lead before moving wider in the straight & making up a few lengths late. Too far back to threaten.

Improved after the first bend & raced worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Was well back and wide on straightening before being untested by rider in the straight. (Rider questioned – must trial).

Shifted across behind runners after the start before racing in midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail nearing the 500m when travelling strongly before offering little response in the straight. Well held.

Pushed forward after the start & raced outside the leader. Obtained cover from the 850m when shuffled back to third. Eased wider approaching the bend before peaking at the 300m & yielding ground thereafter.
Strode forward before racing away from the rail, one pair from the lead. Hard ridden from the 550m before yielding significant ground in the last section. Well beaten.

Steadied & shifted behind runners to race second from last. Shuffled back to last at half-way. Continued at the rear over 8L from lead at the 400m & yielded further ground in last section. Well beaten. (Lame post-race).
Held early lead before being crossed and racing on leaders back from the 1300m. Came under heavy riding approaching the 400m & yielded significant ground in last section. (Poor perf. – must trial).
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, same position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, ran on evenly, headed final 50M.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 850M, led by half length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, inconvenienced near 900M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Lifted front feet on jumping, then bumped, raced at rear on the inside, travelled keenly near 700M, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear, difficult to settle on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest on straightening, closed off strongly to score by 1/2L.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, no clear daylight until 250M, then checked at 150M, closed off nicely thereafter.
Niggled, settled to race outside the lead, bumped at 50M, despite that fought on solidly to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, bumped at 50M, ran on reasonably nonetheless.
Rolled forward to race in box-seat, remained one paced to the line.
Jumped only fairly, sat behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground and ran on nicely.
Raced in front of midfield, wide and without cover, ran on fairly to the line.
Travelled in midfield, along the rail, closed off fairly late.
Slow to jump, settled in behind midfield, wide but with cover, continued to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide, shifted away from heels at 350M then laid out, pretty one paced.
In one-out one-back position, found no extra for final 200M.
Bumped start, sat in behind midfield, 2 wide, steadied near 300M then held up until 200M, ran on thereafter.
Taken back, at rear throughout, never a factor.
In midfield, wide but with cover, run ended 200M out.
Moderate start, settled mainly in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, switched in for a run upon straightening, ran on to gain upper hand close to home.
Broke well, settled one-out-one-back just off the pace, became over nearly 3L back in 4th when pace quickened around the bend, ran on steadily under pressure but unable to peg back the winner.
Unbalanced at start, settled wide in midfield in 7th, similar but wider turning for home, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.

Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate, recovered to join the leaders 3-wide 1100 metres out, pulled to the front 2-wide rounding home bend kicking 2L clear early in straight, swamped under pressure inside the final 50 metres.
Began fairly, soon came forward to share early lead, taken one back for 3rd with cover when pace quickened around home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled better than midfield in 5th on the rail, drifted slightly backward when pace quickened on the bend, fought on steadily on the rail without threatening.
Crowded at start, settled wide in rear of midfield, drifted backward rounding home bend, remained wide into the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, quickly recovered to midfield, came under pressure to challenge after straightening, ran home one-paced. (Blood in trachea)
Settled in last few on the rail from a low gate, switched out for a run upon straightening, ran on steadily.
Broke well to lead from a wide draw, obtained rails run coming onto home bend before drifting one back to 2nd, faded shortly after straightening.
Settled just worse than midfield, dropped to last few into home straight, made up some late ground closing stages.
Crowded at start, settled in last few, baulked for a run early in straight, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Jumped fairly, soon taken well back, saved ground turning for home but did not find much under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly, soon dropped well behind racing wide, widest runner turning in, made no show in home straight.
Never far off the pace, in 5th spot from 1300M, switched wide nearing top of straight, finished off well to lead 150M out, firmly in control final stages.
Up with early pace, 4th on settling, switched wide 600M to challenge, quickened to lead nearing 300M, not pace of winner final 150M, held on 2nd just.
Crossed to a 2-wide spot in rear of midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, finished off fastest, just missed 2nd.
Taken back on jumping, held up near the rear 8Ls back, inclined to lay in home turn, ran on moderately to line but always held by first 3.
Given a patient ride at the rear 8-9Ls behind leader, made some progress final 400M but unable to trouble first 3.
Towards the rear 3-wide, lost cover from 1300M, swung wide into straight, stayed on without threatening.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear as expected, caught wide throughout, stayed on over final 400M but never threatened leaders.
Settled down midfield 4-5Ls behind leader, ran on fairly turning home, never going the pace to challenge.
From draw 10 caught wide on the first bend, strode forward to take lead 1100M, headed near 300M, soon no extra and weakened.
Held up in mid-division, driven out 500M but gave limited response only, never near to challenge.
Up with early pace, tracked leader 2-wide on settling, couldn't go on passing 350M, weakened away.
From draw 1 settled down in rear of midfield, driven along 600M, failed to improve position.

Strolled forward to take early lead, tracked leader 1100M, didn't respond to riding turning home, weakened rapidly. (Jockey : circumstances of the race significantly different from last start when successful.)
Began awkwardly and lost ground, towards the rear always, outpaced turning home, soon beaten.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to score. (Blood in trachea.)

Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, crowded near 1150M, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed very good response early in straight, blocked near 250M, made good progress when clear final 100M to take 2nd.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take a place, good debut.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on rail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from near 800M, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, crowded 500M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths or so back, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, 3 wide from 500M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, sent forward after passing 800M, made contact 500M, very wide into straight, weakened gradually in the run home.
Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 800M, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began smartly from gate 12, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide turning in, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned 6 to 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, slightly improved along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1000M, challenged by rival turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 9 lengths or so back, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, angled out 600M, same margin back turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, travelled keenly early, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from 1050M, a bit closer on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths back, no cover throughout, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Average to begin, taken back to race 3 to 4 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few late.
Began very awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 50M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, make good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, unable to obtain clear run, not able to test properly.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 to 4 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden early, midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Eased at start, at rear, 2 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M despite not suited by the slow pace, lack room 100M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 100M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, no dash in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 100M.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, emptied 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, emptied 250M.
At back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Trapped 3 wide throughout, never competitive.
Pushed along from wide barrier, raced outside the lead, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, wide rounding the Home Turn and on straightening, quickened ground passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, wide on straightening, responded nicely in the straight.
Raced in handy position, passing 700M was left wide and without cover, placed pressure passing 400M, fought well in the straight.
Began only fairly then failed to muster speed despite being hard ridden, raced at back, made some ground passing 100M.
Jumped sharply, Raced midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, gained some ground near 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on rail, held up from 250M to 200M, near 100M again had difficult to obtain clear running, not fully tested.
Urged to race in box seat, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, gave ground passing 150M.
Settled in handy position, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start then detached in middle stages, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, tried to improve near 400M, limited response in the straight, mucus in trachea.
Urged along to take lead, faded out near 100M.

Raced on the leaders back for the majority. Moved three wide around tiring leader passing the 500m, made gradual ground in the straight, struck the lead inside the final 100m & continued to line for narrow win.

Shifted across from wide gate at winning post, before obtaining the rail & getting economical run throughout. Moved away from rail on straightening, shifted inwards at furlong, made steady late ground. Narrowly beaten.

Strode forward before being crossed passing 1200m & racing second away from rail. Moved up to assume lead passing the 500m, raced clear on straightening. Maintained lead until being joined inside final 100m. Close behind.

Began well before being headed & racing in midfield away from rail. Continued in midfield, 4L from lead at half-way. Ran on into forth in in the straight but effectively held margin relative to winner in dash home.

Shifted behind runners to race rearward after first turn. Moved wider with cover passing the 800m. Hard ridden passing the 550m, shifted the widest on straightening before making some late ground to well held forth.

Shifted across to race worse than midfield early, checked when pace slowed near 800m & consequently relegated to second last. Over 7 lengths form lead on cornering before closing off in fastest last section from poor position.

Slow to begin, settled back early, moved wider & improved around field from the 800m, getting within 2L from lead at 600m. Forced 4 wide passing the 600m, peaked shortly after straightening & yielded a few lengths thereafter.

Held midfield position in early & middle stages before moving three wide & improving approaching the 600m. Moved the second widest on straightening before peaking shortly after. Yielded a length or two in final furlong.

Strode forward after start before settling in forth position, away from rail with cover. Moved three wide passing the 600m, cornered around 2L form lead before peaking shortly after straightening. Didn't threaten.
Steadied after start, shifted back to last. Continued a clear last entering last section, and despite making up a length or two relative to leaders was well beaten & was never likely.

Hard ridden after start before crossing to rail in the lead by the 1200m. Headed in the lead passing the 500m when coming under heavy pressure before weakening out noticeably in last section. (Rider questioned).
Raced in midfield on rail in early & middle stages. Shuffled back nearing corner, only 3 runners behind, peaked on straightening & weakened out to well beaten last.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.

Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 3rd.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 4 lengths or so back on turn, wider after passing 400M, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, kept going and worked home nicely to score by 1-1/4L.
Settled in one-out one-back position, ran on well to take 2nd.
Sent forward to take rail and led, found no extra and headed at 150M, just hung onto 3rd.(Whip dropped at 250M)
Eased then raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, improved steadily before closing off nicely late.
Crowded start, at rear thereafter, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on only one paced.
Lost ground shortly after start, in behind midfield along the rail, continued fairly to the line.
Awkward start, at rear along the rail, niggled throughout, closed off fairly late.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed no dash in the straight.
Urged but outpaced, settled midfield along the rail, ran on until weakened late.
In front of midfield, along the rail, emptied inside final 100M.
Urged and settled in box-seat, couldn't sustain run in the straight.
Broke well from a middle draw and tracked the leader, came to challenge rounding home bend and gained upper hand 200 metres out, just held on to the line.
Settled in midfield on the rail, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on well inside the final 200 metres, did best work late.
Held narrow lead on the rail after beginning from the one draw, led the field until joined rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back to rear and waited with, ran on under pressure in straight to be nearest at finish.
Slightly sluggish at start, soon recovered under pressure to be one back in 3rd on the rail, in similar position but 4th rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Travelled just over 2L back in 4th, became 5th when pace slackened over 600 metres out, shifted wide into straight, ran home one-paced.

Pressed forward from a wide gate before settling for 5th and 3-wide without cover, commenced run from the 600 metres reaching within 1L of the leaders around home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled worse than midfield on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on well to finish.
Settled wide behind midfield after beginning from the widest gate, gained slightly closer when pace slackened 600 metres out, very wide turning in, kept on one pace.
Moderate start from a wide gate, trailed the field until making short-lived effort under pressure rounding home bend, widest runner turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled in midfield, gained closer leaving the Rock just before hampered and lost position inside the 500 metres, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Crossed to a 2-wide spot tracking the pace, quickened up strongly passing 300M, strode well clear 150M winning by dominant margin
Jumped well, chased leaders, lacked winner's turn of foot from 300M, kept on steadily for non-threatening 2nd.
Settled down in 5th just ahead of mid-division, kept on final 300M to take 3rd without threatening the runaway winner.
Went forward to be sharing the lead on inside, couldn't hold off winner 250M, ran home one paced final 200M.
Strode forward after the start, shared lead on outside, outpaced by leaders passing 300M, no longer a threat from mid-straight.
Began awkwardly, pushed along to hold a midfield spot along the fence, kept on fairly in the straight, never able to challenge.
Caught wide down the back straight, steadied to a position near the rear entering home turn, wide into straight, made limited progress, never involved.
Taken back on wide draw, settled back in last 7Ls behind leaders, ran past beaten rivals in the straight, never reached leaders.
Dropped back to near last, pushed along 500M, couldn't go on. No impression on leaders.
Slightly slow away, settled in midfield, made the turn awkwardly after 600M, soon beaten on straightening.
Held up 3-wide towards the rear, 6Ls off the pace 400M, struggled home, well beaten.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, found cover after passing 700M, 2 wide from 450M, kept on well to lead narrowly 50M, won by half length.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, carried wider after 450M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner 50M, finished 2nd.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, kept on well to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 750M, a bit closer on turn, angled out 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 400M, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, 2 wide from 800M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 700M, headed turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
