Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 650M, 3 wide turning in, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide in midfield early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, hard ridden from 600M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 8 lengths back, moved closer after passing 1000M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, missed 2nd on line.

Jumped well, sat right behind the leader, difficult to settle early, angled out 1500M, sent forward 1200M, 2 wide in 2nd in the middle stages, challenged the leader turning in, kept on evenly in straight. (Dropped whip near 200M.)
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well in the middle stages, challenged turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, found cover near 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned on rail, slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, made all.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, took rail, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, made good ground.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, suited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased at start, too cover at rear, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
At back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 300M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, never competitive.
Never better than midfield.
Jumped well, race in front of midfield, asked for effort on straightening, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Began only fairly, pushed along to race in front of midfield on rail, passing 1200M travelled keenly and awkwardly placed, shifted out near 500M to improve, quickened near 100M, finished solidly.
Took box seat with nice early speed, improved near 300M, fought well in the straight.
Jumped nicely then sent forward to race behind the lead, placed pressure passing 500M, near 75M was steadied away from heels, finished well.
Settled in handy position on rail, placed pressure passing 400M, made some ground in the straight.
Travelled in handy position, battled hard in the straight, one-paced passing 200M.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, gained some ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on rail, worked home one-paced.
Taken back at start, race behind midfield, niggled near 800M, wide on straightening, one-paced.
Raced at rear on rail, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Urged along to take lead, tried to improve passing 400M, faded out passing 300M.
Settled midfield on rial, always niggled to maintain its position, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, weakened near 200M.
Settled midfield, tried to improve near 600M, weakened near 200M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.

Began only fairly before being hard ridden to improve to midfield away from the rail. Moved wider on cornering, around 6 lengths form lead before finishing hard to strike the lead at the 100m & draw away late.

Ridden forward after start & improved from midfield to race one pair behind lead, away from rail. Moved up within a length of the lead inside the last furlong before being passed by winner soon after. Finished close behind.

Steadied behind runners after start, before soon settling last. Moved the widest runner on straightening when over 8 lengths from the lead before making strong late headway into third in closing stages. Fastest final section.
Raced just worse than midfield on rail, 6.5 lengths form lead at the 800m. Continued worse than midfield on cornering before making steady headway in closing 300m. Not beaten far.
Began fast & strode to lead. Continued in the lead until being joined at the 100m mark by the winner & continued to battle on before weakening a length or two late.
Didn't have the early speed of others & drifted back to 4th last on rail. Continued with only three behind on straightening before making gradual headway in final 300m to not be beaten far.
Raced a touch wide after start before improving slightly to race midfield away from rail. Only 3.5 lengths from lead entering the last section before maintaining that margin to the line.

Steadied after the start, shifted across behind runners, settling third last. Entered the last section in last position over 10 lengths from the lead before making up significant late ground. Second fastest final section.
Strode forward to race outside leader. Continued within a length of the lead until passing the 250m, before peaking on effort & weakening inside the last furlong.

Raced in midfield away from rail, 5 lengths form the lead by the 800m. Hard ridden to improve on cornering before failing to improve position in final section. (Raced greenly, didn't finish off as anticipated – rider).

Raced in midfield on rail, 5 lengths form lead passing the 800m. Ridden along passing the 600m. Five lengths from lead entering final section before yielding a further few lengths in final 250m. Well held.
Slow to begin, consequently racing second last on rail. Had only 2 behind entering last section before failing to make any headway in last section. Well beaten.
Ridden along after the start before crossing to rail in midfield. Came under hard ridding to maintain position passing the 600m before dropping out in the final section to be well beaten.
Strode forward before getting good position on leaders back. Under heavy pressure on cornering & dropped out quickly after straightening. (Bled & Irregular heart rhythm post-race).
Held up in last place, 5 lengths behind the leader, closer on turn, commenced move after passing 550M, wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by half length turning in, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, half length back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at rear on rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Niggled and settled to race in box-seat, finished off strongly, held on to score by a nose.
Travelled in front of midfield, along the rail, worked home gamely, missed by a nose in a tight finish.
Rolled forward and sat in one-out one-back position, continued nicely in a blanket finish for top 3.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, kept on nicely to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide, finished off well to be nearest at the finish.
Forward to take rail and led, ran on one paced to the line.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, ran on until couldn't find extra in the closing stages.
Taken back, at tail, on rail until 600M, improved and dashed home nicely.
Eased and raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, ran on fairly.
Hampered at start, settled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, continued on fairly.
Raced in midfield after jumping awkwardly, on rail, ran on to the line.
Eased back, at rear, 2 wide, did not threaten.
Settled towards the rear, on rail, held ground. (Blood in trachea and see Incident Report)
In midfield, wide and without cover, no turn of foot and emptied late.
Moderate start, settled one from last of small field in 6th just over 3L back, commenced move entering home straight, ran on under pressure to gain upper hand 100 metres out.
Began well from the widest gate of 7, obtained rails run in the lead passing the 900 metres but was soon joined rounding home bend, headed narrowly 100 metres out but fought on well for 2nd.

Broke well to lead early, settled one back in 3rd coming onto home bend, switched 3 wide entering home straight holding every chance early on, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres. (Tactic questioned)

Moderate start, settled just over 2L back in 4th on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, fought on to hold some chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Broke well before settling just over 2L back in 5th, switched out for a run entering home straight but failed to quicken to threaten.
Well there, improved 3-wide to join the leader rounding home bend, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped well behind of the small field and never seen with a chance.
Soon led under 10lb claimer, pressed by rival home turn, waited with until 350M, responded well when asked, kept on momentum to hold off fast finishing rivals late stages.
Shifted across to obtain cover after the start, held up in rear, brought widest to challenge top of straight, closed off fastest to be nearest at the finish.
Restrained to race towards the rear along the 3-path, a shade keen early stages, driven along 450M, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Not hurried after the start, settled down midfield 3-wide, into clear 400M, stayed on mildly to go 4th near line, held by first 3.
Positively ridden, sat just behind the pace, had every chance turning home, advanced to 2nd 300M chasing the winner, effort petered out passing 100M, lost several places late.
Stumbled at the start, recovered to race in midfield along the fence, kept battling in straight, held by leaders always.
Held up towards the rear, 5-6Ls off the pace rounding the home turn, ran on moderately but not quite able to challenge leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, settled down behind midfield along the fence, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without threatening leaders.
Caught wide early stages from draw 14, improved from 1100M to race outside leader, kept on same pace turning in and unable to challenge, swamped by pursuing rivals 150M.
Positioned ahead of midfield about 3Ls off the pace, gave moderate response early straight before outpaced by rivals passing 200M.
Held up behind midfield, raced keenly middle stages, clipped heels and stumbled 750M, responded fairly early straight before crowded for room near 200M, didn't find much afterwards.
Chased leaders along the fence, inclined to race keenly middle stages, didn't respond when driven out 400M, beaten far too easily. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Eased back to last from wide draw, 7Ls back on settling, couldn't go on in the straight, never in the picture.
From draw 10 unable to get closer than 3-wide, lost cover from 900M, 5th at 800M, struggled to keep up 500M, no extra final 250M.

Slightly slow out and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kicked clear early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M, headed close home.
Began fairly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Rider nearly dislodged at start, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide with cover turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide, 7 lengths back, bumped near 900M, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, no cover after 900M, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, wider from 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped with them, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, bumped near 900M, found rail 800M, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned 3 wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from 800M, angled out after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 500M, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but still headed 100M, finished 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, just outpaced by the first two.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, raced tight and blocked early in straight, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back early, found a 2 wide spot near 1000M, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail, 8 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 550M, made minor progress in straight. (Entrapped epiglottis.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, moved closer after passing 800M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 1200M, challenged turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Mucus.)
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 9 to 10 lengths back, closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.

Bumped start, raced at tail in the early stages, sent forward after passing 1000M, took the lead 650M, led by half length on turn, kept on very strongly in straight, easily scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, found cover 1250M, 2 wide from 550M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, sent forward after passing 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began very awkwardly, raced 3 wide with no cover at rear, sent forward after passing 1600M, settled 2 wide, a length or so back from 1200M, found cover 650M, inconvenienced near 400M, weakened in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 650M, very wide into straight, made no progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 1400M, 4 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.

Moderately away, raced prominently but wide in the early stages, took the lead 1600M, found rail 1250M, led by a length in the middle stages, headed near 650M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, just held ground.
Hard ridden forward, took rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Very slow away, took rail at back, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
At rear, trapped 3 wide throughout, never improved.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, no progress.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, dropped off 400M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort near 400M, quickened near 100M to score.
Jumped well then sent forward to take lead, responded well in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Raced in front of midfield, placed pressure near 500M, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished solidly
Began awkwardly and lost ground then ridden forward, rider's saddle shifted back in early stages, settled behind midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, settled towards rear on rail, made ground passing 150M.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure and only one-paced.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Began well, settled in box seat, placed pressure but weakened passing 100M.
Settled behind the lead, tried to improve near 400M, gave ground passing 100M.
On jumping was crowded for room, then taken back, gained some late ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly, then taken back, came under pressure near 500M, no response in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, came under pressure near 500M, faded out in the straight.

Raced in midfield away from rail & maintained that position, 6L from lead at half-way. Moved wider nearing the 400m, 5 wide on straightening. Sprinted quickly, assumed lead at the 100m before drawing away in closing stages.

Strode forward after start before getting good position in fifth, with cover away from rail. Moved three wide on cornering, sprinted up to assume the lead at the 200m mark before being passed by winner at the 100m.
Steadied after start & shifted back to last after 100m. Was a clear last on cornering, well off lead before finishing strongly between runners in the closing stages. Good from rearward position.

Steadied & shifted behind runners to second last in early stages. Moved wider approaching the 400m when still 6.5L from lead. Moved the second widest on straightening before making steady headway in final 250m.
Shifted behind runners to race worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail entering the last section before making up a couple of lengths in late stages without threatening.

Hard ridden after start, strode to lead by the 1300m, crossed to rail soon after. Headed in the lead at the 600m before regaining the lead on straightening. Peaked shortly after & weakened a few lengths in last 250m.
Had nice position two pairs behind lead on rail in early & middle stages. Moved within two lengths of the lead on straightening before fading on run in the final furlong.
Not bustled after start & drifted back worse than midfield away from rail. Pushed the widest runner on cornering before passing a couple in the straight but was too far back to really threaten.
Obtained nice position in midfield away from rail. Moved 3 & 4 wide on cornering, getting closer to the lead on straightening before peaking on run at the furlong & yielding two lengths thereafter.
Held midfield position on the rail after the start. Niggled along entering last section when 4L from lead, stayed close to rail on straightening before weakening out in last 250m.
Strode forward after start before settling in third away from rail without cover. Moved up to assume the lead at the 600m, before peaking on straightening & weakening significantly in last 300m.
Early leader before racing on leaders back from the 1100m. Moved away from rail, 2L from lead on straightening before weakening out badly in last 300m. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, trapped wide early, found rail near 550M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challengers late.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, allowed the rivals to cross near 600M, 2 wide from 500M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just beaten by narrow margin.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 550M, a length behind the leader on turn, finished off well to take a place, just narrowly beaten.

Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line, impressive debut.

Average to begin, positioned on rail, slightly behind midfield, hampered near 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, hampered near 500M, saved ground on turn, no clear running until final 50M, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 750M, 5 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 2 wide from near 600M, 8 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear on rail, 9 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, worked home nicely to score when asked from 200M.
Bumped start, settled to race outside the lead, continued on well for 2nd.
Travelled in about midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and hit the line nicely.
Sat in just behind midfield, wide but with cover, ran on nicely to the line.
Raced just in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, gradually worked forward into the lead, headed near 150M and weakened thereafter.
Asked forward, raced in box-seat, found no extra for final 100M.
Bumped start, settled midfield, wide and without cover, moved at 700M, one paced and emptied late.
In behind midfield, along the rail, ran on to the line.
Taken back, at rear, 3 wide by Home Turn, showed no turn of foot.
Fractious and missed start, at rear throughout, not a factor.
Improved steadily from a wide gate to first few, made the move to take up running 900 metres out, kicked some 2L clear entering home straight, just held off runner-up's late challenge close to home.

Soon gained rails run after start before settling in one back position, hampered and dropped to 4th over 2L back 900 metres out, commenced move on top of home bend, ran on from 3L 3rd into straight to miss narrowly.

Travelled wide in first few in early stages, settled 2L back in 4th on stables bend, gained closer to 1L 2nd coming out of back straight, fought on steadily under pressure but headed for 2nd 150 metres out.
Began well, travelled keenly in early stages when taken back to midfield to 6th, commenced move rounding home bend, made steady headway in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate in early stages, awkwardly placed behind horses rounding home bend, switched in for a run upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began well from the one gate, settled mainly in midfield on the rail, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening, kept on steadily without quickening.
Niggled along before settling just worse than midfield, carried backward towards the rear over 800 metres out, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, ran on past well-beaten horses in closing stages.

Settled in midfield, travelling wide without cover from the 1200 metres, made steady headway in back straight to reach 5th leaving the Rock, went wide and lost position rounding home bend, never recovered.
Settled towards the rear, never better than midfield.
Taken back from the widest gate, made short-lived effort coming off the Rock, dropped back to last few upon straightening.
Niggled along after beginning from a wide-ish gate, took up running coming onto stables bend, led briefly before ceded advantage 900 metres out, gradually weakened from approaching home straight.
Began awkwardly, reserved in midfield about 4-5Ls back in a fast run race, picked up strongly on straightening, led near 50M, won going away.
From wide draw crossed to chase leader along 2-path, took over 250M, kept on well but just unable to hold off winner final 100M.
Began only fairly, failed to muster speed, ended up towards rear 6Ls away, made stealthy progress between runners over final 200M, got up for 3rd 50M.
Always in touch, had every chance turning in, not pace to challenge first 2, held 3rd until 50M.
Tracked the fast pace after beginning well from draw 1, fought on early straight but not pace to challenge leaders, faded late. (Jockey : lacks maturity in this stage of its career / Blood trachea.)
Taken to a 2-wide spot behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without threatening.
Held up behind midfield, saved ground along inside, closed off fairly in the straight, not reached contention.
Settled down in 5th just ahead of midfield, crowded for room 200M, raced tight again final 100M and unable to be ridden out to the finish. (Blood in trachea.)
Reserved near last 8Ls back in a fast run race, stayed on fairly over final 300M, never threatened.
Lost ground when bumped at the start, raced as the back-marker 8-9Ls off the pace, brought to outside on straightening but made no real progress.
Failed to muster speed after the jump, travelled wide no cover behind midfield during the race, had nothing to offer turning home, never in contention.
From wide draw crossed to lead passing 900M, set good pace, headed 250M, weakened rapidly towards the line. (Jockey : action deteriorated over latter stages of the race / Unacceptable Performance.)
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very well to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield early, 2 wide from near 800M, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider near 750M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 800M, no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Began smartly from gate 10, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival from 700M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, better than midfield, sent forward after passing 850M, shared lead in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, no clear run after passing 200M, eased thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 250M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.

Out in line, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, bumped near 850M, same position on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front near 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running until 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at rear, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Moderately away, raced prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 800M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Missed the start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly. (Rider dropped whip near 200M.)
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, bumped near 850M, same position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Pushed forward, pace good, closed off strongly 200M to score.
Pushed forward, pace good, led 200M, overhauled 50M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Slow away, behind midfield, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, pace good, dashed well 150M.
Eased to sit in midfield, pace good, made ground 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, pace good, weakened 150M.
Eased back, pace good, no dash.
Took lead easily, pace good, weakened quickly 200M.
Behind midfield, pace good, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, pace good, dropped off 300M.
Never competitive.
Settled behind midfield on rail, quickened near 200M, finished strongly to score.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, made the turn near the 900M awkwardly, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled at rear, wide on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, worked home solidly.
Began only fairly, settled towards rear, in the early part of straight had some difficulty to obtain clear running, made up nice late ground.
Raced midfield, wide on straightening, ran well in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M.
Urged along to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Wide and without cover for the majority of the race in midfield, one-paced in the straight.
Began well, settled in one-back-one-off position, tried to improve passing 600M, weakened near 200M.
Pushed along to race in box seat, gave ground passing 200M.
Began awkwardly then sent forward to race outside the lead, rounding the Home Turn lay out, gave ground near 300M.
Began only fairly then taken back, placed pressure but no response.
Travelled midfield on rail, tested but no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, near the 900M was crowded, faded out near 300M, finished tailed out.

Obtained good position in 4th away from rail in early & middle stages. Eased three wide approaching the corner before straightening 1L from lead. Sprinted fast to assume lead at 275m before continuing on for impressive win.

Steadied after start, settling fourth last away from rail. Continued rearward on straightening, held up momentarily entering last section before getting clear & finishing strongly in last 300m to snare second closing stages.

Strode forward before racing third on the rail in middle stages. Continued on leaders back on cornering, held up on the rail shortly after straightening before getting clear & finishing off well into third in last section.
Raced in midfield on rail, five lengths from lead at the 800m. Moved away from the rail approaching the corner before working home well between runners in the final 300m to not be beaten far.

Drifted back after the start & raced third from last on rail in early & middle stages. Continued on the inside before shifting in at the 300m & again at the 200m to get clear running. Finished off soundly in last furlong.
Raced in midfield, away from rail, 4 lengths from lead at the 800m. Eased wider on cornering before finishing off evenly in last section. Not beaten too far.
Strode forward, assume lead after 300m before crossing to rail near the 1250m. Continued in the lead on straightening before being joined & headed at the 275m before yielding 5 lengths thereafter.

Had no early speed & shifted across behind runners to second last. Moved three wide approaching the 600m, cornered the widest before straightening just over 3L from lead. Peaked at the furlong & gave a few lengths thereafter.

Very slow to begin, conceding over 4 lengths, consequently racing at the tail throughout. Moved closer nearing bend but was still last on straightening before failing to make any further headway in last section. Excusable.

Strode forward to share early lead before being headed & racing in second from the 1300m. Improved to within half length from lead entering last section before peaking at the 350m & weakening out in final 250m. Well beaten.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, 4 wide turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored, impressive debut.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, finished off well when clear thereafter, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 550M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, raced 6 to 7 lengths back at rear, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, steadied off heels near 150M, eased thereafter.
Slightly slow out, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off one pace.
Began well from gate 9, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail 800M, commenced move 500M, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, peaked turning in, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
At tail as per usual, swung widest on straightening, continued to make good ground, caught leaders to score just prior going to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, held up until about 200M, ran on strongly thereafter for 2nd.
Crowded start, settled in front of midfield, along the rail, closed off nicely inside final 250M.
Awkward start, raced in behind midfield, shifted 3 wide near 800M, ran on well but couldn't find extra for final strides.
Rolled forward, sat in box-seat, closed off fairly despite awkward to heels near 100M.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, stayed on until emptied late.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on the line.
Bumped start, then shifted to race on rail in behind midfield, made slight ground late.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide, ran on one paced to the line.
Niggled and then settled in one-out one-back position, showed no turn of foot. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, eased to be in behind midfield, along the rail, no daylight till 200M, one paced thereafter.
Urged and took some time to muster, obtained lead at 1000M, on rail throughout, run ended at 250M.
Very slow to jump, at rear, not a factor.
Hard ridden to be prominent, trapped wide however, run soon ended after straightening.

Obtained run near the rail in 5th within 3L of pace rounding first bend, dropped slightly further back around home bend, commenced move entering straight and quickened to lead 300 metres out, just held on to the line.
Ridden from a wide gate before settling wide without cover in midfield over 4L back, ran on well from similar position into home straight to just fail to peg back the winner.
Settled just some 2L back on the rail in 4th or 3rd, chased the leaders into home straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Unbalanced at start, settled in midfield on the rail, switched out for a run upon straightening, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in last few, given reminders upon straightening, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back from a wide barrier, remained well behind to home straight, made steady headway down the centre of the track.
Settled wide towards the rear, came under pressure entering home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Ridden early stages travelling mainly in rear of midfield, crowded for room 700 metres out and awkwardly placed briefly entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Broke well from a wide barrier settling 1L back 2-wide, became 4th some 2L back coming onto home bend, renewed effort entering straight but folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled wide without cover early, ridden to dispute lead coming onto back straight, folded up quickly after home turn.
Ridden to lead racing keenly in back straight, led until joined into home straight, soon weakened.
Crowded at start, settled towards the rear, ran home one-paced.
Slow to begin and taken back, remained in last few throughout, found nothing under pressure.
Restrained to race towards the rear, moved away from fence 550M, made rapid headway to lead passing 200M, skipped clear for a dominant victory.
In the rear soon pushed along, 5Ls to make up 400M,ran on hard to chase winner final 200M but held.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, ran on mildly when driven out 400M, couldn't match winner's acceleration mid-straight, one paced late and lost 2nd 50M from home.

Began only fairly, raced keenly towards the rear in a steadily run race, inclined to lay in under pressure in straight and reluctant to shift out for clear running, stayed on over final 200M before being hampered near 100M.
Held up in 5th spot not far off from the pace, battled on in the straight but never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Led uncontested at a steady tempo, quickened to 2L lead early straight, headed passing 200M, no extra towards the finish.
In 4th place early stages, moved closer to be tracking leader approaching the turn, held 2nd to 300M, one paced towards the finish.
Chased leader along the fence, outgunned from 300M, soon out of contention.
Held up mid-division, difficult to settle after 1400M, struggled to go with them on straightening, soon left behind.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, no cover throughout, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two late.
Began well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress early in straight, blocked near 150M, showed some response thereafter but not much room towards finish.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail 950M, commenced move after passing 600M, made some progress in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, a bit closer on the middle stage, angled out after passing 500M, not enough room early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Stumbled at start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made no progress in straight. (Lame right front leg.)
Raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, carried wider after passing 600M, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, very wide into straight, failed to close off in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well after turning in, scored by half length. (Blood in trachea.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 3 wide from near 900M, shared lead turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place. (Rider dropped whip near 250M.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, wider from 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Made contact on jumping, raced prominently on the inside, crossed near 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, angled out 500M, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, checked off heels and bumped near 300M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, a bit closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, bumped near 300M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.

Shifted across to midfield away from the rail after start. Moved the widest runner on cornering, entered last section 4L from lead before sprinting very quickly, assuming lead at the 125m & continuing on to win easily again.

Began fast before being crossed & settling behind leading group, around 2L from lead at the 800m. Moved away from the rail entering the last section before finishing strongly, running into second at the 125m. Clear of third.

Strode forward, raced in third on the rail & keeping joint leaders 2 & 3 wide in early & middle stages. Continued on rail before improving to hold slender lead entering last section. Held lead until being passed at the 125m.

Held early lead before easing back & racing in 4th position, away from rail by the 800m. Moved wider on cornering when travelling well before peaking on effort at the 250m before yielding a length or two thereafter.

Strode forward, raced 3 wide without cover when sharing the lead in early & middle stages. Continued wide before veering out on cornering. Travelled strongly until the 300m before giving little response & weakening out thereafter.

Shifted behind runners after start before racing second from last away from rail. Continued at the back, nearly 8L from lead entering last section. Worked home well in closing stages, passing many runners in dash to line.
Began well before being allowed to drift back to third last after 300m. Second from last entering the last section when 8L from lead before moving wider & making late headway to midfield. (Bled).
Not fast away & drifted back to worse than midfield away from rail in first 300m. Shifted wider on straightening but could not improve in last section & was well held.

Steadied after start & shifted rearward before racing with only 3 behind, six lengths from lead passing 800m. Continued 6L from lead on straightening before peaking inside the last 300m & yielding a further few lengths late.

Obtained a nice trailing position in midfield, racing in the clear, around 4L from lead by the 800m. Moved away from rail on straightening, before being eased out of the race by rider over the final 250m. (Lame post-race).
Not fast to begin before mustering to race midfield on the rail. Came under hard riding on cornering before weakening out in the final section. Well beaten.

Strode forward but unable to cross to rail when effectively sharing lead with horse on outside. Eased away from heels on cornering before peaking on effort & weakening out significantly in the straight.
Bumped at start & lost ground before settling a clear last. Was a clear last on cornering, 9 lengths form lead before weakening a further few lengths in last section. Well beaten.

Raced just behind the leading trio, 3 wide with cover passing the 800m. Came under heavy pressure on straightening before weakening out in last section to be a long last. (Rider concerned about action, must trial).

Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail near 600M, saved ground on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, 4 lengths or so back on turn, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 150M, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd.

Began awkwardly, taken back to race at tail, checked near 1000M, 6 lengths or so back on turn, showed good response early in straight, not enough room near 150M, finished off very strongly thereafter to take a place.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped 3 to 4 wide, 1-1/2L back, found a 2 wide spot near 650M, commenced move after passing 400M, kept on evenly in straight, just missed 3rd on line.

Began smartly from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 950M, took brief lead near 800M, headed 600M, 2nd turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 1, showed good speed to take the lead, headed near 800M, retook the lead 600M, travelled well on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Crowded start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, recovered to race behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Eased to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled
Midfield along the fence, blocked most straight, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, moved forward 800M, dashed well 300M whilst hanging in badly.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300M, dashed well.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, moved forward 800M, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 300M, just held ground.
Eased to sit in midfield, however trapped 3 wide, moved forward 900M into the lead to take advantageous of the slow pace, emptied 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, shuffled back 800M, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300M, no dash.
Slow away, at rear, never improved.
Settled in front of midfield, in the straight responded strongly and quickened passing 200M to score.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground, finished solidly.
Took lead with nice early speed, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground over the concluding stages.
Travelled keenly after 900M when being steadied, settled in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, finished nicely.
Jumped well, settled midfield, wide on straightening, made some ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, in the straight fought hard but finished one-paced.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but worked home one-paced.
Settled at rear, placed pressure near 400M, limited response in the straight.
Raced in box seat, came under pressure passing 500M, gave ground near 150M.
Began only fairly then was checked when crowded for room, raced at rear on rail, gave ground near 100M.
Raced behind leaders, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then sent forward, raced behind the lead, weakened passing 200M.

Began well, raced in second on rail, 4L from lead after first section. Moved closer to lead approaching the corner, moved up to assume lead at the 250m & continued on strongly in last furlong to score easily.

Raced in third away from rail, continued in similar position approaching bend when 2.5L from lead entering last section. Ran into second passing the furlong mark & continued on well. No match for winner.
Drifted back after the first bend when racing in midfield on the rail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering. Moved over heals at the 200m before finishing off steadily into third in final 100m.
Not fast to begin & raced with only 3 runners behind for majority. Moved closer to the lead approaching the corner before finishing off steadily in the final furlong to share third on the line.
Ridden to midfield after the start, racing three wide with cover early before being left without cover approaching 600m. Cornered the widest runner before finishing off fairly in closing 300m.
Strode to midfield, three wide without cover. Improved in second section, moving to third. Just over 2L from lead entering last section before peaking & yielding a few lengths in final 250m.

Steadied after the start & drifted back to second last, over 9L form lead after first section. Continued rearward, six lengths from lead entering final section before effectively maintaining that margin straight. No threat.
Didn't begin fast & drifted back to third last on rail. Was tightened & checked severely nearing the 600m & lost over 4L. Next to last on straightening before making up a few lengths in last section.
Hard ridden, showed fast early speed to lead by 4L in early & middle stages. Peaked & headed at the 250m before weakening out significantly thereafter.
Raced in midfield between runners, 3.5L from lead by the 800m. Moved wider nearing the corner before peaking on effort at the furlong & weakening out thereafter.
Had no early speed & raced at the tail from the start. Continued at the tail, 10 lengths from lead entering the last section before failing to make any headway into that margin. Well beaten.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on very well after turning in, scored by half length.
Crowded start, positioned on rail at rear, a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd on line.

Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, slightly taken back to sit 1-1/2L behind the leader, 2 wide from 800M, same margin back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, bumped near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, found rail near 1100M, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 4 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, 2 wide from 1100M, commenced move after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Crowded start, raced at tail, detached from the main group early, got back to it 800M, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide from 1150M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Eased and raced close to the rear, 2 wide, sprinted home nicely to score comfortably by 2L.
Rolled forward to race in box-seat, worked home nicely in a close battle for the placings.
Raced in just behind midfield, 2 wide, raced ungenerously early, ran on well for 3rd.
Sent forward, took rail and led, continued on one paced to the line.
Travelled in front of midfield, 2 wide, shifted wide at 500M, ran on fairly to the line. (Lost left front plate)
Eased then raced at the tail, 2 wide, improved slightly on the inside track.
Taken back, at rear along the rail, showed dashes until flattened at 200M.
Stumbled at start, sat in behind midfield, away from rail after 900M, was one paced.
Rolled forward, sat outside lead until found cover at 700M, bumped at 300M, did not run on.
In midfield, along the rail, held up till 250M, showed no turn of foot anyway.
In front of midfield, left wide and without cover, improved to sit outside lead at 700M, gave ground in the straight.
Settled in about midfield, wide and without cover from 700M, pressured soon after, faded prior to straightening.
Jumped well from the widest gate, soon took up running on the rail about 950 metres out, hung on well under pressure.
Broke well, travelled just off the pace, commenced move entering home straight, kept on same pace without quickening in the run home.
Chased the leader in 3rd to straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Moderate start, settled mainly in midfield on the rail, 5th some 3L back turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Not far off early, carried wide at the 1000 metres and travelled awkwardly in better than midfield in back straight, ran home one-paced.
Hampered at start, travelled keenly in last few on the rail, saved ground making home bend, kept on one pace without quickening under pressure in straight.
Travelled keenly in midfield when mainly in 8th, went wide into home straight, one-paced in the run home.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, switched out for a run entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken across behind runners from a wide barrier, remained well behind to straight, fought on past well-beaten horses.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th some 3L back, 5th leaving the Rock, hampered on straightening and made no further impression.
Began well from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover in forward of midfield, dropped to midfield rounding home bend and wider into the straight, never recovered.
Lost considerable ground at start, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Crossed to the lead quickly from draw 12, led at good pace, quickened away on straightening, kept on strongly to the line giving rivals no chance.
Not hurried after the start, eased back to near last, kept to inside throughout, made good progress to go 2nd 50M out, no threat to the runaway winner.
Lost ground when crowded for room after start, recovered to race in midfield, kept on steadily over final 300M, not pace to challenge runaway winner, held on for 3rd.
Dropped back to last from wide barrier, 9Ls off the pace from 400M, closed off strongly over final 300M, just missed 3rd. (Jockey was told his ride after 600M had come under notice.)
Settled down midfield 3Ls back, switched to outside on straightening, ran on moderately.
From draw 1 obtained a midfield position just over 3Ls off the good pace, had every chance turning in, briefly went 2nd mid-straight, faded closing stages.
Began awkwardly, caught wide early stages, moved up to race outside leader before home turn, drifted out to center of track entering straight, ran home once paced.
Driven forward, chased leader along 2-path, kept on steadily turning in but not pace to challenge, run ended 100M from home.
Taken across behind runners, held up behind midfield 5Ls back, responded fairly on straightening, no clear run over final 100M.
Positively ridden, chased leaders along inside, no extra passing 200M, outsprinted by rivals.
Lost ground near 1000M, shuffled back to near the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, stayed on fairly, never reach contention.
Never far off the pace, wide no cover from 600M, soon off the bridle, didn't respond to riding and weakened out of the race.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, commenced move 400M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced prominently, 2 wide, crossed after passing 900M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Clean jump, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, sent forward 1200M, positioned 2 wide in 2nd after entering the back straight, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, finished off strongly final 200M to score.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, found daylight 300M, closed off well to take 2nd, good debut.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, found cover 650M, showed good response early in straight, made contact near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to 100M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress, no threat to the first few.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, no clear run until 200M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced very wide with no cover at rear, found cover 650M, last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, in touch in outside, travelled keenly throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, however trapped wide, improved 900M to take advantageous of the slow pace, dominated from 400M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, held up badly 4-2, dashed well when clear for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
At rear, on the rails, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, moved forward 800M, weakened 250M.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed forward, 2 wide, emptied 350M.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Took no part in the race (see incident report).
Taken back at start, settled toward rear on rail, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Settled midfield on rail, improved near 500M, worked home solidly in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on rail, kept improving on rail rounding the Home turn and in the straight, responded nicely when asked for effort.
Settled in handy position, commenced to improve near 450M, near 75M was bumped and became badly unbalanced, not fully tested.
Ridden along to take lead, placed pressure on straightening, near 75M was hampered then raced tight, not fully tested.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, gained some ground passing 200M, finished OK.
Settled in box seat with nice early speed, asked for effort near 400M, worked home one-paced.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, gave some ground passing 100M.
Raced toward rear, widest on straightening, limited response when placed pressure in the straight.
Settled midfield, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, fought hard in the straight but only limited response.
Taken back at start from widest barrier, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield, always niggled, weakened passing 300M.
Raced at tail, in the straight no response when asked for effort.
Broke sharply, sent forward to race outside the lead, hung out rounding the Home Turn, faded out near 300M.

Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on very well to the line. (Rider dropped whip near 300M.)
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 9, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from near 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on rail, 2 wide on turn, very wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on one pace to the line.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3 lengths on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded out start, raced at tail, 9 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 1000M, 3 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, a length or so back on turn, angled out 500M, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 300M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Bumped start, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, sent forward after passing 800M, 3 wide with no cover in midfield on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail, just behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind Midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running until final 100M, showed minor progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Settled behind midfield 7Ls off the steady pace, travelled well, quickened to lead nearing 250M, kept on to hold off the challenge of 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, settled inside the leader, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, 4-5 wide at turn, ran on well for 3rd.
Crossed to lead on fence near 1200M, headed by rival 450M, made steady progress to be 4th without threatening first 3.
Had no speed in the early stages and consequently raced very wide. Made some headway in straight and was crowded near 150M.
Began only fairly, sat in front of midfield, gave brief response turning in, effort levelled off final 200M.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, gave brief response turning in, effort levelled off final 200M.
Driven forward to be chasing leader, sat in 3rd from 800M, checked at 150M, faded thereafter.
Not hurried early stages, raced near last, driven along 450M but just plugged away to the line, made no impression.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, always towards the rear, failed to respond to riding 400M, never a threat.
Slow to begin, at the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, didn't do much in the straight, never in the hunt.
In midfield 2 wide, under pressure home turn, didn't respond to riding, never looked to threaten. (See Incident Report, mucus in trachea)
Driven forward to be chasing leader, in 9th place turning for home, couldn't finish off in the straight, never in contention.
Began well, settled just off the pace in 3rd and later on in 4th some 2L back in back straight, ran on in straight to gain upper hand inside the final 100 metres.
Sluggish at start and given reminders, travelled in last few to straight, ran on well inside the final 250 metres to just fail to get up on line.
Broke well from the one gate, settled in 5th just over 2L back on the rail, ran on without threatening.
Broke well from the widest gate to lead, obtained rails run coming onto back straight, led the field until headed inside the final 100 metres.
Taken back to rear on the rail from a wide gate, remained in last few to home straight, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, ran on under pressure, checked near finish.
Settled in last few, trailed the field into home straight, ran on well down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Travelled wide without cover in better than midfield, made steady headway in back straight to reach 2nd 1000 metres out, faded steadily under pressure after straightening.
Travelled wide in rear of midfield, improved closer to mainly 4L off the pace in back straight, failed to quicken under pressure early in home straight and ran home one-paced.
Travelled wide in last few, fought on steadily without threatening in home straight.
Never better than midfield, gradually drifted towards the rear 1000 metres out, came under pressure entering home straight, one-paced.
Close up early, settled within 2L of pace in 3rd on the rail in back straight, soon weakened after making home turn.
Travelled mainly in midfield in 6th, came under pressure entering home straight, soon weakened.
From draw 1 steadied early stages to obtain cover in midfield, moved out to challenge 500M, quickened nicely to lead 200M, held on well final stages.
From draw 14 moved up along the stand's rail to race just off the pace, responded well final 300M, just denied a hat-trick of wins.
Close up behind the pace, travelled strongly into contention 400M, kept on well to the line.
Always in firing line, couldn't go with first 3 final 200M, battled on for non-threatening 4th.
Prominently placed, kept on evenly down center of track, faded and out of contention 100M.
In touch 2Ls off leader, kept on steadily towards the line but not going the pace to seriously challenge.
Outpaced early stages, settled towards the rear 6Ls away, finished fastest final 400M, made some progress but never reached contention.
Prominent behind leader, outpaced from 350M, soon out of contention.
Led from 800M, couldn't hold off pursuers passing 300M, weakened towards the finish.
Chased leaders, ran on same pace when driven nearing 400M, never threatened.
Never far off from leaders towards the stand's side, driven out 400M but gave only limited response, never going the pace to challenge.
Settled in midfield along the stands' rail, shifted out to challenge passing 500M, failed to quicken.
Slow to begin, lacked early speed, soon detached in rear, didn't respond to riding passing halfway, never in the picture.
Pushed along early stages to hold its position towards the rear, outpaced and detached from field passing halfway, eased when no chance.

Shifted out at start and bumped, unable to slot in early, sent forward after passing 1000M, took the lead 850M, found rail 700M, challenged turning in, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Away well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 850M, commenced move after passing 500M, put pressure on the leader in straight, but always held.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider from 600M, inconvenienced near 450M, made very good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept on very well early in straight, no clear run final 100M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, angled out after passing 600M, 4 wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 650M, showed some response in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, carried wider from 600M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 300M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, positioned on rail at rear, 2 wide from 1100M, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M, closed off well to take a place.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 1400M, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 1100M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened thereafter.

Bumped shortly after start, raced 3w behind midfield in the early stages, carried wider 1100M, sent forward after passing 1000M, 3rd on turn, a length behind, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.

Bumped start, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, no cover from 1200M, a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, checked near 300M, made no progress thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3w, a length or so back, found a 2w spot 1200M, 2-3 lengths back in the middle stages, angled out early in straight, bumped 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced wide with cover at rear, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked turning in, bumped 300M, weakened thereafter.
