Steadied at start, shifted across to rail before improving to midfield. Made continual ground along rail in middle stages. Moved into 3rd position on corner before finishing very fast, assumed lead at 100m & drew away. Easy.

Began fast & assumed early lead before shifting across to rail after first bend. Raced over a length clear on straightening before being caught at the 100m by fast finishing winner. Held second, well behind easy winner.

Held the rail position after start before racing on leaders back throughout early & middle stages. Moved into second position at the 450m when over a length from the lead. Finished off well final 300m to just miss second.

Raced in midfield before being checked badly & losing ground on the first bend, consequently racing near the rear thereafter. Improved position along the rail from the 550m before making up further late ground in the straight.
Checked & lost ground on the first bend, consequently sharing last position by the 850m. Continued a long way from lead on cornering before making good late ground from poor position in straight.

Ridden forward after start, raced in second away from rail before drifting to forth, with cover by half-way. Came under hard riding passing the 500m mark before making the turn very wide & maintaining margin in final 300m.

Raced wide approaching first bend before drifting back worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover early. Left without cover from the 600m before cornering 6L from lead. Made up a length or two late but was never a threat.

Began slow, improved quickly between runners at first bend to race wide in midfield. Moved closer to rail with cover by the 600m. Over 4L from lead entering final section & weakened a further length in straight. (Mucus).

Had no early speed & raced wide at first bend before settling at the rear, wide and with cover. Continued a clear last when over 9L from lead before making up steady late ground from poor position in straight. Never in race.

Hard ridden after start but could only hold midfield position away from rail. Three lengths from lead passing the 800m before drifting further back when being hard ridden entering final section. Well beaten. (Must trial).

Bumped & stumbled badly when taking the first bend, before losing ground & racing ungenerously when relegated worse than midfield. Ridden along from the 450m mark over 7L from lead but only weakened out further thereafter.
Not bustled early before improving position after the first bend to race to second position by the 800m. Came under heavy pressure & began yielding ground from the 450m mark. Finished a long last.
Trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Slow away, pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 200M.
Took rail and led at good pace, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Slow away, took rail at rear, pace good, blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, took rail at back, pace good, made ground 200M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, checked badly 600M, pace good, weakened 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 4 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, pace good, emptied 250M.
Raced midfield, improved passing 400M, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 500M, wide on straightening, continued to gain ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Raced in handy position, commenced to improve passing 550M, responded nicely when placed pressure in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, improved near 500M, wide rounding Home Turn and on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure near 300M, one-paced in the straight.
Sent forward to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, worked home one-paced.
Taken back at start, settled at rear on rail, gained some ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled toward rear on rail, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, placed pressure passing 400M, one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, passing 200M raced in restricted room and not fully tested over concluding stages.
Urged along to take lead, weakened passing 200M.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, faded out near 100M, lame right font next day.

Limited early speed, before settling just worse than midfield. Moved 3 wide with cover passing the 600m, before cornering widest. Sprinted quickly on straightening, made continual ground until striking lead in final stride.

Raced very wide after first bend before ridden forward to midfield. Continued to cover additional ground throughout. Sprinted quickly after straightening, assumed lead inside final 100m before nosed out by winner late.

Strode forward but raced wide after first bend before improving to race outside the leader passing the 800m. Moved up to assume lead at the 150m before being passed by the first two shortly after. Close behind in third.

Strode forward to race in second before being crossed & racing third with cover passing the 800m. Battled hard after straightening, within a length of lead entering final furlong before emptying & yielding a length late.

Shifted across behind runners after start & raced third last away from rail. Continued rearward, over 6 lengths from lead entering final section before shifting wider at the 250m & closing off strongly late. Not beaten far.

Not fast after start before improving quickly to race midfield between runners. Travelled strongly entering final section when 5L from lead. Was making strong ground before being checked at 175m & losing chance thereafter.
Assumed lead shortly after start. Raced over a length clear entering the final section, continued to hold lead until peaking & being headed at the 150m & weakening a few lengths thereafter.
Strode forward to race on leaders back throughout early & middle stages. Continued on leaders back on straightening but could make no further headway in the final 300m.
Began well before getting good position in midfield away from rail. Was 4 lengths from lead entering final section & weakened a further length in the straight. No threat.
Slowest to begin, settled with only one behind. Was hard ridden from the 550m mark before weakening out further in the final section to be well beaten.

Had no early speed before holding midfield position on rail after first bend. Continued on rail & was only 5L from lead passing the 400m mark before weakening out badly in final 300m. Beaten a long way.
Steadied after start & shifted to rear. Raced a long way from the lead passing the 400m mark & did nothing in last section. Was a well beaten last.
Strode forward to assume lead before crossing to rail by the 1300m. Travelled strongly in the lead on cornering before dashing away inside the final furlong & continuing on for dominant win.

Raced in midfield away from rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved three wide with cover passing half-way. Cornered the widest runner & made steady ground into second position behind dominant winner in closing stages.

Raced prominently early before being headed & racing in midfield between runners. Continued in midfield between runners, 4L from lead on cornering. Finished off steadily in final 300m, running into third in dash to line.
Ridden forward before getting good position in forth away from rail in early stages. Came under hard riding at the 550m before battling away to hold 4th position on the line.
Improved after the start to race outside the leaser by the 1300m. Niggled along to stay with leader entering last section before peaking at the furlong & yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Stood flat footed at start & lost significant ground, racing a clear last early. Moved three wide & improved position passing half-way. Battled away gamely in final section after poor beginning.
Steadied & shifted across to race third form last away from rail. Ridden hard to improve entering the final section before making up a length or two in closing stages to finish midfield.
Pushed forward after the start but was left racing three wide without cover throughout. Continued to cover additional ground before peaking at the furlong & yielding a few lengths in closing stages.

Steadied in the early stages & shifted back to race second last. Relegated to last passing half-way before entering last section in that position, over 6L from lead. Held up near the 100m but was never really in the race.

Didn't begin fast before holding midfield position on rail throughout early & middle stages. Cornered close to the rail but failed to make any impression in the straight & weakened out in final stages.
Strode forward early before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 1300m. Travelled well nearing the corner before weakening out in closing 250m. (Lame off-side foreleg day after racing).

Steadied after the start & shifted across to race in midfield on rail, nearly 6L from lead after first section. Had only two runners behind entering final section before doing nothing in straight & finishing last.
At rear, 2 wide, improved along the rail in straight, kept on well to score.
Rolled forward, took rail and led, continued on strongly to take 2nd.
Asked after the jump, sat in front of midfield 2 wide, improved steadily and ran on well for 3rd.
Raced in advance and sat in box-seat, ran on steadily to the line.
Settled to race in midfield, held ground and closed off fairly.
Slotted in behind midfield, still 8 to 9 lengths back on turn, saved ground.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Taken back, along the rail, fought on steadily without threatening.
Travelled in midfield, 3 wide with cover, was one paced in the straight. (See Incident Report)
Settled in about midfield, showed no kick to keep up in the straight.
Raced in midfield, wide and without cover from 900M, gave ground from rounding Home Turn. (Irregular heart rhythm and See Incident Report)
Settled toward the rear on the rail, switched wide for a run entering home straight, ran on well to lead 100 metres out, won readily.
Settled in midfield in 7th on the rail, switched wide for a run approaching home turn, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear of midfield, commenced move out wide on home bend, one of the widest turning in, shifted in early in straight, fought on steadily and lost 2nd late.
Taken back from a wide draw, settled in rear on the rail, switched out for a run entering home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Broke well from a poor draw, in front briefly before settling one back in 3rd rounding first bend, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th, crowded early in straight, found no extra closing stages.
Taken back from a wide draw and waited with, produced good late finish inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, pressed forward in wide run before settling one back in second turning into back straight, disputed lead rounding home bend but drifted wide into straight, soon weakened.

Vied for lead early from a wide gate, took up running coming onto stables bend, led until joined rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began well, settled in 5th within 3L of pace on the rail, gained slightly closer rounding home bend and saved ground turning in, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Broke well, with leaders early before settling 2-wide in 4th within 2L of pace, folded up quickly shortly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began awkwardly settling in last few, dropped to last entering home straight, made no further impression. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped well and led steadily, quickened clear mid-straight, continued on strongly to the line for a dominant victory.
In mid-division, pushed along turning for home, did best work late to go 2nd last stride, no match for the clear winner.
Bustled along after the start, tracked leader in a steadily run race, chased hard on straightening but not pace of winner, went 2nd from 150M until headed last stride.
Settled in 4th spot always in touch, drifted out to center of track on straightening, tried had but held ground only.
Taken back from wide draw, held up behind mid-division, stayed on moderately when switched to outside of straight.
Chased leader, held ground in the straight, faded final 100M.
Settle down in midfield along the fence, 5th turning for home, kept on same pace, no impact on leaders.
Dropped back from wide draw, 7Ls back near the rear, lay in under pressure early straight, closed off fairly.
Began only fairly, towards the rear always, ridden along turning for home but found very little, no impression on leaders.
Began fairly from draw 12, didn't muster speed despite ridden, wide no cover chasing leaders throughout, couldn't finish off. (Jockey questioned.)
Steadied to obtain cover after the jump, ended up in last place 8Ls behind, couldn't quicken passing 400M, never reached contention.
Began only fairly, settled down behind mid-division 5Ls back, soon beaten turning home.

Commenced well, raced at rear on the stands rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off very strongly to score.
Clean jump, showed good speed to take the lead, challenged by rival from 400M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently on the stands rail, challenged the leader from 400M, kept on well to 50M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, kept on evenly final 400M to make frame.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands side, travelled keenly in the middle stages, made contact near 300M, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands side, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands side, hard ridden 400M out, only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the middle track, not enough room until 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle, made contact near 450M, peaked on run 200M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the stands side, made contact near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 14, raced behind midfield on the stands rail, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong.
Began well, raced in the middle track, 2 lengths or so back, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced in the middle track, 2 lengths or so back, hard ridden 400M, showed no response, weakened thereafter.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat 1 out 1 back, pace good, closed off well for 3rd.
Took rail easily and led at good pace, hung on well until 200M overhauled.
Eased back, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, held up 5-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Box seat, pace good, weakened 250M.
Pressed forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, emptied 200M.
Slow away, at back on the fence, pace good, made ground 250M.
Trapped 3-5 wide throughout in midfield, pace good, held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, ran on ok.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, pace good, checked 800M, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, pace good, no progress.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, pace good, never competitive.
Slow away, never a factor.
Settled midfield, improved at 500M, responded strongly to score in the straight.
Jumped sharply, raced outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, responded solidly in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Niggled to take lead, placed pressure near 300M, worked home nicely.
Fast out then settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, made up some nice late ground.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure at 500M, finished well.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, one-paced in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, made the turn near 700M awkwardly and lost ground, limited response when placed pressure.
Began only fairly, settled towards rear, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, limited response.
Raced in front of midfield, niggled to maintain its position near 600M, no response in the straight.
Ridden along but fail to muster speed, raced at rear, wide on straightening, no response when placed pressure.
Wide and without cover throughout in handy position, faded out in the straight.

Had no speed after start before being hard ridden to improve to midfield on the rail. Moved away from rail on straightening before making strong ground between runners, striking the lead at 150m & drawing away late. Easy win.

Ridden forward after start to race outside the leader. Moved up to assume the lead soon after straightening. Held lead until being joined & passed by winner at 150m. Battled on ok to hold second & was well clear of third.
Wasn't fast to begin before improving after start to race midfield between runners. Was only 2.5L from lead entering final section before shifting out at the 250m & closing to third in late stages.
Began well to race in third in the clear before shifting to rail & racing on leaders back. Continued on leaders back on cornering before battling away to hold 4th but was well behind winner.

Began well before shifting across to midfield when racing three wide without cover. Was only 2.5L from lead entering the last section before finishing off ok late but being well behind dominant winner.

Began well before being steadied & drifting right back to second last after 400m. Had two runners behind entering the last section when over 5L from lead before managing to maintain margin when passing a few in late stages.

Strode forward before being headed & settling in fourth on rail. Eased away from the rail approaching the 700m. Moved up only a length from lead entering the last section before peaking at the 150m & weakening out thereafter.

Reared at start before steadying & shifting to race a touch worse than midfield away from rail. Moved the widest runner on straightening but peaked at the 250m & could make no further impression thereafter. Well held.

Began awkwardly losing ground before improving slightly to worse than midfield. Raced keenly in middle stages. Over 4L from lead at 400m, looked a fleeting chance when making ground near the 300m before only battling thereafter.
Held midfield position on rail throughout early & middle stages. Continued on the rail on cornering but peaked on effort entering the final section & weakening out sharply in final 250m. Well beaten.
Steadied & shifted behind runners to race at the tail after 300m. Was a clear last on straightening when 7.5 lengths from lead but could not really make any impression. Was always long way from lead.
Had no speed after the start & raced in last position shortly after start. Cornered second from last when racing on rail & could make no further improvement. Well beaten.
Showed speed to stride to lead shortly after start. Headed in the lead soon after straightening before weakening out in the final 300m to be well beaten.
Improved after start to race in midfield away from rail. Forced three wide approaching the 700m before peaking on effort soon after straightening & weakening out to be a well beaten last.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced prominently, 2 wide, took the lead near 650M, led by a length turning in, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 550M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, moved closer after passing 800M, 3 wide with cover on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, 4 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide from 600M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 750M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn but still 7 lengths behind, passed some tired runners in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, carried wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, moved closer after passing 1100M, a length behind on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, steadied off heels near 600M, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 500M, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, checked off heels near 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong, unacceptable performance.
Began well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 650M, weakened on turn, eased early in straight. (Minor laceration to the superficial digital flexor tendon.)
Travelled in front of midfield, wide and without cover, ran on all the way to score.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, closed off nicely to the line for 2nd.
Taken back, at rear 2 wide, saved ground and continued on fairly for 3rd.
Raced at the rear, along the rail, improved slightly and saved ground.
Rolled forward on the rail, headed passing 150M, one paced.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot. (See Incident Report)
In midfield after crowded for room, pretty much one paced.
Sat behind midfield, 2 wide, gradually gave ground in the straight.
Sent forward, settled outside the lead, stayed on till 250M only. (See Incident Report)
Settled to race in the box-seat, was one paced and emptied for final 200M. (See Incident Report)
Taken back, at tail and on rail, never featured in the straight.
Awkward start, at rear, was never a match.
Settled in midfield on the rail in 6th or 7th, switched out for a run entering home straight, responded under pressure inside the final 250 metres, gained upper hand final strides.
Settled just worse than midfield, wide rounding home bend, ran on well inside the final 250 metres to just fail to get up on line.
Travelled in midfield racing keenly in early stages, ran on steadily under pressure in straight to hit the front 150 metres out only to be collared close to home.
Quickly bounced back from moderate start to settle in 4th over 2L back, commenced move 3-wide approaching home turn and hit the front 300 metres out, led until headed over 150 metres out.
Forward of midfield early, improved to 5th just over 2L back approaching home bend, baulked behind runners until the 200 metres, fought on well to finish.
Soon took up running from the widest gate, obtained rails run over 1200 metres out, led until headed inside the final 300 metres.
Pressed forward from a wide gate soon settling over 1L back in 3rd on the rail after the first 300 metres, chased the leaders into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled 1L back in 2nd from 1300 metres out, held some chance under pressure early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th or 9th, in similar position entering home straight, fought on steadily and never nearer.
Settled in last few on the rail after beginning from a wide gate, made no impression in the run to the line.
Wide behind midfield early, gradually settled further back after the first 300 metres, joint last into straight, made no impression.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, went wide into straight, never featured.
Settled behind midfield, in 9th spot making the turn for home, into clear 400M, ran on strongly to lead near 200M, soon well clear, eased closing stages.
Settled down 6th in mid-division, made good progress from 500M, no match for winner passing 200M, hung on for 2nd.
Not hurried, dropped back towards the rear, switched widest passing 500M, stayed on well to go 3rd near line, no impression on clear winner.
Reserved behind mid-division, saved ground on inside, not clear running early straight, stayed on moderately final 200M, got up for 4th last stride.
From wide draw crossed to a 2-wide spot passing 1100M tracking leader, briefly led 300M, out-finished over final 200M, edged out to 5th near line.
In touch behind leaders, kept on without threatening in the straight, not pace to challenge leaders.
Began only fairly, soon guided to the fence racing in a rearward position, switched out on straightening, stayed on fairly without threatening.
From draw 1 chased leaders in 4th, kept on same pace in straight, out of contention 200M.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover, in last detached, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on fairly when asked, held up or clear running final 100M.
Urged to take the lead, led uncontested, headed 300M, soon no extra and weakened away.
Unable to slot in, caught 3-wide behind midfield, couldn't finish off turning home. (Jockey : didn't travel as well as anticipated and always under pressure to maintain position.)
Chased the pace along the 3-path, wide no cover throughout the race, weakened rapidly passing 400M, eased when no chance. (Mucus.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score by a nose.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, made contact and unbalanced near 700M, same margin back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to take a place.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first few late.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, crossed near 900M, 2 wide on turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, just ahead of midfield, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1-1/2L behind, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to score by a neck.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, blocked near 250M, finished off very strongly thereafter to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.

Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 450M, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, finished off strongly thereafter to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.) (Dead-heat for 4th.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to make frame. (Dead-heat for 4th.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 750M, led by 1-1/2L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed 50M.
Began well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, just ahead of midfield, no cover throughout, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, wider from 450M, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from a tricky draw, raced 4 wide behind midfield, carried wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, angled out 450M, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 750M, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.

Taken back from gate 9, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed good progress early in straight, made contact near 200M, kept on strongly to the line, just narrowly beaten.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail. 7 lengths back, still last turning in, showed very good response early in straight, not enough room near 100M, closed off well thereafter to take a place.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross 800M, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first few late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, wider turning in, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked final 50M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, same position on turn, showed good response early in straight, inconvenienced near 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 800M, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 400M, showed good response early in straight, made contact near 200M, ran on well until badly checked 100M, eased thereafter.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked 50M, eased thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths back, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final 150M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well to win.
Pushed to obtain box seat, favoured by the slow pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Settled in front, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200m.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, moved forward 800M, emptied 400M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, ran on ok.
Pushed to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased back, never improved.
Hung out badly, never competitive.
Ridden to take lead, travelled strongly in lead, responded solidly in the straight, scored by 3.5L.
Settled behind leaders, commenced to improve near 400M, responded nicely in the straight.
Travelled in front of midfield on rail, niggled passing 700M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, ran well in the straight.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Jumped well then settled behind the lead on rail, asked for effort near 350M, worked home well.
Raced in front of midfield, made some ground when placed pressure in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 700M, finished one-paced.
Slow out, not travel well at any stage of the race at rear, not responding in the straight, lame left front next day.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled at rear, placed pressure passing 500M, failed to run on in the straight.
Hard ridden along to obtain forward position, faded out near 100M.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, came under pressure near 600M, weakened in the straight, lame right front next day.

Raced in midfield on rail in first section before moving away from rail passing the 1100m. Eased three wide approaching the 400m, sprinted smartly to assume lead nearing the 200m before dashing away for easy win.
Strode forward to race in second before settling on leaders back. Cornered hard on the rail before battling away to move into second place at the 150m. Over a length clear of third.

Raced in midfield early before improving position around field passing the 1000m to race in second by the 750m. Moved up to share lead at the 250m before being soon passed by winner. Well beaten third.

Shifted behind runners at start, settled near the rear. Was ridden along to hold position approaching the 700m before making steady ground. Moved wider on straightening, passed a few late but was no threat.
Had soft run in midfield on rail. Travelled ok nearing corner but only finished off only fairly to midfield.

Strode forward from wide gate before improving to race outside the leader by the 1200m. Within 2L of the lead on straightening before peaking on effort at the furlong pole & giving a few lengths thereafter.
Ridden forward before assuming lead soon after start. Headed in the lead at the 250m mark before weakening out thereafter.

Good position in midfield early before being shuffled further back in second section. Moved into the 3 wide line with cover approaching 800m before cornering very wide & well off lead. Made no headway in straight.
Had no early speed & soon enough settled at tail. Had only two runners behind when 6L from lead entering final section before failing to make any noteworthy headway in straight.

Restrained at start & drifted back to race third from last on rail. Travelled ok when entering last section only 4L off lead, before peaking soon after straightening & weakening out poorly in last furlong.
Steadied after start & shifted back to second last away from rail. Ridden along approaching the 600m when racing a clear last but yielded significant ground in last section to be beaten a long way.
Raced worse than midfield, three wide with cover for majority. Came under heavy riding approaching the 500m, cornered second last before weakening out abruptly in last furlong. (Lame post-race).
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, showed very good response early in straight, ridden to lead 150M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Began only fairly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but still headed 150M, lost 2nd close home.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 450M, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide and without cover, just ahead of midfield, carried wider on turn, kept on one pace early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Sent forward, took rail and in the box-seat after 800M, worked home nicely to score by 3/4L
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, ran strongly from 150M to take 2nd.
Slow to begin, midfield, continued one paced to the line
Rolled forward, 2 wide, continued to make ground from 200M. (See Incident Report)
Taken back, at rear along the rail, showed little dash 150M.
Pushed to hold the rail, pretty much one paced.
Sat behind midfield, on the rail, ran on until 100M flattened
Sat in midfield, 2 wide, found no extra for final 200M.
Taken back, at rear, 2 wide by Home Turn, headed near 100M and weakened thereafter.
Pushed to roll forward, showed no turn of foot.
Rolled forward, 3 wide from 950M, run ended at 200M.
Attempted to push forward, sat behind midfield from 1350M, not a factor. (See Incident Report)
Soon improved to first few settling some 2L back in 4th, commenced move 3-wide rounding home bend and led over 200 metres out, held on well.
Settled in rear of midfield, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest runner into home straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear of midfield in 8th on the rail, came under pressure inside the final 200 metres and finished off the race nicely.

Broke well, obtained rails run coming onto stables bend settling one back in 3rd, remained in one back on rails but when 5th rounding home bend, saved ground on the inside turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.

Jumped well niggling along before settling in midfield in 7th over 3L off the pace, commenced move coming onto home bend and came within 2L of pace turning in, kept on under pressure without threatening.
Jumped well from the one draw, settled in 6th on rails within 3L of pace, similar when 7th rounding home bend, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on same pace.

Jumped awkwardly from the widest gate, vied for lead out wide early stages before settling outside the lead in 2nd, improved to draw level coming onto home bend but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Taken back from a wide gate, remained well behind to home bend, went very wide into straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Jumped fairly, settled 3-wide better than midfield over 2L back in 5th, made headway from the 650 metres and given reminders approaching home turn, unable to sustain effort after straightening.
Settled in last few, came under pressure after straightening, ran past well-beaten horses.

Pressed forward from a wide gate to lead early, obtained rails run on stables bend, led the field until joined inside the 500 metres, weakened I nside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in last few, never seen with a chance.
Never far off from the pace, travelled well in 5th making the turn for home, quickened up well to lead passing 100M, firmly in control late stages. (Trainer questioned re improved performance.)
Jumped well from inside draw, tracked leaders, responded well on straightening, not pace of winner final 150M, clear 2nd.
Jumped on terms, restrained in midfield, driven along passing 500M, ran on well down outside to go 3rd near line.
In mid-division just over 4Ls behind leader in a fast run race, ran on steadily in the straight, held by first 2, narrowly missed out on 3rd.
Pressed forward from draw 12, tracked leader on outside in a fast run race, hampered top of straight, chased steadily until out-finished final 100M.
Crossed to the lead from draw 9, led them at good pace, couldn't shake off rivals early straight, headed 150M, no extra close home.
Held up towards the rear, responded fairly in straight, never reached contention.
Obtained a good run behind the speed, shifted out 500M to make his run, found less than expected in the finish, gave ground final 100M.
Began fairly, taken across behind runners and travelled in the rear further back than intend, couldn't finish off over final 400M, never in the picture.
Dropped back to near last on settling, 8Ls to make up 400M, made no progress.
Settled down ahead of midfield, pushed along from home turn, soon beaten on straightening.
Began awkwardly lost ground, towards the rear 6-7Ls away, dropped away rapidly turning home, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield early, 2 wide in the middle stages, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 3 wide behind the lead, 2 wide from 800M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, found rail near 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide in the early stages, 2 wide from 800M, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weaken gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, drifted away 300M to score.
At rear, 2-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, pace good, lack room 400M, made ground when clear.
At rear, on the fence, pace good, raced greenly, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, emptied 250M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, pace good, out of fuel 200M.
At back along the fence, pace good, blocked most straight, dashed fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, pace good, lack room in straight, no dash.
Eased to rear, 2 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, pace good, emptied 450M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, pace good, dropped off quickly 400M.
Sent forward, settled behind the leaders, quickened passing 300M, scored unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield, commenced to improve on straightening, made up some nice late ground, finished solidly.
Hampered at start, settled behind midfield on rail, made ground passing 150M, worked home solidly
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort near 400M, gained nice ground passing 200M.
Jumped nicely, niggled along to take lead, responded well in the straight.
Began well, ridden along to race outside the lead, fought well in the early part of straight, gave ground near 150M.
Ridden along but no early speed, settled towards rear, travelled only fairly in middle stages, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight, rider questioned.
Raced midfield, 3 wide with cover, one-paced in the straight when placed under pressure.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 400M, worked home one-paced.
Taken back but raced wide and without cover passing 800M, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, niggled near 1000M to maintain its position, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, limited response.
Raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Wide and without cover throughout outside the leaders, lay in in the straight when giving ground, faded out in the straight.
Settled in box seat, lay in rounding the Home Turn and in the straight when giving ground, finished tailed out.
Strode forward from outside gate, settled outside leader by the 900m. Moved up to assume lead at the 250m before dashing away for very easy win.

Very slow to begin conceding over 5L. Continued a clear last throughout. Over 7L from lead entering last section, moved wider before making good late ground into second late. Well behind winner but very good considering.
Showed good early speed to lead. Continued in lead until being headed by winner at the 250m before finishing off ok to hold third, well behind dominant winner.
Wasn't fast to begin before improving after being ridden along to settle midfield, 3L from lead. Continued to be ridden along around bend before finishing off ok to hold 4th well behind winner.

Steadied after start & shifted back to race just worse than midfield away from rail. Over 5L from lead entering last section before managing to pass a few runners in dash to line without improving margin to winner.
Not bustled after start & drifted back to midfield between runners. Finished off evenly to midfield in final section.
Didn't begin fast before holding midfield position between runners. Left wide without cover from the 800m. Peaked at the furlong & could offer no more thereafter.

Began well before drifting back after the start, racing wide & worse than midfield, 5L from lead by the 800m. Pushed 4 wide form the 600m mark before peaking at the 250m & weakening a few lengths thereafter.
Steadied after the start before drifting back to third last on rail. Cornered on the rail when over 5L from lead before failing to make any headway in last section. Well held.

Had no speed after start & drifted back to second last. Continued well back on cornering, entered last section 6 lengths from lead, held up until the final furlong but was always well back throughout.
Pushed forward before racing on leaders back from the 900m. Peaked at the 250m & gave ground thereafter. Well held.
Had no speed after the start but held the rail position & improved to race in midfield on rail. Hard ridden from the 500m before weakening out in last section to be well beaten.

A touch slow to begin before improving to race in midfield between runners early before drifting back approaching half-way. Shifted wider approaching bend before weakening out sharply in final section. Well beaten.

Ridden hard to improve after the first furlong, worked hard to settle 4th away from rail with cover. Entered last section only 1.5L from lead before weakening out sharply in last 300m. Long last. (Must trial – poor perf).
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 600M, finished off very strongly in straight to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 600M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 1100M, commenced move after passing 650M, 4 wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved closer after passing 1200M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, 3 wide into straight, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, moved closer after passing 1250M, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Rolled forward, take the lead after 900M, closed off nicely to score by 1-1/4L.
Taken back, 3 wide but with cover, raced tight in 200M but fought on solidly to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, ran on reasonably.
Rolled forward to race in front, remained one paced to the line.
Raced in behind, 3 wide with cover at rounding the Turn, saved ground and ran on nicely.
In one-out one-back position, found no extra for final 150M.
Sat in behind midfield, along the rail, closed off fairly late.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Stayed in midfield, along the rail, ran on to the line.
Settled towards the rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, remained one paced to the line.
Stayed in behind midfield, 4 wide without cover, run ended 200M out.
Travelled behind midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot. (See Incident Report)
Midfield, 3 wide no cover, run ended at 300M.
Slow to begin, sat behind midfield along the rail, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well niggling along, settled 2-wide just over 2L back in 4th, commenced move approaching home straight, gained upper hand over 150 metres out.
Jumped well from a wide gate settling one back 2-wide in 2nd, became 3rd into straight, soon came under pressure to challenge but unable to peg back the winner the length of the straight.
Gradually took up running setting a steady pace, led the field until finding no extra over 150 metres out.
Jumped fairly, travelled keenly at the 1000 metres when gradually taken backward early stages, remained one from last into straight, produced good late impression final stages.(Tactic questioned)
Slightly slow out, soon picked up to 5th just over 3L back, remained similar to straight, unable to quicken to threaten.
Began fairly from the one draw, improved steadily to 2L back in 3rd coming onto home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Settled well behind, widest turning in, never a danger.
From draw 12 crossed to the lead before the turn, led slowly, driven out nearing 300M, stuck to task well in the run home, holding off rivals comfortably.
Tracked leader in slowly run race, tried hard to reel in leader in the straight but always held.
Chased the pace on inside, into clear 400M, ran on steadily but safely held by first 2.
Reserved behind mid-division, into clear top of straight, ran on well early straight, peaked on its run passing 150M.
Settled down behind midfield in a slowly run race, fought on steadily to the line, no threat to winner.
Began only fairly then crowded for room, recovered to race in midfield along the fence, kept on same pace in straight, unable to challenge leaders.
Reared abruptly at the start and lost a significant amount of ground, got back to the field 1000M, ran on without threat to leaders in the straight.
Close up behind leaders in slowly run race, one paced early straight, faded passing 200M.
Taken back from wide barrier, 6Ls back in a 3-wide spot towards the rear, wide into straight, never able to challenge.
Raced keenly passing 900M, heavily restrained in midfield, failed to finish off in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, held up towards the rear in a slowly run race, switched wide nearing 400M, couldn't go on.
Steadied early stages from wide draw, held up in the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, failed to make any progress.
Settled midfield, caught wide from draw 13 and no cover passing 900M, weakened over final 300M.
Dropped back, ended up in the rear making the home turn, soon outpaced on straightening, soundly beaten.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Shifted out at start, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.

Slightly slow out, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, showed little response thereafter.

Began well from a wide draw, trapped very wide early, found a 2 wide spot near 750M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, showed little response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, wider into straight, finished off evenly.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly until checked near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, similar position on turn, made little progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Hampered at start, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually after passing 150M.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final 300M. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a nose.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently on rail, shared lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly, just narrowly beaten.
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 8 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress after passing 250M, no threat to the first few.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, one paced thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back, last turning in, taken wide in straight and made some progress. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found cover near 700M, 2 lengths back turning in, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M.
Hampered start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 1000M, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began smartly from gate 10, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length behind the leader turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, angled out 500M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out 250M, finished off evenly.
Out in line, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, in rear pair, 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off evenly. (Blood in trachea.)
Moderately away, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Settled in midfield, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, led 400M, ran on well until 50M overhauled.
Eased back, 2 wide, lack room 5-3, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, on the fence, on heels 500M, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Clipped heels shortly after start, took rail at back, held up most straight, made steady ground.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
Slow away, at rear, 2-3 wide, made ground 200M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, took rail, no progress.
Pushed to take rail and lead, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, dropped off quickly 500M.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, emptied 400M.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide throughout, no progress
Raced 3-5 wide at rear, never a factor.
Broke well then sent forward, settled outside the leaders, 3 wide, responded strongly in the straight, gained ground passing 200M to score.
Began only fairly then was crowded for room, settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 450M, kept making ground in the straight, finished nicely.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, then taken back, asked for effort near 600M, made up nice late ground.
Took lead in one-off position without asking, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Hard ridden along to race behind leaders, kept on rail to save ground rounding the Home Turn, worked home well in the straight.
Raced inside the leader on rail, quickened in the early part of straight, gave ground final 100M, failed to make impression.
Settled at rear on rail, always niggled, one-paced in the straight.
Settled at back, niggled near 600M, made some ground in the straight.
Jumped nicely, settled midfield, very wide rounding the Home Turn, gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, faded out passing 200M.
At the start stumbled, urged along to take forward position, give ground passing 600M, not comfortable in its action, must trial.
Began fast, shifted across to the rail when leading after 200m. Cornered over a length clear in the lead & maintained cozy margin in the dash to line. Solid win.

Improved after the start to race in third away from the rail. Raced keen & near heals in middle stages. Moved three wide nearing the corner, moved to second on straightening but couldn't real in winner. Held second.

Had no early speed & soon settled a long last. Hard ridden throughout middle stages, over 10L from lead passing half-way. Moved wider on cornering before making huge late headway to snare third in closing stages.
Raced to midfield, three wide with cover. Moved 5 wide on cornering before battling away in the straight to not be far behind.

Ridden forward to midfield in early stages before drifting further back in middle stages. Continued worse than midfield entering last section over 5L from lead before making up a few lengths in late stages without threatening.
Steadied after the start, shifted back to second last soon after start. Continued well back on cornering before making steady late ground between runners in the final 300m.

Had no speed after the start & drifted back to third last after first furlong. Niggled to improve passing the 600m, moved wider on straightening, cornered with only one behind before making steady ground to midfield late.
Squeezed at start, lost ground before improving to race in midfield away from rail. Travelled well nearing bend when easing wider, before maintaining position in the straight. No threat.
Hard ridden after start, raced very wide without cover. Continued to be hard ridden & improve in middle stages before cornering only 3.5L from lead. Peaked & weakened out in final furlong.

Showed speed after the start to race on the leaders back. Drifted further from the leading middle stages. Five lengths from lead entering last section when under hard ridding before weakening further late.

Didn't begin fast before being hard ridden to hold midfield position on rail. Drifted further back approaching last section when over 6L form lead. Momentarily held up near 300m but weakened significantly thereafter.

Hard ridden after start, improved to race outside the leader after first furlong. Came under hard riding on straightening & yielded significant ground in straight to finish a long last. (Irregular heart rhythm. Must trial).

Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 2w behind midfield, hampered near 1200M, commenced move after passing 600M, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by 3-1/2L.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, 6 lengths or so back, hampered near 1150M, carried wider from 600M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 wide from 800M, hard ridden after passing 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly.
Average to begin, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out 500M, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began well, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, found rail near 650M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 150M, made minor progress thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.

Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, found rail near 800M, challenged by rival turning in, showed limited response early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, crowded and brushed rail near 1200M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly from gate 12, raced wide with cover at rear, 8 lengths back, hampered near 1200M, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Away with them, raced prominently but trapped wide, found rail near 1150M, 2 lengths back in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, hampered near 1200M, 5 to 6 lengths back in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide better than midfield early, severely checked near 1200M, 4 to 5 lengths back in the middle stages, weakened from 650M, eased early in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)

Placing: PU
Comment: Began well from gate 1, raced prominently, went wrong and pulled up after passing 1300M.
Pushed forward, box seat after 650M, ran on gamely to score from 250M.
Raced in midfield, took the rail after 700M, closed off strongly from 200M onwards.
Sent forward, 2 wide, ran on reasonably.
Raced in behind, checked near 1100M, ran on one paced to the line.
Eased back, at rear 2 wide, pretty much one paced
In midfield after stumbled, 2 wide, found no extra for final 100M.
Sent forward to lead, weakened passing 200M.
Travelled behind midfield, along the rail, lost ground from approaching 150M.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, continued on one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, swung widest on straightening, not a factor.

Placing: UR
Comment: Unseated rider in the race. (see incident report)
Slightly slow out, settled in last few near the rail, saved ground turning for home, baulked for a run until the 250 metres, responded well to assert authority 100 metres out.
Jumped fairly settling just off the pace in 4th or 3rd on the rail, came to challenge upon straightening and hit the front 300 metres out, headed under pressure inside the final 100 metres.
Settled in midfield on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning for home, obtained a clear passage over 300 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in last few on the rail after beginning from a wide gate, switched out for a run entering straight, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, gradually drifted backward to 10th in back straight, renewed effort 4-wide rounding home bend, ran on under pressure without threatening.

Ridden along from a wide gate before settling wide in midfield, lost position over 900 metres out and remained behind midfield into home straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away, remained well behind most of the way to straight despite ridden early, wide rounding home bend and into straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Moderate start, settled wide without cover in last few, fought on steadily without threatening in home straight. (Lame next day.)
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from the widest gate, given reminders approaching home straight, made modest progress early on but had no more to give inside the final 200 metres.
Settled just outside the leader, gained slender lead on top of home bend, headed shortly after straightening, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Began well, settled just off the pace in 3rd about 2L off the pace, remained similar to home straight, faded gradually.
Soon dropped to last few, never nearer.

Broke well, settled some 3L back in 4th turning into back straight, dropped slightly further back to 5th shortly afterwards, came under pressure rounding home bend and soon weakened after straightening.
Led on the rail until joined rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Pressed leader on outside from 850M, took over early straight, quickened clear under top weight inside 200M, kept on strongly to the line, always in control.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, kept on well in the straight but couldn't reel in the winner.
From draw 12 cross to race in midfield, driven out 400M, ran on well to line, just missed 2nd.
Soon led, pressed by rival from 850M, headed early straight, weakened over final 200M, held on for 4th just.
Jumped fairly, settled down 7Ls near the rear, ran on mildly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Not hurried after slow start, settled towards the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, chased steadily, not reached top 3.
Prominent behind leaders, couldn't go on turning home, remained one pace to the line.
Up with early pace, fell back to a midfield position from 800M, couldn't finish off turning home, never threatened.
Slow to muster speed after awkward start, settled midfield, wide no cover from 700M, kept on one paced turning home, weakened inside 200M.
Slow to begin, no closer than 3-wide towards the rear, swung widest home, gave limited response early straight, no extra 200M.
From wide draw dropped back to race towards the rear, wide into straight, didn't respond to riding and made no impression first time on the AWT.
Couldn't keep up early stages, soon detached in last 10Ls away, failed to make any progress in straight, never in the picture.
