Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, found rail near 650M, same margin back turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on very strongly, easily scored.
Began smartly from a wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide behind midfield, found rail near 700M, 8 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Moderately away from gate 1, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, moved closer on turn, hit the front near 300M, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter, just stayed on for 3rd.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced 3 wide at rear, 9 to 10 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made reasonable progress in straight, no threat to the first few.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 550M, same margin back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, headed near 300M, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 11 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Average to begin, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, one paced in straight.
Crowded out start, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still well back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 4 wide at rear early, found a 2 wide spot near 700M, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 11 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly 350M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, pace good, led 400M, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at good pace, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300M.
Slow away, trapped 2-3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield along the fence, pace good, just held ground in straight.
At rear, pace good, made ground 200M.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide, pace good, made ground 250M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, made good ground 150M.
Eased at start, took rail, pace good, on heels 800M, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, pace good, emptied 300M.
Slow away, trapped 3 wide, pace good, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, badly unbalanced 800M, no progress.
Ridden along to take forward position, raced wide and without cover in handy position, quickened passing 300M, finished strongly to score.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, good response in the straight, finished solidly.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, niggled through the race, gained some late ground, finished nicely.
Jumped nicely, settled in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, worked home well.
Slow out, settled behind midfield on rail, difficult to obtain clear running near 300M, made up some late ground.
Slow out, raced at rear on rail, worked home one-paced.
Jumped sharply, settled behind the lead, gave ground near 100M.
Settled midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight, finished one-paced.
Settled at back, asked for effort near 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at tail, tried to improve near 500M, widest on straightening, finished one-paced.
Urged along to take lead, placed pressure in the straight, weakened near 100M.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Proved difficult to settle near 1000M, settled in front of midfield, faded out passing 200M.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure in the straight, weakened passing 300M, failed to make impression.
Lovely run on leaders back throughout. Improved between runners approaching the 200m mark before drawing away strongly in the final furlong to score comfortably.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail. Moved away from rail approaching the 600m before getting clear running on straightening. Made continual headway in final 300m but couldn't get to winner.

Not fast to begin, shifted back to last after the start. Continued near the rear passing the 600m, stayed close to rail on cornering before making good late headway between runners in final the 350m. Closed to third late.

Pushed forward after start, raced wide before improving to race outside leader passing the 1500m. Assumed the lead at the 400m before being headed by the winner at the 225m & yielding a length or two late.

Steadied & shifted across to midfield after start. Shuffled further back in middle stages before moving wider approaching corner. Shifted into clear running at 350m before making up a length or two late without threatening.

Pushed forward after the start, raced outside leader before getting 1,1 from the 1400m. Eased three wide on cornering, continued close to the lead at the 300m before giving a few lengths in last furlong.
Began fast, crossed from outside gate to assume lead. Continued in the lead until being headed shortly after straightening. Battled away bravely until the furlong pole before weakening out.

Steadied from wide gate, before racing in midfield, 3 wide in early & middle stages. Commenced to improve around field passing 800m when racing wide. Only a length form lead on cornering before weakening out in final 250m.
Ridden forward after start before racing in midfield away from rail. Came under heavy riding at the 500m before giving a length or two in final section. Well held.
Raced in midfield away from rail in early & middle stages. Moved wider passing the 600m before peaking at the 250m & weakening out thereafter.

Not fast to begin, drifted back to rearward position after the start. Was a clear last on cornering, moved wider approaching bend. Held up between runners at the 300m & again inside last furlong. Never involved.

Didn't begin fast before racing second from last after start. Relegated to last passing the 900m. Moved wider when ridden along at the 600m, but was always well back & made no improvement in last section.

Shifted back to race worse than midfield in early & middle stages. Improved slightly after moving wider with cover passing the 800m. Pushed the widest on cornering, peaked at the 300m & weakened out thereafter.
Raced just worse than midfield on rail. Began yielding ground from the 600m & weakened out further in the straight to be a well beaten last.
Clean jump, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.

Began well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, bumped 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L behind the leader, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame without threatening.

Began well from gate 13, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 3 wide from near 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled keenly to turn, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, bumped 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, taken back to race at tail, 5 lengths back turning in, no clear running early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, angled out 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Raced in midfield, swung outside on straightening, ran on gamely to score by a short head.
Pressed forward, raced in one-out one-back position after 750M, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Sent forward, along the rail after 800M, ran on reasonably.
Box seat after 900M and raced tight, made minor inroad.
Began fairly, sent forward, 3 wide no cover, ran on fairly to the line.
Began only fairly and lost ground, rolled forward but wide and no cover, found no extra for final 150M.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, did not make ground in the straight.
Taken back, at rear wide but with cover, was one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, showed no response.
Eased back, 4 wide but with cover, made some ground in the straight.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Taken back, at tail and on rail, did not feature.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover, never looked to threaten.
Behind midfield, did not improve and difficult to settle after 1200M, weakened after 300M.
Settled in last few, baulked for a run early in straight, obtained a clear passage 250 metres out, quickened well to assert authority close to home.
Settled in midfield, came to challenge shortly after straightening, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, caught close to home.
Began well from the widest gate settling one from last, commenced move rounding home bend making swift progress on the outside, 4-wide into the straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, trailed the field and wide into straight, ran on steadily under pressure inside the final 300 metres.

Jumped awkwardly, soon picked up to a prominent position before settling just over 2L off the pace in 4th, commenced move 600 metres out and joined the leaders turning in, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.

Crowded at start, travelled keenly in rear of midfield in 7th on the rail, remained similar rounding home bend, made some impression along the rail early in straight but did not find much room 200 metres out, kept on well to the line.

Began well, travelled wide with leaders before taking over inside the 1600 metres, obtained rails run shortly afterwards and led until joined into the straight, overhauled inside the final 200 metres.
Wide in midfield early before improving swiftly to 2nd 1200 metres out, came to join the leader entering home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield in 5th on the rail just over 3L off the pace, saved ground on the inside turning in, held up for a run after the 300 metres, kept on same pace without quickening.

Shared early pace, settled one back after the first 200 metres and became 3rd shortly afterwards, remained in similar one back position turning into straight, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Settled down in 4th about 4Ls off the good pace, picked up speed gradually on straightening, looked to be held by first 2 at 100M but rallied strongly to prevail in a 4-way photo finish.

Reserved in mid-pack about 5Ls behind leaders in a fast run race, lay in under pressure in straight and proved difficult to ride, fought on strongly final 200M, briefly led close home but was caught last stride.
Settled down midfield 5-6Ls back, going strongly when held up for clear running 300M-200M, switched lane making good headway final 100M to be nearest at the line. Unlucky.
Reserved in midfield, pushed along near 500M, quickened well to lead 250M, peaked on its run 100M out, couldn't hold rivals late and beaten to 4th in a blanket finish.
Crowded for room at start, ended up near the rear 8Ls off the good pace, driven out 500M, took a while to get going, ran on towards the line but held by leaders.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear 7Ls back, lay in early straight and held up for clear running passing 300M, stayed on moderately final 200M, awkwardly placed late.
Chased leaders in 3rd, driven out 500M, kept on same pace in straight, soon outsprinted by main rivals.
Caught wide first turn, moved up to vie for the lead on outside, briefly took over early straight, swamped 250M, soon no extra and weakened.
From wide draw switched across behind runners early stages, settled 9Ls off the pace in the rear, steadied 350M when attempting a run on inside, switched out to challenge but couldn't go on.
Dropped back to race in the rear 9Ls off the pace, swung wide home, didn't finish off.
Crossed to the lead from 1600M, soon vied lead with rival setting good tempo, weakened away 350M, dropped out rapidly to finish last.
Began well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, took the lead after turning in, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, angled out 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left hind leg.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 500M, finished off one pace.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried wider from 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line, scored by 1-1/4L.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, finished off well but outpaced by the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, closer on turn, angled out after passing 500M, bumped early in straight, finished off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, angled out 500M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to be nearest on line.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 900M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out 500M, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, carried wider 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, found cover from 900M, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 750M, a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Away with them, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to take a place, nearest on line.

Clean jump, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, 2 wide from 1000M, same margin back to turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, ran on evenly, steadied off heels close home.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out after passing 400M, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.

Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, found cover near 1000M, 3 lengths back in the middle stages, commenced move after passing 500M, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run near 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, hard ridden early to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 600M, showed limited response, very wide turning in, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, peaked and lost position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Pushed to secure box seat, closed off well 200M to score.
Midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the lead, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 100M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground.
Slow away, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Checked start, took rail at back, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
At rear, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, 2 wide at back, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Ridden forward, settled midfield on rail, near 200M had some difficulty obtaining clear running, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, responded strongly in the straight.
Settled towards rear, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, in the early part of straight had difficulty obtaining clear running, finished solidly.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 450M, worked home solidly.
Raced towards rear, passing 500M was awkwardly placed close to heels, made ground passing 100M.
Slow out, settled towards rear on rail, passing 150M had some difficulty obtaining clear running, made up some nice late ground.
Raced at tail, tried to improve but unable to obtain clear running over final stages, not tested.
Sent forward to race behind the lead, placed pressure passing 400M, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, in the early part of straight had difficulty obtaining clear running, passing 150M was steadied when disappointed for run.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover round first turn, after 900M improved to lead, placed pressure passing 400M, gave ground near 50M.
At start stumbled, then ridden along and settled in box seat after 900M, niggled near 500M, gave ground near 100M.

Showed customary early speed to lead. Crossed to rail when leading approaching the 700m. Raced over a length clear on straightening, maintained comfortable lead inside the last 100m before holding off fast finisher.
Not fast to begin, ridden forward to race just worse than midfield between runners. Shifted wider into clear running on straightening before finishing strongly in the last furlong to just miss.

Steadied to midfield but raced very wide without cover. Improved position passing 650m when continuing wide before entering last section in 3rd place. Battled on strongly in last furlong after wide passage (Blood in trachea).

Steadied from wide gate before getting back to a clear last after first 150m. Continued a clear last entering last section, nearly 7L from lead before making substantial late headway in closing stages.
Raced in midfield on rail. Entered last section 3.5L from lead on rail, moved wider after straightening before making up a length in the final furlong.

Strode forward after start, before improving to second position away from rail approaching the 600m mark. Couldn't go with leader on straightening before peaking at the 150m & weakening out thereafter.
Strode forward before being crossed and racing on leaders back. Stayed close to the inside on straightening but could make no further improvement & weakened a length in closing stages.

Had no speed after the start & raced third last away from rail. Hung out & was consequently wide around bend. Straightened the widest runner, well off lead before making up a few lengths in dash to line to finish to midfield.

Had no speed after start but made some ground to midfield when racing wide. Steadied near heals & lost ground passing the 600m. Ridden along after entering last section but failed to make any headway in straight.
Raced in midfield between runners. Under 3 lengths from the lead entering the final section before peaking on effort passing the 250m mark & weakening a further few lengths in closing stages.

Began awkwardly near heels & lost ground after start, racing second last soon after start. Stayed close to the rail on cornering but could make no further headway in the straight & finished well back.

Showed speed after start before being crossed, raced keenly & left wide without cover near the 600m. Had cover momentarily on straightening before dropping out sharply in the last furlong to be well beaten last.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 150M, finished off strongly to score.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, 1-1/2L back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.

Jumped with them, raced wide behind midfield early, sent forward after passing 1200M, positioned 3 wide, a length or so back in the middle stages, no cover on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight, not able to test properly.

Average to begin, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1200M, took the lead near 900M, 2 wide on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.

Jumped well from the widest draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 600M, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 100M, steadied off heels 50M, not ridden out thereafter.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 900M, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Raced at rear on the outside throughout, 5 to 6 lengths back, failed to make any progress in straight.
Raced in behind midfield, rounding the home turn raced tight til 200M, ran on strongly to score.
Raced in midfield initially, rolled forward but wide and without cover after 1200M, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Began awkwardly, taken back, made some ground but pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on fairly in the straight.
Sent forward, 2 wide, ran on to the line.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, save ground but emptied after 100M.
Taken back, along the rail, swung outside on straightening, showed no response.
Raced in midfield initially, sent forward to lead after 1700M, pretty one paced.
Taken back, 2 wide, made minor ground.
Raced in front to lead, along the rail, lost ground in the straight.
Raced in the box-seat, along the rail, made no threats.
Settled towards the rear in 8th, widest runner turning in, finished off strongly down the centre of the track to snatch victory final strides.

Improved from moderate start to one back position near the rail, drifted to over 2L back in 5th on home bend, renewed effort on straightening, fought on steadily to hit the front over 20 metres out only to be caught on the line.

Ridden to prominent position outside the leader early, drifted backward to 4th within 2L of pace coming onto home bend, renewed effort after straightening and led momentarily 100 metres out, caught final strides.

Moderate start, remained wide throughout, towards rear early before improving steadily in back straight to share 2nd on home bend, sustained progress to hold every chance inside the 200 metres only to be swamped late.

Broke well from a wide gate and ridden early, dropped back to 2L 4th into back straight, renewed effort to take up running over 600 metres out and share pace into straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.

Began from a wide gate, tailed off early before ridden to join the rear of the field over 800 metres out, saved ground on home turn coming within 3L of the pace, sustained progress until baulked nearing finish.

Ridden to lead after moderate start from a wide gate, led on the rail from the 1000 metres until headed leaving the Rock, saved ground on home turn sharing pace into straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres.
Began well from the one draw, soon dropped to midfield in 6th about 3L back and became 7th coming out of back straight, made headway rounding home bend and fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well, settled just over 2L back in 5th, became 3L 6th approaching the Rock, kept on at the one pace in home straight.
Crowded shortly after the start and dropped well behind, trailed the field from the 700 metres, no further impression.
Never far off from the pace, moved up to 3rd back straight, driven out and responded well from 400M, led 150M out, ran away for comfortable win on his first up for new stable.
Settled down midfield, tracked path of eventual winner rounding home turn, ran on well to go 2nd late stages but no match for the winner.
Towards the rear early stages, made quick forward move approaching 600M, led from 550M, caught mid-straight, faded towards the line but held 3rd comfortably.

Always prominent along the 2-path, driven out 400M, kept on steadily to the line, no threat from 150M. (Jockey questioned re his riding home turn and told to ensure he rides competitive at all times.)
Dropped back to the rear from wide draw, held up in 9th spot 8Ls off the pace, stayed on moderately on straightening, no threat to first 3.
Away well from draw 1, up with early pace before taking the lead 1100M, overtaken by rival nearing 500M, fought on same pace in straight, faded to 6th.
Reserved towards the rear over 8Ls off the pace early and middle stages, stayed on fairly over final 300M, not reached leaders.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up in last spot nearly 10Ls back, pushed along home turn, made limited progress final 300M.
From wide draw slotted into a 2-wide spot in midfield, bustled along 450M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, switched wide 500M, soon outpaced and dropped out of contention.
Tracked leaders early stages, caught 3-wide no cover from 1000M, struggled to keep up home turn, first to be beaten.
Made contact on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, angled out 350M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after entering the back straight, headed near 650M, retook the lead turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two.
Began awkwardly and bumped, taken back to race at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, still last turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out near 450M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider from 450M, very wide turning in, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, found cover near 750M, 3 wide on turn, carried wider turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 750M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide, took the lead near 650M, hung out badly rounding the home turn, made contact early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider from 400M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Began well from gate 14, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, then crossed to the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Bumped start, raced prominently, nearer to the stand side, hard ridden from 350M, kept on well to take a place.
Began smartly, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden from 350M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on the middle track, no cover throughout, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the middle track, hard ridden from 250M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the middle track, made some progress after passing 400M, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced at rear near to the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Inconvenienced at start, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, weakened from 150M.

Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands rail, hard ridden from 350M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong. (Lame right front leg.)
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away with them, raced prominently on the middle track, could not maintain position from 500M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well to score.
Midfield, 2 wide, raced flat until 200M to make steady ground, just missed by narrow margin.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Eased to sit behind midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pressed forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground in straight.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
Midfield along the fence, ran on fairly.
At rear, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Failed to muster, at back on the rails, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed early, at back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 400M.
Eased back, suited by the fast pace, never nearer.
Ridden along to some distance to race in front of midfield on rail, quickened passing 300M, worked home strongly, scored by 4-3/4L.
Settled towards rear on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, gained nice late ground passing 200M.
Began only fairly, ridden along but only limited early speed, wide and without cover in early stages, near 600M improved to outside the lead, worked home nicely.
Jumped well then sent forward, raced outside the lead, improved to lead near 600M, asked for effort on straightening, finished well.
Raced behind midfield, improved passing 400M, made some ground in the straight.
Jumped sharply then taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 600M, wide on straightening, made up some late ground.
Settled midfield, tried to improve near 550M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 600M, one-paced in the straight.
Sent forward, raced in handy position, worked home one-paced.
Travelled behind midfield, placed pressure near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Raced midfield, placed pressure in the straight but only limited response.
At the start raced in restricted room then taken back, raced detached in the early stages, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, made the Home Turn awkwardly, near 300M was hampered, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged along to take lead passing 1000M, came under pressure passing 700M, faded out passing 600M, irregular heart rhythm.
Strode forward to assume lead after 200m. Travelled well into corner, kicked over a length clear on straightening before drawing away for very easy win.
Strode forward to challenge for lead but was caught 3 wide before easing behind leading trio. Continued 3 wide with cover in middle stages. Made good late ground to snare second in last 50m.
Improved after the start to race second outside the leader. Was over a length behind leader/winner entering the last section before battling away well to hold third on line. Well clear of forth.

Steadied after start & shifted back from wide gate to race worse than midfield. Raced a touch wide but with cover in middle stages. Moved wider on straightening before passing a few runners in late stages.
Ridden forward after start before steadying to race in midfield, three wide with cover. Maintained margin in final section but never looked a threat.
Had no speed after the start & shifted across to rail before improving after first furlong to race in midfield. Moved away from rail at the 400m but gave a further length in last section.
Not fast to begin & raced third last away from rail. Drifted back to last on cornering, 6.5L from lead before moving wider & finishing off fairly to midfield in final section.

Steadied after the start & drifted back from outside gate to settle at the tail. Was well back on the turn before staying on the rail in the straight & maintaining margin in dash home. Never likely from rear.

Crowded after start before improving slightly to race just worse than midfield between runners. Ridden along from the 500m before peaking on straightening & weakening a further few lengths in last section. Well held.

Ridden forward after start before being left three wide without cover outside leader. Continued wide path on the speed in middle stages. Peaked on run entering the last section & weakened out in last 250m after tough trip.

Slow to begin before steadying on the first bend & racing rearward. Raced ungenerously in middle stages before straightening the widest runner. Maintained margin in last section but was always well back. Well held.

Had no early speed & was ridden along early to hold worse than midfield position on rail. Moved away from the rail on straightening, held up & shifted out on multiple occasions in the straight before getting clear late. Never likely.

Strode forward before being crossed & getting good position between runners just behind the leading trio. Came under pressure on straightening, began weakening out passing the 300m before dropping out sharply in last 75m.
Had nice run on leaders back. Came under heavy riding passing the 500m mark before weakening out significantly to finish a long last.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, kept on very well to hold off the challenger.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 850M, moved closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Shifted out at start and made contact, taken back to race at rear on the inside, travelled keenly and shifted out 1050M, moved closer on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 100M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider from 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 1250M, led by half length, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position to turn, no clear running until final 100M, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 to 9 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, eased final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, weakened from 600M, eased thereafter. (Bled.)
Sent forward and sat inside the lead, about a neck off the lead, pulled away from 150M and won by 1/2L.
Ridden to take lead, led by about a neck, finished off well to the line and took 2nd.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 1L behind the lead, fought on gamely to the line, just took 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 2-1/2L behind on centre track, made ground and ran on okay to the line.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, 2-1/2L behind the leader, after 150M dashed slightly and kept on fairly to the line.
At rear, about 5L behind on centre track, pretty one paced.
At rear, about 8L behind the leader and along the outside rail initially, saved some ground at 250M but emptied at 150M.
Settled in about midfield, along the outside rail, flattened approaching 200M.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2L behind on centre track, emptied and headed at 150M.
Raced prominently behind the leaders, 1L off the leader, lost ground after 300M.
Began only fairly, at rear on centre track, did not threaten.
Bumped start, settled to race at rear, ridden prior to 400M but no progress.
Travelled in worse than midfield, 4L behind on centre track, not a factor.
Settled behind midfield, raced greenly and 7-1/2L off the leader, showed no turn of foot.
Settled in rear of midfield on the rail, baulked until the 300 metres, quickened well inside the final 250 metres to lead 100 metres out, just held on to the line.
Travelled keenly in midfield early stages, baulked for a run after straightening, finished off the race well to just fail to get up on line.
Slow to muster settling towards the rear in 10th on the rail, baulked until obtaining a run between runners 250 metres out, ran on well under pressure, did best work late.
Niggled along in first few, quickened early in straight to hit the front briefly over 200 metres out, swamped 100 metres out.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Never far off on the rail, travelled just over 2L back in 5th rounding home bend, angled out for a run upon straightening holding every chance over 200 metres out but hung in and a difficult ride.
Crowded at start, trailed the field to home bend, commenced move out wide 600 metres out, widest runner turning in, ran on quite well down the centre of the track.
Jumped awkwardly, shifted across to near the rail behind midfield, soon came to challenge after straightening, one-paced without quickening.
Soon took up running, ceded advantage for one-back position over 1000 metres out, awkwardly placed on heels early in straight, failed to make any impression inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start from a wide gate, improved steadily to reach 2nd about 1100 metres out, weakened under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide gate but soon dropped to forward of midfield in 6th and wide without cover, in similar position into straight, soon faded.
Broke well from the widest gate, took up running about 1100 metres out and obtained rails run shortly afterwards, led until swamped inside the final 250 metres.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, remained in last few and never a factor.
Chased leaders, pace fast in middle stages, kept on well on straightening, put in sustained effort to reel in the weakening leader near line.
Strode forward, led passing 1000M setting good pace to straight, still had 2Ls advantage 150M, no extra late and caught near line.
Went forward, chased leader in 2nd, not pace to challenge in the straight , held ground final 200M, hung on for 3rd just.
Began only fairly, towards the rear 7Ls back, urged 400M, did best work final 250M, just missed 3rd.
Crowded for room at start, settled down behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, ran on without threat in the straight.
Caught 3-wide behind mid-division, ran on only fairly in straight, never troubled leaders.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover, held up in last 9Ls off the good pace in middle stages, stayed on past beaten horses in straight, never a serious threat.
Niggled along to maintain a midfield spot along the fence, found little when asked turning in, kept on same pace.
Never far off from leaders, 4th turning for home, held ground early straight, run ended 200M, weakened towards the finish.
Held up midfield along 3-path, wide no cover from 900M, kept on same pace in straight, faded 250M.
Positioned just ahead of midfield, 5Ls to make up on clear leader 400M, battled on same pace to 200M, soon no extra.

Fractious in stall, hit its head on jumping and very slowly away, towards the rear always, didn't finish off in the straight. (Jockey : did not travel comfortably at any stage after missing the start.)
Dropped back to race near the rear, made the turn near 900M awkwardly, couldn't go on turning home, soon left behind.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, kept on well after turning in, finished 3rd.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 150M, made some headway thereafter to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 wide with cover at rear, 3 wide on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, positioned 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off one pace.
Began well, raced very wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 4 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, weakened on turn, emptied early in straight.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.

Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back to race 3 wide with cover in midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, not enough room after passing 200M, cleared 50M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 300M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide at rear, carried wider from 800M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, challenged turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover after passing 600M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to score in good fashion.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, checked near 750M, commenced move after passing 400M, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began smartly, raced prominently on rail, got cover from 500M, a length behind the leader on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 450M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 500M, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress early in straight, not enough room near 100M, bumped 50M, steadied off heels close home.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned 2 to 3 lengths on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out 350M, showed limited response early in straight, bumped near 50M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, made contact and unbalanced near 750M, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened from 100M, bumped 50M.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, carried wider from 450M, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Pushed to occupy box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to take rail, settled in front of midfield, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to obtain a spot in front of midfield, 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Behind midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, lack room most straight, made good ground.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
At back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Midfield along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals as usual, out of fuel 250M.
Eased at start, took rail and cover, benefited by the fast pace, never improved.
Raced behind midfield on rail, improved passing 400M, quickened passing near 100M to score.
Settled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, commenced to improve near 500M, responded solidly in the straight.
Taken back at start, asked for effort near 350M, widest on straightening, made up good late ground, finished nicely.
Raced at rear, wide on straightening, responded nicely in the straight.
Pushed along to race midfield on rail, made the Home Turn awkwardly, made some late ground in the straight.
Settled behind leaders, placed pressure passing 400M, passing 250M was steadied when disappointed for running, finished one-paced.
Crowded on jumping, near 1050M was steadied when crowded for room, settled behind midfield, after 600M lost ground when again crowded, limited response in the straight.
Urged to take lead, rider dropped whip passing 200M, placed pressure but weakened near 150M.
Began awkwardly then sent forward, wide and without cover in handy position, gave ground near 200M.
Ridden along to race in box seat, placed pressure near 500M, weakened near 100M.
Taken back at start, held up from near 200M until near 100M, steadied when crowded after 100M, not fully tested.
Jumped well, sent forward to race outside the lead, tried to improve but gave ground in the straight.

Raced worse than midfield between runners. Travelled strongly entering last section before shifting wider on straightening. Improved between runners to strike lead at the 100m before holding challenger late.

Steadied & shifted to midfield but raced wide with cover throughout middle stages. Moved 4 wide & improved position passing the 400m before cornering the widest runner. Closed off strongly in last 300m to be narrowly beaten.

Failed to muster early speed before steadying back to tail. Continued near the rear on straightening, held up for clear running from straightening until the 125m before finishing strongly to close to third in late stages.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout early & middle stages. Shifted in on straightening, sprinted between runners to strike lead at the 175m before shifting around noticeably in late stages. Not beaten far.

Not ridden forward before drifting back to last after the first section. Continued at the tail on cornering before shifting the widest runner in the straight & making good late ground to midfield. (Rider questioned).

Strode to midfield after start before shifting across but caught three wide without cover. Ridden along from the 500m to improve into race but could only maintain position in the straight after wide passage throughout.

Began awkwardly, shifted to last early before racing third last on rail in middle stages. Had only two runners behind on cornering before making up two lengths when finishing off fairly well between runners in concluding stages.
Raced in midfield on the rail throughout. Was three lengths form lead entering last section, stayed hard on inside rail in straight but could only maintaining margin in dash to line. No threat.

Pushed forward after the start before racing in third away from rail with cover throughout. Eased three wide passing the 550m before peaking on effort inside the last furlong & yielding a few lengths thereafter.
Enjoyed good run on leaders back throughout early & middle stages. Stayed close to the inside on cornering, shared the lead momentarily near the 200m before weakening out thereafter. Well held.
Showed customary early speed to stride forward and race outside the lead. Peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakened out in final 200m to be well beaten.
Began well & strode to unchallenged lead. Headed in the lead soon after straightening & weakened out quickly in final furlong. Last.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 2 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to score by a neck.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail near 600M, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a neck.
Commenced well, raced prominently on the inside early, 2 wide from 700M, a length or so back on turn, closed off well to take a place.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first few late.
Bumped start, raced 3 to 4 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6-1/2L back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.

Began smartly from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, took the lead 900M, found rail near 750M, led by half length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, moved closer after passing 700M, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, 2 wide, headed near 900M, positioned 3 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 to 4 wide with cover behind midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, made no progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly and closed heels near 650M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Sent forward, in one-off one-back prior to the 600M turn, stepped up at 200M and caught leader, scored by 1L.
Taken back, 2 wide, swung outside on straightening, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Midfield, along the rail, closed off strongly and continued well for 3rd.
Sent forward, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on strongly.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, badly hampered at 600M, saved some ground closed off fairly.
Midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly to the line.
Severely checked at start, taken back, along the rail, saved ground but emptied after 100M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, showed no response.
Sent forward, along the rail after 500M, lost ground after 150M. (See Incident Report)
Rolled forward, along the rail after 1000M, checked at 600M and lost ground, soon weakened after straightening.
Taken back, 3 wide, never a danger. (See Incident Report)
Crowded start, at rear, 2 wide, made no threats.
Tracked leader on the rail, quickened well under pressure inside the final 200 metres to take charge, kept on well.

Settled in midfield, drifted slightly backward near the Rock, awkwardly placed and lost position over 450 metres out, swung wide into the straight, finished off the race strongly down the centre of the track.
Settled in midfield in 6th on the rail, saved ground on the inside turning for home, quickened to reach 2nd briefly over 150 metres out.
Missed the start, soon recovered towards the rear of the field, commenced move on the outside rounding home bend, one of the widest turning in, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled at the back from the widest gate, came under pressure on the rail rounding home bend and saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

Pressed forward from a wide gate travelling wide without cover in prominent position, improved to dispute lead at the 800 metres, unable to sustain effort and faded under pressure shortly after straightening.
Crowded at start from a wide gate, settled just worse than midfield near the rail, saved ground on the inside turning in, forced to switch for a run over 200 metres out, ran home one-paced. (Lame)
Settled well behind, came under pressure rounding home bend, swung very wide into home straight, went past well-beaten horses.
Well there early settling in 5th just over 3L back, became 6th coming onto home bend, unable to quicken under pressure.
Jumped best and made running to the straight, weakened under pressure inside the final 300 metres.

Improved steadily from a wide gate to chase behind the leader travelling not far off in 4th in back straight, in similar position turning for home, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres. (Jockey reported horse immature)
Soon led, travelled strongly into the straight, kicked well clear 200M, had enough to hold off late challenge from 2nd and 3rd.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled last 6Ls off the pace, ran on well final 300M, nearest finish.
Began awkwardly, reserved in midfield along the fence, chased hard on the runaway leader in straight, nearest finish.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, driven out top of straight, stayed on moderately for 4th, not reached top 3.
Jumped fairly, held up near the rear 5Ls off the good pace, saved ground on inside, kept on steadily on straightening without threatening winner.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, towards the rear always, stayed on fairly in straight and not pace to challenge leaders.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, had his chance, faded final 150M.
From draw 1 stayed close to leader, held 2nd to 200M, no extra and weakened.
Settled behind mid-division, travelled only fairly, brought wide into straight, couldn't finish off. (Jockey : appeared to lose confidence when unbalanced 1000M.)

Didn't show sufficient speed from wide draw, unable to race prominently as intended, caught 3-wide midfield then weakened in the straight. (Jockey : did not appreciate being ridden off the speed and not able to finish off.)
Chased the pace, 3-wide no cover during race, gave ground nearing 400M, soon beaten and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Pressed along to chase the pace but caught 4-wide no cover throughout, gave ground home turn, weakened rapidly to finish distant last. (Unacceptable Performance / Lame next day.)
