Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight and scored.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly.
Away well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, made contact and carried wider near 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Made contact start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress after passing 150M, blocked close home.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide turning, finished off one pace.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (Lame left front leg.)
Jumped well from gate 9, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Missed the start, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 3 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 300, became unbalanced 150M.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace, trapped 4 wide, pace good, held ground in straight.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, pace good, made minor ground 200M.
At back, 2 wide, pace good, ran on fairly.
Slow away, at rear, along the fence, pace good, no progress.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, pace good, soon emptied 400M.
Never better than midfield.
Pressed forward, dropped off rapidly 50M.
Taken back at start, raced last, widest on straightening, quickened passing 200M, responded strongly to score.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, improved passing 500m, responded strongly in the straight, missed by SH.
Moderate start, urged for some distance to take lead, fought well in the straight, beaten by 3/4L.
On jumping was checked when crowded for room, settled behind midfield, asked for effort on straightening, worked home solidly.
Jumped well with nicely early speed, steadied to race in front of midfield, battled nicely in the straight.
Ridden to race in box seat, asked for effort near 400M, worked home well.
Began only fairly, raced midfield on rail, made some late ground in the straight.
Settled midfield, after 900M was left racing wide and without cover, one-paced in the straight.
Settled in handy position, placed pressure passing 500M, gave ground near 100M.
Settled at rear on rail, placed pressure near 400M, finished one-paced.
On jumping was bumped and became badly unbalanced, settled midfield, limited response when placed under pressure.
Settled towards rear, wide on straightening, placed pressure but limited response in the straight.
Jumped nicely, raced outside the lead with nice early speed, gave ground passing 200M, near 100M was checked and lost running.
On jumping was bumped and lost ground, settled behind midfield on rail, faded out in the straight.
Strode forward before being crossed, racing on leaders back from the 900m. Moved wider in straight, sprinted up in a line of 4 at the 100m before proving too tough in closing stages.
Last into stride before racing at the tail. Moved the widest runner on straightening before making solid headway to snare second in closing stages. Good from rear against sit/sprint shape.

Began well before steadying to get nice position in forth away from rail. Ridden along from on straightening before digging deep to join a line of four at the 100m & box on bravely in late stages. Narrowly beaten.

Strode forward to race second, improved to outside the leader from the 600m. Dashed to narrow lead at the 300m, joined in a line of 4 at the 100m before headed late. Finished on same line as place-getters.
Not the fastest to begin, settled on the rail with two runners behind. Shifted outwards at the 400m, moved up within a neck at the 150m before peaking late. Close behind.
Raced second from last on rail, eased away from rail passing the 850m. Eased wider on straightening before finishing off nicely against race shape, not be beaten far despite beating only one home.
Pushed forward, crossed to rail when leading at the 900m. Steadied speed in middle section. Headed in the lead near the 300m before yielding a length or two late. Not beaten far in last place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, angled out 550M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the rival late.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, kept on well in straight to make frame without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 10, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, kept on well to 50M, one paced thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Missed the start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 950M, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out near 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Away with them, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Refused to race, took no part.
Travelled in worse than midfield, along the rail, closed off strongly to score.
Settled one-off one-back, make the turn awkwardly at 900M, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Bumped start and sent forward, along the rail, ran on gamely for 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground after 150M to finish.
Raced in midfield initially, rolled forward after 850M, 3 wide without cover, closed off the race fairly. (See Incident Report)
Rolled forward, along the rail, ran on fairly but weakened after 100M.
On jumping was crowded, taken back, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Slow to begin, taken back, along the rail, found no extra for final 150M.
Travelled in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Bumped start, in front of midfield, along the rail, did not improve.
At rear, remained 2 wide, showed nothing.
Taken back, 2 wide, 3 wide after 650M, saved no ground.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the straight.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, soon beaten turning in, never involved. (Unacceptable Performance)
Settled wide in rear of midfield, 4-wide into home straight, quickened well inside final 300 metres to take command close to home.
Pressed forward from a wide gate to lead crossing to the rail 800 metres out, went nearly 2L clear early in straight, tiring when outsprinted by winner and nearly caught for 2nd closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate sharing early pace, settled one back in 2nd 5-wide allowing race leader to cross for rails run, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Moderate start from a wide gate, soon dropped to last few, 3-wide rounding home bend and into home straight, ran on quite well without threatening.
Travelled mainly 3-wide in midfield despite ridden early, made headway rounding home bend to reach 4th just over 2L off the pace, kept on without quickening under pressure after straightening.
Ridden from the start but soon dropped to rear of midfield wide without cover, improved rounding home bend to join the leaders briefly over 450 metres out, soon found no extra.
Taken back to last from the widest gate but remained 4 wide throughout, kept on well to the line. (Jockey warned for insufficient vigour in home straight)
Settled just worse than midfield, inconvenienced and dropped to last few coming onto home bend, last when given reminders on straightening, ran past well-beaten horses.
Stumbled at start, quickly settled in midfield on the rail, drifted steadily backward rounding home bend, towards rear into home straight, made no further impression.

Soon dropped to last few despite niggling along, carried backward to the last coming onto home bend, trailed the field into home straight and awkwardly placed behind runner 250 metres out, made no further impression.
Jumped fairly niggling along in 3rd just over 2L off the pace, drifted steadily backward along the rail rounding home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Soon recovered from a moderate start to 6th in midfield, similar into home straight, folded up quickly. (Bled) (Lame next day)
Obtained a midfield spot along the 2-path, waited with until 400M, hit the line strongly to reel in leader 50M from home. (Jockey suspended for improper use of whip.)
From wide draw steadied nearing 1500M to find cover, settled down 6Ls off the pace near rear, brought widest home, ran on well to claim 2nd near line.
Never far off from leaders, caught wide no cover after 1000M, moved up to lead 400M, opened up good margin mid-straight, run ended near 100M, caught by first 2 late.
From middle draw ended up 4-wide without cover in midfield, chased hard on straightening, kept on final 200M.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, in last place until making early move 700M, 5-wide home turn, stayed on moderately to the line.
Chased leaders 2-wide, shifted out 550M, kept on one paced to line, always held by leaders.
Dropped back from wide draw, held up near last 6Ls away, switched wider 600M, closed off steadily without threatening leaders.
Bumped by rival at the start, reserved behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, kept on fairly, never going the pace to challenge.
Settled down midfield along the fence, held up for clear running early straight, kept on without threatening when clear.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, went for gap on inside in straight but got severely checked 350M, stayed on mildly to the line thereafter, not reached leaders.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, outsprinted passing 300M, never a threat.
Went for the lead, steadied the tempo nearing home turn, soon headed entering straight, faded away to be beaten over 10L.
Pushed along to obtain a trailing position behind leaders, hampered 350M, struggled home.
Went forward as expected, settled outside leader, gave ground turning in, weakened rapidly. (Bled.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, wider on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.

Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, found daylight after passing 150M, made very good progress thereafter to take a place.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked near 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently, 3 wide, took the lead 1000M, 2 wide turning, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on well to 100M, headed and weakened thereafter.
Began smartly, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1000M, 3/4L back on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 150M, bumped 75M, ran on evenly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, not enough room 150M, bumped 75M, ran on evenly to the line.
Took keen hold, raced 2 wide in midfield, closer turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, only passed a few tired runners in straight.

Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, travelled keenly in the early stages, wider after passing 800M, 4 wide turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, moved closer after passing 950M, very wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off strongly to score by a head.

Made contact at start, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader in the middle track, made good progress final 400M to take a place.
Jumped well, raced at rear in the middle track, 5-1/2Ls back at 400M, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began smartly from gate 14, sent forward to take the lead on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the outside, only showed limited response final 400M, never able to challenge. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced at rear on the stands' side, made some headway final 400M.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M.
Began well, positioned behind midfield in the middle of the track, hard ridden 350M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned behind midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, kept on evenly final 400M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden 300M, showed limited response, weakened final 150M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length or so back, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 250M.
Commenced well, raced a length behind the leader in the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.

Strode forward, raced on leaders back near the 850m before shifting away from rail soon after. Dashed to lead shortly after straightening, raced 2L clear by the furlong mark before holding challenger late.

Couldn't go early speed & soon drifted back to worse than midfield. Raced wide without cover in middle stages before straightening the widest runner, 4L from lead. Finished strongly in concluding stages to be narrowly beaten.
Raced in midfield on the rail, stayed close to the inside on straightening before closing off strongly in final 300m to be beaten only 1 length. Solid again.

Raced in midfield away from the rail in the early & middle stages. Shifted wider on straightening, entered the last section over 3 lengths from lead, before making up a few lengths in sprint home. Not far behind.

Shifted back behind runners after start to race a clear last. Was a clear last on straightening, nearly 7L from the lead, shifted the widest runner before making solid late headway from a poor position to be close behind.

Steadied after the start & drifted back to second last in early stages. Moved wider on the track passing the 600m before making up a length or so when passing a few tiring runners in the last section.

Ridden forward after the start before being crossed and racing third, away from rail without cover. Forced three wide outside leaders passing the 800m. Peaked on effort passing the 300m before giving a length or two thereafter.
Strode forward to lead, crossed to rail near the 850m. Headed by winner soon after straightening before giving a few lengths thereafter.
Strode forward after start to race just behind leaders before racing ungenerously. Checked & lost ground near 800m before entering last section 2L from lead. Weakened out in final 300m.

Fractious at start & began only fairly, consequently racing in midfield early, before improving to leaders back by the 700m. Emptied out shortly after straightening & weakened out poorly in the final 300m.
Restrained after the start & taken back towards the rail & settling worse than midfield. Continued rearward on straightening before weakening out meekly in the last section. Well beaten.

Bumped at start before steadying back to race in a rearward position. Came under hard ridding passing the 500m when second from last before yielding further ground in the straight to finish long last.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.

Jumped well from gate 9, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 1200M, 2Ls back in the middle stages, commenced move after passing 450M, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader, easy run to turn, angled out 350M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail in the middle stages, made some progress in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, 2 wide from 450M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, recovered, took the lead 1200M, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out from 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still 7-1/2Ls back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 1000M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, drifted away 300M to score
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden to secure the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
At back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden early to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
At back, along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 250M, on heels 50M.
Eased at start, at rear 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 600M, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, on heels 700M, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Settled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort near 500M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Improved to outside the lead near 1000M after being left wide and without cover, commenced to improve near 500M, worked home solidly.
Travelled midfield, improved near 600M, ran well in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, improved passing 700M, made up some ground in the straight.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, passing 400M was checked, finished well.
Ridden along but no early speed, settled towards rear on rail, placed pressure near 500M, made up some late ground in the straight.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort near 300M, finished one-paced.
Niggled to race midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 500M, one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, improved near 600M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Crowded at the start then taken back, settled in last, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden along to take lead, came under pressure near 500M, no response in the straight.
Raced in midfield on rail. Came under hard riding passing the 450m before shifting into clear running after straightening & making continual steady ground to strike lead in final few strides.

Steadied after start & raced second last away from rail. Hard ridden from the 400m, moved the widest runner on straightening before closing off strongly in final furlong to charge to second in closing stages.
Had no speed & raced a clear last throughout, shifted the widest runner at 250m when still a clear last before flying home in last furlong to snare a narrowly beaten third.

Not fast to begin, ridden hard to improve after start to race third before getting cover when 4th passing the 800m. Moved up to share the lead at the 150m before being swamped late. Held fourth beaten small margin.
Enjoyed good run in midfield away from rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved closer on straightening before making up steady ground in last furlong to finish just behind.
Bumped at start before steadied back to worse than midfield on rail. Continued near the rear after straightening before making late ground between runners to finish close behind.

Raced wide at first corner before improving to race outside the leader approaching the 800m. Assumed the lead on cornering & continued to hold lead until being joined at the 150m before yielding a length or two late. Ok.

Not bustled after the start, raced ungenerously at first bend before racing in midfield. Continued keen passing the 700m. Entered the last section 5 lengths from lead before making up a few lengths but never threatening.
Fastest to begin & held early lead before being headed & racing on leaders back from the 900m. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before peaking at the furlong & not threatening thereafter.
Shifted across & raced worse than midfield early before improving to midfield at half-way. Continued to race wide & improve position nearing the home corner before weakening out in the straight.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved away from rail on straightening but peaked on effort soon after & offered little in the last furlong. Well held.
Showed early speed and worked to lead after the first corner. Peaked & headed soon after straightening before weakening out badly in the straight to finish long last.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, bumped and unbalanced near 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers, won by half length.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, bumped and carried wider near 550M, very wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide from near 600M, commenced move after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Jumped well from gate 9, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, found rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, bumped and angled out near 550M, moved closer on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out in straight and made some progress.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, bumped near 900M, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, lay out at 200M but hold on to score by 1L.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, continued on strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, made some ground and ran on reasonably.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, saved ground and ran on nicely.
Bumped start, along the rail, ran on fairly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced in behind midfield, along the rail, found no extra for final 100M.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide initially, 3 wide without cover after 450M, did not make ground in the straight.
Taken back, at rear wide but with cover, was one paced.
Eased back, along the rail, made some ground in the straight.
Sent forward to take rail and led, lost ground in the straight.
Sent forward, settled to race outside the lead, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, sent forward, lost ground after 450M, never a factor. (Unacceptable Performance)
Settled within 3L of the pace in 5th on the rail, switched out for a run entering home straight, responded well under pressure inside the final 200 metres to assert authority final strides.
Ridden along from the widest gate, with leaders 3-wide without cover down the back straight, hit the front under pressure on top of home bend only to be outsprinted close to home.
Settled on the rail in 7th in rear of midfield, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear of midfield after moderate start, in similar position into home straight, produced strong late finish under pressure inside the final 200 metres.

Began well with others sharing early pace on the rail, allowed race leader to cross at the Rock for one-back 3rd, angled out for a run into home straight, unable to sustain effort in a tight run closing stages.
Crowded shortly after start losing ground, switched wide for a run into home straight, finished off the race strongly inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled keenly in 4th within 2L of the pace, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, faded steadily under pressure soon after straightening.
Broke well to share early pace, soon taken 2 back to 5th and then some 3L back in 6th in back straight, went wide turning for home, one-paced.
Tightened at start losing ground, remained in last few in 9th, made steady headway under pressure from rounding home bend, never nearer.
Crowded shortly after start and checked dropping to last, trailed the field most of the way, never on terms.
Began from a wide gate, gained slender lead 2-wide outside the 2nd turning into back straight, obtained rails run inside the 700 metres, headed entering home straight and weakened under pressure.
Crossed to the fence 1500M tracking leaders, moved up on inside to challenge in straight, fought hard and gained narrow lead 100M, dug deep to hold on.
Reserved behind midfield, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, challenged strongly final 200M, just held.
Chased leaders 2-wide, in touch turning, fought on well to the line for close 3rd. (Jockey : disadvantaged when saddle shifted back rounding Home Turn.)
Went forward as expected, led along rails from 1500M, drifted out from fence on straightening, kept battling for the lead, faded final 100M.
Not hurried, settled towards the rear along fence, badly held up 200M to 100M and no clear run again near finish, not fully tested.
Taken back to the rear from wide draw, over 10Ls off the pace middle stages, urged along 450M, widest into straight, stayed on moderately down outside.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, ended up towards the rear, ran home fairly over final 300M, well held by leaders.
Settled down midfield along the fence, made mild progress on straightening, had to switch lane near 150M, not pace to challenge leaders final stages.
In mid-division, raced keenly passing 1000M, swung wide into straight, kept on evenly, outsprinted final 150M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled last over 10Ls off the pace, responded fairly on straightening, never near to challenge.
Held up behind midfield, wide no cover from 700M, wide into straight, lacked further response passing 250M.
Chased leader in clear 2nd, outsprinted passing 300M, soon dropped out of contention.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, briefly headed early in straight, hard ridden after passing 300M, retook the lead near 150M, kept on well to the line, scored by a narrow margin.

Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, bumped near 900M, same position on turn, took the lead early in straight, hard ridden after passing 250M, peaked and headed near 150M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Away well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, travelled keenly near 800M, 3 wide on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.

Made contact at start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from near 800M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight 250M, finished off well without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned right behind the leader on rail, bumped near 900M, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.

Crowded out start, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked on run near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, commenced move from 600M, very wide into straight, showed some response early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 800M, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 900M, 4 wide with no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight. (Bled.) (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow tempo, overhauled 150M, ran on for 2nd.
Slow away, midfield 2 wide, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Eased at start, raced 3-5 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, at back along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, little dash.
Hard ridden early, at back 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, suited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At start was bumped and badly unbalanced, niggled along to race inside the lead, quickened passing 200M to score.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 500M, worked home solidly.
Fractious in barrier and slow out, raced at rear, gained nice late ground passing 150M, stalls test.
Began awkwardly then ridden along to take lead, raced greenly, finished well.
Settled midfield in the middle of track, asked for effort passing 500M, worked home well.
Raced behind the speed on outside rail, asked for effort near 400M, awkwardly placed over concluding stages, not fully tested.
Settled in handy position, always niggled, finished one-paced.
Badly crowded at start, niggled to race in forward position, gave ground near 100M.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 400M, limited response.
Raced at rear, limited response when placed pressure.
Raced in handy position, placed pressure but gave ground passing 200M.
Raced at back in the middle of track, no response when asked.
Fractious in barrier, raced behind midfield, weakened near 400M, stalls test.

Good run on the rail, 3.5L from lead at the 800m. Moved away from rail on straightening, moved closer at the 300m before engaging in two horse battle in last furlong. Got nose down on line to win by narrowest margin.
Good run on leaders back on rail throughout. Eased wider to make line of 3 on straightening, dashed to lead soon after, held narrow lead from the 300m until being nosed out right on wire.

Checked after the start, consequently lost ground before improving soon after to race in midfield. Moved wider on straightening, over 3L from lead entering last section before making strong late headway for closing third.

Raced in midfield on rail in middle stages, 5L form lead passing the 800m. Shifted out shortly after straightening, before getting clear running passing the 300m. Closed off steadily in the last 250m to be not far behind.
Began awkwardly before being steadied back to a clear second last. Cornered with only one behind, before making up continual late ground to be beaten only 1.5L after racing near the rear throughout.

Ridden forward after start, shared lead in first furlong. Continued to be pressured on outside by joint leader in middle stages. Joined & headed after straightening before battling on ok late. Not beaten too far.

Raced in midfield away from rail throughout. Just over a length from the lead entering the last section, continued to not be far behind until peaking inside the last furlong & yielding a few lengths late.

Ridden hard but could only manage to race in midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Eased wider nearing corner before straightening the widest. Shifted towards outside rail in straight when making some headway to midfield.
Settled worse than midfield on rail. Continued in the second half entering the last section when 4L form the lead, before maintaining margin in the straight without threatening.

Began well but was steadied after the start to race in midfield away from rail. Raced 5L form lead at the 800m before moving closer to the lead on straightening. Peaked at the 150m & tired out sharply in last 100m.
Showed no early speed & raced with only two behind in early & middle stages. Ridden along approaching the corner before making no headway in the straight. Well held.

Strode forward to share lead, racing away from rail. Continued to apply pressure in middle stages when joint leader. Peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakened after doing too much in middle stages.
Slow away, shifted back to last before weakening out sharply from half-way. (Must trial – poor performance).
Raced wide without cover in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Began yielding ground approaching the corner before weakening out significantly in straight. (Must trial – poor performance).
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well in straight to hold off the rivals, scored by a neck.
Commenced well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very well, just always held by the winner.
Fast into stride, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 500M, 5 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.

Moderately away, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1250M, positioned 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back in the middle stages, peaked turning in, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 600M, very wide turning in, failed to quicken in straight.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced very wide with no cover, slightly behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, weakened early in straight.
Took the lead, along the rail, battled on to the line to score.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, kept on to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made some ground and ran on reasonably.
At rear, 2 wide, raced tight at 350M, saved ground and battled on to the line.
Crowded on jumping, 2 wide, closed off nicely to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, couldn't be ridden out over the concluding stages.
Raced in midfield initially, taken back after 850M, swung widest on straightening, ran on fairly to the line.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, was one paced.
Taken back, at rear, along the rail, no clear run until 50M and not fully tested.
Raced in behind midfield, wide but with cover, did not feature.
Taken back and at rear, along the rail, swung wide on straightening, did not feature.
Midfield initially, taken back after 950M, lost ground after 450M, not competitive in the straight.
Raced in midfield initially, along the rail after 800M, weakened and headed at 150M. (Lame Right Front)
Rolled forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, in the straight finished tailed out. (See Incident Report and Blood in trachea)
Began well, settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, quickened well to gain upper hand over 100 metres out.
Soon taken back to midfield in 7th, came under pressure after straightening, fought on well to snatch 2nd late.
Ridden from a wide gate to take up running on the rail rounding the first bend, led and keenly at times in back straight, found no extra over 100 metres out and lost 2nd final strides.
Recovered from a moderate start to settle in 4th within 3L of the pace, held the same into home straight, made moderate progress without threatening.
In midfield on the rail travelling keenly at times in back straight, made up good ground under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden positively from a wide gate travelling wide around first bend, remained wide without cover in forward of midfield in back straight, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Soon taken well behind, finished off the race strongly inside the final 200 metres.

Began well from a wide gate, pressed forward around the first bend before settling one back in 2nd in back straight, found nothing under pressure after straightening. (Irregular heart rhythm) (Lame next day)
Travelled in worse than midfield, made modest progress without threatening.
Settled in last few to home straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track, never nearer.

Soon crossed for rails run in worse than midfield, in similar position turning for home, looked improving when steadied from heels 200 metres out, made no further impression. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began well from the widest gate, soon taken back to rear of midfield but wide without cover, lost position into home straight, one-paced in the run to the line.
Soon taken back to last from a wide gate, trailed the field most of the way, never a danger.
Settled in better than midfield in 5th on the rail within 4L of the pace, held similar position to home straight, soon weakened under pressure.
Settled in midfield 2-wide, ran on strongly from 300M, prevailed in a blanket finish.

Steadied early stages to obtain cover, held up in rear pair 6-7Ls off the pace, improved along inside on straightening, unable to obtain clear running until 200M, closed off nicely when clear, got up for 2nd in a blanket finish.
Crossed to the lead 1350M, led slowly before quickening up 600M, kept on well in the straight, caught by first 2 near line.
Reserved in midfield along the inside, switched out 500M, ran on well final 350M, narrowly missed 3rd spot.
Began fairly, settled towards the rear 4-5Ls back, brought wide for clear run in straight, finished off well to be nearest at the line, lost out in a blanket finish for minor placings.
Held up towards the rear, 4Ls away from leader 400M, brought widest into straight, closed off well for close 6th beaten 1 length
In touch behind leaders, responded well turning in and loomed up mid-straight to challenge leader, peaked on its run 100M, swamped by rivals late stages.
Moved up to race outside leader, taken keen hold, held ground early straight, faded passing 200M. (Jockey : raced too keenly in the middle stages, didn't finish off under top weight.)
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, held up in rear pair just over 6Ls off the pace, kept on moderately final 400M, always held by leaders.
Tracked leaders, unable to keep up passing 300M, out of contention mid-straight. (Jockey dropped whip 150M.)
From draw 9 raced wide no cover after 1400M, travelled keenly and improved to race outside the lead middle stages, gave ground badly in the straight after tough run, eased.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled well to turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to score on his debut.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd despite being bumped near 250M and 150M, just beaten by a neck.
Away well, positioned 2 wide slightly behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 500M, closed off well to make frame.

Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed to cross near 900M, a length or so back in the middle stages, carried wider 550M, hit the front early in straight, kept on well to 100M, headed and weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, not able to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M, made minor progress thereafter.

Jumped well from gate 1, raced prominently on rail, crossed near 850M, a length back in the middle stages, 2 wide from 550M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, improved along the rail on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.

Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, took the lead after passing 1000M, found rail 850M, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened from 200M.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Shifted out abruptly on jumping, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, peaked 300M, ran on evenly to the line.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, found a 2 wide spot near 950M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out on jumping and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off one pace.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, finished off one pace. (See Racing Incidents.)

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back, found rail 600M, moved a bit closer along the rail turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, travelled keenly 1000M, 3 wide with no cover in the middle stages, carried wider turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.

Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move after passing 800M, took the lead near 400M, kept on very well after turning in, scored by a neck.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 wide on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from near 800M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, headed after entering the back straight, a length or so back on turn, kept on well until blocked final 25M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after entering the back straight, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, moved closer after entering the back straight, 4 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, taken back to race at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 700M, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back in the middle stages, hard ridden from 600M, very wide on turn, one paced in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, made contact near 1100M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped on jumping, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, sent forward from 1100M, took the lead after entering the back straight, headed 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back at 800M, weakened from 600M.
Began well, sat 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, lost position from 900M, 8 lengths back on turn, finished last.
Eased to obtain box seat, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 300M.
Eased back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Slow away, benefited by the fast tempo, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, soon emptied 500M.
Jumped nicely, ridden along to take lead, responded solidly in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Hard ridden to race outside the lead, asked for effort near 300M, worked home solidly.
Raced in front of midfield, placed pressure near 300M, fought well in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, made up some late ground in the straight.
Began only fairly then ridden along to race in box seat, gave ground near 50M.
Settled in handy position, placed pressure but worked home only one-paced.
Jumped sharply, raced midfield, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight, lame right front next day.
Soon after start clipped heels, blundered badly and lost ground, settled at rear on rail, made some ground in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, placed pressure on straightening, awkwardly placed over concluding stages and not fully tested.
Raced wide and without cover throughout in handy position, 4 wide rounding the Home Turn, at entrance to the straight bumped with a runner and became badly unbalanced, weakened passing 100M.
Urged along then raced wide and without cover throughout outside the leaders, weakened near 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, came under pressure near 400M, faded out in the straight.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Travelled strongly entering last section, moved away from rail on cornering, dashed to lead inside final 100m & drew away strongly late.

Hard ridden after start, battled for early lead before assuming lead near 1100m (very fast early sections). Raced 2L clear on straightening, maintained lead until swamped at 100m. Held second, big effort. (Rider questioned).
Raced in midfield away from rail throughout. Moved three wide nearing bend when 4L from lead before finishing off well to run into third in final 100m. Not beaten far.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Stayed close to the rail on cornering before passing a couple to run into a non-threatening forth.

Raced wide passing winning post first time before settling one away from rail from 1200m. Continued 10L from lead at half-way before field compressed, 5L from lead at 400m. Passed a couple in straight without threatening.

Steadied & shifted back to worse than midfield after the start. Raced over 10L from lead passing half-way. Ridden along from 450m to improve, cornered the widest runner, finished off soundly from rearward position.
Had a nice run in third on rail throughout. 2L behind leader on straightening but could offer no more in the final furlong & weakened out late. (Mucus in trachea post-race).
Strode forward before getting good position in 4th behind fast early speed. Came under hard riding passing the 500m, raced tight on cornering before weakening out in the final 250m.
Steadied back after the start & raced with only one behind throughout early & middle stages. Moved wider passing the 500m but failed to make any headway in the last section & was well held.

Had no speed after the start, improved slightly to race worse than midfield passing the 1200m. Continued on the inside rail entering last section when over 6L from lead, before weakening out further in straight. Well beaten.

Strode forward to share early lead, very fast early sections, before being headed & racing behind leader from passing the 1000m. Hard ridden before cornering & weakened out after doing too much in early stages.
Had no early speed & raced a clear last throughout. Continued a long last at half-way before weakening out significantly in the straight. Beaten a long way.
Began only fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, led by 3/4L at 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, headed 50M, lost 2nd on line.
Began very awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made very god progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 7, raced 4 lengths back on rail, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 3 wide, a length or so back early, sent forward after entering the back straight, 2 wide from 700M, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, carried wider after passing 400M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position in the middle stages, very wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (Bled.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently but trapped very wide, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Settled to race in the box-seat, closed off nicely to the line and score by 3/4L.
Sent forward and settled to race outside the lead at 1200M, worked home well to take 2nd.
Settled in one-off one-back position, made ground and ran on reasonably.
Eased to be in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest on straightening, saved some ground and continued on to the line.
At rear, along the rail, made ground and ran on fairly to the line.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide without cover, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
Stayed in midfield, along the rail, did not make ground in the straight.
Sent forward, along the rail, was one paced. (See Incident Report)
Eased back, along the rail, stayed on until emptied passing 100M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, not competitive in the straight.
Reared at start and lost ground, taken back, never a factor.
Settled in midfield near the rail after a moderate start, commenced move rounding home bend and switched wide for a run into the straight, ran on under pressure to hit the front 100 metres out.

Ridden to hold forward of midfield position in 6th on the rail, remain similar until shifted out for a run entering home straight, switched back in for a run over 250 metres out, made steady headway without threatening.
Began well before taken some 2L back to 3rd on the rail, in similar position turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well to lead, made running until narrowly headed on straightening, swamped for a placing inside the final 100 metres.
Ridden forward from the widest gate settling one back 2-wide, commenced move approaching the home turn hitting the front briefly after straightening, soon found no extra.
Settled well back from a wide gate, snuck up on the rail rounding home turn, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled just worse than midfield early, gradually drifted towards the rear of the field, produced some late impression early in home straight. (Tactic questioned)
Broke well from a middle gate before shifting back to 3-wide without cover in 5th or 4th about 2L off the pace, faded after straightening.
Settled well back, briefly baulked behind runners upon straightening, made no further impression.
Slowly away, made steady headway along the rail towards the rear of midfield, steadied behind heels coming out of back straight, saved ground on the inside turning for home and soon weakened.
Gradually drifted over 2L back to 4th despite ridden along, slightly further back in 5th leaving the Rock, weakened under pressure in home straight.
Travelled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, widest runner turning in and soon weakened.
From draw 11 went forward to be chasing leader 2-wide, led 250M, kept on strongly to line holding off pursuing rivals comfortably.
Jumped on terms, pushed along to hold a midfield spot just over 4Ls off the pace, raced tight inside 200M, did best work late to go 2nd near line.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up near last, responded well on straightening, chased hard final 150M to go 3rd near line.
Slow to begin, settled down behind midfield, wide into straight, closed off steadily, just missed 3rd in a close finish.
Chased leaders in 4th, had every chance turning in, not pace to challenge winner, in contention for minor placings until weakened closing stages.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear along inside, had to shift to outside nearing 200M to improve, finished off well.
From wide draw taken across to race in midfield, not far off from leaders turning, kept on steadily in straight, outsprinted final stages.
Chased the pace, held ground early straight, faded final 150M.

Ended up racing in detached last, pushed along 800M but not making ground, ran past beaten horses in the straight only. (Jockey : didn't travel well in early stages and not able to keep pace with the field.)
Quickly into stride, led at good pace, headed 250M, no extra nearing 100M, weakened.
Not far off from pace but 3-wide no cover throughout, unable to quicken turning in, weakened 200M.
Positioned ahead of midfield, failed to go on passing 300M, never threatened.

Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, finished off strongly to score on line.
Began smartly from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just couldn't hold off the winner on line.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out after passing 550M, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider from 550M, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hard ridden after passing 600M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, weakened turning in, eased final furlong.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, led 400M, overhauled 50M.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, took rail at back, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear.
Eased back, 2 wide, blocked most straight, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, trapped 3-4 wide at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Midfield on the rails, lack room in straight, checked 250M, no progress.
Took rail and lead easily, however soon out of fuel 350M.
Trapped 3-4 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 400M.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort near 400M, responded solidly to score.
Raced behind leaders, quickened near 300M, worked home solidly.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, made up some late ground in the straight.
Travelled midfield, fought hard in the straight, worked home one-paced.
Travelled midfield, one-paced when placed under pressure in the straight.
Raced at tail, tried to improve passing 600M, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 500M, worked home one-paced.
Taken back at start, placed pressure passing 500M, limited response.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure but weakened near 200M.
Began awkwardly then niggled along to race outside the lead, gave ground near 300M, mucus in trachea.
Urged forward, travelled wide and without cover throughout outside leaders, gave ground in the straight.
Raced wide and without cover throughout in handy position, gave ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, came under pressure passing 600M, finished tailed-out, must trial.
Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Moved wider on cornering, sprinted quickly after straightening, continual headway until striking lead inside last 50m.
Enjoyed good run on the leaders back on rail. Eased over heels on straightening, sprinted to assume lead at the 300m & continued in lead until overhauled by winner inside the last 50m.

Reared & consequently missed the start by big margin. Improved steadily to join the field by the 850m. Shifted wider on straightening, & again at the 250m before storming home into 3rd position in closing stages. Big run.
Strode to midfield between runners, 3.5 lengths form lead at the 800m. Eased wider on the corner, made up a few lengths running into 4th place in concluding stages. Close behind.

Hard ridden at start but didn't have the speed of others, settling just worse than midfield between runners. Continued in second half, 4L from the lead entering last section before making up a few lengths in dash home.

Strode forward to be prominent, raced wide before improving to assume the lead near 800m. Continued to hold the lead on straightening before being headed at the 300m. Battled on well in closing stages to not be beaten far.
Not fast to begin, worse than midfield before improving along rail, 4L from the lead at the 800m. Finished off steadily in last section to finish in midfield but not beaten far.
Steadied after start & shifted to rearward position away from rail. Had only one runner behind, some 6L from lead on cornering before making up a few lengths in final furlong to finish midfield.

Strode forward to race prominently in early sections before steadying when close to heels near the 1000m. Eased wider on cornering, peaked on effort at the 250m before weakening out meekly in last 150m.
Had no speed after start & raced worse than midfield on rail. Continued on rail, 4L from the lead on straightening but failed to improve in last section & was well held.

Ridden forward from wide gate before racing 3 wide in midfield. Left without cover from the 750m. Came under hard riding on straightening, before weakening out in last section after wide passage throughout.
Showed speed to muster through to lead. Headed in the lead by wide runner at the 800m before weakening out meekly in the straight. Well beaten.
Steadied after the start & raced second from last. Always well back & was well beaten.
Showed speed to race outside the leader. Steadied near the 750m before weakening out badly in the straight to be beaten a long way.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, checked off heels near 700M, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, sat right behind the leader on rail, awkwardly placed for a short distance near 900M, saved ground on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Out in line, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, no clear running after turning in, steadied off heels near 300M, found daylight 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Bounded at start with jockey lost a stirrup iron, detached from the field early, got back to it near 850M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Away well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 750M, moved closer on turn, wider into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, checked near 700M, 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off one pace.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 850M, hard ridden after turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths back, travelled keenly from 800M, 4 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide, 3 lengths or so back, carried wider after passing 750M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Settled to race in the box-seat, took led at 100M out and scored by 3/4L.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, saved ground and kept on to take 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, closed off strongly for 3rd. (Bled from both nostrils)
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, kept rolling and ran on fairly.
At rear, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, pretty one paced.
Midfield, 2 wide, made some ground in the straight.
Midfield initially, rolled forward after 1400M, 3 wide with no cover, made some ground until emptied passing 150M.
Taken back, 2 wide, was one paced in the straight.
Eased back, along the rail, made some ground until flattened late.
Raced at rear, along the rail, ran on but saved no ground.
Rolled forward, 2 wide initially, along the rail after 1500M, lost ground and no more fuel at 300M.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, did not feature.
Sent forward, 2 wide, in the straight continued to lose ground.
Taken back to rear of midfield in 7th from the widest gate, strolled to lead over 200 metres out, won unextended.

Broke well to lead from a wide gate, soon taken back to 3rd or joint 3rd just over 2L back, commenced move entering home straight holding slight chance briefly early in straight but eventual winner too good.
Broke well from a wide gate before taken back to midfield on the rail, switched out for a run on straightening, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Travelled in rear despite ridden early, ran on steadily inside the final 250 metres, did best work late.
Moderate start, settled in 4th just about 3L off the pace, gained slightly closer on the rail rounding home bend, baulked early in straight, ran home one-paced.
Improved steadily from a moderate start before settling just outside the leader, shared the pace briefly after straightening but soon found no extra.
Stumbled on jumping, gradually dropped to last few despite hard ridden, dropped to last and widest runner turning in, produced good late impression inside the final 300 metres.
Soon took up running after a moderate start, led the field until joined after straightening, gave ground under pressure inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Began awkwardly losing ground, recovered steadily to forward of midfield in 5th some 4L back, in similar position turning for home, unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, recovered steadily along the rail to rear of midfield, faded after straightening.
Began awkwardly and soon dropped to the last, trailed the field to the 600 metres when saved ground approaching home straight, made no further impression after straightening.
Began well from a wide gate, soon dropped towards the rear while travelling wide without cover, remained similar rounding home bend and into the straight, soon weakened.

Reserved near rear, shuffled back to last making the home turn, moved closer 700M, wide into straight, let down strongly, caught runaway leader near line and completed a clean sweep of the 4yo Classic Series.

Soon dropped back to race in the rear, taken keen hold, wide no cover from 1000M, made forward move to take lead before 800M, kicked 3-4Ls clear early straight, kept on well only to be caught near line.
From draw 1 settled along the fence in a position just ahead of midfield, shifted out 700M, soon pushed along, briefly went 2nd inside 300M, held ground final 200M.
Taken across to race along the fence, behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace on settling, stayed on mildly final 400M but never a serious threat.
Crossed to the fence, shared lead until entering back straight then raced in a trailing spot behind leader, fought on same pace in the straight, no threat final 200M.
Settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, driven along 500M, made some progress early straight, held ground final 200M.
From wide draw shifted across to race at the back of the field, moved away from fence 700M, held up early straight, shifted further out to challenge, ran on mildly.
Raced in midfield along the 2-path, moved out 600M, ran on fairly in the straight, no impression on leaders.
Settled down behind midfield 5Ls off the pace middle stages, switched out 800M to make his move, wide into straight, responded fairly, couldn't go on 200M. (Deep wound to right stifle.)
Held up 3-wide in midfield, wide no cover from 1200M, 4Ls off leader home turn, not quickened in straight, never threatened.

Prominent early stages, raced keenly, took outright lead entering back straight, came under pressure 600M, no extra final 250M. (Jockey : circumstances of the race led to the horse not able to see out the distance.)
Went forward, wide no cover until 1200M, tracked leader until gave ground 600M out, already beaten when turning for home.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear racing along the 3-path, struggled to keep up passing 600M, left behind turning into straight.
Chased leaders in 4th, pushed along 700M, run ended nearing 350M, weakened to last.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed very good response, took the lead 100M, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.

Made contact at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just held.

Began only fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, same position on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just held.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Made contact on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, peaked and headed near 100M, ran on evenly to the line, missed frame on line.
Commenced well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, closer on turn, kept inside after straightening and made some progress.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made some progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made little progress when clear thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began smartly from gate 10, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the winner final 50M.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, nearest on line.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, 3 wide turning, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, moved closer after passing 1000M, raced 3w with no cover, a length or so back in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 to 4 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, steadied off heels near 1000M, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Took keen hold, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
