Moderately away, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, gradually improved from 700M, took the lead near 500M, kept on very well after turning in, easily scored.

Began well from gate 11, raced 3w slightly behind midfield early, 6 lengths or so back, 2w from 1200M, commenced move after passing 500M, 4-1/2L lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 800M, 2 wide from 550M, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider from 550M, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned on rail at rear, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Out in line, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, finished off one pace.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced prominently, 2 wide, took the lead near 900M, led by half length, headed near 550M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider from 450M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, headed after entering the back straight, weakened from 600M, eased final 150M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, made early move 900M, led 600M, hung on well to win.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Took rail and led at fast sectionals, hampered 600M, held ground in straight.
Pushed early, behind midfield, 2 wide, held up 5-2, made ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, no progressed in straight.
Eased at start, took cover, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Eased to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, checked 600M, dropped of 500M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Behind midfield, clipped heels near 200M and dislodged rider.
Raced 3 wide and with cover in midfield position, quickened near 100M to score.
Raced towards rear, asked for effort passing 450M, continued to make ground in the straight, finished solidly, missed by Head.
Raced outside the lead, placed pressure near 400M, worked home well.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground.
Jumped sharply, wide and without cover throughout in handy position, ran on well in the straight.
Niggled to take lead with nice early speed, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort near 400M, over concluding stages held up and not fully tested.
Taken back at start, placed pressure on straightening, one-paced.
Jumped well, raced in box seat, tried to improve pressure near 400M, one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced 3 wide and with cover behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, no response when asked.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail, moved away from the rail approaching the corner when two lengths from lead. Dashed up to assume lead at the 150m & had enough in hand to win by half length.

Had good run on leaders back throughout. Awkwardly placed behind the leader in early part of straight before getting through tight running at the 175m & finishing well to run into second place in final 100m.

Showed early speed to assume lead before crossing to rail after passing the winning post first time. Continued in lead, racing over a length clear passing half-way. Headed at the 150m before hold onto 3rd place in closing stages.

Slow to begin, awkward near heels before crossing to rail after start. Improved from tail to race in midfield after first section. Stayed close to inside on cornering, held up near the 200m before finishing strongly late.

Strode forward to race in second place, away from rail. Travelled well in second when over 1L from the lead at half-way. Moved closer to lead on straightening before peaking at the 200m & yielding two lengths late.

Began well before steadying to race in midfield away from rail. Continued between horses in middle stages, 3L form lead at half-way. Moved wider on cornering when 2L from lead before weakening slightly in last furlong.
Not fast to begin before striding to midfield but racing 3 wide with cover throughout. Moved wider entering last section when 3.5L from lead before failing to offer any more in last 250m.

Shifted across behind runners & raced at tail. Continued at the rear 8.5L from the lead at half-way. Moved wider on cornering, shifted very wide soon after straightening when under pressure before passing a few late. (Vets).
Crowded & lost ground at start before racing second last throughout. Continued with only one behind, 5L from lead entering last section. Did little in the straight & was well held.
Raced in midfield away from the rail throughout, around 5L from lead in early & middle stages. Moved closer to be only 3.5L form lead entering last section before weakening out to be well held.

Bumped at start & then failed to muster early speed before shifting back to third last. Moved 4 wide passing the 500m when improving before forced very wide on straightening. Peaked early in the straight & weakened sharply.
Raced to midfield after start but left 3 wide without cover throughout. Began yielding ground approaching the corner before weakening out sharply in the straight. Well beaten last.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to score by a head. (Lost left hind plate.)
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just missed by a head.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, half length back, there to turn, closed off well, just missed by a neck.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on well after turning in, just unable to hold off the first few late.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 350M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away and made contact, raced very wide at rear early, bumped near 700M, moved a bit closer after passing 650M, 2 wide on turn, made some progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide at rear, bumped near 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, detached from the main group after passing 700M, weakened thereafter, unacceptable performance.
Settled to race in the box-seat, took led at 100M out and scored by 2-1/2L.
Sent forward to take the rail and led, kept on going but was no match to the winner.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, save ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, kept rolling and ran on fairly.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground and close off fairly.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, pretty one paced.
At rear, along the rail, found nothing in the straight.
Missed the start, settled in midfield and 2 wide, swung wide on straightening, showed no turn on foot. (See incident report)
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, was one paced in the straight.
Slow to begin, taken back and raced detached, not competitive in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4 wide and no cover, saved no ground.
In midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the straight.
Pressed forward from a middle gate settling mainly just over 2L back in 4th, commenced move approaching home turn and hit the front upon straightening, hung on well under pressure.

Settled well back, travelled 3-wide without cover throughout back straight, commenced move rounding home bend and went wide into the straight, finished off the race strongly down the centre of the track, did best work late.
Settled mainly in midfield on the rail in 6th, switched out to challenge entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in midfield in 7th, commenced move entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in worse than midfield on the rail, switched out to challenge entering home straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Inconvenienced at start, settled in worse than midfield, commenced move wide around home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Soon taken back to last few from a wide gate, saved ground on the inside turning for home, badly hampered early in home straight and checked over 250 metres out, made no impression in closing stages.
Taken back to last few racing keenly most of the way to the Rock, saved ground turning for home and baulked for a run 200 metres out, kept on well closing stages.
Began well from the one gate, settled mainly about 2L off the pace on the rail, gained closer briefly entering home straight before weakening under pressure.

Travelled wide in midfield after pressing forward from the widest gate, moved further forward 3-wide without cover to 3rd down the back straight, hung out very wide making home turn and never recovered.
Improved steadily from a wide gate before settling just outside the leader, disputed lead briefly entering home straight and soon weakened.
Soon took up running after beginning from a middle gate, obtained rails run coming onto the first bend holding slender lead in back straight, folded up quickly after headed making home turn.
Began fairly, recovered to race behind midfield, switched wide 400M for his challenge, closed off strongly to lead 80M out, firmly in control.
Dropped back from wide draw, held up last early stages, moved closer from 650M, ran on strongly under top weight to claim 2nd near line.
Never far off the pace, tried hard in straight, not pace of winner final 150M, lost 2nd near line.
Began awkwardly, reserved behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, swung wide near 400M, stayed on for modest 4th.
Chased leaders in 4th, responded well early straight, out-sprinted final 150M.
Led uncontested after jumping from draw 1, set steady pace, headed 200M, weakened towards the finish.
Settled midfield along the inside, kept on final 300M but not pace to challenge leaders.
Chased leader 2-wide, kept on same pace early straight, weakened final 150M.
Shuffled back to race near last, plenty to do turning in, couldn't finish off.
Bustled along after the start, chased leaders in 3rd, no extra final 200M, weakened.
Dropped back to race at the rear 3-wide, soon beaten turning home. (Jockey : saddle shifted back after the start causing inconvenience during race.)
Travelled wide without cover towards the rear, couldn't go on in the straight, never involved.

Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail, 2 wide from 500M, no clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 300M, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, closed off well to take 2nd. (Minor laceration to the inside of the right hind heel.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, commenced move after 450M, hit the front early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider from 550M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Out in line, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Taken back from gate 13, no early speed, detached from the main group early, got back to it near 600M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, moved closer on turn, widest into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, in traffic early in straight, (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 800M, sat right behind the leader on turn, no clear running early in straight, weakened from 250M. (Blood in trachea.)
Away well, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 700M, took brief lead after turning in, headed near 350M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, took the lead 950M, found rail 750M, led by half length on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, drifted away 300M to score with ease.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Eased at start, took rail, checked badly 800M, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed early, sat 2 wide in midfield, progressed steadily 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail behind midfield, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back early, trapped wide, moved forward 1200M, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M weakened.
Eased at start, trapped 3-5 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 400M, run ended 150M.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, checked 800M, no progress.
Midfield along the fence, weakened 200M.
In front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 500M.
Trapped 3-4 wide throughout, never better than midfield.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Hard ridden forward, eased out of race 800M.
Urged along, raced behind leaders, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Settled box seat with nice early speed, asked effort near 400M, responded solidly in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, improved passing 500M, gained nice ground passing 100M.
Settled towards rear, placed pressure passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Bumped at start then failed to muster speed, raced at rear, one-paced in the straight.
Ridden to take lead, placed pressure at 400M, limited response in the straight.
Settled towards rear, limited response when placed under pressure.
Raced at back, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, raced greenly when placed pressure in the straight, weakened near 100M.
Hard ridden forward for some distance, settled outside the lead, weakened on straightening.
Raced at tail, tried to improve near 700m, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Hard ridden & showed early speed to cross to the lead. Continued in the lead over a length clear on straightening & had enough in reserve to hold late challenger.
Race din midfield on rail. Two lengths from the lead entering last section, squeezed between runners inside last furlong before finishing off strongly in concluding stages. Well clear of third.

Raced wide in midfield early before improving position to race outside the leader by the 900m. Came under hard riding when leader kicked away on straightening before battling away to hold well held third.
Steadied across to midfield soon after start before racing keenly in middle stages when 3 wide with cover. Moved wider again on straightening before making steady late ground in last section.

Showed some speed after the start to race third, away from the rail in early stages. Obtained cover near the 900m. Around 4L from the lead entering last section & effectively maintained that margin in dash to line.
Began awkwardly & missed the start before settling near the rear. Stayed close to the inside on straightening before making up late ground to midfield from the rear.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Only 3.5L from lead entering last section but could make no further improvement & was well held in midfield.

Didn't have the early speed of others & drifted back worse than midfield after start. Ridden along from the 600m, cornered with only 3 behind before passing a few tiring runners to midfield. Well held.

Allowed to drift back after start & soon raced at the tail. Hampered near the 900m. Continued at the rear, 7.5L from the lead entering the last section before shifting the widest runner & passing a few to midfield. No threat.
Steadied from widest barrier & shifted across when 3 wide near the rear. Effectively maintain position in the final section & was never likely.

Ridden forward after the start before being left 3 wide without cover in midfield throughout. Forced very wide on cornering before offering very little & weakening last 300m. (Must trial – unacceptable perf).

Steadied & drifted back to worse than midfield after start. Crowded near 1000m, before being restrained & relegated to second last near the 800m. Hard ridden prior to cornering & made no headway in last section. Well held.

A touch slow to begin before mustering quickly to improve to midfield on rail. Moved away from rail nearing the home corner, 3L from lead entering last section before weakening out in last 300m. (Lame next day).

Showed good early speed, crossed near the 1100m & racing on leaders back before momentarily racing ungenerously soon after. Moved wider on straightening before weakening out sharply in final furlong. Last.
Began well, raced 4 wide, 3 to 4 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off well to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.

Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 750M, a length or so back on turn, made good progress early in straight, hit front 250M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 300M, ran on evenly to the line.

Jumped with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, showed some response until blocked near 250M, cleared 100M, one paced thereafter.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, angled out turning in, hampered 300M, made no progress thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 750M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 550M, no clear running early in straight, checked near 300M, weakened and eased thereafter. (Minor laceration to the left hind fetlock.)
In midfield, along the rail, ran on well to the line and scored by 1/2L.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with no cover, saved ground, raced tight after 150M but kept on to take 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, saved ground, raced tight after 150M but closed off strongly for 3rd. (See incident report)
Ridden forward to take rail and lead, kept up until weakened at 150M.
Rolled forward, along the rail, ran on one paced.
At rear, along the rail after 750M, saved ground but emptied at 150M.
At rear, 2 wide after 750M, made some ground in the straight.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Rolled forward and 2 wide after 650M, stayed on until 300M and lost ground.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
Taken back, along the rail, ran on but only saved minor ground.
Rolled forward, settled one-out one-back, not competitive.
Midfield, 2 wide, approaching the 300M became very unbalanced and did not feature. (See incident report)
At rear, 2 wide, showed nothing in the straight. (Lame left front and blood in trachea)
Close up, responded well to hit the front over 150 metres out, just held off runner-up's strong late challenge.
Close up early settling just over 2L back in 7th near stands rails, angled off the rail to challenge inside the final 300 metres, quickened well under pressure and just failed to get up on line.
Travelled just over 2L back in 7th early in the centre of the track, commenced move coming onto the course proper, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from the highest gate to lead near stands rails, led until headed over 150 metres out.
Moderate start, settled in last few near the centre of the track, came under pressure from the 400 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.

In rear early after an awkward start from low draw, improved down the centre of the track to better than midfield within 2L of pace coming onto the course proper, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and unbalanced dropping behind midfield, made some late impression near stands rails inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well, settled in midfield, one-paced under pressure. (Blood in trachea)
Ridden to hold prominent position early, lost touch coming onto the course proper, dropped out tamely.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, never better than midfield, faded onto the course proper.
Not far off, weakened under pressure inside the final 300 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Dropped steadily to last place approaching the course proper, found nothing under reminders.
Travelled ungenerously in midfield most of the way, dropped out under pressure after coming onto the course proper.
Soon dropped to the rear, raced awkwardly halfway out, never on terms.
Never far off the pace, made good headway from 450M, vied for lead final 200M, dug deep and just prevailed.
Settled ahead of midfield, came through to challenge for lead 300M, went head to head with rival final 200M, just held.
Niggled along early stages to hold a position behind midfield, held up top of straight before finding clear passage inside 300M, not pace of first 2 final 200M.
Dropped back and settled towards the rear, swung wide 500M, chased on steadily, inclined to lay in final stages and difficult to ride.
Reserved in midfield 2-wide, stayed on mildly final 300M, no impression on first 2.
Chased leader in a steadily run race, lacked a finishing kick on straightening, ran home one paced.
Held up behind midfield, responded only fairly in straight, never reached leaders.
Unable to slot in from wide draw, 4 wide no cover from 800M, steadied 300M, unable to quicken in straight, never threatened.
Sent forward, caught wide until 800M, pressed leader home turn, led briefly early straight then weakened away 200M.
Dropped back from wide, raced in last 8Ls away middle stages, swung widest from 550M, only went past well beaten horses in the straight, never involved.
Slowly into stride, ended up near last 7Ls off the pace, never in the picture, ran past well beaten horses in the straight
Began only fairly, ridden to take up a position behind midfield, proved difficult settle 1300M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Aggressively ridden early stages chasing leaders, dropped back to midfield position nearing home turn, wide no cover from 800M, weakened passing 300M.
Began fairly from draw 1, urged forward to lead from 1300M, pressed by rival from 800M, lost lead 350M, dropped out rapidly.

Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, saved ground throughout, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on well to hold off the challengers, scored by a neck,

Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover early, 2 lengths back, found a 2 wide spot near 1100M, same margin back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Began fairly, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, wider after passing 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, not enough room early in straight, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 3 lengths back, no cover from 1100M, gradually improved after passing 700M, a length back turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, steadied off heels and wider near 1000M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider on turn, finished off evenly.

Began fairly from a tricky draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover at rear in the early stages, found cover after passing 900M, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.

Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hampered and carried wider 1000M, no cover in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail 1150M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back to race 5 lengths back on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line, easily scored.
Away with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line, no threat to the winner. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 500M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Began only fairly, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced 2 wide at rear early, found rail 850M, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 250M, finished off evenly when clear thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar positon on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar positon in the middle stages, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar positon on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, a bit closer turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lost left front plate near 300M.)
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Raced at tail throughout, never competitive. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away from gate 11, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 2 lengths or so back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well throughout, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame. (Lame right front leg.)
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, no early speed, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Began fairly from gate 1, no early speed, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from gate 10, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide, slightly better than midfield, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently but trapped very wide, 3 wide on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, gradually lost position after passing 800M, emptied early in straight, finished last.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, benefited by the fast sectionals, progressed steadily 350M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, led 300M, overhauled 50M.
Hard ridden to hold the fence in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
At back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, ran on until 150M weakened.
At back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 350M, run ended 150M.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Eased to obtain box seat, out of fuel 200M.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up with the field, detached, raced flat until 200M made some ground.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, never nearer.
Eased at start, trapped 4 wide, never progressed.
Trapped 4 wide throughout in midfield, dropped off 400M.
Settled midfield, wide on straightening, continued to make ground in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Settled behind leaders, quickened passing 200M, worked hone solidly.
Crowded on jumping, raced midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground, finished solidly.
Urged along from widest barrier to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, finished nicely.
Raced behind the lead on rail, commenced to improve near 500M, worked home well.
Settled in front of midfield, placed pressure near 600M, made some late ground in the straight.
Crowded on jumping, travelled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, gained some ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, settled behind midfield, worked home one-paced.
Raced in handy position, limited response when placed under pressure, gave ground passing 200M.
Began only fairly, raced at back, limited response when placed pressure in the straight.
Urged along, raced in front of midfield, placed pressure passing 550M, weakened passing 200M.
Taken back at start, settled towards rear, no response in the straight.
Began very awkwardly then checked away from heels, raced at tail, weakened in the straight, must trial.
Wide and without cover throughout, finished tailed out, lame right hind next day, must trial.

Began well before drifting across from wide barrier to race in midfield. Raced tight & bumped on the point of the corner. Shifted wider soon after before charging home strongly to score narrowly in final stride.
Showed early speed to lead. Raced clear on straightening, maintained over 2 length lead inside last 150m before laying out under pressure & being caught by fast finisher in final few strides.

Raced in midfield in early & middle stages. Ridden along from the 600m, stayed close to the inside on cornering. Moved over heals at the 300m before working home steadily to run into third place in final 100m.
Had good run on leaders back throughout. Couldn't go with leader who kicked clear on straightening but battled away ok in concluding stages to hold non-threatening forth.

Had no early speed despite being hard ridden & drifted back to third last. Shifted wider approaching the home corner when over 5L from lead. Passed a few when making up late ground from rearward position.

Began awkwardly & lost ground, consequently racing near the rear early. Improved position around runners passing half-way before cornering very wide. Sprinted to second at the 200m before weakening a few lengths thereafter.

Didn't begin fast & soon raced near the tail on the rail. Continued near the back, 5 lengths from the lead on straightening, shifted back towards the rail at the 350m before maintaining margin late. No threat.

Raced wide without cover just behind lead in early stages before drifting a length further back & getting cover approaching half-way. Held up momentarily on cornering when 3.5L from lead before offering nothing final 300m.
Hard ridden from gate ten to race 4 wide outside the leaders throughout. Peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakened out significantly in the straight.
Steadied & raced keenly when racing 4 wide with cover throughout. Continued very wide around home corner before offering nothing after straightening. Beaten big margin.
Steadied & crossed to race near the rear. Relegated back to last approaching half-way. Under pressure when 8L from the lead at the 400m before weakening out further in straight. Beaten long way.
Showed speed after the start to race outside the leader. Came under immediate pressure around the home corner before weakening out very quickly from on straightening. (Must trial).
Began very awkwardly, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, 7 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to score.

Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, raced tight 750M, commenced move after passing 600M, 4w turning in, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, no cover from 900M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight without threatening.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, raced tight near 750M, carried wider on turn, made some progress until crowded near 50M, not able to ridden out thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 1000M, angled out near 600M, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.

Commenced well, raced prominently, 3 wide, took the lead after passing 1200M, found rail near 900M, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.

Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, headed near 1200M, sat a length behind the leader in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back early, found rail near 900M, 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 900M, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 to 3 wide with slightly behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Sent forward, 2 wide initially and along the rail after 750M, kept on going to score rather comfortably by 3L.
Sent forward to take the rail, 2 wide after 500M, kept on going but was no match to the winner.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover after 450M, kept rolling and ran on fairly.
Raced in front, 3 wide but with cover after 450M, battled on to the line.
Began awkwardly and raced in midfield, along the rail, kept up until weakened at 200M. (See incident report)
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn on foot.
In midfield, 3 wide with cover, pretty one paced.
At rear, 2 wide, showed no turn on foot.
Raced in worse than midfield, wide with no cover, pretty one paced.
Taken back, along the rail, not competitive in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, in the straight lost ground.
At rear, wide but with cover, nothing in the straight.
Settled within 2L of the pace on the rail, angled out to challenge entering home straight, hit the front under pressure inside the 300 metres, won easily.

Settled in worse than midfield on the rail, commenced move coming onto home bend gaining to 4th some 3L back into the straight, sustained progress to reach 2nd over 100 metres out but never troubled the winner.
Pressed forward from a wide gate eventually gaining slender lead upside of the 2nd entering back straight, in similar position turning for home but overhauled inside the final 300 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in last few on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend, stayed on past well-beaten horses closing stages. (Lame next day)
Led early stages on the rail, narrowly headed turning into back straight, held similar position turning for home but unable to sustain effort inside the final 250 metres.

Amongst leaders early stages despite the moderate start, settled in 6th within 3L of the pace turning into back straight, slightly worse entering home straight, kept on one pace under pressure. (Lame next day)

Began well from a wide gate, travelled very wide with the leaders rounding first bend before settling one back 3-wide without cover in back straight, held similar position rounding home bend, soon weakened.
Settled well behind from the widest gate, trailed the field to the 500 metres, snuck up on rail turning for home, made no impression in home straight.
Settled in worse than midfield, came under pressure when wide into home straight, made no impression after straightening.
Settled well behind from a wide gate travelling wide without cover, bumped and went the widest entering home straight, kept on same pace under pressure.
Prominent early settling in midfield, gave ground under pressure after coming out of back straight. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Jumped fairly settling wide towards the rear, made short-lived effort coming out of back straight, soon weakened inside the final 400 metres.
Not far off to home straight, dropped out tamely. (Jockey said horse was not comfortable on the surface when questioned)
Settled in midfield, gave ground under pressure from over 800 metres out.
Held up behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace middle stages, picked up strongly from 300M, made rapid headway to lead close home.
Strode forward, led from 1200M, set good pace middle stages, kicked clear 250M, just couldn't hold off fast finishing winner late, clear from rest.
Led early stages, tracked leader from 1200M, fought on same pace in the straight, no threat to first 2 final 150M.
Restrained and settled towards the rear, switched lane 300M to challenge, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 4th.
Gradually moved forward to be tracking leader on settling, run ended 200M, weakened towards the line.
From draw 1 tracked leaders early stages, dropped back to race ahead of midfield 1000M when pace quickened, fought on same pace in straight, no threat final 200M.
Reserved near last, over 8Ls off the pace making the turn for home, made minor progress only, not reached leaders.
Settled down behind midfield, pushed along 600M, kept on same pace in straight, never dangerous.
Not hurried, reserved near the rear 6-7Ls off the pace, 3-wide trip, widest from 600M, failed to run on.
From wide draw crossed to a 3-wide position in midfield, came under pressure 600M, couldn't go on entering straight, soon no impression.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, ridden along 600M out, couldn't muster speed, never threatened.
Strolled forward, tracked leaders, struggled 400M, soon gave ground.
Shifted across behind runners, raced at the rear 9Ls off the pace, failed to pick up on straightening, never involved.
Settled just ahead of midfield, pushed along 600M, couldn't go on in the straight, beaten 250M, eased.

Commenced well, positioned 1-1/4L behind the leader, hit the front near 200M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader near to the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed good response, finished 2nd.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, a bit closer in the middle stages, finished off well to take a place.
Jumped well, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, no clear running until 100M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, showed some response in the final 400M, no threat to the first few.
Began well, showed good early speed, took the lead 700M, led by 3/4L at 400M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away, raced prominently, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final 100M. (Roarer.)
Jumped well from gate 1, raced behind midfield in the middle of the track, made minor progress in the final 400M.
Away well from barrier 14, raced at rear on the stands' rail, 3 to 4 lengths back, made little progress final 400M.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths or so back, nearer to the middle of the track, showed limited response after passing 400M, weakened gradually final 150M.
Slightly slow out and made contact, positioned 2 lengths or so back in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, only showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently, peaked shortly after passing 400M, weakened final 250M.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the stands' rail, weakened gradually after passing 400M.
Progressed forward steadily to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Pushed early, midfield, 2-3 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
At back, on the fence, checked 500M, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace, checked again 100M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
At back, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, emptied 400M.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort passing 300M, responded strongly to score.
Ridden to take lead, placed pressure in the straight, responded nicely, worked home solidly.
Settled midfield, improved near 400M, quickened passing 300M, finished nicely.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield, placed pressure near 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Travelled towards rear, tried to improve near 600M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind leaders on rail, came under pressure near 550M, gave ground passing 200M, must trial.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, no response in the straight.
Began well & race don leaders back throughout. Moved away from the rail on straightening, dashed to lead at the 200m before drawing away for comfortable win late.

Began very fast to assume lead, headed on outside at the 1000m before regathering lead from the 800m. Continued in lead until being headed by winner at the 200m. Fought gamely to hold second, length clear of 3rd.

Shifted across after the start before improving to midfield between runners from the 1000m. Eased 4 wide approaching the home corner before finishing off steadily to third place inside the last furlong.

Improved after the start but left 3 wide without cover just behind the leading pair. A length from the lead on straightening before emptying out at the 200m & giving a length or two late after wide passage.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Moved wider on straightening, 2L from the lead entering final section but could offer no more in last 250m & was well held in midfield.

Crowded on jumping before shifting back behind runners to race at the tail. Had only one behind on cornering before drifting out in the straight when making late ground to midfield. Sound effort considering race shape.
Hampered at start & lost ground before improving position along the rail to midfield. Stayed close to the inside on cornering but peaked on effort at the 250m & gave a few lengths late.

Shifted behind runners to settle second last. Relegated back to last on cornering, moved the widest runner on straightening before making up some ground from the rear in a race that shaped to suit on-pace.
Began only fairly & consequently raced third form last on inside. Stayed close to the inside on cornering, but could make no headway once tested in the final 300m. Well held.
Enjoyed good run in midfield between runners. Shuffled a few positions further back on cornering but could make no further headway in the straight & was well held.
Hard ridden from wide barrier, improved to assume lead from the 1000m before racing outside leader from the 800m. Hard ridden on cornering before peaking soon after & weakening out in straight.

Crowded at start, rushed forward after 100m, before being restrained when awkwardly positioned. Lost ground when racing greenly, consequently 6L from lead at the 800m. Weakened significantly in last section & was well beaten.

Had a good run in third, away from rail with cover in early & middle stages. Only two lengths from lead on cornering but began yielding ground soon after straightening & tailed out in the straight to be well beaten.

Began well before drifting back after the start to race worse than midfield, wide & with cover throughout. Forced wider near the 650m before cornering very wide. Weakened out badly in last section & was long last.
Taken back from gate 7, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 800M, 4 wide turning in, finished off strongly to score.

Commenced well, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, crowded and bumped 350M, took the lead 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.

Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 lengths or so back turning in, checked off heels near 450M, no clear running until 300M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to frame without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 650M, 3 wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 6, positioned on rail behind midfield, wider turning in, 2 to 3 lengths back at 400M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, 2-1/2L turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lad, travelled well to turn, bumped and unbalanced near 350M, weakened thereafter.

Began well from gate 10, raced 3 wide better than midfield, moved closer after entering the back straight, 2 wide from 900M, peaked turning in, weakened and eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, battled on to the line to score.
In midfield initially, along the rail and rolled forward after 850M, continued on strongly to take 2nd.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, saved ground and ran on gamely.
Taken back, 2 wide, swung wide on straightening, saved some ground and ran on reasonably.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, shifted in under pressure and weakened passing the 100M.
Rolled forward initially, midfield after 750M, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Rolled forward, along the rail, lost ground after 150M.
Began awkwardly, at rear, 2 wide, showed no turn on foot.
Began fairly, at rear, along the rail, pretty one paced after 200M.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, lost ground in the straight.
At rear, along the rail, never a factor.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, run ended at 250M.
Hard ridden to be prominent, 2 wide after 800M, run soon ended after straightening. (See incident report)
Rolled forward, 2 wide, did not quicken in the straight.
Well there, took up running 900 metres out and soon crossed to the rail, hung on well under pressure.

Led early, ceded advantage to eventual winner 900 metres out and held same one-back position on the rail to home straight, baulked before obtaining a clear run inside the 300 metres, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well, soon taken back to middle of small field just about 2L back in 5th and 3-wide without cover, came to challenge entering home straight and fought on steadily without threatening.
Inconvenienced at start losing ground, soon recovered to over 3L back in 6th on the rail, made modest progress in home straight to be nearest at finish.
Recovered quickly from a moderate start, restrained mostly in 2nd and 3-wide without cover until coming onto home bend, kept on under pressure until swamped for position inside the final 100 metres.
Taken to well back of small field after beginning from the widest gate, fought on steadily in home straight without threatening.
Jumped fairly in middle of small field, restrained to last few 1000 metres out, widest runner turning into home straight, made no further impression.

Crowded at start losing ground, soon recovered to 5th just over 2L back while racing keenly, hampered and lost position coming onto home bend, renewed effort briefly and dropped out tamely from 2L 5th early in straight.
Pressed forward, enjoyed uncontested lead, quickened clear 300M, kept on strongly to maintain a dominant margin at the finish.
From wide draw steadied early stages to obtain cover, towards the rear, brought wide into straight, closed off well to go 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Held up 2-wide in midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, pushed along 550M, stayed on mildly for 3rd, no threat to runaway winner.
Never far off the pace, stayed on mildly final 400M for non-threatening 4th.
Tracked leader (the eventual winner), driven out 400M, fought on steadily, held 2nd to 50M, lost several places late.
Raced in mid-division, 3-wide no cover during race, made home turn awkwardly and raced greenly under pressure in the straight, kept on final 300M without threat.
Never better than midfield, 5Ls to make up top of straight, failed to make progress.
Settled down behind mid-division, had rail run, not going the pace to challenge in straight, made no impression.
Chased leader 2-wide, kept on same pace early straight, weakened final 250M.
Bumped at the start, shifted across behind runners, held up last almost 10Ls behind leader, ran past beaten horses in straight, never near to challenge.
Failed to muster speed, raced near the rear 8Ls back, struggled from 500M, never involved.
Crowded for room on jumping, held up behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, wide into straight, couldn't finish off.

Saved ground from draw 1, moved up to 5th at 800M, kept on same pace early straight, got badly unbalanced when bumped with rival 200M, eased. (Jockey : may not have appreciated racing at the prevailing track surface.)
Settled behind midfield, commenced to lay out from Home Turn, bumped with rival several times 200M-150M and became badly unbalanced, eased towards the line. (Mucus.)
Began smartly from gate 1, raced prominently on rail, led by 3/4L turning in, kicked clear early in straight, ran on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1-1/2L back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Away with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out and stumbled, detached from the main group early, got back to it near 600M, still 8 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, headed turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, weakened after passing 600M, eased early in straight.
Moderately away, raced 4 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 150M, peaked and headed 50M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Out in line, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 to 4 lengths back, wider turning in, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after 1000M, moved closer on turn, showed good response early in straight, took brief lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear, 5 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, kept on evenly early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced very wide with cover at rear, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1000M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Inconvenienced at start, trapped very wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back in the middle stages, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, found rail near 850M, travelled well on turn, no clear running early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently but wide, took the lead after passing 1000M, challenged turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Began fairly, raced very wide in midfield, no cover after 1000M, a bit closer in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.

Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hard ridden after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, no cover throughout, weakened from 550M, finished tailed out.
Settled in box seat, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground 300M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M emptied.
Hard ridden early but not muster, on heels 1400M, 2 wide at back, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide at rear, ran on fairly in straight.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, dropped off quickly 600M.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve on straightening, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Urged along to take lead, asked for effort near 350M, responded solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Jumped nicely, settled in front of midfield on rail, niggled after 800M, fought well in the straight, missed by Neck.
Jumped well but no early speed, wide and without cover throughout in midfield, made up some late ground.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield, continued to make ground in the straight, finished well.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear, wide on straightening, finished one-paced.
Raced in handy position, tried to improve near 400M, worked home OK.
Raced at rear, rounding the Home Turn and in the early part of straight held up for clear running, disappointing for running near 100M.
Taken back at start, travelled keenly in middle stages, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Shared lead in one-off position, no response in the straight when placed pressure.
Raced behind midfield on rail, came under pressure near 500M, no response in the straight.
Settled towards rear, tried to improve but no response in the straight.

Ridden across from outside barrier to race midfield away from rail. Moved three wide passing 500m, improved quickly nearing corner. Sprinted fast on straightening, dashed to lead at 200m before holding late challengers.
Began well, crossed after first bend & drifted to midfield on rail. Stayed close to the inside rail on straightening before making strong late ground to charge to fast finishing second late.

Ridden along to hold worse than midfield position away from rail. Moved three wide with cover near the 700m & wider passing the 500m. Straightened the widest runner before finishing strongly for close up third.
Raced in midfield away from rail with cover. Shuffled back a few positions on cornering before finishing off well in last 250m to be close behind.
Badly crowded at start & consequently raced at the tail. Moved wider nearing bend, effectively last horse into the straight before finishing strongly in last furlong to be just behind. Good debut.

Badly crowded & lost ground at start before racing at the tail. Ridden hard to improve into race from the 550m before finishing off steadily from the rear to not be far behind despite being steadied near line.

Steadied & allowed to race in midfield on rail. Drifted further back passing the 500m, held up on cornering, no clear running at the 200m & not tested in dash to line. Not beaten far. (Rider questioned – see report).

Ridden forward before improving to take the lead at first bend, crossed to rail by the 900m. Continued to hold the lead until being joined by the winner at the 200m before yielding a few lengths late in the race.

Not fast to begin & drifted back to race third last. Steadied from heals near the 400m & consequently shared last position on straightening. Stayed close to the inside but could only pass a few tiring runners late. Well held.
Strode forward, held lead momentarily before racing on leaders back from the 900m. Just over a length from the lead on straightening before peaking soon after & weakening out to beat only two home.

Ridden along after the start before racing in midfield, 3 wide without cover throughout. Improved position in second section to corner just over 1 length form the lead before weakening out from the 250m after wide passage.

Not fast away, improved after first bend before striding to second place near the 800m. Only a length form the lead on cornering before peaking on effort soon after straightening & weakening out sharply from the 300m. Last.
Bumped start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked 150M, headed near 50M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, closed off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 1-1/2L back on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 3 wide behind midfield, made contact near 1050M, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, made contact near 1050M, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Shifted in at start and made contact at start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, rolled forward, 2 wide, battled on to the line and closed off strongly to score by 1L.
Taken back, along the rail, battled on gamely but couldn't hold off the winner, settled for 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, continued on nicely to the line for 3rd.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide with no cover, saved ground and ran on fairly. (See incident report)
Taken back, along the rail, stayed on well to the line.
Rolled forward, along the rail, found no extra for final 150M.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, did not make ground in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, one paced and emptied passing 100M.
Began awkwardly, eased back, 2 wide, was one paced. (See incident report)
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, dropped off in the straight.
At the rear and raced detached, never a factor.
Rolled forward, along the rail, lost ground in the straight.
Jumped best from the one draw, ceded advantage to track pacemaker coming onto stables bend, renewed effort coming out of back straight and led over 450 metres out, hung on well to the line.
Settled behind midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran on well inside the final 200 metres.
Soon dropped to midfield despite ridden early, snuck up to 5th on the rail rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled just better than midfield mainly in 5th within 3L of pace, became 2L 4th rounding home bend, fought on to be nearest at finish.
Crowded at start before settling in rear of midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, fought on down the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Settled well behind from a wide gate, saved ground on inside turning for home, finished off the race well and did best work late.
Settled within 3L of pace mainly in 4th on the rail, gained closer coming onto home bend and reached 2nd shortly after straightening, unable to sustain effort closing stages. (Bled)
Settled in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, finished well inside the final 200 metres.

Jumped fairly, took up running coming onto stables bend, steadied pace in back straight, headed by eventual winner over 450 metres out, folded up quickly inside the final 250 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Pressed forward from a wide gate travelling 3-wide without cover better than midfield, shifted slightly backward for cover over 3L off the pace coming onto back straight, dropped out rounding home bend.
Settled well behind from the widest gate, never on terms.
Vied for lead early, settled in 3rd some 2L back 3-wide without cover down back straight, dropped away quickly on top of home bend.
Chased leaders in a 3 wide position without cover, quickened up smartly to lead inside 200M, held on well when challenged by 2nd and 3rd late stages.
Slow to begin, recovered to race in midfield along the fence, ran on well on straightening, nearest finish.
Settled down 2-wide in midfield 3Ls back, chased hard and kept finding to the line, nearest finish.
Began fairly, shifted across to settle behind midfield, ran on moderately on straightening, safely held by top 3.
Restrained from a wide draw to the rear of the field, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, pushed along home turn, closed off fastest down outside of track. (Bled 2nd time.)
Disputed lead along the fence, headed passing 200M, faded towards the finish.
Chased leaders 2-wide, badly held up and going nowhere from top of straight until 200M, couldn't make up ground when clear. (Jockey questioned re his ride, no further action taken.)
Dropped back from wide draw, settled near last, chased one paced in the straight and never close enough.
Tracked leaders along the rail, kept to inside on straightening, failed to quicken under pressure, no threat final 150M.
Disputed lead on outside, weakened mid-straight, dropped away.
Settled down midfield along the 3-path, pressed along 500M but couldn't go on, did nothing in straight.
Held up towards the rear, came under pressure home turn, already beaten top of the straight.
