Began very awkwardly, showed no early speed, raced at tail, moved closer after passing 500M, not enough room near 250M, cleared 200M, finished off very strongly to score.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed good response, but still outpaced by the clear winner final 100M, finished 2nd.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, kept on well to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact shortly after start, raced prominently, near to the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 450M, kept on well to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths on the stands' rail, weakened gradually final 400M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased back, benefited by the fast pace, blocked 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Just behind the front runners, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Slow away, at back, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room until 150M, made good ground.
At back, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Midfield, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast pace, on heels 150M whilst weakening.
Pushed to share the lead at fast sectionals, ran on until 100M emptied.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, soon out of fuel 350M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
At back, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pushed to share the lead at fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, dropped off 500M.
Never competitive.
Settled in handy position, quickened near 300M, worked home strongly and scored unchallenged.
Raced midfield, improved passing 400M, finished solidly.
Ridden along but no early speed, raced at rear, made up some nice late ground.
Slow out, raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, gained some ground in the straight.
Settled behind leaders on rail, fought hard but only one-paced in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, placed pressure near 500M, worked home one-paced.
Raced at tail, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Slow out, raced midfield, finished one-paced when placed pressure.
Slow out, settled towards rear on rail, placed pressure but only limited response.
Took lead with nice early speed, tried to improve passing 400M, gave ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, 3 wide with cover, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden to race outside the lead, faded out passing 300M.
Stumbled at start, wide and without cover near 1400M, not comfortable in its action throughout, eased down over 300M, must trial.
Mustered speed after the start to lead. Raced two lengths clear entering the last furlong before having enough in hand for comfortable win.

Ridden forward but left three wide no cover in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Entered last section just under 2L from lead before finishing strongly in closing stages to second. Good given wide passage.
Began well before steadying and getting good run away from the rail in midfield. Two lengths from the lead entering the last section before finishing off steadily between runners to be close behind.

Steadied from wide gate & drifted back before being relegated to last place after first section. Continued near the rear, forced wide on cornering, bumped heavily soon after before making some late headway without threatening.
Improved after the start to race outside the leader after the first furlong. Was within a length of the lead entering the last section before weakening a few lengths in the final furlong.

Didn't begin fast but improved after start to race in midfield away from rail. Moved wider approaching the corner but could make no further headway in the last section & could only finish midfield without threatening.
Raced in midfield on the rail. Moved away from the rail on cornering but could make no headway in the last section & was well held in midfield.

Steadied after start & shifted back to race third last. Forced wider when racing tight on cornering before being awkwardly placed & bumped heavily soon after. Made no improvement in final 300m but wasn't the worst.
Began awkwardly & lost ground before improving slightly along the rail after the first section. Continued near the rear on cornering but made no headway in straight & only beat one home.
Slightly slow to begin before mustering speed quickly to hold the rail & race on the leaders back. Came under hard riding entering the last section before weakening abruptly in the final 300m. Last.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, bumped early in straight, finished off very strongly to snatch victory in a ding-dong battle.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, bumped early in straight, finished off very strongly, just narrowly beaten.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 3w behind midfield early, 2w from near 900M, angled out after passing 500M, unable to obtain clear running until near 250M, made very good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, raced 4 wide at rear early, 3 wide from near 900M, angled out after passing 550M, no clear running early in straight, made good progress thereafter, no threat to the first few.

Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, blocked 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced very wide with no cover, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from the widest draw, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began fairly, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, angled out 450M, weakened early in straight.
At rear, 2 wide, in the straight saved ground and closed off strongly to score by 1-1/4L.
Rolled forward, 4 wide no cover initially, 2 wide after 800M, ran on gamely but couldn't hold off the winner.
Raced at rear, 3 wide but with cover, saved ground and close off strongly for 3rd. (See incident report)
Sent forward, settled one-out one-back after 800M, kept up and stayed on well to the line.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, made some ground in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, ran on and saved minor ground.
Slow to begin, at rear, along the rail, saved some ground but emptied after 150M.
Bumped start, in midfield, pretty one paced.
Rolled forward, along the rail, showed no turn on foot after 100M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, 2 wide, was one paced.
At rear, along the rail, never a factor.
Rolled forward, wide with no cover, lost ground in the straight.
Travelled in rear of midfield to straight, ran on steadily despite tight run 150 metres out, gained upper hand final strides.
Settled in last few on the rail, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along from the widest gate, took up running inside the 1100 metres and obtained rails run coming onto home bend, maintained narrow advantage until swamped under pressure close to home.

Broke well before settling mainly in forward of midfield, saved ground on the inside turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure from 5th just over 2L back into the straight, unable to sustain effort close to finish.
Travelled in last few from a wide gate, very wide into home straight, obtained a clear passage over 200 metres out, finished off the race well.
Began well from a wide gate, restrained back to midfield and raced wide throughout, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began well from a middle gate, well there in 3rd in back straight, improved to join the leader rounding home bend, kept on before folding up quickly inside the final 150 metres.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled in last few before making headway wide around home bend, fought on under pressure down the centre of home straight, never nearer.
Ridden along in first few on the rail, some 2L back in 4th rounding home bend, saved ground turning in, faded steadily under pressure in straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon recovered to rear of midfield in 8th, hampered 500 metres out, ran home one-paced without quickening.
Moderate start from a wide gate, pressed forward to soon take up running and cross to the rail, ceded advantage about 1100 metres out, faded steadily under pressure in home straight.
Not far off most of the way to home straight, one-paced and hampered 250 metres out.
Crowded at start before settling well behind, never seen with a chance.
Never better than midfield, dropped out after straightening.
Travelled in 5th place just ahead of mid-division, 4Ls off the good pace on settling, quickened nicely to lead passing 300M, kept on well final 200M to hold off the persistent runner up.
Held up in midfield, travelled well into contention, moved up to make a strong challenge from 300M, held by winner final 150M.
Positively ridden to track leaders, raced more prominent than usual, in touch turning for home, fought on well final 400M to hold 3rd. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Settled down in midfield along the fence, 5Ls off the pace making home turn, not clear run early straight, steadied 200M losing momentum, stayed on well to line, unlucky not to be 3rd.
Began awkwardly, held up towards the rear, 6Ls off leader 800M, made steady headway from top of straight, not clear run 200M, kept on towards the line.
Not hurried, reserved towards rear 6-7Ls off the good pace, responded fairly entering straight, held by leaders always.
Chased leader in a race run at good tempo, came under pressure 600M, briefly led early straight, run ended 250M, no extra final stages.
Settled near last, over 8Ls behind leader in a race run at good tempo, brought wide for home, failed to close off.
Shifted across behind runners, raced at the rear 10Ls off the pace at one stage, pressed along 600M, made no real progress and only ran past beaten horses.
Chased leaders on inside, driven along 450M, outpaced passing 300M, soon out of contention.
Crossed to lead near 1400M, took them along at good pace, headed top of the straight, no extra 250, weakened to last.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead on the stands' rail, travelled well throughout, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, easily scored.
Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, kept on well in the final 400M to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, made some progress in the final 400M to take a place, no threat to the first two. (Lame left hind leg with a minor wound to the left hind pastern.)
Slightly slow out and bumped, raced at rear in the middle track, 4 lengths or so back, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader, 2 away from the stands' rail, similar position to 400M, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear in the middle track, passed some tired runners in the final 400M, never a threat to the first few.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently on the stands' side, ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong.
Made contact shortly after start, positioned behind midfield in the middle track, made no impression in the final 400M.
Bumped start, positioned in midfield in the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, peaked on run near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned behind midfield on the stands' side, made no impression in the final 400M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, showed limited response after passing 400M, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced at rear on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, blocked near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned behind midfield on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed no response, weakened thereafter.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off well to take 2nd, good debut.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take a place.
Began well, raced prominently but wide, took the lead 1050M, found rail near 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well to 200M, peaked and headed 150M, stayed on evenly to the line.
Shifted out on jumping and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, carried wider from 500M, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Fast into stride, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 950M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide at rear, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Bumped start, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight, eased final 150M.
Began well before being crossed & getting perfect run in midfield away from rail. Improved into tight running between horses at the 300m before dashing to lead at the 175m & racing clear late. Easy.
Raced in midfield away from rail. Shifted wider on cornering, sprinted quickly on straightening, unbalanced near the 300m before finishing off strongly to second thereafter. Clear of third.

Enjoyed good run just behind leading pair away from rail. Moved up within a neck of the lead inside the 200m mark before being joined & past quickly by the winner soon after. Fought on well late to hold third.

Didn't have the early speed of others & drifted back to race worse than midfield between runners. Continued in the second half on cornering, entered last section 4.5L from the lead before finishing off well in late stages.

Improved to midfield after first 300m but left racing 3 wide no cover throughout. Raced tight & bumped between runners at the 300m before battling on well late. Good effort given wide passage throughout.

Maintained position in midfield on the rail throughout. Stayed close to the inside on straightening, 3.5L from the lead entering last section, held up momentarily near the 200m before finishing off soundly in closing stages.

Strode forward from wide barrier, improved to race outside the leader by the 1000m. Moved up to share the lead soon after straightening before being joined by winner at the 175m & yielding a few lengths thereafter.

Began awkwardly & lost a length before improving along the rail, just worse than midfield throughout. Moved away from the rail on straightening, 4L from lead entering last section before making up a length to midfield late.

Steadied after the start & drifted back to race worse than midfield, three wide with cover. Continued on the outside on cornering, straightened just under 5L from lead but could make no further headway in dash to line.

Pushed forward before getting good run on leaders back. Moved away from the rail after straightening when only 1.5L from lead before peaking on effort at the 250m & weakening out thereafter. Well held.
Strode forward after start to speed to lead. Joined in the lead soon after straightening, peaked on run at the 250m before weakening out thereafter. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Had no early speed & raced near the tail throughout. Continued near the rear on cornering, 6L form the lead entering last section before weakening out further to be well beaten.
Not bustled after start & settled at the tail soon after. Was a clear last throughout middle stages, over 9L from the lead on cornering before making no headway in last section. Well beaten.

Steadied from wide gate & shifted behind runners to race with only one runner behind. Forced very wide on cornering when racing second last before weakening out sharply from the 250m to finish a long last.

Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, finished off strongly, just missed.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield early, 3 wide after entering the back straight, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M, made good progress thereafter, just missed frame.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made reasonable headway in straight.

Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 250M, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Bled.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, same position to turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 300M, overhauled 150M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden early, took box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Eased back, took rail, raced keenly, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 300M, dashed fairly.
Eased back, took rail, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Slow away, never competitive.
Raced in handy position on rail, asked for effort near 400M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, improved near 450M, worked home strongly.
Taken back at start, raced at back, improved near 450M, widest on straightening, made up some nice late ground, worked home solidly.
Wide and without cover until 1000M, settled behind leaders, fought well in the straight.
Sent forward, raced in box seat, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, finished well.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, placed pressure near 350M, worked home one-paced.
Travelled keenly in early and middle stages in the lead, one-paced in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, tried to improve near 400M, finished only one-paced.
Slow to begin, raced towards rear on rail, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then taken back, settled behind midfield, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden but no early speed, raced at tail, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, after 1000M was left wide and without cover, faded out in the straight.
Hard ridden to race handy to the lead away from the rail in third. Improved to second passing the 600m. Moved up to assume the lead passing the 100m mark before holding margin late.
Soft run in midfield on rail. Moved between runners after straightening before making steady late headway to close to second in final few strides.
Strode forward, shared early lead before taking outright lead after first furlong. Joined & headed by winner passing the 100m mark before caught in final few strides for second. Just behind.

Began well, shared early lead before racing leaders back from the 800m. Awkwardly placed & momentarily held up near the 200m, got clear & was finishing off well before again awkwardly placed & not ridden out to line.
Shifted across from wide gate after the first bend to race worse than midfield away from rail. Moved the widest runner on straightening before making solid late headway to not be far behind.
Raced in midfield away from rail, keen throughout middle stages. Only 2L from the lead entering the last section before yielding a further length in dash to line. No threat.

Steadied after start & sifted across to race in midfield on rail. Shifted wider when improving between runners nearing corner. Put under full pressure on straightening but offered limited response. (Not comfortable – rider).

Not fast to begin, steadied & shifted back worse than midfield on rail. Continued in second half entering last section, 5 lengths from the lead, failed to make any headway into margin in dash to line.

Restrained after the start & steadied back to share last place. Raced three wide when at the tail in middle stages. Continued wide & was the last horse to straighten, passed a few in late stages but will still well beaten.
Raced in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide on cornering before giving limited response in the straight. Weakened late to be well beaten.
Not fast to begin, restrained approaching first bend & settled at the tail. Continued near the rear entering last section & weakened a further few lengths to be beaten 10L.

Began awkwardly & settled to third last on rail. Drifted further back to share last place on the rail passing the 800m. Continued at the rear entering last section & weakened out further in straight. Last. (Lame post-race).
Bumped shortly after start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 600M, led by a length on turn, kept on very strongly in straight and scored.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from 700M, 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 600M, 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, stayed on for 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, found rail near 700M, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, 3 wide turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Began well from a tricky draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 700M, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Bumped start, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 600M, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Away with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased thereafter. (Lost right hind plate near 800M.) (Lame left front leg next day.)

Placing: PU
Comment: Very slowly away, soon pulled up. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled in midfield, along the rail, battled on to the line and score by 1L.
In one-out one-back position, closed off gamely, only to miss by 1L.
Rolled forward, along the rail, kept rolling and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward to take rail and led, stayed on but headed by first three inside final 50M.
At rear, along the rail, kept up until weakened at 150M.
At rear, 2 wide after 550M, ran on one paced.
Stayed in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Bumped start, midfield, remained one paced to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, saved no ground in the straight.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, in the starlight lost ground.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide with no cover after 500M, did not run on.
At rear, 2 wide, nothing in the straight.

Settled in forward of midfield in 6th about 3L off the pace, gained closer to 2L 5th over 700 metres out, improved further rounding home bend and into the straight, gained upper hand over 100 metres out.

Pressed forward from a wide gate travelling wide onto the 1200-metre bend, tracked the leader throughout back straight, hit the front turning for home but headed over 100 metres out, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled in last few, made progress to within 3L of pace in midfield when pace slackened in back straight, one of the widest swinging for home, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield on the rail, carried back in slackened pace in back straight, in last few turning for home, finished off well inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a low draw, obtained cover one back in 3rd passing the 1200 metres, remained in similar position into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon detached, recovered to reach the main body of the field when pace slackened on stables bend, commenced move 4-wide on top of home bend, ran on well down the centre of the track.

Pressed forward after a moderate start, settled some 2L back in 4th rounding first bend, became 6th midway down back straight, in similar position when 4-wide turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover in midfield before moving closer up in back straight, very wide turning in, kept on same pace without quickening and tightened near finish.

Moderate start, niggled at early before settling in 5th on the rail within 3L of pace, raced keenly in slow pace down back straight, saved ground turning in but tightened on rails early in straight, kept on without quickening.

Settled well behind on the rail from a wide gate, travelled keenly behind runners when pace slackened early in back straight, saved ground turning for home but badly crowded over 250 metres out, made no further impression.
Settled just worse than midfield, came under pressure from approaching home bend, found nothing in the straight. (Mucus)

Jumped fairly from a middle gate, took up running coming out of the first turn and steadied up the pace, held lead until headed into home straight, hampered when beaten early in straight and folded up quickly.
Settled in mid-division, travelled well into straight, challenged strongly from 300M, just prevailed.
Never far off the pace, pushed along 500M, responded well and vied for lead from 150M, just held.
Chased leaders, put in another consistent performance, kept on well final 300M for modest 3rd.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, closed off final 400M fastest, nearest finish.
Prominent early, raced keenly, improved to race outside leader 700M, driven out 300M, took narrow lead mid-straight, outsprinted final 100M.
Slowly away, dropped back from wide draw to race towards the rear, closed off steadily in straight but comfortably held by leaders.

Restrained to race behind midfield, swung home wideset, finished off mildly but never seriously threatened. (Jockey : instructed to ride more quietly as horse had not been finishing off its recent races.)
Began fairly, soon taken to the fence, settled behind mid-division in 8th spot, ridden along 400M, lacked finishing effort.
Steadied early stages and taken across behind runners, raced in last detached, 10Ls to make up 400M, made some progress but never near to challenge.
Settled down midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on same pace in straight, never threatened.
Tracked the pace, driven nearing 300M, failed to quicken.

Took outright lead early stages, pressed by rival from 700M, no extra passing 200M, weakened rapidly to finish last. (Jockey : off the bridle 700M when rival moved up to its outside, didn't finish off.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, commenced move after passing 750M, took the lead near 500M, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challenger, scored by a head.

Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield early, 4 wide after entering the back straight, commenced move after passing 750M, took the lead 600M, headed 500M, pressed winner all the way to the line, just missed.
Crowded start, positioned on rail in midfield, lost position 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover after 1200M, made contact near 600M, 2-1/2L turning in, finished off evenly.

Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, trapped very wide early, 2 wide from near 1200M, made contact near 600M, allowed rival to cross near 550M, a length back turning in, finished off evenly.
Away well, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, dropped to midfield near 600M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out abruptly at start and made contact, sat right behind the leader on rail, dropped to midfield after passing 600M, 3 lengths back not turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L in the middle stages, headed near 600M, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, same margin back to turn, made little progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, finished off one pace. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents)
Out in line, raced behind midfield on the inside, dropped to last on turn, showed nothing in straight.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, finished off strongly to score.

Jumped well from gate 13, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M, finished 2nd. (Jockey dropped whip near 150M.)
Away well, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide towards rear, bumped turning in, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 to 4 wide behind midfield, similar position in the middle stages, bumped turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1000M, challenged by rivals turning in, headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter, eased final 75M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Eased back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M to score.
At rear, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Pressed forward, took tail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M weakened.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden early, settled in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Pushed early, at back, 2-4 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Bumped start, eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, sat 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked and checked badly in straight, not tested.
Slow away, trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, no dash.
Bumped start, eased back early, however trapped very wide, moved forward 1500M to sit outside the leader, harmed by the fast tempo, soon out of fuel 350M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 250M, on heels 150M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 500M.
Ridden to take lead, travelled comfortably, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear on rail, improved near 600M, wide on straightening, gained nice ground in the straight, finished solidly.
Began awkwardly, raced behind midfield on rail, responded solidly in the straight. (See incident report)
After 1200M was left wide and without cover, improved to outside the lead near 1000M, placed pressure passing 550M, stayed on in the straight, finished well.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure but finished one-paced.
Raced in handy position, commenced to improve passing 700M, worked home one-paced.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, gave ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, tried to improve near 400M, made up some late ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort passing 700M, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced midfield on rail, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, no response in the straight, lame right front next day.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 500M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
On jumping stumbled badly and lost ground, then ridden forward, raced in front of midfield, faded out in the straight.

Steadied behind runners after start, raced worse than midfield. Moved wider & improved quickly passing 500m, sprinted quickly on straightening to assume lead at 275m, dashed clear, ridden quietly late. Held fast finisher.

Bumped & checked after start before shifting to the fence at tail.Continued at the rear, badly held up behind runners nearing corner, moved wider in straight, flew home final furlong to get within a length.Clear of third & unlucky.

Began awkwardly & lost a length before mustering speed to race in midfield between runners. Moved wider on cornering, dashed to second approaching the 250m before battling away to hold well beaten third.
Had a soft run in midfield on rail throughout. Moved away from inside on cornering, shifted out to clear running near the 200m before finishing off fairly to well beaten fourth.

Strode to be prominent after the start, raced in second early before getting cover in third by the 900m. Moved wider prior to straightening, closer to lead at 300m before peaking on effort late & weakening to midfield.

Raced on leaders back throughout. Badly held up behind leader from cornering until passing the 200m, before again being held up near the 100m. Got clear late & finished well when race was all over. Should have been closer.
Shifted behind runners after start & settled with only two runners behind. Improved position between runners approaching the bend before managing to maintain margin in final section to midfield.

Didn't have the speed of others despite being hard ridden at start & drifted back to race just worse than midfield on rail. Continued on the inside on cornering but failed to improve & was well beaten to midfield at finish.

Bumped heavily at start before being ridden forward when racing wide early. Covered extra ground when improving around runners to race outside leader passing the 1000m. Hard ridden on straightening before peaking at 250m.

Not bustled after start & steadied across to race at the rear away from the fence. Moved three wide with cover when after 400m. Hard ridden to improve form the 500m, but could only maintain margin. Well held.
Showed good early speed to cross the field & assume lead. Joined & headed soon after straightening & weakened out in the final furlong to be well beaten.

Bumped heavily at start before drifting back after being forced wide on first bend. Relegated to last near 500m when under hard riding. Yielded significant further ground in straight. (Mucus in trachea, must trial-poor perf).

Not fast to begin, hard ridden to hold midfield position before being left 3 wide with cover throughout. Began yielding ground from the 600m before weakening out further. Beaten a big margin. (Must trial-poor performance).

Bumped heavily between runners after start before being forced very wide at first corner & then racing 4 wide without cover in midfield. Began losing ground from the 600m, beaten a big margin. (Must trial-poor performance).
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well after turning in, just able to hold off the challenger late.
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the outside, a length back turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at tail, 11 lengths back turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Stumbled at start and bumped, raced at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped wide, no cover throughout, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight.
Rolled forward, along the rail, 400M shifted out, battled on to the line and score by 3/4L.
Rolled forward and led, along the rail, closed off gamely, only to miss by 3/4L.
Taken back, 2 wide initially, 3 wide with cover after 500M, saved ground, kept rolling and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward, 2 wide, saved ground but emptied the final 50M.
Midfield, 2 wide, near the 900M traveled keenly, kept up until weakened at 100M. (See Incident Report)
At rear, along the rail, ran on one paced.
Raced in midfield initially, rolled forward after 1000M and travelled wide without cover, weakened after 200M.
Taken back, along the rail, saved some ground and finished off evenly.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Midfield, wide but with cover, weakened final furlong.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not run on.
At rear, 3 wide with cover, nothing in the straight.
Midfield, 3 wide with cover, in the straight lost ground.

Began well from the one draw, settled over 2L back in joint 4th approaching first turn, renewed effort entering home straight, switched off the rail for a clear run over 200 metres out, quickened well to take charge close to home.

Pressed forward from the widest gate to take up running passing the 1000 metres, obtained rails run coming onto home bend, held over 1L break early in straight but collared inside the final 50 metres.
Moderate start, made headway on the rail before inconvenienced and shuffled backward passing the 1000 metres, angled out for a run entering home straight, finished off the race strongly.
Broke well before settling just worse than midfield, fought on under pressure and did best work late.
Well there, settled about 2L back in 3rd coming onto home bend, one-paced under pressure throughout home straight.
Settled in rear from a wide gate, commenced move upon straightening, ran on and did best work late.
Raced wide throughout, prominent early before drifting to 6th in forward of midfield, fought on steadily in straight without threatening while hanging.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, chased leader most of the way until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Last into straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Well there early stages before settling just some 3L back 2 wide in joint 4th, faded into straight.
Prominent when crowded early dropping to last few, made modest progress in straight without threatening.
Settled in midfield in 7th on the rail, faded under pressure in home straight.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, settled towards the rear, 4Ls to make up 400M, widest cornering, closed off strongly to get past leader near line.
Away quickly to take the lead, gave a kick passing 300M, kept on well to line, headed final stages.
Chased leaders along the 3-path, no cover from 700M, responded well in straight, worked home solidly for 3rd. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Began fairly, ended up in 4-wide position chasing leaders, no cover from 800M, battled on over final 300M without threatening leaders. (Jockey questioned re riding position.)
Reserved near last, waited with until 400M, stayed on without troubling first 3.
From wide draw rolled forward to race outside leader, placed under full pressure on straightening, unable to quicken and weakened over final 150M.
Bounded at the start losing ground, recovered to be chasing leaders passing 1000M, kept on same entering straight, no threat final 200M.
Jumped on terms, pushed along tracking the pace, keenly from 700M, tried hard on straightening but lacked further response.
Settled in midfield on the inside, nudged along 500M but never going the pace to challenge.
Soon taken to the fence, settled towards the rear, 4Ls to make up 400M, failed to run on in straight.
From wide draw slotted into a 2-wide spot in midfield, bustled along 450M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Began fairly, raced in the rear, failed to pick up on straightening, eased when no chance. (Bled.)
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by 2 to 3 lengths turning in, kept on very strongly in straight to score.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 450M, kept on evenly in straight.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and made some progress.

Jumped well, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 900M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 9 lengths or so back turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, raced 4 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away with them, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover after passing 700M, gradually dropped position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Away well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, stayed on for 2nd.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 3rd on line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off well thereafter to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight, no threat to the first few.

Began fairly from a tricky draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back to race 6 lengths back on the inside, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off one pace.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground to turn, no clear running early in straight, made no progress when clear thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently on the outside, 2 lengths back turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Away well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground throughout, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.

Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challenger.

Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 650M, 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3/4L back, same position on turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide from 750M, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, carried wider near 650M, 5 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced very wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, hung in 250M, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened 100M.
Eased to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
Eased at start, 2 wide at rear, on heels 600M, harmed by the slow tempo, dash well 200M.
Eased at start, checked 600M, took rail, lack room 300M, little dash.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, little dash.
Checked start, at back, on the fence, severely checked 600M, dashed well 150M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, however trapped 3 wide, moved forward 700M, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to obtain the lead, clocked slow sectionals, soon emptied 350M.
Began awkwardly then taken back, travelled comfortably, commenced to improve passing 700M, quickened passing 100M, worked home strongly to score.

Crowded at start then taken back, raced at rear, near the 800M was taken wider and without cover, near 700M was steadied to obtain cover, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, gained nice late ground, finished nicely.
Settled in box seat, commenced to improve passing 800M, responded nicely in the straight, finished well.
Settled in front of midfield, mid-race improved passing 1000M, took lead rounding the Home Turn, gave ground near 50M, rider question tactic.
Settled behind midfield, mid-race improved near 900M, one-paced in the straight.
Hard ridden to take lead, was challenged passing 900M, asked for effort passing 450M, limited response in the straight.
Raced midfield, improved to outside the lead passing 1300M, came under pressure passing 800M, no response in the straight.
Near 2000M was checked when crowded for room, settled towards rear on rail, tried to improve passing 700M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, dropped back passing 800M, no response in the straight.
Slow out and raced at rear, moved forward passing 1800M, after the 1300M was left racing wide and without cover in handy position, weakened after 700M, finished tailed out, must trial.
Had good position in midfield away from rail soon after the start. Moved wider on cornering, made gradual headway to share the lead at the 75m before digging deep in closing stages to score narrowly.

No speed after start & drifted back to second last. Ridden along to improve passing the 700m, before making steady headway nearing corner. Shifted wider at 250m before finishing strongly in concluding stages to just miss.

Showed early speed to improve & race outside leader before easing to leaders back after first section. Moved away from rail & closer to lead near the 700m. Moved up to share the lead at 75m before caught in closing stages.

Ridden forward after the start & improved to race in third place away from rail. Moved wider passing the 750m, improved to assume lead passing the 600m. Continued in lead until being passed at the 75m. Close behind.

Raced in midfield away from rail. Continued in midfield entering the last section, made continual steady headway in the straight until being awkwardly placed near heals in concluding stages. Not beaten far.

Began well before steadying & racing on leaders back in early stages. Shuffled back to midfield after first section. Continued on rail, only 2.5L from lead entering passing the 400m before failing to make any further headway.
Steadied from wide gate & shifted back to race at the tail. Continued at the rear entering the last section before passing a few when making some headway to midfield. Never in race.

Had no speed after the start & drifted back to race third last on rail. Shared last position entering last section before moving the widest runner on straightening, passed a few tiring ones late but was well held.

Not bustled at start & shifted across to race worse than midfield away from rail. Moved three wide with cover & improved to be only 3L from lead in midfield by the 600m. Began yielding ground from the 500m & was well beaten.

Had no speed after start before ridden hard to hold midfield position on rail. Shuffled further back mid-race before coming under heavy pressure passing the 600m. Failed to make any improvement & was well beaten
Showed speed to lead shortly after start. Headed in the lead passing the 600m before straightening only a length from lead. Weakened out sharply in the final furlong to beat only one runner home.
Steadied from widest gate to race near after start before improving wide, around runners to move to 4th by the 700m. Came under heavy pressure at 600m before weakening out to last in the straight.
Bumping on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, scored by a head.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly in straight, missed 3rd on line.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out near 500M, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Bumping on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Bled.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace. (Blood in trachea.)
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, ran home gamely to score by 2-3/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly to the line to hold onto 2nd.
Rolled forward and raced outside the lead, 2 wide initially, took the lead after 400M and on rail at turns, ran on.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, swung wide on straightening, saved ground and ran on fairly.
At rear, 2 wide, saved some ground in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on one paced.
Midfield, along the rail, saved minor ground and weakened after 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, run ended after 200M.
Midfield initially, rolled forward after 1050M, wide with no cover, pretty one paced.
At rear, along the rail, swung wide on straightening, weakened late.
Rolled forward to lead, along the rail, in the straight lost ground.

Placing: UR
Comment: Unseated Rider
Began well before settling over 2L back in 5th, saved ground on the rail turning in, quickened to hit the front over 150 metres out, won readily.
Worked his way forward from a wide gate to lead early in back straight, obtained rails run in the front over 700 metres out, led the field until headed over 150 metres out.
Began moderately, soon recovered to midfield in 7th, gained 6th rounding home bend, saved ground entering home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide in last few from the widest gate, trailed the field near the rail from the Rock, saved ground turning in, switched in for a run 200 metres out, did best work late.
Settled not far off in 4th, went 3-wide rounding home bend and wider into the straight, kept on steadily without quickening.

Led early stages, narrowly headed on the rail turning into back straight, remained one back rounding home bend, switched out to challenge entering home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, prominent before tightened on the rail twice and shuffled backward to 8th about 900 metres out, saved ground on the rail making home bend, ran home one-paced.
Very slowly away, recovered to 9th turning into back straight, only kept on at the one pace under pressure in the run to the line. (See Racing Incidents)
Pressed forward from a wide gate to close-up 2nd racing mainly 3-wide, became 3rd rounding home bend, dropped further back after straightening
Soon taken back to last few, difficult to settle early in back straight, made no impression in the run to the line. (Questioned for disappointing
Settled 3-wide in midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, faded in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Moved up to chase leader, driven to lead nearing 200M, kept on well to line.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, responded well on straightening, chased winner home but always held.
Lost ground when throwing its head in the air as the start was effected, settled towards the rear, ran on mildly to go 3rd near 100M, unable to trouble first 2.
From wide draw restrained to race in the rear, 8Ls off leader home turn, widest into straight, ran on well to take 4th close home.
In mid-division, advanced to 4th 400M, lacked finishing effort in the straight, held ground final 250M.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, settled down 3-wide towards the rear, ran home fairly, no impression.
From wide draw dropped back to race at the rear, 7Ls off the pace 400M, made limited progress, never troubled leaders.
Away quickly from draw 1, led uncontested, caught nearing 200M, no extra towards the finish.
In mid-division, raced wide without cover, kept on same pace on straightening, no threat at any stage.
Jumped on terms, held up along the fence behind midfield, failed to pick up turning home, never involved.
Settled down in 4th 4Ls off the leader, couldn't go on in the straight, weakened badly from 250M to finish last.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, finished off very well to score on line.
Began smartly from gate 10, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, finished off very well to take 2nd, just missed.
Away with them, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, travelled keenly after passing 700M, a bit closer not turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Began fairly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed and weakened final 100M.
Fast into stride, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back on turn, taken very wide in straight and made minor progress.
Began well, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
