Began smartly from gate 13, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 900M, travelled well in the middle stages, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead after passing 100M, kept on very well to score.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, kept on very well after turning in, peaked and headed near 100M, finished 2nd.
Clean jump, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover after passing 900M, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Slowly away and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider on turn, made some progress in straight.
Away well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Bounded in the air on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced very wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Trapped 3-4 wide in midfield, closed off strongly 400M to score.
At back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Took rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Pressed forward, sat outside the leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on until 100M weakened.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, weakened 300M.
Midfield, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 4-2, little dash when clear.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Midfield, along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 4-2, no dash when clear.
Slow away, at rear on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
In front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, hung out badly, emptied 400M.
Never competitive.
Sent forward, travelled nicely, placed pressure near 300M, worked home strongly to score.
Ridden along from wide barrier, settled outside the lead, improved on straightening, issued challenge near 100M, responded solidly and missed by SH.
Hard ridden for some distance after start, raced behind midfield, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
On jumping was crowded, settled in box seat, fought well in the straight.
Settled towards rear, asked for effort passing 500M, gained nice ground in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced in front of midfield, placed pressure near 500M, kept on to the line.
Settled behind leaders, raced greenly, one-paced in the straight.
Began awkwardly, made the turn after the 900M awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, after the 900M was left racing wide and without cover, limited response in the straight.
Jumped sharply, urged along to push forward, wide and without cover throughout outside the leaders, gave ground near 200M.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced at tail, no response in the straight.
On jumping was crowded, settled towards rear on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, no response in the straight.
Raced greenly at rear, widest on straightening, never in it.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, faded out in the straight.

No early speed & ridden along to race to midfield before being left wide & without cover from 800m. Shunted six horses wide on cornering before dashing up to take lead at the 275m. Continued to dig deep late to win.

Steadied & crossed soon after the start to race just behind leading group away from the rail. Momentarily held up behind leader on straightening. Improved between runners at the 300m before finishing well to hold 2nd.

Strode forward, raced in 4th position before shifting down to rail to race on leaders back from half-way. Shifted away from rail on cornering, moved up to share the lead at 350m before continuing on strongly in late stages.

Not bustled after start & drifted back to race just worse than midfield on the inside. Held up around the home turn well still well back before shifting wider at 350m & finishing strongly in last furlong to closing fourth.
Stumbled at start, shifted across behind runners to worse than midfield. Moved wider with cover around the home bend before finishing off well in the last section to be just behind. Not beaten far.
Steadied from wide barrier before shifting back to last in early stages. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before passing a few runners when finishing off steadily from the rear.

No early speed before being allowed to drift back to last after first section. Was a clear last on cornering, 5L from the lead before shifting to be the widest runner & finishing off strongly to midfield in late stages.

Pushed forward after start, raced 4 wide no cover before improving to assume narrow lead near 1000m. Raced outside leader from 700m. Joined soon after straightening before weakening out in the final furlong. Well held.

Steadied after start before being ridden along to hold position near the rear. Moved wider at the 600m, second widest on cornering with only one runner behind. Passed a few tiring horses late but was never likely.

Steadied after start to race in midfield away from rail. Eased wider passing the 600m before being forced 5 wide on straightening. Moved up to share the lead at 300m before peaking soon after & weakening last furlong.

Mustered speed to race just behind leading group before drifting back to midfield position on rail. Moved away from rail passing the 600m, maintained position relative leaders until the 300m before weakening out thereafter.

Maintained midfield position between runners throughout early & middle stages. Continued between runners on cornering, only 2.5L from lead entering last section before offering nothing in the final 300m & weakening out.

Ridden along to hold rail position before improving to lead after first furlong. Headed in lead at 1000m before regaining lead near 700m. Joined soon after entering last section before yielding significant ground final 250m.

Strode forward after start to be prominent before settling in third place away from rail after 600m. Shunted four wide on cornering before peaking at the 400m & yielding significant ground in the last section. Last.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, found a 2 wide spot near 750M, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped wide in midfield, no cover throughout, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd. (Lame left front leg next day.)

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, peaked and headed final 50M, missed 2nd on line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 5 lengths back, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, not enough room near 200M, made good progress thereafter to be nearest on line.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, kept to inside after straightening, no enough room near 300M, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.

Shifted in at start and bumped, trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 1000M, positioned 2 wide in 2nd on turn, hit the front early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Commenced well, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, kept on well to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, challenged turning in, headed early in straight, eased final 300M. (Bled.)
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover initially, 2 wide after 650M, battled on to the line and score by 1-1/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide after 850M, saved some ground and ran on fairly to hold onto 2nd.
Rolled forward and took the lead, along the rail after 900M, hold on but weakened in the last 100M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground and ran on fairly.
At rear, 3 wide with cover, made ground in the straight late.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, ran on one paced in the straight. (See Incident Report)
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
In midfield, 3 wide with no cover, was one paced.
Seated behind leader after 900M, along the rail, hardly improved.
At rear, along the rail, made no impression.
Raced in worse than midfield, rounding the Home Turn hung out and lost ground, must trial around a bend.
Raced in midfield initially, rolled forward to race outside the lead after 900M, lost ground in the straight. (See Incident Report)
At rear, 2 wide, not competitive in the straight.

Ridden forward before taken back to 3L 5th over 1000 metres out, commenced move entering the straight, fought on dourly to gain slender advantage inside the 200 metres, just prevailed in the bobbing of heads.
Pressed forward to join the leader, hit the front briefly early in straight before headed by eventual winner inside the 200 metres, fought on well in the ding-dong battle only to be pipped at post

Broke well from a wide gate and soon taken back for rails run, trailed the field before improving steadily from the 1200 metres to reach 5th just over 2L back on top of home bend, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Settled in 6th in worse than midfield, became 7th and further back coming onto home bend, fought on steadily despite hanging early in straight, never threatening.
Settled in rear, became last passing the 1200 metres, went wide into home straight, fought on under pressure to snatch 5th inside the 100 metres.
Soon took up running setting a sound pace, soon headed upon straightening and faded gradually under pressure.
Began well, travelled awkwardly when snatched back, just over 2L back in 4th approaching first bend and in similar position turning for home, dropped out shortly after straightening.
Moderate start before gaining steadily to 3rd some 2L back approaching the first turn, remained similar turning into home straight, folded up quickly shortly after straightening.
Tracked the pace early stages when pace was steady, moved up from 1200M to press the pace, quickened to lead inside 400M, went clear mid-straight, kept on well to the line.
In touch, 4th making the home turn, about 3Ls to make up on eventual winner Exultant at 400M, fought on well to be nearest finish.
Settled 5th of 7, just over 3Ls off the pace at 800M, ran on mildly in straight, not reach first 2.
From outside barrier shifted across to race at the back, 5Ls off the pace making home turn, stayed on moderately over final 400M, no threat.
Crossed to the lead from 1700M, led steadily until 1200M when pressed by rival, under pressure 600M to hold its position, headed inside 400M, no extra final 200M. (Mucus.)
Chased the pace 2-wide, under pressure to keep up when pace quickened 700M, soon beaten turning home.
Towards the rear, caught racing wide and no cover in a 7 runner race, wide into straight, didn't finish off.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, slightly improved along the rail on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Away well, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning, kept on well in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, not enough room early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out and made contact near 600M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.

Began well, sent forward to race prominently, slightly taken back 900M, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back in the middle stages, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, travelled keenly in the middles stages, made contact 600M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.

Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide early, slightly taken back 900M, raced 3w with no cover, a length back in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide from 750M, half length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, trapped very wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, peaked turning in, headed and weakened early in straight, eased final 250M. (Blood in trachea.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score on line.
Shifted in abruptly at start, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped 4 very wide, 2 lengths back, 3 wide from near 1000M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 600M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 200M, showed little response thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths back, closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and made little progress.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.

Fast into stride, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, similar position in the middle stages, showed good response after turning in, took the lead near 100M, kept on well to hold off the rival, scored by a head.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, same position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Away well from a wide draw, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, gradually moved forward after passing 1600M, positioned 1 out 1 back from 1300M, challenged the leader 650M, peaked turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 7 lengths behind the leader, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider after passing 400M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Made contact at start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
Pushed to keep up behind midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, drifted away 250M to score.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader, not suited by the fast pace, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Settled in front of midfield along the rails, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 3rd.
At back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, progressed steadily when clear.
Hard ridden to cross in front of midfield, 2 wide, held ground in straight.
Slow away, at back, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Slow away, at rear, suited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200M.
Box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, soon weakened 300M.
Eased at start, 2 wide at back, favoured by the fast pace, held up most straight, ran on ok when clear.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, suited by the fast tempo, attempted to made ground around the field 4-5 wide from 600M, no progress.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 2-3 wide in front of midfield, emptied 350M.
Raced in box seat, asked for effort near 400M, quickened near 100M to score.
Took lead without asking, placed pressure near 400M, fought nicely in the straight.
At the start was steadied when crowded for room, settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 400M, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced in handy position, placed pressure passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Until near 900M wide and without cover, settled outside the lead, worked home one-paced.
Near 900M was left racing wide and without cover in handy position, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, moved to midfield passing 800M, 3 wide with cover, tried to improve passing 600M, wide rounding the Home Turn, limited response in the straight.
Slow out then taken back, raced towards rear on rail, asked for effort near 400M, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly, checked away from heels after 1000M, mid-race move passing 700M, very wide rounding the Home Turn, limited response in the straight.
Raced at back, tried to improve passing 600M, widest on straightening, no response when asking in the straight.
Raced at tail, tried to improve passing 700M, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Began awkwardly then taken back, 3 wide with cover, no response.
Steadied from widest gate, shifted back to last. Continued in last place when cornering very wide before sprinting very quickly to move to lead passing the 100m & drawing away impressively.
Showed early speed to stride to the lead. Raced a length clear at the furlong marker before being quickly joined by winner at the 100m. Battled strongly to hold second, clear of third.

Steadied after start & raced near the rear. Commenced to improve from the 500m when racing very wide approaching bend. Hung in sharply on straightening, sprinted well to move to third at the 150m & held that position late.

Raced on the leaders back early before being steadied when keen near the 900m & drifting back to midfield. Drifted further back approaching the corner before finishing off steadily to move to forth in the closing stages.
Had limited early speed & raced worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail on cornering when third from last before finishing off only steadily between runners in last section.

Hard ridden at start to challenge for lead, raced 5 wide early stages before shifting outside the leader by the 600m. Came under immediate pressure on straightening before weakening a few lengths to midfield in last furlong.

Shifted across after first bend to race in midfield between runners. Drifted slightly further back after half-way before cornering near tail. Badly checked soon after straightening before running to midfield late. Had excuse.

Ridden forward after start before eventually getting cover when drifting back behind leading trio near the 600m. Came under hard riding entering the last section before yielding a few lengths in last 250m.

Ridden forward to race prominently before being crossed after first bend & racing just behind leaders. Shifted & raced on leaders back near 700m. Came under hard riding at 450m before weakening significantly last furlong.

Crowded on jumping before settling near the tail between runners. Continued at the back on cornering, checked & lost ground near the 250m before untested in late stages. Probably should have been closer.

Hard ridden & improved to challenge for prominent position early. Continued to work hard after the first bend when 3 wide before settling behind leading pair. Emptied out on straightening & weakened out sharply in last 250m.

Ridden forward early but was caught wide at first bend before easing back to midfield, 3 wide with cover. Continued in second half on straightening before being badly checked 250m & eased out of race thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Commenced well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 750M, 1-3/4L back on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, closed off well without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Began well, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made little progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Commenced well, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide with no cover from 750M, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began very awkwardly from the widest draw, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried wider from 750M, moved a bit closer after passing 600M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, battled on to the line and scored by 1-1/4L.
Settled behind the leader after 1100M, along the rail, closed off gamely, only to miss by 1-1/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, save ground and ran on well to the line.
Rolled forward, along the rail, stayed on but emptied in final 75M.
Rolled forward, along the rail after 1200M, stayed on until weakened at 50M.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on fairly inside final 100M once cleared.
Midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
At rear initially, attempted to roll forward and travelled wide with no cover after 650M, remained one paced to the line.
Bumped start, midfield, 2 wide, saved no ground in the straight.
At rear, along the rail, did not run on.
At rear, 2 wide, didn't improve.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, nothing in the straight. (Blood in trachea)

Broke well from the one gate, settled in midfield in 6th on the rail some 3L back, obtained a clear run shortly after straightening and quickened well under pressure inside the final 200 metres to take charge 50 metres out.
Settled in last from a wide gate and waited with, trailed the field into home straight, did not find much room 200 metres out, finished off the race well to snatch 2nd near the line.
Amongst the leaders early stages before taken one back to 3rd on the rails, remained same into home straight and hit the front on the rail inside the 200 metres, found no extra when headed late.
Amongst the leaders early, drifted back to 5th just over 2L back shortly afterwards, remained similar into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Travelled wide without cover in midfield early stages, improved steadily down the back straight to join the leader passing the 600 metres, held every chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres.
Ridden early, held narrow lead on the rail until joined into home straight, kept on until finding no extra to hold place inside the final 100 metres,
Ridden early from a wide gate, moved up to chase in 2nd turning into back straight, gradually drifted one back leaving the Rock, unable to quicken to challenge in home straight.
Jumped moderately settling in rear, shifted wide into home straight, produced good late impression in the centre of the track.

Moderate start, soon recovered to just worse than midfield on the rail, travelled keenly approaching the Rock, saved ground rounding home bend to reach within 2.5L of the leader, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Began well but soon taken back to last few travelling keenly 700 metres out, awkwardly placed behind runners early in straight, produced some late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, travelled keenly in midfield in 7th, switched wide for a run entering home straight, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.

Broke well to share early pace, soon taken back to rear of midfield but remained racing 3-wide without cover, lost position sharply inside the 400 metres swinging widest into home straight, made no impression. (Lame next day)
From draw 1 enjoyed a rail run in a position just ahead of midfield, moved up to 3rd 450M, responded well in straight to lead near 50M and fended off runner up close home.
Reserved behind midfield, 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on well to finish nearest on the line.
Positively ridden from wide draw, crossed to rail 1200M, tracked leader into the straight, led mid-straight, all out, caught by first 2 final stages
Given a quiet ride, settled near the rear 7Ls back, made steady progress from 400M, got up for 4th late.
Held up on the inside, 5Ls back in mid-division, urged along 500M, ran on moderately in the straight but always held by leaders.
Began fairly, moved up to the lead passing 1200M, set even pace to straight, headed near 200M, faded towards the line.
Taken across behind runners, settled near last 7Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly final 300M, not troubled leaders.
Chased leaders in 4th, pushed along 500M but not quickened, well held by leaders in the straight.
Held up in midfield 2-wide, lost ground when severely hampered by a weakening rival 450M, kept on fairly in straight, never threatened.
Began awkwardly, settled down 3-wide in midfield, no cover from 1000M, couldn't go on in the straight, soon behind.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled 8-9Ls back at the rear, failed to run on passing 400M. (Lame LH leg / Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Caught wide first turn, strode forward to track leader, commenced to give ground rapidly 500M, heavily eased in the straight. (Bled.)
Quickly into stride, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Commenced well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead near 200M, peaked and headed 75M, stayed on for 3rd.

Moderately away from gate 11, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 900M but still 3 wide, a length back turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide with cover from 600M, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Clean jump, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, bumped near 200M, ran on one pace thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, challenged by rival turning in, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and crowded, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, carried wider after passing 450M, weakened early in straight.

Bumped and unbalanced at start, positioned 1-1/4L behind the leader, ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, took the lead near 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, peaked and headed 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, made contact near 400M, hard ridden after passing 300M, kept on well until 100M, no extra thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, made contact near 400M, hard ridden near 300M, showed limited response, weakened final 100M.
Pushed to secure box seat, kicked away 250M to score.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 2 wide behind midfield, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased back, trapped 4 wide throughout, made good ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Eased back, 2 wide, on heels 250M, made ground 150M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast pace, out of fuel 150M.
Took rail and lead easily hung on until 150M weakened quickly.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail, checked 800M, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Trapped 3 wide, never better than midfield.
Sent forward, raced comfortably in the lead, passing 1000M was challenged then niggled to maintain its position, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, wide on straightening, fought well in the straight.
Taken back at start, awkwardly placed passing 400M, placed pressure near 400M, finished one-paced.
Settled midfield, improved passing 1000M to outside the lead, 3 wide rounding the Home Turn, gave ground near 200M.
Raced behind the lead, improved to outside the lead passing 1000M, weakened near 300M.
Raced in midfield on stand side rail. Shifted in to clear running near the 300m before finishing strongly to strike the lead near the 100m before drawing clear in late stages.
Raced in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Responded strongly when asked passing the 300m, improving to second soon after before being over-run by winner late. Good debut.
Showed early speed to assume the lead. Drifted across to the stand side rail after the first furlong. Continued in the lead until being joined at past near the 100m. Held third.
Bumped at start before racing in midfield early. Improved steadily to race third entering the last section before finishing off fairly to hold fourth.

Showed some speed after the start before settling in midfield on the back of the leader. Improved to second place entering the last section, only a length from the lead, before yielding a few lengths in last furlong.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Finished off steadily in last section to hold midfield position.

Crowded & raced near the tail early before drifting further back in middle stages, entering last section 7 lengths from the lead. Drifted in towards the center of track before running on nicely to midfield from the rear.
Bumped at start before racing in midfield nearer to center of track. Continued in midfield but could offer no more in the final 250m & gave a few lengths in closing stages.
Crowded at start & raced at the rear throughout. Never involved.
Restrained after the start, raced near rear before being inconvenienced passing the 800m. Continued over 9L from lead entering last section & never featured.
Showed speed from the start, racing prominently in early stages. Came off the bridle entering last section when less than 2L from the lead before weakening out sharply in final furlong. Well held.

Began only fairly and raced worse than midfield nearer to stand side rail. Continued last of the main bunch, 4.5 lengths from the lead entering last section before weakening out further in last 300m. Well beaten.
Raced in midfield nearer to middle of track. Ridden along from the 400m mark when over 4L from the lead before weakening out sharply in last furlong. Long last.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Commenced to buck for a considerable distance near the 800m & was retired out of the race soon after. (Must trial).

Made contact and unbalanced at start, raced in 2nd, a length behind the leader, similar position on turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed good response, hit the front 200M, kept on well to the line and scored.

Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, angled out 550M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 200M, made good progress thereafter to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well without threatening.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide with cover from 700M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Away with them, raced 2 wide, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few. (Jockey dropped whip near 350M.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, bumped and unbalanced near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened steadily final furlong.
Commenced well from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover from 950M, moved closer after passing 800M, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Took keen hold, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened after passing 300M.
Raced next to the leader, along the rail, worked home nicely and scored.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, closed off strongly in straight to take 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved ground and ran on well to the line.
Rolled forward, 2 wide initially and along the rail after 450M, continued on nicely to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, showed some dashes in the straight and saved ground.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with no cover, ran on one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, wide but with cover, show no turn on foot.
At rear, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight.
At rear, along the rail, did not feature.
Rolled forward, wide initially, 2 wide after 600M, lost ground in the straight. (Lame left front)
Midfield, 2 wide, nothing in the straight.
Settled about 4L back on the rail 5th or 4th, gained closer rounding home bend, quickened well to hit the front 200 metres out, won readily.

Travalled keenly just worse than midfield before steadied and shuffled backward towards the rear 1300 metres out, renewed effort when very wide rounding home bend, finished off the race well down the centre of home straight.
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th, gained closer to pace just over 3L back rounding home bend, 4th upon straightening, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear of midfield, improved steadily under pressure early in straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Taken back sharply for rails run from the widest gate, travelled in last few to the straight, baulked for a run over 200 metres out before making good late impression closing stages.
Crowded at start and soon dropped to last few, remained similar to the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.

Took up running from a wide gate, obtained rails run 1300 metres out setting a fast pace in the second quarter, maintained over 2L advantage into home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Moderate start, travelled wide and well behind, came under pressure from around home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well, settled just over 3L back in 4th, drifted back to 5th rounding home bend and went 4-wide into the straight, made no further impression after straightening.

Began in last few travelling wide throughout, pulled his way forward to midfield in 7th approaching the 1200 metres, lost position rounding home bend, made no impression in the straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Niggled at early stages before settling just worse than midfield on the rail, made no impression in home straight.
Prominent on the rail to the 400 metres, folded up quickly.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Pressed forward from a wide gate settling some 1L back in 2nd, came under pressure passing the 600 metres, soon weakened.
Began fairly, settled near last, moved up to be 5th top of straight, clear run from 300M, responded strongly to lead nearing 100M, held off runner up to win in class record time.
Steadied from the outside barrier, raced at the rear 6Ls off the pace, moved closer nearing home straight, ran on well final 400M, just held.
Restrained near the rear early stages, moved up to be track leaders from 1100M, travelled well into straight, led from 350M until caught by first 2 nearing 100M, weakened.
Tracked leaders early stages, in 5th spot from 1200M, swung wide 550M, ran on fairly, no threat to first 3 final 150M.
Restrained on jumping from draw 1, settled down midfield along the fence, shuffled back to near last nearing top of straight, gave limited response.
Crossed to the lead 1700M, led them along at good pace, headed inside 400M, no extra and weakened final 200M.
Caught wide no cover from 1700M, strode forward to race outside the lead 1200M, driven along 500M, not quickened, faded away mid-straight.
Towards the rear, settled 7th of 9, brought wide 600M, couldn't finish off, eased off mid-straight when no chance. (Jockey reported respiratory noise.)
Took up a prominent spot tracking leaders, left flat footed when pace quickened 700M, gave ground from 300M to finish last. (Jockey unable to detect any obvious abnormalities.)
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Bumped start, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 9 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced towards rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 500M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 9 to 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away, trapped very wide in midfield, slightly taken back after 1000M, found cover near 700M, 7 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, a length behind the leader, 2 wide on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Shifted in abruptly at start and bumped, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 900M, carried wider after passing 500M, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Away well, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, not enough room early in straight, cleared 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover from 550M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, raced prominently but trapped very wide, 2 wide from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress early in straight, made contact near 150M, not ridden thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.) (Lame left front leg next day.)
Stumbled at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, checked near 700M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide from 600M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final 200M.

Strode forward, improved to race in third after first 400m. Just over 2L from the lead entering last section before making continual steady ground to strike lead in final 100m. Drew away in closing stages to win comfortably.

Hard ridden after the start & improved to race second, well behind big margin leader. Continued 4L behind leader passing the 800m, Moved up to assume lead at the 350m before being caught inside the final 100m. Held second.
Raced in midfield on the rail throughout. Shifted back in towards the rail on straightening before closing off nicely in last 300m to move to third place in closing stages.

Began well before being steadied to race in midfield away from the rail. Eased three wide nearing the final corner, entered last section 3 lengths from the lead before finishing off steadily to fourth. Not beaten far.

Shifted behind runners after the start but was left racing wide throughout. Continued in second half, nearly 10L from the lead nearing half-way. Made solid late headway to midfield in final section from rearward position.

Improved position after first furlong to race third, before steadying to get cover by the 900m. Dashed up to be a length from the lead soon after straightening before peaking on run at the furlong & yielding a length late.

Crowded & steadied at start before being left three wide without cover in midfield. Continued wide passage in middle stages, straightened 6L from lead before making up a length or two when holding midfield position to line.

Began well, ridden forward to lead. Travelled keenly in middle stages when maintaining 4 length lead at half-way. Continued a length clear on straightening before being headed at the 350m & weakening out in last furlong.

Began fairly before racing worse than midfield between runners. Raced keenly before being tightened for room & losing ground passing the 800m. Cornered well back before making up a few lengths to midfield after incident.

Began only fairly & crowded before racing worse than midfield, wide with cover before shifting closer to rail near 900m. Over 6L from the lead entering last section before failing making any noteworthy headway thereafter.

Raced to midfield soon after start before being steadied away from heals & drifting further back passing the 900m. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before weakening out in last section. Well held.

Crowded after the start before shifting behind runners & racing on inside rail. Improved along rail approaching the 900m before being badly checked near the 800m & lost considerable ground. Didn't run on but had excuse.
Steadied after the start & shifted back to last. Continued near the rear, straightening over 10 lengths from the lead before failing to make any headway in dash to line. Well beaten.
Bumped at start before steadying & racing second from last. Hard ridden prior to straightening when a long way from lead before weakening out further to be a long last.

Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, found a 2 wide spot near 650M, angled out after passing 400M, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted in abruptly at start and made heavy contact, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, trapped very wide slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 900M, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, showed some response in the run home.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Took rail easily, led at fast sectionals, made all.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Eased to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, blocked 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed early, 2 wide in front of midfield, just held ground in straight.
Took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 250M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, no dash.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, no progress.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Settled midfield on rail, battled well in the straight, finished strongly to score.
At the start was bumped and lost ground, settled behind midfield, widest on straightening, quickened passing 150M, finished solidly.
Ridden forward, settled in handy position on rail, responded solidly in the straight when asked for effort.
Ridden along to take lead, placed pressure on straightening, fought well in the straight.
Settled towards rear on rail, asked for effort near 350M, continued to gain ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, worked home one-paced.
Moderate start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wide on straightening, finished one-paced.
Hard ridden forward, after 1000M improved to an insufficient room and was checked near 800M, settled in front of midfield, tried to improve near 500M, finished fairly.
Jumped well and sent forward, settled behind leaders, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged along to race in forward position, faded out passing 200M.
After 1000M was severely hampered, raced midfield, weakened near 100M.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, no response throughout.

Steadied after start & raced a clear last. Niggled along throughout middle stages to hold position at tail. Moved wider passing 500m, clear last on straightening before motoring home last furlong to snare lead on post.

Raced on the leaders back through early & middle stages. Moved away from the rail approaching the 400m, improved to assume narrow lead near the 50m mark before being caught right in line by fast finishing winner.
Steadied, allowed to drift back to race second last. Moved wider & commenced to improve from the 600m before making continual late headway in the straight to be narrowly beaten.

Strode forward to assume early lead before being challenged & headed momentarily in middle stages. Regained outright lead at the 700m, raced over a length clear entering last section before being caught inside last 50m.

Raced in midfield away from rail before shifting down to the rail near 600m. Steadied & lost a length near 450m when close to heels before getting clear running near the inside on straightening & finishing off steadily to midfield.

Settled in good position between runners behind leading trio. Lost some ground when checked behind tiring runner at 550m before shifting into clear running on cornering. Finished off steadily in straight without threatening.

Steadied after start & drifted back towards the rear. Entered last section with only one runner behind, 7L from the lead. Stayed close to the inside after straightening & passed a few to midfield but was never a threat.

Steadied when crowded at the start & settled just worse than midfield away from rail. Maintained position 5L from the lead entering last section when racing between runners before making no headway in straight. Well held.

Strode forward from wide gate to race prominently before being left wide but with cover throughout. Ridden along approaching the 400m before peaking on effort soon after straightening. Gave significant ground in straight.

Bumped & lost some ground after the start before settling worse than midfield on rail. Hard ridden from the 700m before commencing to give ground from the 550m. Weakened out further in the straight & was well beaten.

Pushed forward after start, moved to narrow lead away from rail near the 1100m before racing outside leader from the 700m. Began yielding ground from the 600m & weakened out significantly in last section.

Pushed forward after the start but was left racing three wide without cover throughout. Continued wide passage, only a length form the lead at the 650m before weakening out significantly from the 600m. Long last.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, ran along at strong tempo, led by 1-1/2L turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position to turn, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 400M, taken wide in straight and made good progress to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start, taken back to race 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.
Missed the start, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still 9 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Crowded start, trapped very wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped and unbalanced at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 2 wide after entering the back straight, weakened from 450M, emptied early in straight.
Rolled forward, along the rail after 700M, ran home gamely to score by 2-1/4L.
Seated behind the leader, along the rail, ran on fairly to the line to hold onto 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 600M, made steady ground and closed off fairly. (See incident report)
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, showed some dashes in the straight but emptied after 150M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, saved some ground and kept on until the 150M.
At rear, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with no cover, did not improve in the straight.
At rear, along the rail, brushed the rail at 450M, did not feature.
At rear, 2 wide, remained at the rear and did not threaten.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, nothing in the straight.
Began well to lead from a low draw, ceded advantage for one back position coming onto first bend, came to tackle the leader entering home straight, gained upper hand over 100 metres out.
Ridden forward from a wide gate to take up running before the first bend, obtained rails run passing the 1200 metres and led until narrowly headed over 100 metres out.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled in forward of midfield in 5th just over 3L back in back straight, became 6th approaching the Rock, went wide into home straight, ran on to just fail to get up on line.
Settled in rear on the rail from a wide gate, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran on well between runners to be nearest at finish.
Began well, settled two back in 4th with rails run, gained 3rd going up the Rock, held some chance throughout home straight but swamped for a placing final strides.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th just about 5L off the pace, went wide into home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield on the rail just over 4L back, gained 5th briefly passing the Rock, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily under pressure.
Travelled in last few, came under pressure rounding home bend, widest runner into the straight, produced good late finish down the centre of the track.
Settled just worse than midfield in 8th on the rail just over about 6L off the speed, saved ground turning for home, kept on same pace under pressure.
Not far off in 3rd or 4th, kept on before giving ground inside the final 200 metres.
Began well from the widest gate, settled well behind before first bend, trailed the field to home straight, unable to quicken under pressure.
Went forward from draw 10, crossed to the lead 700M setting good pace to straight, responded strongly under pressure and shook off nearest pursuer 100M, held on well from fast finishing 2nd late.
Taken back to race behind midfield, crept closer from 500M, wide into straight, stayed on well to claim 2nd near line, nearest finish.
From draw 1 never far away from leaders, chased steadily over final 400M on the inside, got up 3rd near line.
Rushed forward from widest draw, vied for lead on outsider from 800M, battled on well in straight, held 2nd till nearing 50M, edged out to 4th close home.
Taken back from wide draw to race in last about 9Ls off the pace, had to shift across the field to find clear running in the straight, ran on well.
Shifted across behind runners to obtain cover, settled 2nd last, 8Ls to make up 400M, widest into straight, stayed on well down outside.
Settled ahead of midfield, never far off the pace, made his move passing 500M, chased on steadily early straight, flat final stages.
Began only fairly, held up behind midfield, switched wide 400M, ran on same pace to line, drifted out under pressure.
Up with early pace, tracked leaders from 800M, driven 450M, ran on one paced under pressure faded late stages.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled towards the rear 7-8Ls off leader, brought wide into straight, closed off only fairly, never troubled leaders.
Chased leaders, pushed along 500M, kept on same pace turning home, no extra final 200M.
Never better than midfield, 8th at 400M, weakened final 200M to last.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide from 750M, commenced move after passing 450M, showed some response early in straight, blocked 200M, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to score.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide from 700M, improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 850M, angled out 400M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away well, trapped very wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer on the first turn, found cover 600M, commenced move 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made reasonable progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider 400M, no clear running early until final 150M, finished off evenly thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, sat 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 200M and 50M, not able to test properly.
Even break, sent forward to race prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide after passing 1000M, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight weakened gradually thereafter.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Made contact on jumping, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, travelled well to turn, took the lead 450M, kept on very well in straight, won by 1-3/4L. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.

Taken back from gate 9, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 650M, commenced move after passing 550M, bumped 450M, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off well to make frame, no threat to the first few. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, headed near 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, inconvenienced 750M, found rail 700M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in midfield early, 2 wide from 750M, 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, unable to slot in, trapped very wide with no cover in midfield, similar position on turn, bumped 450M, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, trapped 4 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 750M, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Hard ridden to secure box seat, closed off well 250M to score.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 400M for 3rd.
At rear, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, made minor ground 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Slow away, took rail at back but raced ungenerously, improved towards the lead from 1100M, emptied 350M.
Settled midfield on rail, held up in the early part of straight, quickened passing 200M to score.
Jumped well then taken back, placed pressure passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Raced in front of midfield, asked for effort near 500M, fought well in the straight.
Raced at tail, always niggled, held up in the early part straight, gained ground passing 100M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, worked home well.
Taken back at start, asked for effort near 500M, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly then ridden along to race in box seat, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground near 100M.
Crowded at start, raced behind midfield, made the Home Turn awkwardly, limited response in the straight, blood trachea.
Began only fairly then urged along to take lead, took lead near 900M then travelled keenly, weakened passing 200M.
Settled midfield, placed pressure on straightening, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, taken wider passing 500M, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Settled midfield, wide and without cover throughout, gave ground in the straight, finished tailed out, bled.

Enjoyed good run in midfield on the rail, two pairs behind lead. Moved away from rail near 700m before entering last section only 2L from lead. Dashed to the front at the 175m & had enough in hand to hold late challenger.

Unbalanced at start before racing in midfield, wide & without cover throughout. Raced keenly passing 750m before moving wider on cornering. Closed off strongly in last section for fast finishing second. Clear of third.

Not bustled at start & drifted back to race just worse than midfield away from rail. Entered last section 3.5L from lead before making continual steady ground between runners to move to well held third in closing 50m.
Strode forward from wide gate before improving to race outside the leader from the 1200m. Moved up to assume lead passing the 300m before being passed by the first two at the 175m. Well held fourth.

Strode forward close to lead early before getting good position away from rail behind leading duo. Eased three wide on cornering, travelled strongly before peaking on run at the 200m & yielding a few lengths late.

Shifted behind runners after the start & settled a clear last. Continued at the tail, 7 lengths form lead entering last section before making strong closing ground to midfield. Was too far back but ran on ok.
Raced in the clear in midfield in early & middle stages. Shifted away from the rail after cornering when just over 2L from lead before failing to make any further improvement. Well held.

Improved position soon after the start to race in midfield away from rail. Lay outwards throughout middle sections & consequently was awkward & very wide on home corner. Offered little in the last 400m & was well held.
Shifted behind runners after start & raced second last. Continued near the rear, over 4L from the lead entering last section before passing a few tiring runners to midfield but never proved a factor.
Crowded on jumping & consequently drifted back to race just worse than midfield on rail. Awkwardly placed near heals near the 800m. Weakened out further in final 300m & was well beaten.
Showed good speed after the start to stride to lead. Headed in the lead passing the 300m mark before weakening out meekly in last furlong. Well held.
Began very awkwardly & lost ground, consequently racing third last on rail. Continued near the rear on straightening before weakening out further in closing stages to be well beaten.

Hard ridden after the start to improve to race on leaders back. Continued close to the lead before being bumped & steadied passing the 400m when searching for running. Stopped badly in last 300m & was well beaten.

Tightened soon after start & lost position consequently racing in second half. Moved the widest runner on cornering when second last before being steadied out of race in final 250m. (Horse felt sore behind-rider).

Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, hard ridden after passing 350M, hit the front 250M, kept on well to hold off the challengers, won by a neck.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest at finish despite hampered near 125M. (Finished 4th, promoted to 3rd.)

Made contact at start, raced prominently but trapped wide early, 2 wide from 1000M, half length back on turn, took the lead early in straight, headed 200M, kept on evenly to the line. (Finished 3rd, demoted to 4th.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, no cover throughout, similar position on turn, closed off well without threatening the first few.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Out in line, positioned 1 out 1 back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Clean jump, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover from 1000M, peaked on turn, weakened and eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
At rear, 2 wide after 850M, closed off nicely inside final 100M to score by a head.
At rear, wide with no cover after 850M, saved ground and ran on gamely to hold onto 2nd.
Raced in front of midfield, wide with no cover, led briefly in the straight until weakened after 100M.
Midfield, wide but with cover, made steady ground and ran on fairly.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, passing the 250M checked and one paced thereafter.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, showed some dashes in the straight but emptied after 150M.
At rear, wide but with cover, remained one paced to the line.
At rear, wide but with cover, swung widest on straightening, did not improve in the straight.
Rolled forward, along the rail, not competitive.
At rear, along the rail, remained at the rear and did not threaten.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in straight.
Raced in midfield, wide but with cover, never in it. Not competitive, must trial.
Rolled forward, along the rail, lost ground in the straight. Not competitive, must trial.

Began well from the one draw, niggled along on the rail about 2L off the pace in 4th, became 3rd rounding home bend, sustained good progress inside the final 200 metres to just get up on line. (Jockey lost whip 100 metres out.)
Soon took up running, obtained rails run 1000 metres out, kicked over 2L clear inside the 300 metres, unable to sustain effort closing stages and pipped at post.
Taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field to the 400 metres, ran on well down the centre of the straight, nearest at finish.
Crowded shortly after the start, settled in midfield in 5th about 4L off the speed, in similar position into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, widest runner into straight, inconvenienced 300 metres out, fought on well without threatening, tightened close to home.
Recovered quickly from a moderate start to reach 1L 2nd after the first 200 metres, chased the leader into straight, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Began well, settled just off the pace in 3rd, hampered and dropped back to 4th some 2.5L back 800 metres out, fought on steadily in home straight. (Jockey said saddle shifted 800 metres out.)
Settled in last few, kept on well to the line.
Slowly away, always in last few, never nearer.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, picked up strongly when driven out 350M, led inside 200M, held on well towards the finish.
In touch with leaders in a fast run race, chased on well over final 200M, got up 2nd 50M but always held by winner.
Raced prominently as expected, chased leader in fast run race, took over 350M, fought on well until inside 200M, lost 2nd 50M.
Towards the rear of midfield in a fast run race, driven along halfway, made steady progress.
Held up midfield in a fast run race, ran on steadily from 400M but never quite able to challenge.
From draw 14 raced along the stand's rail in midfield, kept battling to the line but safely held by leaders.
Began only fairly, dropped back behind runners, awkwardly placed 500M, finished off mildly, not clear run 150M, not reached leaders.
Settled in mid-pack 4Ls off the fast pace, gave limited response under top weight, well held by leaders.
Strode forward to take lead, set very fast pace with 2nd section completed in less than 20s, headed 350M, couldn't sustain run and weakened final 200M. (Mucus.)
Held up in midfield towards the center of track, kept on same pace under pressure 400M, faded final stages.
Slowly away, raced towards the rear of the field, driven out 400M but never going the pace to challenge, no threat at any stage.
Settled in mid-pack early stages, shuffled back 600M, couldn't pick up under pressure.
In midfield about 3Ls away, pushed along halfway, didn't respond to riding. (Jockey : didn't travel as strongly as anticipated, came off bridle 600M and unable to finish off.)
Chased leaders, came under pressure 500M, weakened to last inside 200M.

Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide near 900M, travelled comfortably on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off strongly to take 2nd on line.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, awkwardly placed near 700M, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running until approaching 150M, made some progress thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off one pace.
Shifted in at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight. (Lost right hind plate near 1250M.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter. (Mucus in trachea.)
Began well from the widest draw, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1100M, raced in 2nd in the middle stages, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, checked near 700M, well back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly, just narrowly beaten.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place.

Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, hard ridden 350M, showed good response, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the challengers late.
Commenced well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well until no extra final 50M.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back turning in, made some headway early in straight, no clear running after passing 200M, not able to test properly.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide towards rear, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began very awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, wider on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, unable to slot in, raced very wide and without cover, a length or so back, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
