Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly to snatch victory in a ding-dong finish.

Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide after passing 700M, same margin back on turn, made contact early in straight, made good progress thereafter to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.

Commenced well, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, found rail near 750M, a length back on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, carried wider after passing 400M, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, trapped very wide in midfield early, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back after passing 800M, angled out 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, no clear running until 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 700M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 750M, peaked on turn, hampered early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast sectionals, made steady ground to score.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked fast sectionals, hung on until 150M weakened.
Failed to muster at back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 150M.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 250M.
Pushed early, in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, however checked badly 300M, no dash in straight.
At back, 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, never improved.
Eased at start, benefited by the fast tempo, never competitive.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 600M, severely checked 300M.
Taken back at start from widest barrier, raced towards rear, asked for effort near 350M, quickened passing 100M to score.
At start became unbalanced when crowded for room, then ridden forward to take lead, responded nicely in the straight, missed by SH.
Settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, placed pressure near 400M, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Raced behind leaders, niggled passing 500M, finished well in the straight.
Jumped well, settled in box seat, placed pressure passing 500M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, worked home well.
Ridden to race outside the lead, commenced to improve near 300M, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Settled midfield, tried to improve near 400M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled towards rear on rail, tried to improve on straightening, held up over concluding stages and was not fully tested.
Raced midfield on rail, placed pressure but only limited response, bled.
Travelled wide and without cover throughout in handy position, came under pressure passing 500M, weakened in the straight.
Raced at tail, always niggled, no response throughout.
Raced wide in midfield position, near 650M was steadied and tried to obtain cover, widest on straightening, faded out in the straight, heart irregularity.
Strode forward, touch wide early before getting good run one away from rail behind leading pair. Moved up to assume lead at the 250m before drawing away late for easy win.

Began well before drifting back after first bend to race worse than midfield. Moved wider & commence to improve passing the 500m before finishing strongly in final 300m to snare fast finishing second in closing stages.

Shifted behind runners early before racing wide & improving position to midfield passing the 800m. Left wide & without cover from the 700m. Dashed to second passing the 200m before being caught for 2nd on line.

Steadied after the start & drifted back to second last near the 900m. Continued near the back on cornering before finishing strongly, making up good late ground to well held forth from rearward position.
Improved after start to race outside leader. Shared lead soon after straightening before peaking on effort at the furlong & yielding a length to midfield in closing stages.

Raced last early before moving slightly closer to midfield on rail after the 800m. Steadied near 650m before being checked & losing ground when crowded near 450m. Passed a few when making ground to midfield but had excuse.

Ridden forward from wide gate before shifting across to midfield after first bend. Checked & drifted further back nearing the 950m. Only 3.5L from lead entering last section before weakening a further few lengths in straight.
Steadied after start & drifted back to last after the first bend. Was a clear last, long way from lead on cornering before making up a length from a poor position to well held midfield margin.

Showed good speed, raced outside leader before being crossed & racing third. Shifted down to rail near 700m to race on leaders back. Hard ridden approaching straight before weakening out sharply in last 300m. Well beaten.
Showed good speed to assume early lead. Raced keenly throughout first 500m. Joined & headed soon after straightening before weakening out significantly in straight to beat only one home.
Ridden along to hold midfield position in the rail in early stages. Became unbalanced & lost ground passing the 400m before weakening out sharply in the straight to be a long last.
Crowded on jumping, raced behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off very strongly to score on line.
Began smartly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just missed.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Crowded on jumping, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few late.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start and unbalanced, raced at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced prominently but 3 wide early, found a 2 wide spot near 600M, a length or so back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, carried wider after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, checked off heels 600M, angled out after passing 450M, showed limited response in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider from 400M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, box seated, along the rail, ran home strongly inside final 150M to score.
Midfield, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, worked home nicely for 2nd.
Raced in front of midfield, wide with no cover, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Sent forward and raced outside the leader, kept on going to the line.
Taken back, 2 wide after 600M, in the straight saved ground and continued on to the line. (See Incident Report)
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, showed some dashes in the straight but emptied after 100M
Rolled forward, along the rail, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
At rear, along the rail, saved minor ground in the straight.
Bumped start, midfield, 2 wide, saved no ground. (See Incident Report)
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, weakened passing 100M.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, not competitive in the straight.
Ridden early, amongst the leaders before taken one out one back passing the 900 metres, quickened well to assert authority inside the final 200 metres.
Began well from the one draw, settled just off the race and mainly in 4th, came under pressure rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Awkward start, quickly recovered to vie for lead 3-wide early stages, gained narrow advantage 2-wide passing the 900 metres, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Crowded at start, settled in midfied in 7th or 6th on the rail, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Recovered quickly to midfield after a moderate start, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish despite hanging and a different ride.
Began well to lead early stages, narrowly headed passing the 900 metres, came to share the pace turning into home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Gradually settled well behind 3-wide after beginning from a wide gate, remained wide into home straight, produced good late impression.
Moderate start, gradually improved to one back position early stages, drifted over 2L back to 5th in back straight, went wide for a run into home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.

Taken back from the widest gate, improved to third last 900 metres out and gained to 9th near the Rock, saved ground turning for home to reach within 3L of pace briefly, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Settled well back from a wide gate, trailed the field to home straight, made no further impression.
Travelled keenly and wide in midfield to home bend, folded up quickly. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Caught wide no cover until passing 1100M, chased leader to straight, took narrow lead nearing 200M, battled hard final stages to hold off rivals on both sides.
Settled 5th never far off from the pace, loomed to challenge from 300M, kept going well to take 2nd in a close finish.
Settled well behind mid-division, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, let down strongly from 300M, nearest finish.
Outside the lead early stages, tracked the pace from 1100M, responded well when driven top of straight, challenged for the lead from 200M, kept on to the line just missed out on a minor placing.
Soon led, took them along at good pace from 1600M-800M, fought on well in straight, headed near 200M, lost several places final stages.
Held up in midfield 4-5Ls off the pace on settling, battled on behind leaders final 300M, never seriously threatened.
Settled down 2-wide in mid-division, came under pressure after 500M and finished off the race only one-paced. (Mucus.)
In 4th chasing leaders, held ground in the straight, faded final stages.
Settled behind mid-division, saved ground on inside, kept on same pace in the straight, never involved.
Began very awkwardly, towards the rear, commenced to race keenly after 1100M, pushed along entering home turn, ran on only fairly making limited progress.
Dropped back for cover, settled near last, didn't finish off on straightening.
From wide draw steadied in early stages to obtain cover, held up last 9-10Ls off the pace middle stages, failed to pick up in straight, never in the picture.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 850M, very wide on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made reasonable headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well without threatening.
Clean jump, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider after passing 800M, 2 lengths back on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, no clear run early in straight, showed limited response thereafter.

Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently early, found rail near 1100M, positioned right behind the leader in the middle stages, 2 wide from 750M, peaked on turn, kept on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide from 950M, 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, trapped very wide, slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out and made contact 900M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out 850M, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved forward after passing 1000M, positioned 3 wide, a length back on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line, just stayed on for 3rd.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages, a length or so back on turn, finished off evenly.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, angled out 550M, blocked and bumped early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to be nearest on line. (Lost right front plate.)
Clean jump, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide turning, bumped early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 850M, angled out after passing 550M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Commenced well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, took brief lead near 850M, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, kept on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths back on rail, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, briefly headed near 850M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Slowly away, positioned towards rear on the inside, commenced move after passing 1000M, made contact and carried wider 900M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, carried wider after passing 1000M, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (Roarer.)
Eased to sit in midfield, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Slow away, at back, harmed by the slow tempo, unleashed strong finishing efforts 200M.
Prominent, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Bumped start, at back, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear.
Shared lead at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Midfield, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M, run ended 100M.
Pushed early, midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased back, not suited by the slow tempo, lack turn of foot.
Tailed out at rear, struggled to keep up until 300M, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace, lack room 100M.
Checked start, at back, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At rear, never improved.
Pushed to share the lead at slow sectionals, hung on until 250M emptied.
Pushed early but never muster, not competitive.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 500M, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Ridden to take lead, responded solidly when asked for effort in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Settled in box seat, held up until passing 350M, worked home well.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, made up some late ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, gained ground passing 150M, had difficulty obtain clear running over concluding stages.
Raced in one-back-one-off position, remained one-paced in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, finished one-paced.
On jumping was crowded, raced at rear on rail, lost left hind plate at 50M, worked home one-paced.
Raced at tail, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but gave ground near 150M.
Hard ridden from wide barrier to race outside the lead, faded out near 200M.

Placing: TNP
Comment: As the start was effected became fractious, lost a considerable amount of ground and effectively took no part in the race.
Raced in midfield away from rail, eased three wide passing the 800m & improved closer to lead nearing the 600. Moved up to share lead at the 150m before digging in late to score narrowly.

Steadied after start, taken back worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from rail & improved between runners at 850m. Shifted 4 wide when improving nearing 500m. Dashed up to share lead at 150m before just missing on line.

Held midfield position along the rail in early & middle stages. Held up behind the heels of tiring runner near corner, shifted wider on straightening, closed off strongly in last 350m to charge to fast finishing third.

Raced prominently before shifting across outside the leader from 900m. Crossed & obtained cover passing 700m. Only a length from lead entering last section & fought hard in concluding stages to maintain that margin late.

Bumped heavily before improving after the start to race in midfield away from rail. Forced wider on the track at the 900m, a raced slightly wide around bend. Made steady late ground in final section to be close behind.

Showed speed after the start to lead. Joined in lead passing the 700m. Shook off challenger approaching the 200m before being headed & passed by the closers at the 150m. Battled on gamely late to not be far behind.

Checked at start & lost ground, consequently racing at the tail. Ridden along to improve near 600m before taken wider on cornering. Long way from lead on straightening before making good late ground from poor position.

Not fast to begin, improved to midfield on rail, Travelled keenly in middle stages before being checked from heals near the 900m. Moved away from rail passing 600m, before making a few lengths to midfield in last section.
Race prominently after the start before settling in forth away from rail. Drifted a length further back approaching the corner before making no significant headway in the last section.

Ridden along after start before being steadied after 100m when unsuccessfully trying to obtain cover before improving position to race outside the leader by the 700m. Peaked at 250m & weakened sharply in last furlong.

Shifted across from outside gate but was left racing wide when third from last soon after start. Continued to cover extra ground, with cover in middle section. Cornered the widest runner & could make no headway in straight.

Steadied & shifting across to race near the tail in early stages. Relegated back to a clear last passing 900m. Continued last, entered final section nearly 10L from the lead before failing to make any noteworthy headway.

Showed speed before being crossed & racing on leaders back. Hard ridden but began to yield ground passing the 600m before weakening out sharply in the straight. Beaten significant margin. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Had no speed after the start & drifted back to second last between runners. Hard ridden approaching the corner before weakening out further in the straight to be beaten a big margin in last.

Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead after passing 1150M, found rail 950M, travelled well on turn, kept on strongly to the line, won by a length.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.

Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 200M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Clean jump, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1150M, allowed rival to cross near 950M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, passed some tired runners in the run home.
Out in line, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Shifted in on jumping and made contact, raced 3 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, very wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 800M, 3 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after passing 800M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Sat in front of midfield, on centre-track, battled on to the line in final two strides.
Sent forward to share lead, on stand-side, kept on nicely to the line.
Bumped start, raced prominently, on centre-track, saved some ground and closed off fairly.
Raced in midfield, one horse from outside rail, made ground and closed off okay.
Hard ridden to be prominent, on centre-track, after the 400M hung in and flattened passing 100M.
At rear, on stand-side, made ground and closed off well.
In midfield, on centre-track, flattened passing 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, on stand-side, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, on centre-track, did not improve.
Bumped start, prominent initially, lost ground and found nothing in the last 200M.
Began fairly, at rear, on centre track after 600M, not competitive.
At rear, on centre track after 500M, made no impression. (See Incident Report)
At rear, on stand-side, found nothing.
Bumped start, at rear, on centre track, weakened from 550M.
Began well from the one draw, settled in midfield in 5th, crowded before switched out for a run after straightening, fought on dourly to just get up on line.
Settled well behind after a moderate start, trailed the field to home straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.

Travelled wide without cover throughout, taken back early before making steady progress to rear of midfield in 6th approaching home bend, quickened to gain narrow lead over 200 metres out, caught close to home. (Tactic questioned
Settled in last few, 3-wide rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to hold some chance 200 metres out, but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Began well, settled in forward of midfield in 4th for cover, commenced move into home straight, held every chance until finding no extra inside the final 100 metres, hampered late.

Broke well from a wide gate, travelled wide about 3L back in joint 2nd in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend and shared pace briefly into home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 300 metres.

Settled on the rail in joint 2nd over 3L off the pace, gained within 1L of the leader when pace slackened on home bend, unable to quicken under pressure in the straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon recovered to midfield from moderate start, lost position when awkwardly placed behind runners approaching home bend, kept on at the same pace in the run to the line.
Slowly away, travelled in rear on the rail, saved ground turning for home, kept on.
Moderate start from the widest gate, went forward keenly to lead by over 3L 1200 metres out, steadied pace rounding home bend, headed inside the 400 metres and soon weakened.
Restrained after the start, held up towards the rear, badly hampered 300M when improving between horses, recovered to launch a strong challenge, got up close home.
Began awkwardly, chased the pace, loomed up 400M, took over 250M, kept on well to line, caught close home.
Taken back after the jump, reserved near last, nudged along 550M, finished off well to almost take 2nd at the line. (Shifted out under pressure 50M, requiring jockey to stop riding.)
Chased leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield when pace slackened middle stages, travelled keenly, moved up to 3rd 350M, fought on steadily to line for modest 4th.
Began awkwardly, soon moved to the lead under 10 lb claimer, took them along slowly before quickening up home turn, headed passing 250M, no extra close home, weakened rapidly.
Dropped back to race towards the rear, took closer order passing 900M, wide into straight, made some headway early straight but run ended 150M from home.
Held up midfield along the fence, shoved along 600M but gave limited response only, well held by leaders at the finish.
Tracked the pace, pushed along 550M, failed to quicken under pressure, no threat from 200M.
Restrained behind leaders, proved difficult to settle when pace slackened middle stages, wide no cover from 900M, crowded for room 300M, kept on same pace to line.
Crowded for room on jumping, not helped by slow pace, left racing 4-wide no cover from 900M, beaten horse turning in. (Jockey : circumstances of the race didn't suit.)
Settle at rear early stages, wide no cover from 1400M, strode forward to outside leader when tempo slowed in middle stages, soon struggled turning for home, dropped away rapidly 350M.
Began well, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer after passing 800M, very wide into straight, showed very good response, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Took keen hold, raced 2 wide at rear, carried wider on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, unable to obtain clear run until 150M, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, bumped near 250M, ran on evenly to the line.
Away well, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length in the middle stages, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, raced tight and bumped near 300M, showed limited response thereafter, weakened final 100M.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, showed no response, weakened final 100M.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, travelled keenly near 900M, saved ground on turn, no clear running in straight, not able to test properly.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 3 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, raced tight and bumped 300M, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, briefly headed on turn, retook the lead early in straight, kept on very well to hold off the rivals, won by half length.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 550M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, wider after passing 550M, kept on well in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.

Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, blocked again near 200M, showed good response final 100M to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, briefly led on turn, headed early in straight, kept on well to 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Out in line, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly in the middle stages, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Lifted front feet on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, 5 lengths back turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Began very awkwardly, positioned on rail in midfield, very difficult to settle near 950M, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd, missed by a neck.

Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, kept to inside after turning in, blocked 250M, cleared after passing 200M, finished off well to take a place.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 wide after passing 600M, moved a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to make frame, nearest on line.
Average to begin, taken back to race at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly without threatening the first few.

Moderately away, trapped very wide early, positioned 3W, 2Ls or so back after entering the back straight, no cover from 700M, moved closer on turn, challenged the leader early in straight, peaked 100M, no extra thereafter.

Crowded on jumping, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide, took the lead after passing 850M, found rail 700M, travelled well on turn, challenged early in straight, kept on well to 100M, headed and weakened final 50M.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 100M. (Bled.)
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden early, in front of midfield, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, favoured by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Eased at start, took cover at back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Took rail easily, led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M weakened.
At back, suited by the fast pace, checked 600M, held up 400M, made good ground 100M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, just held ground in straight.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied in straight.
Slow away, never a factor.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, out of fuel 500M.
Hard ridden forward, dropped off rapidly 700M.
Niggled to take lead, travelled comfortably, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort near 550M, worked home solidly in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield, placed pressure passing 700M, gained some ground in the straight.
Shortly after the start was checked when crowded, settled towards rear on rail, made up some late ground in the straight.
Settled midfield, widest on straightening, finished one-paced.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, worked home one-paced.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced, then was ridden along and near 1600M was steadied away from heels, settled behind midfield on rail, one-paced when under pressure.
Raced behind midfield, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Raced towards rear, no response in the straight, roarer.
Ridden to race outside the lead, came under pressure near 500M, weakened in the straight.
Taken back at start, no response when placed pressure, trainer questioned tactic.
Taken back at start, faded out in the straight.
Showed blistering early speed to lead comfortably. Raced well clear on straightening before extending margin further in the straight to win by wide margin. Impressive.
Raced in midfield between runners. Awkwardly placed near heels at 600m, bumped & unbalanced soon after. Eased into clear running on cornering before finishing off well to move to second at 75m.

Ridden forward but was left racing wide & without cover in midfield throughout. Improved to be closer to the lead passing the 600m, dashed to second soon after cornering before headed in that position near the 75m.

Didn't have the early speed of others, raced in midfield on rail. Bumped & lost a length near 600m before cornering with only 2 behind. Stayed close to the inside in straight before passing a few to a well beaten fourth.

Not the fastest into stride, mustered speed quickly to be midfield. Checked when near heels at 800m & continued keenly in middle stages. Battled onto midfield finish but was well behind big margin winner. (Mucus post-race).
Slowest to begin & raced in last position throughout. Shifted wider on straightening will still last before passing a few tiring runners late. Not a bad debut considering proximity to second.

Showed customary early speed to race in second place around a length from the lead throughout the middle stages. Couldn't go with leader on straightening & peaked on effort soon after. Weakened in closing stages.

Ridden forward before shifting across to race on leaders back. Close to leaders heels & cornered awkwardly near 600m. Only 2L from lead on straightening before weakening out quickly final 250m. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Steadied after start & shifted back from outside gate to race second last. Moved wider on the track passing the 600m, continued with only one behind on straightening before weakening out further to finish 9 lengths last.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 700M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 550M, 2 to 3 lengths back turning in, angled out early in straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made minor progress.

Moderately away, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 800M, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, travelled keenly in the early stages, no cover from 700M, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lost left hind plate.)
Average to begin, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Sent forward to take rail and led, kept on nicely to score by 2-3/4L.
Settled to race in behind the leader, ran nicely to hold onto 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover initially, 2 wide after 700M, saved ground and closed off fairly.
At rear, along the rail, raced tight at 300M and saved ground.
Raced in midfield, checked at 1100M, 3 wide with no cover, stayed on well to the line.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, found no extra for final 150M.
Bumped start, stayed in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Bumped start, raced in front of midfield, along the rail after 750M, was one paced.
At rear, along the rail, saved minor ground and emptied after 100M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, dropped off in the straight after 100M.
Began fairly, raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, never a factor.
At rear, 2 wide, did not improve in the straight.
Pressed forward to hold prominent position travelling 2-wide in 4th most of way in back straight, quickened to hit the front upon straightening, hung on well.

Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled 2-wide in 6th in back straight, commenced move approaching home bend, awkwardly placed behind runner briefly early in home straight, ran on late under pressure.
Settled in rear of midfield on the rail, commenced move rounding home bend and switched out into straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start, settled towards the rear on the rail, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily.
Quickly recovered from moderate start to settle in forward of midfield in 5th on the rail, remained similar into the straight, one-paced under pressure.
Settled in rear of midfield, went wide into home straight, one-paced.
Settled well back, came under pressure turning into home straight, finished off the race well down the centre of the track inside the final 100 metres.
Settled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Taken back from the widest gate, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest runner into straight, made no further impression. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Lame next day)
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, found nothing in home straight.

Ridden positively from a wide gate, travelled keenly outside the leader in back straight, improved to hit the front over 400 metres out, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside the final 300 metres.
Made running to the 450 metres, weakened out of contention from 2nd into straight. (Mucus)
Soon led on jumping from draw 1, took them along at even pace, kicked away from 300M, won unchallenged.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden early stages, crossed to race in midfield, shaken up 400M, closed off steadily to go 2nd nearing 150M, never troubled winner.
Soon taken across, settled towards rear 5Ls behind leader (the eventual winner), under the pump 500M, made some progress down inside of track without threatening winner.
Held up in mid-division, saved ground along the fence, 3-4Ls to make up 400M, kept working to the line, just denied minor placing.
Chased leaders along the fence, lacked a strong finish when asked on straightening, held ground to 150M, faded.
Dropped back to settle last 7Ls back, brought widest in straight, closed off moderately but never near to challenge.
Began well, raced just outside the lead, hung on for 2nd until 200M, faded towards the line.
Sat behind leading pair, kept on same pace turning in, out of contention 200M.
From wide draw dropped back to race 3-wide near last, no cover from 900M, ridden and stayed on fairly from 300M, checked 150M. Never threatened. (Epiglottic entrapment.)
Restrained after the start, settled near rear 5Ls off the pace, struggled from 450M, soon beaten. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead near 500M, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very strongly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take a place.
Average to begin, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, not clear run near 75M, ran on well thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.

Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 9 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 75M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame right hind leg.)
Began well, sent forward to take the lead but trapped 3 wide, peaked and headed 500M, weakened early in straight.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, closed off well to take a place.
Fast into stride, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 4 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home, no threat to the first few.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, bumped early in straight, made some progress thereafter.
Shifted out at start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, weakened gradually in straight.

Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, bumped early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Stumbled at start, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the fast pace, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, overhauled 250M, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to secure box seat, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, raced keenly, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
At rear, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden throughout to maintain position at back, never improved.
Hard ridden early, took rail at back, suited by the fast pace, no dash.
Midfield, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, made ground 100M.
Slow away, at back, never competitive.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 300M.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, responded solidly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Ridden along to race outside the lead, asked for effort near 300M, responded well when placed pressure, finished nicely.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, made up some late ground in the straight, finished well.
Raced midfield, 3 wide with cover, wide on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, held up in the early part of straight, worked home one-paced.
Raced towards rear, placed pressure near 750M, widest on straightening, made some ground in the straight.
Niggled to settle in box seat, tried to improve passing 400M, gave some ground passing 100M.
Began awkwardly then taken back, raced at tail, one-paced in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, steadied away from heels passing 200M, finished one-paced.
Jumped nicely, wide and without cover throughout in handy position, became unbalanced in its action passing 200M, limited response.
Raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, no response in the straight.
Travelled towards rear, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled at rear on rail, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden along to take lead, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, weakened near 300M, lame left hind next day.

Good position in running when forth, away from the rail stalking the leading pair. First to come under vigorous riding approaching the bend before finishing strongly in the straight to charge to narrow lead in final stages.
Strode to lead soon after start & enjoyed very slow first section. Continued to hold narrow lead until being caught by winner in inside final 50m. Held narrow second.
Pushed forward to race outside leader. Moved up to effectively share the lead near the 50m before over-run by fast closing winner. Narrowly beaten.

Began only fairly & settled two pairs back inside another runner. Just under 4L from the lead entering the last section before finishing off strongly in closing stages to be just behind. Fastest last section.

Not ridden after start & settled in second half when a little wide in early & middle stages. Was just under 4L from the lead entering last section before making good late headway to be beaten less than a length.
Didn't have the early speed of others & settled at the rear. Shifted wider on straightening before entering last section over 5L from lead. Made up a few lengths in straight but never threatened.

Drifted back after the start & raced near the rear. Continued at the tail nearing the bend before being forced wider on straightening. Made up a few lengths relative to frontrunners in straight but still beat only one home.
Improved soon after the start to race on leaders back. Came under hard riding on cornering before weakening out in the straight to last.

Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, travelled keenly near 850M, 2 wide on turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, hit the front 300M, kept on strongly to the line, won by 2-1/4L.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 900M, found rail 800M, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed 300M, kept on evenly to take a place.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, positioned 1 out 1 back, carried wider after passing 750M, hard ridden after turning in, showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.

Crowded out start, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, raced wide behind midfield, 4 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 850M, carried wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped with them, raced wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened after passing 500M when hard run took effect.
Raced in one-off one-back position, worked home nicely and scored by a neck.
At rear, 2 wide, worked home strongly and finished a neck behind.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground and closed off fairly.
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, stayed on and found no extra inside final 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, badly held up for a run from on straightening and closed off fairly.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, continued run until emptied passing 150M.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, was one paced.
Bumped start, at rear, along the rail, inconvenienced after 200M and weakened thereafter.
Crowded at start, at rear, 2 wide, made no impression.
Sent forward and took lead, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Asked but failed to muster speed, in worse than midfield, made no impression.
Rolled forward, along the rail, found nothing in the Straight.
Slow to begin, at rear, saved no ground.
Ridden along after crowded at the start, travelled in rear of midfield before making headway on the outside rounding home bend, sustained effort in the straight to gain upper hand close to home.
Began well, settled wide in 5th over 3L back, became 6th rounding home bend and 4-wide into straight, quickened well to hit the front 200 metres out only to be headed close to home.
In last few, switched wide into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began from a wide gate, travelled prominently throughout, came to dispute lead upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Crowded at start losing ground, remained well behind despite ridden along, trailed the field to the 200 metres, ran on well past well-beaten horses.
Broke well, niggled along in front before ceded advantage over 900 metres out, 2L back in 3rd on the rail rounding home bend, kept on under pressure before finding no extra closing stages.
Slowly away travelling well behind, saved ground on the turn, made up good ground in home straight.
Midfield throughout, niggling along early stages, came under pressure upon straightening, kept on one pace without threatening.

Ridden along in worse than midfield, carried wide onto home bend and drifted backward, wider into straight, kept on well past well-beaten horses in the run to the line. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Always in last few, saved ground turning in, kept on one pace without quickening.
Began well, took up running inside the 900 metres, led the field until joined 400 metres out, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden along in first few, drifted back to 4th over 2L back rounding home bend, kept on before weakening under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Settled just better than midfield on the rail, gained closer rounding home bend, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly after straightening.
Tracked leader, took over nearing 500M, kicked clear on straightening, kept on gamely late stages to hold 2nd and 3rd at bay.

Settled down in 3rd, moved out to a 3-wide position without cover from 1100M, nudged along home turn, made a sustained run in the straight, held by the much higher rated winner. (Jockey questioned riding tactics.)
Settled down 4th of 7, moved closer to leaders entering home turn, tried hard in the straight but couldn't reel in the winner, just missed 2nd.
Held up towards rear, driven out 550M, ran on fairly final 400M, not reached first 3.
Held up behind midfield, 5th of 7, couldn't quicken in the straight, soon out of contention.
Dropped back to race in last, came under pressure 600M, never in the picture. (Lame next day.)
Led at good pace early stages, pressed by rival 600M, weakened out of the race from 400M, finished tailed out.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, found rail 600M, moved closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to snatch victory in a very close finish.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, moved closer on turn, hit the front 300M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, wider on turn, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten. (Lost left hind plate near 1000M.)
Crowded on jumping, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 700M, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Away well, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield, carried wider after passing 1000M, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well to 100M, no extra thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Hampered at start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide after passing 700M, a bit closer on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 1000M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Bumped start, raced wide slightly better than midfield, no cover after 950M, moved closer on turn, took the lead near 650M, kicked clear after turning in, soon in command, eased final 50M, impressive.
Slowly away, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover towards rear, wider on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, there to turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to take a place, no threat to the winner.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, angled out after passing 800M, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, positioned on rail towards rear, angled out after passing 700M, 6 lengths back turning in, no clear running early in straight, made some progress final 300M.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, headed after passing 700M, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Away with them, raced 3 to 4 wide slightly behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, lost positon on turn, made no progress in straight.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 5 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross after passing 1000M, 4 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled keenly throughout, unable to maintain position after passing 600M, weakened early in straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Stumbled badly on jumping, dislodged his rider shortly after start.

Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Only 2.5 lengths from lead entering the last section before finishing quickly between runners passing the 100m & getting nose down right on line for narrow win.

Not fast to begin but mustered speed to race in midfield. Travelled strongly on cornering before dashing through a gap at the 300m. Surged to narrow lead at 50m before being caught right on the wire for narrowest of defeats.
Hard ridden after the start & assumed lead soon after beginning. Continued to hold narrow lead under hard ridding before being caught by first two passing the 50m. Close behind in third.

Steadied after start & shifted across from outside barrier to settle rearward. Was a clear last on cornering, shifted to be the widest runner after straightening before finishing very strongly in final 250m for close up 4th.

Drifted back before settling in midfield, four wide with cover throughout. Continued to cover extra ground, was the widest runner on cornering before making strong headway in final 300m to be beaten only a length on line.

Strode forward after start before being left wide & without cover outside the leading pair. Continued with a length of the lead until peaking in the concluding stages & yielding a length late after tough trip.

Raced in midfield, three wide but with cover for majority of early & middle stages. Momentarily held up near the 400m when only 2L from the lead before finishing off evenly to midfield in concluding stages.

Pushed forward to race on the leaders back. Continued to follow the leader on straightening, only 1.5L from lead entering last section before yielding a few lengths when offering little in the final 250m.

Strode to midfield but was left racing 4 wide without cover throughout. Continued not far from the lead at the 250m before emptying out soon after & weakening a few lengths in last furlong after very wide passage throughout.

Bumped after start before settling third last between runners. Awkwardly placed on cornering before being held for clear running until 300m. Shifted wider before finished off moderately in closing stages. (Mucus in trachea).
Showed speed after the start to race outside the leader in second position. Peaked on effort soon after entering the last section before weakening out in final furlong.
Crowded at start before shifting behind runners to settle at rear. Continued near the rear on cornering before finishing off only moderately along the rail in the final stages. No threat.

Slow to begin, conceding over a length before mustering speed to improve to midfield on rail. Entered last section only 2.5L from lead before offering limited response & weakening out to last in concluding stages.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped on jumping, raced 2 wide behind the lead, dropped to midfield on turn, kept on evenly in straight to take 3rd. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned right behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly. (Bled.)
Stumbled at start, raced wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, passed some tired runners in straight.

Bumped on jumping, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, a length or so back, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, carried wider after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (Distressed post-race.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide better midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail just behind midfield, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily to score.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Pushed to take rail in midfield, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 200M.
Midfield, trapped wide, ran on only fairly in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 400M.
Slow away, never better than midfield.
Never competitive and tailed out.
Pressed forward, dropped off quickly 800M.

Placing: PU
Comment: Never competitive, went amiss 500M.
Settled in front of midfield, improved near 450M, battled well in the straight to score.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure near 450M, fought hard in the straight, missed by Neck.
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Urged along, raced inside the leader, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 100M.
Settled towards rear, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, worked home one-paced.
Jumped sharply then ridden along to take lead in one-off position, placed pressure but gave ground some passing 200M.
Raced at rear, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Slow out, raced behind midfield on rail, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced in handy position, placed pressure passing 500M, weakened near 250M.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, raced detached in middle stages, no response in the straight, lame both fore next day.
Settled midfield, came under pressure passing 700M, weakened in the straight.
Travelled wide and without cover throughout in handy position, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn and faded out in the straight.
Began fast and assumed uncontested lead. Continued in lead on cornering, sprinted clear soon after straightening & then drew away further in dash to line to win very easily. Impressive win.

Pushed forward to race outside the leader. Continued within a length of the lead on cornering before being dropped off by winner soon after. Battled on well late to finish clear of third but was no match for impressive winner.
Raced on leaders back throughout. Couldn't' go with the winner on straightening before holding a well beaten third. Well clear of fourth in a leader dominated race.
Didn't have the early speed of others & settled in midfield away from rail. Hard ridden to improve prior to the corner before making no further headway in straight. Well beaten 4th.

Steadied soon after start & shifted back to race second from last away from rail. Continued second last entering last section, 6 lengths form the lead before making no notable headway in leader dominated race.
Shifted out at the start before settling third from last on the rail. Stayed close to the inside on straightening but weakened out further in the straight to be well beaten.

Strode forward before shifted away from rail at first bend to race 1,1. Niggled along throughout middle stages to hold position. Lost touch with first 3 approaching the bend before weakening out significantly in straight.
Checked when crowded for room soon after start before racing at tail throughout. Made no improvement after cornering & tailed out to a long last.

Began smartly, raced better than midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, hit the front near 150M, kept on well to hold off the challengers.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Commenced well, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, finished off evenly.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 400M, made some headway early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on one pace thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, 8 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Taken back to race at rear, still well back on turn, very wide into straight, showed some response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground and closed off nicely to score by a neck.
At rear, along the rail, swung widest on straightening, ran on gamely and finished a neck behind.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, along the rail after 700M, saved some ground and closed off fairly.
Pressed forward, 2 wide after 700M, stayed on and found no extra inside final 100M.
Slow to begin and raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, closed off fairly in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made ground steadily.
Sent forward, along the rail, continued run until emptied passing 100M. (Lame left front)
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 450M, was one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide after 600M, show no turn on foot.
Bumped start and sent forward, along the rail, lost ground after 200M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made no impression.
Bumped start, near the 1000M gave ground, eased down after 600M. Finished tailed out, must trial. (See Incident Report)

Jumped fairly from a low gate, travelled some 3L back in 5th on the rail, gained slightly closer to 4th over 1000 metres out and 2nd into straight, sustained effort to hit the front passing the 200 metres, kept on under pressure.
Settled in midfield on the rail, gained closer rounding home bend coming within 2L of the pace, fought on steadily in straight but unable to peg back the winner.
Pressed forward from a wide gate to lead on the rail over 1300 metres out, led the field until finding no extra and headed inside the 200 metres.

Hampered shortly after start settling well behind, detached from the main body of the field most of the way, widest runner in last place turning for home, finished off the race well down the centre of the straight.
Settled not far off in 4th early stages, became 5th over 1000 metres out, came under pressure turning for home, kept on before finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in rear of midfield, given reminders rounding home bend, kept on one pace under pressure.
Crowded at start settling well back, saved ground turning for home, ran on past well-beaten horses in straight.
Settled in last few, went very wide into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track. (Lame)
Settled just worse than midfield 3-wide, 4-wide rounding home bend and wider into straight, one-paced.

Pressed forward from a wide gate travelling very wide around first bend before settling 2L back in 3rd 3-wide without cover in back straight, drifted wider rounding home bend, folded up after straightening.
Settled towards the rear, saved ground on the inside turning in, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Settled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, came under pressure around home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Pressed forward from the widest gate travelling very wide without cover in midfield around the first bend and in back straight, weakened shortly after straightening.
Ridden forward from a wide gate, settled one back in 2nd coming onto back straight, chased leader to the 500 metres and weakened.
Chased leaders in a fast run race, showed good acceleration passing 300M, led inside 100M, kept going strongly to the line.
In midfield about 3Ls away, responded well on straightening, kept on final 200M to go 2nd in closing stages.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, given a waiting ride, covered more ground than rivals from home turn, closed off strongly final 300M to go 3rd near line.
Reserved near last in a fast run race, had 7Ls to make up 400M, finished off well down the outside of straight, just missed a place.
Driven to the lead, set fast pace to straight, kept on well until headed inside 100M, faded and edged out to 5th near line.
From wide draw went forward as expected, chased leader in a fast run race, couldn't sustain run passing 200M, lost several places near the finish.
Bustled along after the start but unable to go with leaders in a fast run race, towards the rear making home turn, stayed on fairly without threat.
From draw 12 caught wide no cover chasing leaders in a fast run race, weakened passing 200M.
Began fairly, settled in detached last, held up for clear running after 300M before making mild progress final stages.
Settled down behind midfield, came under serious pressure 500M, never near to challenge.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, ended up racing in midfield, couldn't go on final 400M. (Jockey : didn't travel strongly at any stage.)
Up with early pace, struggled to hold its position 700M, soon beaten on straightening. (Jockey reported abnormal breathing noise when under pressure in straight.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, improved along the rail on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a head.
Bumped start, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, just missed by a head.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 650M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider on turn, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, trapped 3 wide early, positioned 2 wide better than midfield after entering the back straight, carried wider after passing 550M, peaked turning in, one paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider after passing 600M, failed to close off in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, carried wider on turn, very wide into straight, finished off one pace. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Bumped start, trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 1350M, positioned outside to the leader in the middle stages, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never a threat. (Lame left front leg next day.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
