Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, moved closer on turn, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 250M, closed off well to take a place.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Away with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, moved closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and inconvenienced near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 700M, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Quickly into stride, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began very awkwardly, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made little progress in straight.

Average to begin, positioned on rail better than midfield early, travelled keenly and shifted out after passing 1050M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced wide on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final 200M.
Behind midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, closed off strongly when clear.
Hard ridden to take rail, shared the lead at very fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 50M overhauled
Eased at start, took cover, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 350M.
Pushed to share the lead in 2 wide at very fast sectionals, hung out at bends, ran on until 150M weakened.
Pushed early, sat in front of midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made minor ground.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made late ground 150M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
Slow away, at back took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress, checked 200M.
Slow away, hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 250M.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Slow away, became badly unbalanced and attempted to buck for some distance. Retired out of the race.
Took forward position on outside rail with nice early speed, responded strongly when asked for effort, scored unchallenged.
Ridden from inside barrier, raced behind the speed, asked for effort near 300M, finished solidly.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400m, made ground passing 200M.
Rolled forward and took lead, placed pressure passing 400M, kept on to the line.
Raced towards rear, lay out throughout, made up some late ground, lame right front next day.
Raced inside the leaders close to middle of track, one-paced when placed pressure.
Settled at back, placed pressure near 400M, gained some ground passing 200M.
Settled midfield on outside rail, worked home one-paced.
Travelled midfield, limited response when placed pressure, rider concerned its action, OVE.
Settled midfield, placed pressure but no response, mucus trachea.
Raced midfield near the middle of track, faded out passing 150M.
Raced behind midfield close to middle of track, weakened near 150M.
Travelled midfield, came under pressure passing 400M, faded out passing 200M.
Raced at tail on rail, tried to improve but no response throughout.

Began well, ridden along before shifting across in midfield away from the rail. Moved very wide approaching the bend, made strong late headway to move to lead near the 150m before holding narrow margin on line.

Raced in midfield away from rail. Moved wider approaching the corner, wider on straightening before entering last section 3L from lead. Made strong late ground to get within a very short margin on line.

Mustered speed after the start to improve and share the lead from the 900m. Kicked away on straightening, held lead until being caught by winner inside the 150m before fighting on strongly late to close-up third

Showed speed & held the early lead before steadying and racing behind leading trio. Entered last section only 2 lengths from lead, improving to second position soon after before finishing off steadily to be close behind.

Failed to muster speed before improving under hard riding to race midfield, wide & without cover. Continued wide passage middle stages before cornering very wide. Made strong late ground final section to finish close behind.
Enjoyed good run on leaders back. Continued on rail entering last section when less than 2 lengths from the lead before peaking on run at the 200m before yielding a length or two in closing stages.

Not fast away before settling worse than midfield between runners. Ridden along on cornering before entering last section over 5L from lead. Maintained margin in the dash to the line without threatening.

Crowded at start & lost ground before shifting across behind runners to settle near the tail. Continued with only one runner behind on straightening before making no real noteworthy headway when finishing to midfield.

Raced just worse than midfield on the rail throughout early stages before drifting back to third last passing the 800m. Ridden along approaching the corner before failing to make any headway into margin. Well beaten.

Pushed forward from gate 10, worked very hard 3 wide when sharing lead before shifting to race outside lead from the 600m. Dropped off leader on straightening before weakening out sharply from the 400m.

Strode forward after start to share early lead when racing between runners. Steadied near 700m & obtained cover when racing behind leading pair. Weakened out sharply after straightening & was beaten big margin. (Must trial).
No early speed & settled at the tail of the field away from the rail. Lost further ground on cornering before weakening out further in the last section to be a very long last. (Must trial).
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers.

Commenced well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, moved closer on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider in the middle stages, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Crowded out start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned 1 out 1 back, travelled keenly in the middle stages, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, showed limited response in straight.
Bumped start, trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 1000M, positioned outside to the leader in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off one pace.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, inconvenienced near 850M, wider on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced towards rear, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, failed to close off in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on nicely to score.
Settled to race in midfield, 2 wide, ran on strongly in the straight.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, 3 wide with no cover, improved steadily to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on well.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover, made ground and ran on to the line.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, improved steadily to the line.
Bumped start and sent forward, along the rail, found no extra approaching 150M.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, crowded for room passing 350M and made marginal ground only.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, crowded for room passing 350M and emptied after 100M.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, was one paced. (Heart irregularity)
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Rolled forward, 2 wide, never a factor.
At rear, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, found nothing and eased down at 200M.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 3-wide behind midfield in back straight, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on well under pressure to take charge close to home despite shifting ground.
Settled in midfield most of the way, saved ground making final turn, quickened well along the rail to hold every chance inside the final 200 metres only to be overshadowed close to home.

Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate and slow to muster despite ridden along travelling 3-wide in midfield most of the way, commenced move rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to hold some chance inside the 200 metres.
Chased the leaders most of the way, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Prominent early, gradually settled in midfield in back straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Crowded at start losing ground settling in rear on the rail, saved ground making final turn, ran on steadily under pressure.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, improving until joining the leader in back straight, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.

Refused to settle in early stages pulling forward to 3-wide without cover on first bend and throughout back straight, improved steadily to join the leaders into home straight, folded up quickly shortly passing the 200 metres.
Mainly in midfield before steadied and lost position about 1300 metres out, dropped to last few coming onto home bend, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate trailing the field most of the way, wide into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Began well from the one gate, held narrow running until joined around home bend, fought on gamely until finding no extra and swamped inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden forward from a moderate start, settled one-out-one-back in 4th or 5th to home straight, folded up quickly under pressure. (Questioned for riding instruction)
Shaken up after the start, crossed to the lead 900M, kicked on again when asked 350M, held on well from 2nd and 3rd late.
Not far from leaders early stages, shuffled back to near last before home turn, made good headway up the fence final 300M and challenged winner late stages, nearest finish.
Settled midfield 3Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, restricted room 200M, did best work late to be nearest at the finish.
Quickly into stride, track leaders from 900M, tried hard in the straight but couldn't get closer to winner, faded final 100M.
Moved up to be 4th entering home turn, 3-wide no cover chasing leaders, held ground in the straight, no threat from 150M.
In touch with leaders, kept on same pace in straight, always held, never seriously threatened.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled 3-wide behind midfield, kept on fairly in the straight, never dangerous.
Slowly away, dropped back to race in last, stayed on final 400M, not reached leaders. (Jockey : elected to steady his mount after slow start to avoid covering ground.)
Dropped back from wide draw, near last and over-raced middle stages, awkwardly placed top of straight, made limited progress to the line.
Settled behind mid-division, kept on same pace in straight, never near to challenge.
Strode forward to be pressing the pace on outside, under pressure 500M, gave way 300M.
Unable to slot in, caught 4-wide no cover in midfield, couldn't go on in the straight.
From wide draw steadied in early stages to obtain cover, raced near the rear, struggled to keep up entering straight, left behind 200M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers, scored by a neck.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just missed.

Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 200M, angled out thereafter and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just missed.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, finished off well without threatening. (Rider dropped whip near 100M.)
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, same position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Away well, positioned right behind the leader early, 2 wide after passing 1100M, a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.

Began fairly, raced keenly in midfield, 2 wide, awkwardly placed near 1150M, commenced move after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, 4 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, moved a bit closer on turn, hard ridden after passing 350M, hit the front 200M, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.
Moderately away, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well early in straight, blocked near 200M, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just held.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Commenced well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Moderately away from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced very wide behind midfield early, found cover near 850M, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, 6 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Began well before drifting back to midfield on rail. Moved away from rail approaching corner, improved between runners when racing tight near the 300m before getting clear & sprinting strongly in final 150m top score.

Obtained good position racing on the leaders back. Stayed on rail on straightening, sprinted quickly to assume narrow lead at the 200m, caught by winner inside the last 75m before fighting on bravely in closing stages.

Crowded at start before mustering speed & improving to race midfield away from rail. Moved wider on cornering, made continual ground be close to lead at 200m before being outsprinted by winner. Raced greenly late. Good debut.

Wasn't fast to begin & settled worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider after straightening, made strong late ground final 300m before being inconvenienced near the 50m. Closed hard again near line. Good debut.

Began well but was steadied & drifted back after the start to race just worse than midfield, wide with cover. Entered last section 5.5 lengths from lead before finishing off strongly in closing stages to not be far behind.

Strode forward after start & obtained good position 1,1. Travelled strongly entering last, dashed up to share the lead near the 200m before laying in under pressure in final furlong when yielding a few lengths late.

Bumped at start before being steadied & shifting back to last. Continued a clear last on cornering, entered last section nearly 9 lengths form lead before finishing off well to midfield in closing stages from poor position.
Ridden forward from gate 11 to shift across & race outside the leader. Moved up to narrow lead passing the 300m before being headed soon after & weakening out in final furlong.

Drifted back after the start & was relegated to second last near the 900m. Continued near the rear entering last section when nearly 9 lengths from the lead before passing a few tiring runners in closing stages. No threat.
Showed good speed when ridden forward after the start to lead. Joined in the lead passing the 300m before weakening out in the final furlong to be well beaten.
Improved position after the start to race in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Moved wider just prior to straightening before yielding a further 3L in last section to be well beaten.

Improved after the start but was left racing three wide without cover in midfield throughout. Began yielding ground when continuing wide passage around the home bend before weakening out sharply in straight.

Steadied away from heals after the start before shifting behind runners to race near the tail. Stayed close to the inside on cornering but weakened out further in the final 300m to be beaten a long way.

Bumped & unbalanced at start consequently losing ground & racing near the rear. Continued at the tail, 9 lengths from the lead entering last section before weakening out significantly in the straight. Beaten a huge margin.

Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, easily scored.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back, saved ground throughout, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 7, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly. (See Racing incidents.)
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, peaked on turn, gradually lost place in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
At back, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M to score.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, blocked most straight, closed off strongly when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 300M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 200M.
Midfield along the fence, suited by the fast pace, however blocked most straight, ran on fairly when clear.
Slow away, hard ridden but not muster, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made ground 150M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 150M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, bumped early, took rail, never improved.
Slow away, never competitive.
Travelled midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 600M, issued challenged passing 200M, battled strongly to score.
Urged along to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, finished solidly, missed by Head.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear, niggled from 650M, widest on straightening, made up nice late ground, finished nicely.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort near 400M, responded well in the straight.
Began awkwardly, passing the winning post on first occasion was checked away from heels and lost ground, raced midfield, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield on rail, placed pressure but finished only one-paced.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 500M, worked home one-paced.
Ridden along to take lead, came under pressure near 400M, gave ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, tried to improve near 600M, near 350M was steadied and lost ground, no response in the straight.
Settled in handy position, came under pressure near 500M, near 350M was checked and lost running, must trial.
Wide and without cover throughout, raced behind midfield, no response in the straight.

Didn't have the early speed of others & drifted back after the first bend to race third from last on rail. Continued with only 2 behind on cornering, bumped near 175m before finishing very strongly thereafter for upset win.

Showed good speed to race outside early leader before being crossed and racing third, away from rail past the 900m. Moved up to assume the lead at the 150m before being caught in final few strides by fast finishing winner.

Raced in midfield on the rail throughout early & middle stages. Travelled strongly nearing the corner, before making up a few lengths in the straight to charge to third in closing stages. Not far behind.

Began awkwardly before racing in midfield on the rail. Steadied near the corner before being momentarily held up on straightening. Shifted towards the rail at 250m before closing of nicely in late stages to be close behind.

Slow to begin before improving after first bend to race in midfield away from rail. Moved three wide to improve passing the 500m before making up a length in final section to run to midfield without threatening.

Steadied at start & shifted behind runners to race third from last away from the rail. Moved slightly closer nearing corner, made steady ground early in straight, bumped at the 175m before finishing evenly thereafter.

Began fairly, hard ridden to improve position after first bend, raced to lead passing 900m before crossing to rail near 700m. Headed in the lead at the 150m before yielding a few lengths late after doing too much work early.

Steadied from widest barrier & shifted back to second last after first bend. Continued near the rear, 7L from lead entering last section, moved the widest runner on straightening before making up a few lengths to midfield.

Hard ridden at barrier rise to hold early lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 700m. Ridden along prior to cornering before weakening out in the final section to be well beaten.

Obtained good position in midfield between runners in early stages before obtaining 1,1 position soon after. Hard ridden approaching the 400m mark before peaking on effort near the 200m & yielding a few lengths thereafter.

Showed some early speed before drifting after the first bend to race three wide without in midfield. Moved even wider approaching the 400m before peaking on effort soon after straightening & weakening out to second last.
Steadied after the start & raced a clear last after the first bend. Continued last entering the last section when over 8L from the lead but failed to pass any runners in the dash to the line. Last.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight and scored.
Slightly slow out and crowded, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 350M, made good progress in straight to take 3rd on line.
Taken back from gate 8, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to make frame.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail, same position to turn, angled out after passing 350M, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly, steadied off heels close home.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off one pace.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, finished off one pace.
Lifted front feet on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Out in line, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide and without cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
Sent forward and took lead, kept on going to score.
Settled to race behind midfield, along the rail after 600M, close off strongly in the straight to take 2nd.
Settled in one-off one-back position, kept going and ran on nicely for 3rd, finished 3/4L behind.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, saved some ground in the Straight and ran on well.
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 550M, continued on one paced to the line.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide after 500M, improved steadily to the line. (See Incident Report)
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide after 500M, pretty one paced. (Substantial amount of mucus and lame left front)
Rolled forward and raced behind the leader, along the rail, found nothing after 150M.
At rear, along the rail after 600M, was one paced.
Began fairly, raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, nothing in the Straight. (Substantial amount of mucus)
Raced in midfield, 2 wide and lay out near 550M, not competitive.
At rear and detached, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.
Well there settling one-out-one-back in 4th, commenced move rounding home bend holding every chance from upon straightening, gained slender advantage inside the 100 metres.

Pressed forward from the widest gate travelling 3-wide with leaders rounding the first bend, disputed lead from over 1100 metres out, hit the front under pressure entering home straight only to be headed inside the 100 metres.
Settled well behind, saved ground turning for home, ran on to be nearest at finish despite a tight run closing stages.
Settled towards the rear, commenced move passing the 500 metres, went very wide turning for home, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled at the back, went widest turning for home, ran on in the centre of the straight to be nearest at finish.
Crowded shortly after start, settled towards the rear on the rail, pulled forward to midfield in 5th rounding first bend, travelled keenly early in back straight, ran home one-paced.

Jumped awkwardly from the one draw, taken one back for cover on the rail, raced keenly in similar position in 3rd early in back straight, chased leaders into home straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 100 metres.
Obtained slender lead with rails run passing the wining post the first time, held the same until narrowly headed into home straight, folded up quickly inside the 300 metres.
Began well, restrained for cover, became 5th 2-wide in midfield upon settling, shifted wide turning into home straight, never recovered.
Settled along the fence about 4Ls back in mid-division, kept responding to pressure in the straight, strongly pressed leader from 150M, got up last stride.
From draw 1 obtained a trailing spot behind leader, moved up to challenge 400M, soon led on straightening, fought on well, pressed by eventual winner 150M, caught last stride.
From wide draw dropped back to race in last, made his move 750M, wide into straight, stayed on steadily to the line.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, over 5Ls to make up at 400M, ran on well to be nearest at the finish.
Restrained to race in midfield 4-5Ls back, made mild progress on straightening, near 200M had to switch lane for clear running, kept on evenly final stages.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, towards the rear early stages, shuffled back to last 650M, widest into straight, stayed on without reaching leaders.
Held up behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, driven along 350M, stuck on fairly, no threat to leaders.
Did some early work to go forward, led uncontested to straight, headed top of straight, battled on until no extra final 100M.
Settled behind midfield, driven wide home turn, kept battling to the line but never close.
Settled 4th, always in touch, pushed along 450M, didn't run on, ran well below expectation. (Jockey : disappointing effort despite up in grade / Unacceptable Performance.)
Strode forward chasing leader, in trouble passing 500M, beaten before straightening, eased 200M when no chance.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, hit the front after passing 200M, kept on very well to hold off the challengers.
Moderately away from gate 11, sent forward to race 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd, always held.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to take a place.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 400M, made some progress in straight, no threat to the first few.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, found rail near 500M, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Away well, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed after passing 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Away with them, trapped vey wide behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Jumped well, showed no early speed, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced very wide towards rear, 8 to 9 lengths back turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.

Began well, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, slightly taken back after 1000M, found a 2 wide spot in midfield 800M, 5Ls back turning in, peaked early in straight, blocked 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight. (Blood in trachea.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, ran on well to score.
Eased to sit in front of midfield along the fence, closed off well 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 250M.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3-4 wide at rear, dashed well 200M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, dashed fairly.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, lack turn of foot.
Slow away, at rear, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, emptied 300M.
Slow away, never competitive.
Took lead with nice early speed, responded strongly in the straight, scored by 4L.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort near 400M, worked home nicely
Raced 3 wide with cover in front of midfield, commenced to improve near 500M, made up some ground in the straight.
On jumping was crowded, settled midfield, worked home one-paced.
Raced in front of midfield, fought hard but finished only one-paced.
Ridden along but no early speed, raced midfield, 3 wide with cover, widest on straightening, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, detached in early and middle stages, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced outside the lead, placed pressure on straightening, gave ground near 300M, blood in trachea.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, always back, no response in the straight.
Raced midfield on rail, in the straight placed pressure but no response.
Raced behind midfield, came under pressure near 500M, faded out in the straight.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced, wide and without cover throughout in handy position, weakened in the straight.

Had soft run in midfield, eased away from inside rail approaching 600m. Shifted wider on straightening, entered last section only 2.5 lengths from lead before making continual late headway to strike lead in final few strides.

Ridden forward from wide barrier to assume narrow lead after 250m. Continued narrow lead away from rail until racing outside leader from the 1000m. Regained lead at 250m before being caught in final two strides. Clear of 3rd.

Began well, led momentarily before being headed on outside. Held rail before improving to regain the lead near the 1000m. Held narrow lead on straightening, headed at the 250m before giving a length to third in last 150m.
Improved after start to race in midfield on the rail. Shifted wider to obtain clear running soon after straightening before finishing off steadily to not be far behind.

Slow to begin & raced a clear last. Commenced to improve position when three wide with cover from the 900m, before cornering the widest runner. Made some ground in final 300m but was never close enough to threaten.

Shifted across to midfield from wide gate before getting position away from rail. Moved 3 wide to improve near 800m before entering last section less than 2L from lead. Peaked on run at 200m & weakened a few lengths late.
Had a good run on the leaders back throughout. Niggled along on cornering before peaking at the 250m & weakening out a few lengths to midfield in concluding stages.

Shifted across after the start to race just worse than midfield on the rail. Shuffled back to third last approaching corner, stayed hard on rail & improved position on straightening. Only maintained margin in last section.

Began well before being steadied & shifted across to midfield away from rail. Continued in midfield around 6L from the lead at half-way. Shuffled further back on straightening before failing to improve in straight.

Limited early speed & eventually settled in midfield between runners. Drifted further back in middle stages before coming under heavy riding & losing ground passing 550m. Made no improvement in last section & was well beaten.

Slow to begin & raced second last after the start. Moved three wide & commenced to improve approaching the 900m. Continued wide passage in middle stages before peaking on run on cornering & weakening out in final section.

Strode forward after start before getting good position 1,1. Raced a touch keenly in second section. Entered last section only 1.5 lengths from the lead before weakening out sharply in final 250m to be beaten a big margin.

Crowded on jumping & then had no speed consequently racing near the rear. Relegated back to last approaching 1000m. Continued a clear last & under pressure on cornering before failing to make any ground. Beaten a big margin.

Had no early speed despite being hard ridden & raced worse than midfield. Continued to be ridden along in middle stages to hold positon before cornering long way from lead. Weakened further in the straight to be a long last.
Average to begin, raced 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away from gate 12, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, a bit closer on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but still headed 150M, stayed on to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved closer along the rail on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, carried wider on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Away well, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 700M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on one pace to the line.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final 250M.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 500M, very wide turning in, showed little response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 700M, commenced move 550M, very wide turning in, showed little response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, inconvenienced near 650M, wider turning in, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Niggled and sent forward to lead, kept on going to score.
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 850M, saved some ground and ran on well to take 2nd.
Settled in midfield position, along the rail, continued on well finished 1-3/4L behind.
At rear initially, raced in worse than midfield after 600M, continued to make ground to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved minor ground and ran on fairly.
Sent forward, along the rail, was emptied passing 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, kept going until emptied at 200M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide passing 850M, found nothing after 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, was one paced.
Bumped start, at rear, 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Rolled forward, wide with no cover, steadied at 350M, not competitive thereafter.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, improved slightly in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, lost ground after 150M.
Bumped start, at rear, along the rail, did not feature.

Moderate start, travelled some 2L off the pace in 7th, shifted off stands rail over 500 metres out before shifting back out to stands rails coming onto course proper, fought on under pressure to just get up on line.
Always well there, fought on dourly to hit the front over 100 metres out only to be caught close home.
Settled just off the pace on stands rails, hit the front coming onto course proper, unable to sustain effort and headed over 100 metres out.
Broke well and travelled up with the pace early, lost touch when pace quickened over 500 metres out, recovered good late ground closing stages.
Crowded at start, soon taken across in rear near stands rail and poised for a run, came to challenge inside the 500 metres but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Made running until approaching course proper when narrowly headed, unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside final 150 metres.
Settled in midfield just over 2L back near the centre of the track, kept on same pace under pressure without quickening.
Close up early before dropping over 2L back to midfield despite niggling along, kept on until faded inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly and soon dropped to last few despite niggling along, never seen with a chance travelling down the centre of the track. (Lame)
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, in last few throughout and never seen with a chance.
Soon lost touch dropping gradually to tail-end halfway out.
Jumped on terms, held up on inside just ahead of midfield, moved out to challenge top of straight, gave strong kick from 300M, led near 100M, continued on well to line.
Began only fairly, settled down midfield, kept chasing but no match for winner, got up 2nd near line.
Vied for lead on outside setting a good tempo, led from 300M, caught near 100M, lost 2nd close home.
Ridden quietly as usual, 8Ls off the pace making the turn and came home widest, fought on well to the line, just missed 3rd.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, settled towards rear and had a ground saving trip, moved out to challenge 300M, kept on steadily.
Scrubbed along to take up a trailing position behind leaders, hard ridden to chase from 500M, tired and weakened final 150M.
From wide draw taken across to race behind midfield, kept on steadily final 400M but always held.
Settled towards the rear 7-8Ls off the good pace, responded fairly early straight, no impression leaders.
Failed to muster speed, dropped to clear last passing 1000M, on straightening ran past well beaten horses only. Never involved.
Held up midfield, 5Ls off the pace making the home turn, brought wide on straightening, couldn't sprint with them. Never threatened.
Ridden to chase leaders from draw 11, couldn't go on inside 300M, weakened rapidly. (Jockey : travelled only fairly and did not finish off the race.)
Vied lead along the fence, lay out middle stages, weakened 250M. (Jockey : made to work throughout the race with a rival racing to its outside but nevertheless disappointing.)
Crowded for room on jumping, failed to muster speed, ended up behind mid-division, struggled form top of straight, soon beaten. (Lame RF leg.)
Positioned just ahead of midfield, never far away from the pace, failed to finish off turning home, eased mid-straight when no chance.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from gate 13, detached early, got back to it 700M, still 9 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made reasonable headway in straight.

Began well, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, moved closer in the middle stages but still trapped 3 wide, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, positioned on rail better than midfield, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong. (Sustained a minor laceration to the left front fetlock.)
Began only fairly and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide on turn, outpaced near 500M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Out in line, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight to hold off the challengers.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest gate, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Shifted in at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length back turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, trapped wide in midfield early, steadied off heels near 1000M, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail after passing 900M, 2 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, still last turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider after passing 700M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, positioned slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide after passing 900M, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Shifted in at start, positioned right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)

Fast into stride, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, commenced move after passing 400M, finished off very strongly to score.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead after passing 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight but still headed 100M, lost 2nd on line.
Moderately away from gate 9, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, no cover after passing 650M, moved a bit closer on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, got cover after passing 700M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide, 3-1/2L back, same position on turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, made contact and unbalanced near 550M, 3 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide, a length back, 2 wide after passing 650M, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, made all.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, held ground for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
At back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 150M.
In front of midfield, 2-3 wide, made ground 250M.
Eased back, along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, emptied 300M.
Eased at start, took rail, suited by the fast pace, however blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Eased at start, sat 2 wide at rear benefited by the fast tempo, lack room in straight, ran on fairly.
Eased to sit in midfield trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Eased at start, never improved.
Raced outside the lead near 900M, issued challenge passing 400M, passing 200M lay in, worked home strongly to score.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, responded solidly in the straight.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, improved passing 400M, made nice ground in the straight.
Settled midfield, after 800M was awkwardly placed and after 700M lost its position, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, worked home solidly.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced, then taken back, travelled at rear on rail, responded nicely in the straight.
Urged along to take lead from widest gate, placed pressure passing 350M, gave ground near 150M.
Wide and without cover throughout, tried to improve passing 400M, finished one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, tried to improve on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced towards rear, wide on straightening, placed pressure but only limited response.
At the start was crowded for room and lost ground, raced at tail, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Travelled in front of midfield, placed pressure near 300M, gave ground in the straight.
Ridden to settled behind the speed, came under pressure passing 400M, weakened in the straight.

Steadied after first furlong and shifted in to get cover when racing in midfield. Eased wider on cornering when nearly 4L from the lead before finishing strongly to dash to lead inside final 50m. Strong win.

Had good position on the rail just behind the fast early speed. Improved along inside to assume lead when travelling strongly near the 450m. Raced 2L clear on straightening, before being caught in final 5 strides. Big run.
Raced in 4th position in the clear behind fast early speed. Stayed close to the inside on straightening before making up a few lengths in the straight to be just behind in third.

Hard ridden to race prominently, held second between runners with leader working hard on outside. Dropped 2 lengths behind leader on straightening before emptying out soon after. Probably did too much work early.

Shifted across behind runners from outside gate to race in midfield away from. Over 7 lengths from the lead entering the last section before making up a few lengths in late stages but was too far back to figure.

Ridden vigorously & worked very hard when racing wide and holding narrow lead. Continued to race wide before being headed in lead by the 450m before weakening out in straight after doing too much in early stages.

Was a touch slow to begin & consequently raced at the tail, a long way from the fast leaders throughout. Continued last entering last section, a huge margin from lead before passing a few tiring runners late. Well beaten.

Stumbled badly & crowded after start consequently losing ground before improving quickly to midfield after the first furlong. Continued in midfield on cornering before weakening out in the straight. Well beaten.

Began only fairly, had no early speed & raced third last throughout. Continued a long way from lead entering last section before making no headway. Well beaten. (Failed to stretch out-rider). (Must trial, unacceptable perf).

Crowded after start before showing no speed & racing at the tail. Ridden along to hold position in fast run middle stages. Shared last place on cornering when a long way behind leaders before making no headway. Long last.
Commenced well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late, finished 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide from 800M, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped start, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, crossed near 750M, 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening. (Lost right front plate.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 9 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths or so back, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 7 to 8 lengths back, 3 wide from 600M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 10 lengths back on turn, emptied early in straight.
Bumped start, settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, showed good kick approaching 150M, continued on to score impressively by 2L.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off gamely for 2nd.
Bumped start, raced in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, along the rail passing the 1000M, improved and closed off fairly.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, saved ground and ran on well.
Slow to begin, at rear, along the rail, was one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, shifted in abruptly near 150M, pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, remained one paced to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide after 550M, saved no ground in the straight.
Bumped start, sent forward, along the rail, lost ground in the straight.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, headed when found no extra passing 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, severely checked passing 1000M, eased down after 600M. Finished tailed out, must trial. (See Incident Report)
Pressed forward to obtain rails run settling one back in 3rd and 4th into back straight, fought on dourly under pressure to hit the front inside the 200 metres.
Ridden forward from a wide gate settling not far off in 5th, came under pressure entering home straight, fought on steadily to hold some chance but unable to draw level throughout.
Settled in midfield 2-wide, commenced move rounding home bend going wide into straight, ran on under pressure without threatening.

Travelled just worse than midfield on the rail after a moderate start racing awkwardly in slow pace around stables bend, in similar position home bend and saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, similar into home straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Slowly away, settled at the back on the rail, angled out for a run entering home straight, fought on steadily without quickening.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, settled in front on the rail rounding first bend while steadying the pace, joined in the front coming onto home bend, folded up quickly inside the final 180 metres.
Settled in last few on the rail, shifted 2-wide coming onto home bend, went wider into home straight, fought on steadily.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, disputed lead around first bend before restrained outside the leader in back straight, gained narrow lead briefly entering home straight, soon weakened.
Settled 2-wide just worse than midfield, came under pressure rounding home bend, found nothing after straightening and made no impression inside final 200 metres.

Travelled 3-wide without cover in midfield and improving to 3rd into back straight, drew level with the leaders rounding final bend but unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres. (Jockey warned for wide run.)
Jumped awkwardly settling well behind, made steady headway coming onto home bend when widest, dropped to tail-end on straightening.
Positively ridden out the gate, chased leader, took over mid-straight and kicked away to win by dominant margin.
Settled 4Ls off the pace in midfield, responded well on straightening, got up for 2nd 50M but couldn't get closer to the runaway winner.
Soon driven to the lead, set good pace to straight, no match with winner mid-straight, fought on to hold 3rd.
Reserved in midfield 5Ls off the pace, scrubbed along 450M, chased steadily but run ended passing 100M, pushed out of a place near the line.
From draw 1 moved up to track leaders, fought on early straight but couldn't keep up with them passing 200M.
Broke well, restrained to sit just behind leaders, held ground early straight, faded 150M.
Dropped back to race at the back of the field, ridden along 600M, ran past beaten horses in the straight, no threat to leaders.
Caught wide chasing leaders, lost cover from 850M, couldn't kick on turning home, just one paced in the straight.
Positioned in midfield along the 2-path, failed to pick up turning in, no threat to leaders. (Jockey : abnormal breathing noise concluding stages. Vet reported epiglottic issue.)
Checked after the start, always towards rear 7-8Ls off the pace, last turning in, never involved.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled behind midfield, couldn't go on final 300M, weakened badly mid-straight.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, towards the rear 7Ls away from leader, didn't respond to jockeys' urging from 400M out. (Overreach wound LF leg.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, took the lead 200M, kept on well, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3-1/2L back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight, peaked and headed 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced prominently but trapped wide, bumped near 550M, 2 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Clean jump, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Reared leaving stalls, raced at tail, 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter, checked final 50M.
Began only fairly, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back, bumped and carried wider on turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Moderately away, raced prominently on the stands' rail, took the lead after passing 600M, kept on very well final 400M, easily scored.
Away with them, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed some response, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, headed after passing 600M, hard ridden 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily to score.
Eased back, sat 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed early, midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 200M.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly
Sat in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Midfield, trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast sectionals, dropped off 500M.
Ridden along to take lead, travelled nicely on outside rail, responded strongly when asked for effort, scored by 5L.
Settled behind the speed, commenced to improve passing 500M, worked home nicely.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure near 400M, finished well.
Began very awkwardly, raced midfield close to middle of track, worked home well when placed pressure.
Travelled behind the leaders, asked for effort passing 500M, came home well.
Hard ridden along to race in a forward position, gave ground near 200M.
Jumped well, niggled to settle in front of midfield, tried to improve near 400M, remained one-paced.
Ridden along from inside barrier, settled inside the leaders in the middle of track, gave ground passing 200M.
Slow out, raced at rear, limited response when placed under pressure.
Raced inside the leaders, passing 300M lay out when placed pressure, gave ground passing 200M.
Slow out, raced detached in early stages, no response when placed pressure.
Travelled midfield, placed pressure passing 500M, weakened passing 200M.
Settled towards rear, raced greenly, weakened near 200M, rider report the horse made abnormal breathing noise, OVE.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on outside rail, faded out near 300M.

Had limited early speed & drifted back to last after first furlong. Continued at rear on straightening, sprinted quickly between runners near 300m, struck lead at 220m before drawing away in closing stages. Soft win.

Crowded & raced last early before improving to midfield. Improved onto leaders back near half-way, obtained clear running along rail, moved to second at 200m before finishing off well. No match for winner, clear of 3rd.

Had a nice run in midfield, away from the rail behind the leading trio. Moved wider on cornering, entered last section only 1.5L form lead, moved up to share lead near the 300m before being left behind by winner soon after.

Held narrow lead in early stages before racing between runners in a line of 3 at the front. Shared lead after straightening before drifting out under pressure at 350m. Battled on ok in concluding stages for well beaten 4th.

Had no early speed after the start & drifted back to second last. Continued at rear entering final section, less than 3L from lead. Shifted wider at the 350m before finishing off only fairly to midfield in concluding stages.

Ridden forward to hold the rail before improving to share the lead after 400m. Held slender lead nearing the 300m mark before peaking soon after & yielding ground sharply in last furlong. Well beaten.

Raced wide on the track in early stages before drifting back to obtain cover in midfield near 1000m. Drifted further back passing half-way before cornering 4L from lead. Offered no response in straight & was well beaten.

Ridden forward and sat three wide without cover in a line of three at the front. Continued to cover additional ground throughout before peaking soon after straightening & weakening out to last. Rider questioned.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, kept on well but still headed 100M, finished 2nd.
Slowly away, positioned slightly behind midfield on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Average to begin, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, similar position on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, challenged turning in, headed early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced very wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, battled on to the line and scored by 1-1/4L
Began awkwardly, settled in midfield, raced tight near 800M, closed off gamely, only to miss by 1-1/4L.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, ran on well but emptied in final 100M.
Began awkwardly and at rear, along the rail, badly checked near the 800M, saved ground and ran on well to the line. (Lame Right Front)
Rolled forward, along the rail, stayed on but emptied in final 100M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide near 550M, was one paced.
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 650M, stayed on until weakened at 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, saved minor ground in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail 650M, saved no ground in the straight.
Crowded start, at rear, did not feature. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, raced in midfield, near the 800M severely checked and did not run on.
Midfield, badly crowded for room near the 800M, didn't improve.
Began well from a wide gate, settled 2L back 2-wide in 4th, came to tackle the leaders under pressure after straightening and hit the front inside the 300 metres, held on well.

Settled just over 3L back in 5th 2-wide, raced keenly from the 1300 metres dropping slightly back to 6th, came to challenge entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening. (Blood in trachea)
Hard ridden early, settled in 8th on the rail about 5L off the speed, became 7th over 1000 metres out, angled out for a run entering home straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track.

Travelled in forward of midfield on the rails racing keenly at times, snuck up on the rail turning in but baulked for a run after straightening, switched in into the clear and quickened under pressure inside the final 250 metres.
Settled one back in 4th or 3rd on the rail, baulked for a run upon straightening until passing the 300 metres, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, given reminders to keep up with the pace early, remained in last few into home straight, saved ground on the rail turning in, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear of midfield from a wide gate, carried further back towards the rear 1200 metres out, produced good late impression inside the final 300 metres.

Pressed forward from a wide-ish gate, shared the lead on the rail before gaining over half a length clear passing the 1200 metres, led until joined into home straight, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.

Began well from the widest gate, travelled wide amongst the leaders early stages, settled some 1L back in 2nd from the 1200 metres, quickened to draw level entering home straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 250 metres.
Slowly away and always in last few, never seen with a chance. (Blood in trachea)
Began well, travelled strongly behind leader, quickened up challenge for lead 200M, gained upper hand final stages.
Sent forward, crossed to the lead before home turn, joined by winner near 200M, refused to give in, rallied back but unable to get the upper-hand.
Chased leader, every chance turning home, fought on well, outsprinted by first 2 final 200M.
Scrubbed along after the start, taken to fence in a rearward position, battled steadily to the line, well held by first 3.
Restrained after the start, travelled keenly 1100M when being steadied to obtain cover, wide on the turn, kept chasing in the straight but never going the pace to challenge.
Began only fairly, caught 4-wide no cover towards the rear, stayed on mildly down outside of straight, not reach leaders.
Settled 3Ls off leaders, couldn't quicken in the straight, just battled away.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide spot without cover, kept on same pace early straight, faded 200M.
Lost a considerable amount of ground after stumbling badly at the start, detached at the rear, never involved.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, angled out 500M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 150M, kept on strongly to hold off the challenger.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, ridden after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, positioned behind midfield on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, half-length back on turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Out in line, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M but only showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Stumbled at start, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 600M, 5 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor, unacceptable performance.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, slightly hampered near 500M, 4 lengths back turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7 to 8 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail early, angled out 800M, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, carried wider 800M, lost position on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.

Had fast early speed to come across from outside gate & assume uncontested lead. Raced over a length clear entering last section, joined in the lead by runner-up at 100m before digging deep in final strides for narrow win.

Had soft run in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Moved away from the inside on straightening, sprinted quickly passing 300m, moved up to share lead at 100m before being nosed out on line. Just missed, clear of 3rd.

Ridden forward but was crossed by winner & settled in leaders back position. Couldn't stick with the leader after entering the last section but battled away ok in concluding stages to hold well beaten third.

Steadied after start & taken back to second last. Moved the widest runner on straightening when a long way from lead before making up significant late ground to run to a well beaten 4th. Good run considering circumstances.
Steadied after the start & drifted back to race worse than midfield away from the rail. Shifted wider entering the last section when still well back before making up a length or two in final furlong.
Good position 1,1 throughout early & middle stages. Forced wider by runner-up entering last section before peaking at the 300m & weakening out in the final 250m.
Improved after the start to race in second, away from rail. Peaked on run soon after straightening & yielded over 6 lengths in the final 300m.

Raced in midfield away from the rail, cornered awkwardly at the 900m before easing wider on cornering. Four lengths form the lead entering last section but doubled that margin when racing greenly in straight. Never likely.
Raced in midfield on rail in early stages. Moved away from inside passing the 500m, entered last section 4.5L from lead before weakening out to be beaten 10L on line.
Crowded & lost ground at start & consequently raced at the rear. Continued a clear last on cornering & made no noteworthy improvement in straight. Well beaten.
Lost ground after the start & raced worse than midfield on rail. Cornered with only two runners behind before weakening out further in the straight to be a long second last.
Wasn't fast away but improved to midfield before being left three wide without cover throughout. Weakened out after straightening after covering extra ground. Long last.
