Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, ridden after 200M, showed very good response, easily scored. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, quickly moved to the stands' side, 1 to 2 lengths back, kept on evenly final 400M to take a place.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the stands' side, moved to the middle track after passing 450M, unable to obtain clear running until 150M, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the stands' rail, peaked in the middle stages, ran on evenly to the line.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the stands' side, 6 lengths or so back, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Stumbled shortly after start, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden and moved to the middle track after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield, 2 to 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden from 400M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began well, positioned right behind the leader on the stands' rail, lost position in the middle stages, one paced in the final 400M.
Jumped well, raced behind midfield, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced towards rear, hard ridden and moved to the middle track after passing 400M, failed to make any progress. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Moderately away, raced at rear on the stands' rail, showed nothing final 400M, well beaten.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Out in line, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed no response, weakened and eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
At back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden to take rail, led at very fast sectionals, hung on until 150M emptied.
In front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
At rear, on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made ground.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, no progress in straight.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, raced keenly, on heels 650M, no dash.
Eased at start, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, on heels 650M, weakened 500M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the very fast pace, emptied 300M.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve passing 700M, responded solidly, quickened passing 150M to score.
Niggled to take lead, asked for effort passing 500M, worked home solidly, blood in trachea.
Settled outside the lead, placed pressure passing 600M, finished nicely.
Taken back, asked for effort but only one-paced in the straight, failed to make impression.
Raced at tail, no response throughout, finished last.

Showed speed after start & raced outside leader. Travelled very strongly on straightening, moved up to assume lead near the 350m before continuing strongly in final furlong to win comfortably on line.
Raced in midfield away from rail. Eased wider approaching the corner, sprinted well but raced greenly in straight before closing within a length on line.
Improved after first section to race in midfield on the rail. Shifted out into clear running near the 300m before making steady late ground in final furlong to move to third inside final 50m.
Pushed forward before getting position 1,1. Boxed on well after straightening before being caught for third in closing stages. Not beaten far.

Improved after first furlong to race in midfield between runners. Continued in second half entering last section before making up a length in final furlong. Not beaten far. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Had no speed after start & drifted back to second last. Continued near the rear on straightening before making up a few lengths relative to winner when running on to midfield from rearward position.
Hard ridden at start to hold lead. Headed on the outside soon after straightening before weakening out in final 250m to be well held.

Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Ridden along before straightening before yielding a further length in the straight. Wasn't the worse effort considering wide passage but was never a winning threat.
Drifted back after start & raced last on rail. Effectively maintained position in the final section & never really played a major role.

Raced in midfield after first furlong before drifting back when racing very wide without cover throughout. Continued wide around home bend before entering last section at the tail. Wide & rearward throughout & never involved.

Raced in midfield after start before steadying & drifting back to settle worse than midfield passing the 900m. Ridden along to improve passing the 600m before offering no response & weakening further in straight.

Didn't begin fast but improved to race on leaders back before drifting 3L behind leader near 800m. Only 1.5L from lead entering last section but offered no response after straightening & weakened out poorly to be well beaten.

Ridden forward from wide gate before three wide without cover in 4th.Continued close to lead nearing the 300m before peaking soon after & weakening out sharply in closing stages after tough run throughout. (Lame next day).
Steadied after start & shifted to the rear. Continued near the rear on cornering, continued rearward passing furlong mark, checked near the 150m but was always well back regardless. Last.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 750M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off strongly to score.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 3 wide at rear, no cover on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Away with them, positioned right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 300M, kept on well to take a place, no match to the first two.
Moderately away, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, angled out after passing 450M, closed off well to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, 2 wide from 650M, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, positioned 5 to 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, showed limited response in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover slightly better than midfield, 2 wide after passing 750M, commenced move 500M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 10, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, found a 2 wide spot near 650M, commenced move after passing 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 650M, checked 600M, peaked turning in, ran on evenly to 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, steadied off heels near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began awkwardly, at rear, along the rail, kicked away from 200M, ran on nicely to score.
In front of midfield, along the rail, headed by winner near 250M, but battled all the way to finish 1L behind.
Raced in midfield initially, at rear after 1200M, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, closed off nicely inside 200M.
At rear initially, rolled forward after 950M, 3 wide with cover after 650M, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, rolled forward, 2 wide after 1050M, stayed on but emptied in final 150M.
At rear initially, after 1400M checked and rolled forward after 1200M, 3 wide no cover, was one paced.
Crowded start, at rear, along the rail, saved ground and ran on well.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line. (Lame Right Hind)
Began awkwardly, raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight.
Midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, kept on one paced to the line. (Mildly Lame Left Front and Sore Left Front Tendon)
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide didn't improve and lost ground.
Rolled forward and led, along the rail, in the straight lost ground. (See Incident Report)
Settled in midfield, commenced move after straightening and quickened well to snatch victory close to home.
Recovered steadily from a moderate start to stalk the leader on the rail, held similar position into straight, fought on steadily under pressure but outsprinted close to home.
Began well from a wide gate, led off the rail before gaining rails run 2L in front 1200 metres out, swamped inside the final 100 metres.
Settled just better than midfield over 4L back in 5th, commenced move entering straight and ran on steadily under pressure.
Ridden from a wide gate before settling some 2L back in 3rd near the rail, kept on same pace in straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, wide in last few when hampered and dropped further back over 1000 metres out, saved ground on rails turning into straight where produced good late finish.
Soon taken back from the widest gate and waited with, went wide into home straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track but never threatening.
Settled in midfield on the rail, moved closer to 4th over 3L back coming onto home bend, saved ground on the rail turning in, faded under pressure.
Jumped awkwardly and taken back to last few where travelling keenly, inconvenienced about 1100 metres out, saved ground on the inside entering home straight, ran home one-paced.
Jumped very awkwardly losing ground, settled towards the rear in 10th on the rail, gained slightly closer to midfield in 6th coming onto home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, never better than midfield, held 9th on the rail some 7L back rounding home bend, unable to quicken under pressure in straight.
Travelled wide towards the rear, very wide without cover rounding home bend and into straight, found nothing.
Began well from a wide gate, gradually taken back in midfield but remained wide without cover throughout, dropped further back turning into straight.
Began awkwardly settling just worse than midfield, unbalanced and hampered on top of home bend and gave ground.
Settled 3Ls off the pace, quickened strongly on straightening, pulled away from 200M, won by dominant margin.
Began awkwardly, failed to muster speed despite ridden along, held up towards the rear, stayed on to go 2nd near line, no chance with runaway winner.
Chased leader, no match with winner early straight, battled on, held 2nd until concluding stages.
Restrained in a rearward spot, about 5Ls to make up 400M, ran on steadily down outside for distant 4th.
Led early stages, tracked pace from 1100M, fought on one paced on straightening.
Up with early pace, took outright lead from 1100M, fought on to 200M, faded. (Jockey : not intended to lead, strode forward 1200M to avoid covering unnecessary ground. / Lame next day.)
Unable to slot in from wide draw, caught 3 deep at rear, not pace to challenge in straight, no extra final 150M.
Saved ground on inside, always in touch, couldn't go on in the straight, no impression final 200M.
Commenced well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader, moved closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 150M, ran on well, won by 2 lengths.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, 9 lengths back, moved closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made very good progress to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Bumped start, sent forward to race in 2nd, a length back, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but still headed 150M, weakened close home, missed 2nd on line.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 550M, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider after passing 600M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer in the middle stages, still 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 11 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in straight.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight, eased final 50M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, raced wide with cover at rear, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide from 500M, had every chance in straight, kept on well but just no match to the winner.
Began well from gate 12, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 150M, stayed on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, positioned behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, still last turning in, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed near 250M, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Lame right front leg next day.)
Away with them, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened after passing 500M. (Roarer.)

Began well before being crossed and racing in midfield on rail. Moved away from the inside on straightening, shifted wider again at 350m before making continual headway to strike lead in final strides. Narrow winner.

Began well before settling in midfield between runners. Moved closer to lead near half-way before cornering 2L behind. Made continual headway to strike lead inside final 100m before being caught by winner last few strides.

Raced in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Moved away from the inside approaching the corner, shifted wider entering the last section before closing off strongly in final 250m to narrowly beaten third.

Checked near 900m & raced wide in the second half. Improved position in middle stages when continuing to cover extra ground. Five lengths behind on straightening, closed off strongly in concluding stages to not be beaten far.

Showed speed to lead before crossing to rail near 850m. Raced over 1.5L clear entering the last section before being headed inside the final 100m & tiring a length or two late. Not far behind after setting the speed.

Steadied after start before being inconvenienced near the 1000m. Again hampered near 950m & consequently relegated to last. Clear last on cornering before moving wider & making solid late ground from poor position.

Raced in midfield between runners early before drifting further back passing half-way. Entered last section over 5 lengths from the lead before making up a few lengths when running on to midfield from rearward position.

Crowded at start, raced near the rear before being checked near the 1000m & racing at tail. Continued near the tail on straightening before making up a length or two when running on to midfield from the back.

Raced in midfield after start before losing ground when checked near the 950m & consequently racing wide with cover thereafter. Entered last section 4 lengths from the lead & effectively held position in dash to line.
Improved after start but was left racing 3 wide without cover in 4th place. Cornered very wide before peaking on effort at the 300m & weakened out after covering additional ground throughout.
Ridden forward after start before crossing to rail & racing on leaders back. Entered last section only 2.5L from lead but weakened out meekly in final 300m. Well beaten.
Crowded at start before improving position to race outside the leader nearing the 800m. Came under hard riding on straightening & weakened out sharply in final 250m.
Raced in midfield on rail after start before drifting further back after first furlong. Made no improvement after straightening & beat only one runner home.
Began only fairly & settled third from last. Moved wider approaching the corner but did nothing in the straight & was a well beaten last.

Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to score.

Began awkwardly and bumped, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 700M, sat right behind the leader on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, wider after passing 400M, closed off well to take a place.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Made contact shortly after start, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, took the lead 800M, found rail near 700M, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, 2 wide from 700M, 4 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, inconvenienced near 200M, made minor progress thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 400M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, still 8 lengths back turning in, made little progress in straight.
Began well from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, very wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight. (Lost left front plate in the early stages.)
Hard ridden to secure box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 3rd.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, on heels 600M, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, benefited by the slow sectionals, no dash.
Eased at start, 3 wide at rear, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, crowded for room 400M, dropped off afterwards.
Slow away, never competitive.
Settled behind midfield, improved near 500M, widest on straightening, quickened passing 200M to score.
Settled outside the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home solidly.
Raced in box seat, commenced to improve passing 400M, responded nicely in the straight.
At start lost right front plate, travelled midfield on rail, asked for effort near 500M, finished one-paced.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, in the straight fought hard but only one-paced.
Settled midfield, passing 1400M was checked, wide on straightening, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, tried to improve near 600M, limited response in the straight.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, came under pressure near 600M, gave ground in the straight.
Urged along after start, steadied away from heels near 1600M, raced towards rear, came under pressure passing 800M, no response in the straight.
Slow to begin, settled at rear, placed pressure but no response, passing 100M was checked.
Ridden along to take lead, came under pressure passing 500M, weakened in the straight.
Reared and very slow to jump, raced at tail, near 600M lost left front plate, placed pressure passing 500M, no response in the straight, must trial.

Shifted behind runners after start to race midfield away from rail. Moved wider approaching the 400m, second widest on straightening before making strong ground to strike lead at 75m & just hold out fast finisher.
Had nice position 1,1 throughout. Moved wider nearing the 350m to avoid tiring runner, awkwardly placed near the 200m before rocketing home in closing 100m to go down by narrowest margin.

Pushed forward before being crossed & racing on leaders back. Travelled well nearing corner, dashed up to assume lead at the 250m, battled hard to continue in front until being claimed by winner at the 75m. Just behind.

Steadied & taken back to last. Continued at rear entering last section when 7.5 lengths from lead. Moved wider on straightening before making very strong late ground to close to forth, less than a length behind on line.

Raced to midfield but left three wide without cover. Two lengths from lead entering last section, improved to share lead near 200m before peaking late. Beaten under a length, creditable given wide trip throughout.

Steadied from outside gate at start before improving to just worse than midfield away from rail. Moved wider passing 500m before cornering the widest. Made continual steady ground in straight to be less than 2L behind.

Crowded at start & consequently raced in midfield on rail. Moved away from rail nearing 400m when under 4L from lead before being badly checked by tiring runner at 350m. Never picked up in straight but had genuine excuse.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Stayed close to the inside approaching corner when 3.5 lengths from lead. Could only maintain position in the straight & never provided a threat.
Ridden forward after start to lead. Raced over a length clear on straightening before being headed at the 250m & weakening out sharply in last furlong. Well beaten.

Hard ridden at start but failed to show any speed before shifting across to race second last on rail. Came under hard riding at the 450m before offering no response in the straight & being well beaten.
Steadied at start & shifted back to race in final trio. Continued near the rear throughout before weakening a further few lengths in the straight & beat only one home. Beaten 9L.
Improved after start to race second, away from rail without cover. Began yielding ground quickly from the 450m before tailing out quickly in the straight to be a long last.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, there to turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, raced wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Away well, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out 200M, finished off strongly to take a place. (Dead-heat 3rd.)
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged turning in, kept on well in straight but still headed 100M, tired last bit and missed frame.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, hampered near 650M, 3 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 150M but only showed limited response, checked 50M, eased close home.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide from near 650M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened thereafter.

Moderately away from gate 11, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, hampered near 650M, saved ground on turn, kept on well early in straight, severely checked near 50M, eased thereafter. (Rider dropped whip near 50M.)
Shifted in at start and bumped, trapped wide in midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Midfield, wide no cover, battled on to the line and scored by a neck.
Rolled forward and led, along the rail, battled on to the line to take 2nd. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, midfield, 3 wide but with cover, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Settled to race in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on well to the line.
Bumped start, raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, checked in the Straight and awkwardly placed near 50M.
Rolled forward, 2 wide after 600M, ran on fairly to the line.
Taken back, along the rail, crowded for room in the Straight and pretty one paced thereafter.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, showed no response.
At rear, 2 wide, was one paced.
At rear, 2 wide, did not feature.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight.
Crowded start, midfield, 2 wide, made no threats.

Settled towards the rear on the rail, shifted 2-wide passing the 900 metres, inconvenienced when attempted to improve passing the 600 metres, renewed effort in straight and quickened well to assert authority near finish.
Ridden positively before settling outside the leader, hit the front entering home straight kicking 1L clear briefly only to be caught by the eventual winner close to home.
Travelled 3-wide but with cover behind midfield on the far side, went widest into home straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled some 2L back in 5th, commenced move entering home straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Restrained in midfield early stages but travelled keenly most of the way in back straight, commenced move turning in for home and ran on under pressure but unable to sustain effort closing stages.

Began well from a middle gate travelling prominently 3-wide without cover most of the way, came to challenge upon straightening holding some chance, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Well back, dropped to last into home straight, produced impressive late finish inside the final 200 metres.
Settled well behind on the rail from a wide gate, remained in rear in similar position to straight, angled out for a run upon straightening, ran on past well-beaten horses.

Taken back to rear 3-wide from the widest gate travelling keenly around the first bend, remained wide without cover in back straight and on final bend before going wider into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Held up in midfield on the rail, remained same into home straight, switched in for a run but ran into heels at the 200 metres.
Began well settling just off the pace on the rail, chased behind the leader until finding no extra early in home straight.
Attempted to make all taking advantage of the low draw, held narrow lead until headed into home straight, folded up quickly. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Tracked leader, travelled well into straight, quickened to lead 250M, well in control final 200M, never challenged.
Slotted into a 2-wide spot in midfield just over 4Ls off the pace, awkwardly placed top of straight, switched 250M, ran on well to go 2nd nearing 100M without threatening winner.
Not hurried after the start, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, driven passing 500M, brought wide on straightening, stayed on well to go 3rd just in time, not reached first 2.
Jumped on terms, settled just ahead of midfield, well placed to strike top of straight, not pace to challenge leaders final 200M, lost 3rd near line.
From draw 12 dropped back to race at the rear, swung widest home, stayed on moderately down outside of track.
From wide draw steadied to obtain cover early stages , settled 2-wide towards rear, wide into straight, stayed on fairly final 300M, never threatened.
Tracked leaders in 4th, always in touch, kept on one paced in the straight, no impression on leaders final 200M.

From draw 1 scrubbed along to take up running, travelled keenly in the lead, headed passing 300M, faded mid-straight. (Jockey : not able to finish off due to the manner his horse travelled in middle stages.)
Restrained after the start, held up towards the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, responded fairly turning in, never a threat to leaders.
Taken back from wide draw, reserved in the rear 9Ls back, made limited progress in the straight.
Chased leader 2-wide, under pressure to keep up passing 500M, weakened in the straight.
Soon taken across behind runners, held up behind midfield, couldn't finish off turning in, weakened to last mid-straight.

Moderately away, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late. (Lost right front plate shortly after start.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared after passing 250M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, weakened close home, just stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, closed off well to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, made some headway thereafter without threatening.
Away with them, taken back to race at tail, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, there to turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight. (Laceration to the left front cannon.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, trapped very wide in midfield, no cover throughout, 3 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, peaked turning in, weakened gradually in straight.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide from 750M, commenced move after passing 500M, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 100M, in command close home.
Moderately away, raced towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, hard ridden after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd on line.

Jumped with them, forced very wide in the early stages, 2 lengths back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 3 wide from 800M, 2 wide turning in, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently on rail, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 100M, no extra close home.
Away with them, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, allowed rival to cross near 950M, carried wider 750M, no cover on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began very awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced wide with cover behind midfield at the early stages, dropped to rear after passing 1000M, 8 to 9 lengths back turning in, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, still well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Hampered at start, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, checked near 600M, 6 lengths back turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 800M, raced tight near 600M, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.
Stumbled at start, trapped very wide in the early stages, a length or so back, sent forward after passing 1100M, 2 wide from 800M, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Hard ridden early, settled in midfield, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
At back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, led 400M, emptied 100M.
Pushed early, sat 2 wide behind the leaders, raced keenly, not suited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, weakened 250M.
Eased to rear, 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, made good ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, not suited by the fast pace, on heels 300M, weakened onwards.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide in the lead, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
At back along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, no dash.
At back, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, suited by the fast pace, raced flat until 150M made minor ground.
Eased back, raced keenly, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, checked 800M, emptied 300M.
Niggled to race in front of midfield, issued challenge near 200M, quickened near 50M to score.
Jumped nicely, settled in handy position, commenced to improve passing 450M, responded strongly in the straight.
Hard ridden from widest barrier to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, fought nicely in the straight.
Settled in handy position, asked for effort near 400M, battled well in the straight.
Urged along to race behind the lead, placed pressure near 450M, responded well in the straight, close to line was awkwardly placed and not fully tested.
Settled midfield, 3 wide and without cover passing 800M, continued to make ground in the straight, worked home well.
Settled midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, finished well.
Slow out then hard ridden to race behind midfield on rail, gained some ground in the straight.
Taken back, raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, worked home one-paced.
Raced towards rear, placed pressure but only limited response in the straight.
Taken back then raced detached, became unbalanced near 950M, no response throughout.
Settled midfield, came under pressure passing 550M, weakened passing 200M.
Taken back, raced greenly, wide rounding the Home Turn, gave ground in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, came under pressure near 500M, faded out passing 300M.

Drifted back after start to race worse than midfield on rail. Shifted wider after straightening, 5 lengths form the lead, before finishing strongly in last furlong to strike narrow lead final few strides. (Lame RF next day).

Raced in midfield before being pushed three wide with cover after first bend. Hung outwards in middle stages before cornering 3L from lead. Finished strongly in final 300m, before being caught by winner in final strides.
Showed early speed to cross to rail when leading after 200m. Maintained length lead entering last section before being joined & headed in closing stages. Close behind third, well of 4th.

Not the fastest away but travelled well when racing worse than midfield between runners. Eased wider passing the 600m mark before corning second widest. Made continual late ground to close to 4th. Good debut.

Showed speed to stride forward, 3 wide without cover early before steading passing 800m to get 1,1. Raced tight when forced wider on cornering before peaking on effort at the 200m & giving a length or two late.
Began well before being crossed & racing on leaders back. Race tight when moving away from inside on cornering before peaking at the furlong & wilding a few lengths late.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Stayed on the inside on straightening, 3L from the lead entering last section before failing to improve & never threatened when weakening out to be 5L behind.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Drifted further back passing the 700m when being niggled along. Shifted wider on cornering before effectively holding position in dash to line. No threat.
Drifted back after start to settle third from last. Continued near the rear in cornering before passing a few tiring runners in closing stages but never making any noteworthy headway into margin.

Steadied after the start & shifted across behind runners to race second last. Continued near the rear, over 6 lengths from lead entering last section before failing to make any rear headway in straight. (Lame RF next day).

Began well to race in midfield before hard ridden to improve approaching the 800m when only 2.5 lengths from lead. Continued between runners on cornering before weakening out meekly in final 300m. Well beaten.
Improved after the start to race to second, away from the rail. Entered last section a length behind the lead before weakening out sharply in final 300m. Beaten over 9L.

Was the slowest to begin before being shifted back to last. Moved wider passing the 500m but continued last on cornering, over 7L from the lead. Did nothing in straight & beat only one home when 10 lengths behind.

Trapped four and 5 wide in midfield throughout. Drifted further back passing 700m before being relegated to effectively last when cornering the widest. Never improved after covering additional round & was long last.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off well to take a place, missed 2nd on line.

Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress early in straight, no clear run near 200M, angled out thereafter and finished off well to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned right behind the leader, there to turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 1000M, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider after passing 600M, 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well from a tricky draw, trapped very wide early, taken back to race at rear after 1400M, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, headed early in straight, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked 200M, headed and weakened shortly thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame right front leg.)
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
In front of midfield, along the rail, battled on to the line and scored by 1-1/2L.
Rolled forward and raced outside the lead, 2 wide, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Slow to begin, taken back, along the rail, saved ground and closed off strongly.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, raced tight and checked near 250M, ran on well to the line. (See Incident Report)
Bumped start, raced in one-out-one-back position after 900M, kept on until 150M and faded gradually
Rolled forward, 3 wide with no cover, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed some dash approaching 150M to save ground.
At rear, 2 wide, saved minor ground in the straight.
Raced in midfield, wide with no cover, was one paced.
At rear, along the rail, did not feature.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight.
Bumped start, rolled forward, along the rail, lost ground after 200M and gave ground. (See Incident Report)
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, did not feature.
Raced in behind midfield, near 700M raced ungenerously and checked, gave ground thereafter.
Made all setting a sedate pace to the 800 metres, quickened up rounding home bend and even faster in the straight, held on well.

Recovered quickly from the sluggish start to be midfield on the rail, drifted back to rear when pace quickened on top of home bend but saved ground turning in, ran on strongly in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled just off the slow early pace in 3rd on the rail, commenced move upon straightening, fought on well only to be caught for 2nd close to home.

Settled within 3L of the slow pace on the rail, remained in similar position until approaching home straight, tight between runners when pace quickened inside the 300 metres, made up good late ground closing stages.
Travelled not far off in 4th, looked swamped by wide runners making final turn, fought on steadily without threatening.
Pressed forward to dispute lead around the first bend, settled 1L back 2-wide in back straight, unable to sustain effort under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Taken well back from a wide gate, switched wide for a run entering home straight, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Settled just worse than midfield on the rail from a wide gate, in similar position into straight, held up for a run from inside the 300 metres to over 200 metres out, not able to be tested in closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly from a wide gate losing ground and settling at the back, went very wide turning in for home, ran past well-beaten horses in closing stages.
Settled in forward of midfield in 6th just over 3L off the pace, 4-wide rounding home bend and into the straight, failed to quicken with others in the run to the line.
Travelled keenly early on in the slow pace and in rear of midfield in back straight, 5-wide rounding home bend and into the straight, failed to quicken with others despite coming under pressure.
Settled towards the rear from a wide gate, circled the field rounding home bend, widest runner in midfield turning in for home, found no extra shortly after straightening.
Tracked the pace, quickened up strongly to lead 250M, soon drew away for wide margin victory.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, stayed on steadily to go 2nd near line, no threat to runaway winner. (Lame next day.)
Reserved behind mid-division 7Ls off the pace, kept on mildly over final 300M, no threat to runaway winner.
Caught wide no cover early stages, strode forward to join leader 1000M, vied for lead early straight, no match with winner mid-straight, no extra late lost 2 places near line.
Not hurried, settled near last 8Ls back, made some progress final 300M but never seriously threatened.
Crossed to the lead 1400M, pressed by rival 1000M, fought on in the straight until weaken final 150M.
Taken back from wide draw, held up near last 8Ls away, stayed on passing beaten runners in the straight, never near to challenge leaders.
Settled ahead of midfield, came under pressure 600M, failed to finish off. (Unacceptable Performance / Lame next day.)
Switched off to race in last, 10Ls behind leader at 400M, ran on fairly passing beaten horses.
In mid-division, travelled keenly 1100M, couldn't go on entering straight, made no impression.
Raced keenly early stages, checked 1400M and lost ground, moved forward to track leaders middle stages, run ended 200M, weakened.
From draw 1 settled just ahead of midfield along the inside rail, found nothing when asked on straightening, never involved.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, 2 wide from 700M, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, a bit closer on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame,

Began well, raced 2 wide, a length so back, similar position in the middle stages, 3 wide turning in, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.

Commenced well, unable to slot in early, slightly taken back after passing 1100M, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield in the middle stages, 5 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, led by a length turning in, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began only fairly and bumped, raced 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on one pace to the line.
Away with them, raced prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Made contact shortly after start, forced very wide, 2 lengths or so back, found cover near 700M, 3 to 4 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened and eased final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to score.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 450M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, there to turn, no clear running until final 150M, made some headway thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wide after passing 550M, made some headway early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 12, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield, similar position on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 1-1/2L back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, eased thereafter.
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, eased final 100M. (Lame left front and right hind legs.) (Mucus.)
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, wider from 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide behind midfield, there to turn, one paced in straight.

Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out 400M, took the lead 250M, kept on very well, easily scored.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd on line, no threat to the winner.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, wider turning in, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the winner.

Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter, lost 2 places on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, dropped to midfield in the middle stages, angled out after passing 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Away well from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off one pace.
Slowly away, detached early, got back to it in the middle stages, still 9 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight. (Heat stress post-race.)
Took keen hold, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.

Shifted out at start and bumped, hard ridden early but only showed limited speed, trapped very wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, positioned outside to the leader 600M, weakened after passing 450M, eased final furlong.
Average to begin, raced prominently, 2 wide, unable to maintain position in the middle stages, emptied early in straight, unacceptable performance.
Pressed forward steadily, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon overhauled 400M, ran on for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, suited by the fast tempo, blocked 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Checked start, at back, along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made ground.
Midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on ok in straight.
At rear, trapped 2-4 wide, suited by the fast tempo, ran on only fairly.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide at back, no dash.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, harmed by the fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3-4 wide at rear, checked 350M, no dash.
At back, never competitive.
Trapped 3 wide throughout in midfield, dropped off 400M.
Settled midfield, improved near 450M, fought strongly to score in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, battled well in the straight, missed by SH.
Ridden forward to take lead, travelled comfortably, responded strongly in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Raced in front of midfield, made the turn near 900M awkwardly, held up in the early part of straight, gained some ground in the straight.
Jumped nicely, niggled to race outside the lead, gave ground passing 150M.
Urged to settled behind leaders, weakened passing 200M, rider question tactic.
Began awkwardly then bumped a runner, became unbalanced and lost ground, one-paced in the straight.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure but only limited response, failed to make impression.
Raced behind midfield, lay out rounding the Home Turn, finished one-paced.
Raced behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 450M, gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, no response when placed pressure.
Settled towards rear, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Travelled at tail, widest on straightening, no response throughout.
Strode forward from gate 14 before slotting into 1,1 position after 400m. Moved up to take narrow lead at 350m before digging in strongly last furlong to win.

Began well before steadying and shifting across to midfield away from rail. Shifted into clear running after straightening, made good ground to move to second passing the 300m before finishing well to hold second.
Improved after start to race on leaders back. Held up in early part of straight, improved to third soon after 300m mark before finishing well to hold that position on line.

Not bustled, drifted back to worse than midfield before shifting down to rail passing 1300m. Moved away from rail nearing the 600m, before improving between runners after straightening & closing to 4th inside last furlong.

Bumped at start then failed to muster speed consequently racing second last. Moved wider & improved to midfield nearing the 900m. Moved the second widest on cornering before passing a few in dash to line.

Failed to improve after start & consequently settled in midfield. Drifted further back middle stages before being awkwardly placed & shuffled back to last entering last section. Passed a few in dash home but never likely.

Shifted across behind runners after start to settle at tail. Continued at the back on cornering, stayed close to the inside on straightening before passing a few to midfield but never threatening, beaten 5L.

Drifted back after start before shifting down to rail after first furlong before improving to midfield. Continued in midfield position 3.5L from lead passing 800m. Did little in the straight & was beaten.

Raced worse than midfield before improving position in middle stages when racing three wide with cover. Moved 4 wide on cornering, entered last section only 2.5 lengths from lead before peaking & weakening out last 250m.

Showed good speed after start to hold initial lead before racing outside leader in middle stages. Regained lead before near 600m before being joined & headed by winner near the 350m. Weakened out sharply in final 300m.

Steadied after start & taken back to third last after start. Relegated to second last near the 1300m. Continued at back before moving the widest runner on cornering. Failed to improve in straight and was beaten nearly 10L.

Strode forward, raced prominently but left three wide without cover, outside leading pair. Came under hard riding & commenced to yield ground before cornering before tailing out in straight to be beaten big margin.
Held the rail and improved after start to assume narrow lead approaching the 1200m. Headed in the lead approaching the 600m before weakening out significantly from on straightening to be a long last.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 750M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challenger.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to take 2nd, just missed by a narrow margin.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held by the first two.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back turning in, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide from 800M, 4 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Bumped on jumping, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail, 9 lengths back turning in, passed a few tired runners in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 250M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, forced wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back turning in, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 8 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Out in line, raced 3 wide towards rear, 10 lengths back turning in, showed nothing in straight.
In front of midfield, 2 wide after 700M, improved steadily to the line and scored by a Neck.
At rear, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off nicely to take 2nd.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, stayed on but headed after 75M.
Raced in one-out-one-back position after 700M, in the Straight was brushed and ran on well to the line. (Lame Right Front)
Sent forward, along the rail after 800M, kept on until 200M and faded gradually.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, showed some dash approaching 150M to save ground.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, 3 wide no cover, was one paced. (See Incident Report and "Roarer")
Sent forward, along the rail, lost ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Began awkwardly and at rear, along the rail, did not feature.
At rear, 2 wide, made no ground.
Bumped start and raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide after 700M, gave ground after 350M. (Substantial Amount of Mucus and Lame Right Front)
Moderate start from the two draw, settled one back on the rail to home straight, obtained clear run on the inside shortly after straightening and gained upper hand 200 metres out.
Settled behind midfield in 7th from the widest gate, quickened well from wide into straight to just fail to get up on line.
Began well from the one draw to lead, joined rounding home bend but re-gained narrow advantage early in straight, unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Jumped fairly, travelled prominently and wide early stages, improved to dispute lead around home bend, kept on same pace early in straight until finding no extra over 200 metres out.
Trailed the field most of the way, given a reminder over 400 metres out, ran on past well-beaten horses in the run to the line.
Close up, faded shortly after straightening.
Awkward start, settled in 6th within 3L of pace to home straight, found no room and hampered 350 metres out, no further impression thereafter.
Crowded at start and dropped to the rear in 8th, commenced move off the rail rounding home bend, made no impression from rear and wide into the straight.
Improved steadily to prominent positon 3-wide, remained in similar no-cover position to straight, weakened under pressure.
Crowded for room on jumping, settled down 2-wide behind midfield, moved up swiftly from 400M to challenge for the lead, gained upper hand 150M.
Led from 1300M, dropped back to 2nd home turn, responded well from 400M, vied for lead with eventual winner until 150M, held final stages.
Held up behind mid-division along the fence, 4Ls off the pace 400M, responded mildly in straight, got up for 3rd late but not getting to first 2.
Dropped back to the rear 6Ls off the pace, ran on steadily under top weight, just missed 3rd.
Settled down in 2nd, raced keenly from 1100M, improved into lead 800M, headed 350M, run ended 150M, faded to 5th.
Never far off from leaders, saved ground on inside, kept on same pace from straightening, never seriously threatened.
Raced 3-wide in midfield, lay in under pressure in straight, just battled home, never looked likely.
Slow to begin, reserved near the back of the field, kept on fairly in the straight, did not threaten.
Always in touch, gave limited response early straight, weakened passing 300M.
Began fairly, assumed running in midfield, raced wide without cover from 1500M, soon beaten on straightening.
Settled 3-wide at the rear, 6Ls to make up turning in, didn't respond to riding and failed to finish off the race. (Jockey unable to provide any excuses for the disappointing run.)
Bumped start, taken back to race at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared after passing 300M, finished off very strongly to score.
Commenced well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced prominently but trapped wide, took the lead 1250M, found rail near 900M, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 wide on turn, carried wider after passing 500M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 250M, peaked shortly thereafter, weakened gradually final 100M.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, restrained and allowed rival to cross after passing 1150M, 3/4L back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the narrow lead on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed good response but still headed 150M, kept on well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths or so back in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Out in line, raced towards rear on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, made some headway to make frame without threatening.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, nearer to the stands' side, hard ridden from 400M, only showed limited response, peaked on run 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, raced at tail in the middle of the track, kept on well final 400M, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced in the middle of the track, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, ridden after 300M, showed limited response, weakened thereafter.

Shifted in on jumping and bumped, raced in the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, moved closer in the middle stages, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well from gate 14, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length or so back on the stands' side, peaked 500M, weakened final 300M.
Began fairly, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, peaked on run 400M, weakened gradually thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, peaked in the middle stages, weakened final 300M.
Jumped with them, positioned a length behind the leader, nearer to the middle track, peaked 500M, weakened thereafter, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
