Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight to hold off the challenger.

Slightly slow out, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 150M, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, half length back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Away with them, raced prominently, 3 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Box seat, lack room 400M, closed off strongly to score whilst racing greenly.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, blocked 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, hung on until 150M overhauled, checked 50M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, blocked 400M, dashed well when clear.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, harmed by the slow pace, lack room in straight, little dash.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, weakened 250M.
At back along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room in straight, little dash.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide outside the leaders, out of fuel 250M.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Checked start, at back, 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Trapped 4-5 wide throughout in midfield, emptied 300M.
Jumped sharply, settled in handy position, placed pressure near 700M, quickened passing 200M to score.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield on rail, travelled keenly in middle stages and checked away from heels near 1050M, fought strongly in the straight, heat stress after racing.
Settled midfield, niggled near 1000M, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Took lead after 1400M, commenced to improve on straightening, fought well in the straight.
Niggled to take forward position, raced behind the lead, asked for effort passing 500M, responded nicely in the early part of straight, gave some ground near 50M.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 400M, gained some ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 700M, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced towards rear on rail, placed pressure passing 600M, made some ground in the straight.
Raced at back, niggled near 1000M, widest on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, after 1100M was left racing wide and without cover, placed pressure passing 450M, rider dropped whip passing 50M, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, improved to midfield near 1100M, hard ridden near 700M, no response in the straight.
Settled in handy position on rail, came under pressure near 700M, gave ground near 200M.
Raced at rear, tried to improve passing 800M, wide rounding the Home Turn, weakened in the straight.
Taken back at start, improved to handy position near 1000M, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, faded out in the straight.

Began fast to lead. Travelled very strongly in middle stages, raced a little greenly entering last section before drawing away inside final furlong to win my very big margin. Super impressive debut, class record.
Bumped at start before improving to race in first 4. Moved to second entering last section & finished off well to hold that place but was no match for winner.
Raced in midfield between runners. Closed off well in final 150m to move to third in final 50m. Good debut.
Raced on the leaders back when between runners in midfield. Battled on ok in final furlong to hold 4th on line. Only half-length behind second.
Showed speed to race prominently just inside the leader, closer to stand side rail. Continued close entering last section before peaking at 200m & being caught for third in final 50m.
Bumped at start before racing in midfield closer to center of track. Maintained position relative to placed horses in final section & held midfield finish.
Began very awkwardly & lost ground before settling worse than midfield. Improved slightly to midfield after half-way before holding midfield position on stand side rail in last section.
Began awkwardly from inside barrier & consequently raced near the rear throughout. Passed a few in final section when racing near center of track but was never a threat.
Bumped at start before drifting back to race near the rear. Hard ridden from before halfway & never featured.
Raced in midfield after start before drifting further back after first 400m. Niggled along passing half-way before weakening out further in last 300m to be well beaten on debut.
Bumped at start before showing some speed soon after to race in first three. Niggled along passing the 400m mark before weakening out in the final 300m to be beaten over 10L.
Raced in midfield closer to the center of track. Was only just over 2L from lead entering the final section before tiring badly in final 300m to be beaten over 10L.

Was slightly slow to begin & consequently raced near the tail on the stand side rail. Relegated to clear last after first 400m, before making no improvement in last section & beating only one runner home.
Raced in midfield on stand side rail in early stages before drifting further back after first 300m. Crowded & lost ground near the 400m before tailing out to be a long last.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on strongly in straight, easily scored.
Jumped well, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, bumped turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, kept on evenly in straight to take a place.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths or so back turning in, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to quicken in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 length back turning in, showed nothing in straight.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race in 2nd, 1 to 2 lengths back turning in, weakened early in straight.
Began well, raced prominently on rail early, allowed rival to cross 700M, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, peaked on turn, severely checked near 400M, eased early in straight.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, kept on to score.
Rolled forward and raced behind the leader, along the rail, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Sent forward, sat outside the lead, battled on to the line for 3rd.
Sat one-out one-back, ran on well for 4th.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, improved steadily in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground steadily.
Midfield, 2 wide, stayed on but emptied passing 100M. (Lame Left Front)
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide no cover, show no turn on foot. (Epiglottic Ulceration)
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, lost ground after 100M. (See Incident Report)
At rear, made no impression. (Rider expressed concern about the horse's action)
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, didn't threaten.

Began well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on the rail, became 4th some 3L back rounding home bend, saved ground turning in, hit the front from tiring pace-setter 300 metres out and never looked back.
Settled towards the rear on the rail after a moderate start, commenced move shortly after straightening and obtained a clear run over 250 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field from the 1200 metres, ran on well inside the final 300 metres down the centre of the track.
Settled wide in midfield or slightly better, over 3L back in 6th 2-wide rounding home bend, soon came to challenge upon straightening, ran home one-paced.
Settled some 2L back in 3rd to 5th, in similar position turning for home, kept on same pace without quickening.
Ridden along after a moderate start, settled in rear of midfield in 9th on the rail, in similar position until shifted 2-wide rounding home bend, failed to quicken to challenge in straight.
Improved steadily from a moderate start to lead after the first 200 metres, ceded advantage coming onto home bend, gradually faded under pressure after straightening.

Niggled along in first few after beginning from a wide gate, came to dispute the lead passing the 1000 metres and went 2L clear rounding home bend, headed by eventual winner 300 metres out and weakened.
Settled wide in rear from the widest gate, widest turning in, one-paced in straight.

Broke well from a wide gate but soon taken back to worse than midfield, saved ground on the inside turning for home, produced short-lived effort early in straight, unable to sustain run inside the final 200 metres. (Bled)
Prominent briefly, settled in midfield, inconvenienced and lost position 900 metres out, wide into home straight, ran home one-paced.
Gradually settled in last few, ran home one-paced.
Recovered quickly from a moderate start along the rail to reach forward of midfield, saved ground on the inside turning for home, soon weakened after straightening.
Wide without cover in better than midfield to the 500 metres, soon weakened.
Jumped well from draw 1, led steadily, quickened up 400M, drew well clear mid-straight, kept on final stages, had enough to hold off fast finishing 2nd.
Never far off 3Ls away from leader, closed off well from 300M, chased hard final 150M, nearest finish.
In midfield, bustled along 500M, ran on steadily for distant 3rd.
Failed to muster speed, settled near last 8Ls off the pace, closed off final 400M fastest, but too much to make up on leaders.
Towards the rear, 8Ls to make up 400M, made limited progress on straightening.
Settled outside leader, couldn't quicken turning in, held 2nd until mid-straight, weakened towards the finish.
Slow to begin, towards the rear 10Ls back, ran past beaten horses in the straight, never factored.
Tracked leaders in a 2-wide spot, outpaced 500M, gave little response when asked, eased final 150M. (Jockey : didn't stretch out at any stage of the race / Unacceptable Performance.)
Settled just ahead of midfield, failed to pick up speed in straight, faded 200M.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, under pressure 600M, soon gave ground.
Stumbled at the start, lacked the speed to go with them, always at rear, detached turning in, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)

Placing: DNF
Comment: Chased leaders, came under pressure 500M, weakened rapidly on straightening, eased down. (Bled.)
Jumped well, raced 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide on turn, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 wide turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked on run near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 1-1/2L back on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress final 200M to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began fairly from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, easy run to turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, only showed limited response, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield early, 3 wide from 1050M, 4 lengths or so back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced prominently on rail, allowed rival to cross near 850M, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind the lead, carried wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 3 wide on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, dropped towards rear on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 10 lengths back, moved a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Away with them, forced wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, weakened after passing 600M, eased thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, checked off heels near 650M, wider turning in, made very good progress in straight to score.
Out in line, raced 2 wide behind midfield, awkwardly placed near 650M, 4 lengths or so back turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take a place.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first few late.
Began smartly, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out early in straight, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, wider turning in, peaked early in straight weakened final furlong. (Mucus.)
Jumped well from gate 13, raced prominently but trapped wide, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.

Steadied & shifted behind runners to settle last of main group. Stayed on rail on cornering before being held up until 300m. Shifted into clear running before sprinting strongly between runners to snare lead final strides.

Began well, raced prominently, crossed near the 900m before moving away from inside immediately after when racing third. Moved up to assume lead near 300m before being caught by fast finishing winner in final few strides.

Not fast away but improved quickly after start to race in midfield. Crowded & lost a length near 900m before entering last section under 2L from lead. Raced greenly in straight but made continual late ground to close up 3rd.

Mustered speed quickly after start to assume lead after first furlong before being headed on outside near 900m. Improved to share lead at the 300m before battling on gamely in later stages to hold forth, less than 2L behind.

Settled in midfield between runners after start before being inconvenienced near 900m & drifting back to third last of main group. Eased wider on straightening, dashed up & looked a threat at 250m before peaking late.

Steadied after start & shifted back to second last away from rail. Moved the widest runner on straightening when 3.5L from lead before finishing off steadily to midfield without threatening from the rear.

Settled worse than midfield on the rail soon after start. Awkwardly placed on cornering, made steady ground once clear before being checked & losing ground near 150m. Not tested late & should have finished length closer.

Has a soft run in midfield on the rail throughout. Continued less than 2 lengths from the lead at the 300m mark before being passed by the fast finishers in concluding stages. Not beaten far but was never a threat.

Shifted across to midfield from wide gate but was left coving additional ground when wide with cover for majority. Continued wide passage on cornering, entered last section 3L from lead before peaking & yielding ground late.

Ridden forward but caught wide & without cover behind leading trio. Continued to cover additional ground around bend before entering last section a length from lead. Emptied out passing 300m before giving ground thereafter.

Hard ridden at start, raced outside early leader before assuming lead away from the rail from the 900m. Continued to hold narrow lead on straightening before being joined at 300m & weakened out sharply in final furlong.
Very slow to begin & lost considerable ground & consequently trailed the field for the majority. Was never going to play a part after the start & was a complete forgive run. (Must trial).

Moderately away, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but still headed 100M, finished 2nd.
Quickly into stride, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 1100M, 6 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer after passing 700M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, wider on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Slow away, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M
Eased to sit just off the leader in 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the slow pace, held ground in straight.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, emptied 200M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
At rear, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Slow away, raced greenly throughout, never competitive.
Settled midfield, awkwardly placed from some distance near 800M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 200M to score.
Raced detached in early and middle stages, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home strongly, rider questioned.
Ridden along but no early speed, travelled wide and without cover outside the leaders, fought well in the straight.
Settled behind midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 300M, gained some nice ground in the straight.
Hard ridden forward, raced outside the lead, responded well in the early part of straight, one-paced passing 50M.
Settled behind midfield, asked for effort passing 500M, one-paced in the early part of straight, made some ground passing 100M.
Ridden along to take lead, placed pressure in the straight but gave ground passing 50M.
Settled midfield, placed pressure near 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 400M, gave ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, detached in early and middle stages, widest on straightening, no response in the straight.
Urged along to race in handy position, tried to improve passing 350M, weakened near 150M.
Failed to muster speed despite being ridden along, raced towards rear, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.

Shifted across after start to race worse than midfield between runners. Shifted wider to improve position passing 400m when over 4L from the lead. Finished strongly in final furlong to dash to narrow lead in final strides.

Began well before being crossed after first bend & getting good position 1,1. Moved 4 wide around home corner, dashed to lead at 175m & looked the winner before being caught by fast finisher in final strides.

Had nice run on leaders back throughout. Moved over heels approaching the corner, improved to share lead on straightening before being joined at the 175m. Battled on gamely late to hold third, beaten under a length.

Showed good early speed to come across from outside barrier and position outside the leader after the first bend. Hung out around home corner before finishing off soundly late to be only a length behind.
Obtained good position in midfield inside runners throughout early & middle stages. Entered last section just under 3 lengths from the lead before finishing off steadily to not be beaten far.
Hard ridden after start to maintain lead. Joined in the lead soon after cornering before yielding two lengths in last furlong. Not beaten far.

Steadied after start & settled between runners at the rear. Moved wider when improving passing 600m before forced very wide on cornering. Made up a few lengths when running on to midfield from rearward position.

Bumped & unbalanced at start before steadying after first bend to get good position in midfield away from rail. Eased wider entering last section when under 3L from lead before failing to make any improvement in straight.

Tightened for room on jumping before being caught three wide without cover after 300m. Continued wide passage, nearly 4L form lead near 800m. Forced wider on bend but never improved in straight. No threat.

Slowest to begin before settling worse than midfield on rail. Improved along rail passing 400m before steadying & shifting away from inside when tightened for room at 350m. Failed to close off in final stages & was well held.
Fractious in barriers, commenced awkwardly, bumped on multiple occasions & consequently settled at the tail. Was second from last on cornering, made no improvement in straight & was well beaten.

Steadied from wide barrier after start & shifted back towards the tail. Continued rearward, a clear last on cornering when 6.5 lengths from lead before failing to improve & finishing a similar margin behind in last.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.

Made contact shortly after start, trapped wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 700M, positioned outside to the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly, missed 2nd on line.
Moderately away from gate 11, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, got cover after passing 500M, kept on evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made little progress in straight.
Reared at start and bumped, positioned on rail behind midfield, there to turn, angled out early in straight, made some progress in the run home.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made minor progress early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at rear on the inside, inconvenienced near 500M, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, showed nothing in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, improved steadily and hit the line strongly in the last 50M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, saved ground and battled on to the line for 2nd.
Raced in one-out-one-back position, saved ground but headed after 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, improved steadily in the Straight.
Sent forward, 2 wide, stayed on well but headed passing 150M.
Began awkwardly and raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced. (Lame Right Front)
Sent forward, along the rail, was one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, did not threaten.
At rear, along the rail, did not feature.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, found nothing.
At rear, 2 wide, never a factor.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide no cover, lost ground in the straight.

Moderate start, settled towards the rear in 9th on the rail, commenced move going up the Rock to come within 3L of the pace in 6th on home bend, quickened well in straight to assert authority near the line.
Driven to lead briefly before headed entering back straight, remained close up in 2nd until improving around home bend to lead into straight, caught by fast-finishing winner inside final 50 metres.
Soon taken back to last few and waited with, baulked for a run early in straight, shifted out to obtain a clear passage over 200 metres out, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Began well from the one draw but soon dropped over 2L back to joint 5th on the rail, gained closer passing the 600 metres and chased the leader into straight, kept on same pace.
Crowded at the start settling well behind, trailed the field to home straight, switched wide making home turn, fought on steadily without threatening.
Recovered quickly from moderate start to a prominent position, settled just off the pace most of the way in 2L 4th to home straight, found nothing under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Began well, raced keenly while taken back to midfield in 8th or 7th, remained similar into home straight, kept on under pressure until finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Recovered well from an awkward start from an awkward draw to take up running at the 1000 metre bend, led on the rail until headed into home straight, folded up quickly.
Inconvenienced at the start before settling in last few, remained similar into home straight, never a danger.
Very wide in midfield in early stages, gave ground steadily from approaching the 600 metres, fanned very wide as a back-marker entering home straight, never recovered.

Caught very wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, improved closer to pace and closer to the rail to 3-wide in 2L 3rd, inconvenienced when behind midfield early in straight, made no further impression.
Sluggish at start, improved to wide in midfield early in back straight, dropped out of contention approaching home turn.
Jumped on terms, held up in midfield, let down strongly when gap opened up near 200M, led 80M out, won going away. (Lame next day.)
Pushed along after the start, chased leaders on settling, responded well on straightening, not winner's pace from 150M, held clear 2nd.
Went forward, vied for lead on inside, opened up a good lead 350M, caught near 80M, faded towards the line, held on for 3rd just.
Ended up in a 3-wide spot from widest draw, never far off from leaders, kept on steadily final 300M, just missed 3rd.
Settled behind mid-division, pushed along 550M, stayed on past beaten horses, no serious threat to leaders.
Chased leaders along the fence, couldn't quicken when driven along nearing 400M, kept on same pace.
From wide draw vigorously ridden forward, vied lead on outside, weakened 250M.
Held up 2nd last, 6Ls to make up 400M, failed to make any progress.
Chased leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, hung out badly from 550M, eased down early straight. (To barrier trials around a bend.)
Held up in mid-division along the fence, couldn't go on from top of straight, soon weakened. (Lame next day.)
Began only fairly, soon detached from the field, never in the picture.
Out in line, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move after passing 600M, hit the front 400M, kept on very well in straight to score.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 600M, moved closer on turn, inconvenienced near 400M, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, trapped 3 wide early, positioned 1 out 1 back after passing 1200M, there to turn, commenced move 400M, kept on well in straight without threatening.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, raced at tail, 10 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, commenced move after passing 650M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position in the middle stages, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight after passing 200M, showed limited response thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.

Jumped with them, took the early lead, headed near 1400M, allowed rival to cross near 1250M, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle stages, angled out 400M, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead near 1200M, travelled well in the middle stages, led by 1/2L, peaked and headed near 400M, weakened early in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)

Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, checked early in straight, finished off strongly to snatch victory in a ding-dong finish.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Commenced well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, closed off well to take a place.
Began smartly, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well, peaked and headed 50M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, steadied off heels near 150M, no extra thereafter.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, led by a neck turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide at rear, steadied off heels near 1100M, wider after passing 800M, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 13, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the outside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, led 200M, just missed in last few strides.
Midfield along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily for 3rd.
Took rail and lead easily, not suited by the fast sectionals, overhauled 200M.
Slow away, took rail at back, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed forward, on the fence, just held ground in straight.
Pushed early, midfield, 2 wide, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, however no progress.
At back, trapped 3 wide, on heels 300M, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly in straight.
At back, trapped 3-4 wide, no dash.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, never improved.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide in midfield, emptied 350M.
Eased at start, never a factor.
Jumped sharply then ridden along to race in one-back-one-off position, responded strongly when asked for effort, quickened passing 150M to score.
Settled in front of midfield, improved near 500M, finished solidly.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 500M, fought well in the straight.
Raced midfield, commenced to improve passing 500M, gained some ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, passing 900M commenced to travel keenly, placed pressure passing 600M, made some nice ground in the straight.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure near 400M, worked home one-pace.
Jumped well then taken back, passing 900M commenced to travel keenly, fought hard but only one-paced.
Slow out, settled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 500M, finished one-paced.
Jumped nicely, raced outside the lead, placed pressure on straightening, weakened passing 200M.
Niggled along to take lead, placed pressure but gave ground passing 150M.
Raced midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages, gave ground passing 200M.
Began fairly then taken back, came under pressure passing 700M, no response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, no response.
Left wide and without cover passing 1200M in handy position, came under pressure near 500M, faded out passing 300M.

Began well before drifting back to third last away from rail in small field. Eased wider on straightening, entered last section 1.5L from lead, moved closer under no riding at 300m before dashing away in final furlong to win.

Steadied after start & shifted back to last on rail. Continued near the rear on cornering, shifted wider entering last section when 3L from lead before finishing strongly in final furlong for fast finishing second.

Lost a length at start before improving to race in midfield on rail. Travelled strongly between runners on cornering, held up momentarily soon after before closing strongly in final 250m to snare close up third on line.

Raced third early before getting good position 1,1 after being crossed near 1000m. Eased three wide on cornering, moved up to share lead when asked for full effort at 300m before finishing off well to be length behind.

Steadied after start & shifted back to second last away from rail. Continued at the back, just over 3L from lead entering last section before passing a few tiring runners to midfield without threatening.
Raced on the rail before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 900m. Ridden along on straightening before failing to improve in last section when weakening out to midfield. No threat.

Steadied to obtain cover after start but was left racing wide before improving around field to race outside leader from the 1000m. Continued outside the lead until peaking on run at 300m & giving 5L thereafter.
Strode forward before crossing to the rail when leading near the 900m. Continued in lead until being joined & headed at the 300m & weakening out to last thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 750M, commenced move 500M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, similar position to turn, angled out after passing 500M, bumped early in straight, made very good progress thereafter to take 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take a place.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 950M, a length or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, raced prominently but trapped wide, 2 wide from 750M, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to 150M, headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, bumped early in straight, made some progress thereafter, no threat to the first few.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 150M, made no progress thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Jumped well, raced prominently but trapped wide, took the lead after passing 1000M, found rail near 900M, led by half length on turn, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Away well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
At rear, 2 wide, made good ground inside final 300M and scored by 4L.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, at rear and along the rail, saved ground and ran on strongly to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, saved ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide, swung widest on straightening, ran on well to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide after 750M, saved some ground and ran on well.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, hung in badly in the Straight and not properly tested, must trial.
Bumped start, at rear, 2 wide, improved gradually in the Straight.
Sat one-out one-back, was one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, shifted in near 200M and one paced thereafter.
At rear, along the rail, did not feature.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, lost ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, did not run on.
Sent forward, along the rail, gave ground after 200M.
Sent forward and lead after 700M, 2 wide, gave ground near the 200M.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, settled in rear of midfield, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, quickened well to hit the front inside the 200 metres, won readily.
Settled in midfield, travelled keenly passing the 700 metres, inconvenienced over 300 metres out, finished off the race well.
Settled just off the pace on the rail, chased the leaders on the rail into home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Close up early settling in 5th just over 2L back, in similar position turning into home straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Slow into stride, soon recovered to join the leaders, taken one-out-one-back to joint 3rd rounding home bend, ran home at the one pace.
Soon took up running, kicked some 2L clear after straightening, headed inside the 200 metres, found no extra. (Mucus)
Settled just worse than midfield, gained closer approaching home bend, kept on steadily in home straight.
Settled in last few from a wide gate, kept on one pace without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly, soon taken back to rear, fought on steadily in straight without threatening.
Soon dropped towards the rear, made no show in the run to the line.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th just over 3L off the pace, faded steadily after straightening.
Ridden from the widest gate to join the leaders 3-wide, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled at the back from a wide gate, tailed-off into home straight, never seen with a chance.

Placing: UR
Comment: Dislodged rider shortly after start.
Reserved in midfield, travelled strongly into straight, quickened up smoothly to lead inside 300M, kicked clear final 200M, bolted in. (Class record time.)
Close up behind leaders, tried hard in straight, stood no chance with the runaway winner but held on 2nd well.
Fast into stride, pressed leader from 800M, led on straightening, no match with winner mid-straight, kept battling to hold 3rd at the line.
Began only fairly, held up behind mid-division, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 4th.
Crowded for room at start, shuffled back to race in last 7Ls off leader, worked home steadily form off the pace
Dropped back and taken across to race along the fence, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, stayed on fairly final 400M.
Chased leaders 2-wide, couldn't quicken in straight, kept on same pace to line, never troubled leaders.
Reserved to race behind midfield, 4Ls to make up 400M, just one paced to the line.
Crowded for room at start, dropped back to a 3-wide spot towards the rear, responded fairly when driven in the straight, no threat to leaders.
From wide draw steadied early stages for cover, settled 3-wide behind midfield, couldn't go on in the straight. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Began fairly, ridden to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, under pressure prior 600M, couldn't finish off. (Jockey : did not seem to be comfortable with the strong tempo / Lame next day.)
Soon led, pressed by rival from 800M, headed top of straight, weakened rapidly over final 250M.
Settled towards the rear failed to respond on straightening, eased final stages. (Bled.)
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders, badly unbalanced when jumped a shadow on the track 850M, eased down.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Began smartly, took the lead easily, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Began awkwardly, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1000M, raced in 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, checked off heels 1000M, 4 wide with no cover on turn, made no progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, weakened on turn, no cover in the middle stages, slightly hampered and dropped towards rear after passing 550M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off well to score.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, a length or so back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Bounded in air at the start and unbalanced rider, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well without threatening.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line. (Lame right front leg.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, angled out 500M, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, kept on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away well, positioned on rail towards rear, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear throughout, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Strode forward before racing in second along the rail, just inside leader. Moved up to assume lead on straightening before finishing strongly in last furlong to maintain margin clear of fast finisher.

Limited early pace & drifted back after start to race in midfield on rail. Continued on rail on straightening, 5L from lead entering last section before finishing very strongly last 250m to get within half-length on line.

Began fast before being headed & racing fourth on rail. Travelled strongly approaching corner, stayed on inside on straightening, moved within a length of lead at furlong before finding first two too strong late. Held third.

Steadied after start & drifted back to third last away from rail approaching first bend. Moved the widest runner on cornering, entered last section 4.5L from lead before finishing strongly in last 250m to just miss third.

Slow to begin conceding 2L before mustering to race worse than midfield on rail. Steadied passing the 750m when racing keenly, held up after straightening before getting clear near 300m & closing strongly to just miss third.

Raced prominently in first furlong before drifting back to midfield on rail. Continued on rail when entering last section 3.5L from lead before shifting out at 250m (rider suspended) and making up a length in closing stages.

Began fairly before ridden forward from wide gate & improving to midfield away from rail. Travelled well entering last section when 2L from lead before peaking on run inside last 100m & giving a length late. Not beaten far.

Steadied after the start & directed back to last. Continued at the rear on cornering, moved the widest runner entering last section when 6 lengths form lead before halving margin in dash home. Good effort from poor position.

Began well before being steadied & shifting across to midfield when racing three wide with cover throughout. Moved second widest on cornering but failed to improve on margin in last section & was well held in midfield.

Improved quickly to assume narrow lead after first furlong. Continued in lead when racing away from rail in middle stages. Joined & headed by the winner soon after straightening before weakening out in last furlong.

Began awkwardly, bumped & unbalanced before improving to midfield away from rail. Moved three wide with cover passing 800m when 3L behind. Ridden along on straightening before emptying out 250m & weakening thereafter.

Strode forward from wide gate but left racing three wide without cover outside lead. Continued wide passage on speed, entered last section only a length from the lead before emptying out at 250m & weakening after tough run.

Ridden along after first furlong before settling between runners in midfield throughout middle stages. Continued between runners, 4L from lead on cornering before being badly checked at 250m & losing all chance thereafter.
Drifted back after first furlong before being relegated to second last between runners passing the 900m. Continued at the tail on cornering before weakening out to long last. (Lame post-race).

Average to begin, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a head.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Away with them, trapped 3 wide early, 2 lengths back, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 2 wide from 750M, a length back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.

Began only fairly and crowded, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, settled in midfield in the middle stages, commenced move 500M, 4 wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 650M, 3 lengths back on turn, finished off one paced. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide behind midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, 4 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, ran one evenly to the line. (Blood in trachea.)
Began well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Crowded out start, positioned 3 to 4 lengths behind the leader on the inside, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Eased to obtain box seat, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield along the fence, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
At back, 2 wide, dashed well 200M.
Slow away, 2 wide at back, dashed well 250M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 2-4 wide, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to take the rail and lead, hung on until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, weakened 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, out of fuel 200M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, sat 2 wide, no dash.
Checked start, at rear along the rails, no dash.
Eased at start, never a factor.
Raced behind midfield, improved near 450M, wide on straightening, quickened near 100M to score.
Raced behind the lead with nice early speed, responded solidly in the straight, missed by Neck.
Taken back at start, asked for effort passing 500M, wide on straightening, made some nice ground in the straight.
Wide and without cover throughout, fought well in the straight, over concluding stages was awkwardly placed and not fully tested.
On jumping was crowded, travelled behind midfield on rail, held up passing 200M, finished well.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, gained some nice ground in the straight.
Settled in handy position on rail, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Settled in front of midfield, placed pressure near 400M, finished one-paced.
Race midfield on rail, in the straight placed pressure but only one-paced.
Jumped sharply then ridden to take lead, came under pressure passing 400M, gave ground near 100M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure near 400M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
On jumping was crowded, raced towards rear on rail, tried to improve passing 400M, no response in the straight.

Obtained good position in midfield when racing in clear in early & middle stages. Hard ridden passing 500m, moved the widest runner on cornering before finishing very strongly last 250m to strike lead 75m & win drawing away.

Raced prominently before being crossed & getting perfect run in midfield away from rail. Moved wider to improve approaching 400m when 4L from lead. Dashed up to assume lead near 150m before being passed by winner at the 75m.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail throughout. Moved away from rail just prior to corner before shifting wider on straightening & closing steadily to third in final furlong.

Steadied approaching winning post & drifted back worse than midfield away from rail. Over 6L from lead entering last section before shifting the widest runner on straightening & making good late ground to be beaten under 2L.
Improved passing winning post before getting good position 1,1 throughout. Eased 3 wide on cornering, moved up top share lead near the 200m before peaking & being over-run last 150m.
Shifted across behind runners after start to race at tail. Continued along the rail on cornering before halving margin in last section when running on late. Not beaten far.
Didn't have the speed of others & shifted back to race worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from rail approaching 400m when 5L from lead before making up a length or two late without threatening.
Steadied after the start & drifted back to second last before being relegated back to last by the 1200m. Passed a few in straight but was still beaten 8L.

Showed early speed to hold lead, shifting across to rail by the 1200m. Raced nearly two lengths clear on straightening, held lead until being caught at 200m before weakening badly thereafter. (Mucus in trachea post-race).

Improved after start, raced wide on first bend when improving to second. Ridden along entering the last section before weakening out nearly in the straight to be over 10L behind. (Lame right fore-leg next day).
Bumped at start & consequently raced near the rear. Drifted further back nearing corner, last on straightening before weakening out further in straight to be beaten a big margin.
Began well, before racing on leaders back early stages. Niggled along entering last section before weakening out sharply in straight to be a long last.
Jumped with them, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 800m, 2 lengths back on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on well to the line.
Out in line, raced 3 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, inconvenienced near 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, 3 wide, found rail 800M, headed 600M, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, kept on well early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rivals to cross after entering the back straight, 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, no extra final 100M. (Blood in trachea.)

Began smartly from a tricky gate, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 800M, took the lead 600M, led by 1 to 2 lengths on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Crowded on jumping, positioned on rail behind midfield, 7 lengths back on turn, one paced in straight. (Mucus.) (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, still well back on turn, made no progress in straight.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Moderately away from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide, gradually lost position after passing 700M, eased early in straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, showed good kick approaching 150M, continued on to score by a neck.
Settled in front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly and battled on to the line for 2nd.
At rear, along the rail, raced tight after 700M, saved ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward, along the rail, stayed on but headed after 50M.
Bumped start, sat one-out one-back, stayed on but emptied passing 50M.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide no cover, showed some dash in the Straight.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, along the rail, raced tight passing the 900M, pretty one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, remained one paced to the line. (Blood in Trachea)
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, saved no ground in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, emptied after 150M and lost ground.
At rear, swung widest on straightening, nothing in the Straight.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, 2 wide, made no impression.
Broke well to lead setting a steady pace to the 800 metres when headed, commenced run to re-gain lead into straight, shifted out under pressure 150 metres out and just held on to the line.

Settled just off the pace early stages, became 6th some 3L back early in back straight, commenced move from midfield turning in and ran on under pressure to just fail to get up on line, carried wide 150 metres out.

Soon came to join the leaders early stages, settled just off the pace in 3rd into back straight becoming 4th some 3L back when pace quickened passing the 800 metres, saved ground on the inside turning for home, kept on same pace.
Settled just better than midfield on the rail, shuffled back to rear of midfield passing the 800 metres, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on under pressure without threatening.

Settled wide in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, improved closer to pace turning into back straight, dropped back to midfield when pace quickened passing the 800 metres, fought on steadily from wide into straight.

Moderate start, travelled very keenly on the rail pulling his way forward to midfield around first bend, ran off the rail for rapid progress to lead passing the 800 metres, led the field until overhauled inside the final 300 metres.
Settled behind midfield travelling keenly early in back straight, wide towards rear entering home straight, produced good late impression down the centre of the track.
Improved steadily from a moderate start to join the leaders 3-wide, became 3rd some 2L back when pace quickened passing the 800 metres, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Began well but soon taken back to midfield, shuffled back towards the rear when pace quickened passing the 800 meters, went very wide turning into home straight, kept on steadily under pressure.
Settled in last few from a moderate start, dropped to last into straight but saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.
Settled in rear for cover after beginning from the widest gate, similar turning for home, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, held up in rear, trailed the field to the straight, never nearer.
Chased leader, made sustained progress on straightening, led near 50M, strong to the line.
Soon led, travelled keenly from 1200M setting fast pace to straight, kept on well to line, caught near 50M.
Chased leaders 2-wide, finished off well final 300M to secure the minor placing.
Settled down midfield 5Ls off leader, kept on steadily on straightening, held by leaders.
Restrained to race behind midfield, 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on without threatening first 3.
Always close up behind leaders, 4th on settling, held ground in the straight only and safely held.
Held up towards the rear 8Ls off the pace, not going well enough to challenge in straight, worked home fairly.
Began fairly, raced in mid-division, travelled keenly from 900M, driven along 500M, held ground in the straight.
Soon taken across to the fence, settled behind midfield, held up early straight, couldn't quicken when clear.
Dropped back from wide draw, raced in last over 10Ls off the pace, responded fairly on straightening, never looked likely.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, settled near last, plenty to do turning home, failed to run on when asked.
Steadied early stages to obtain cover, held up near last 9Ls behind leader, found nothing in the straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score, impressive.

Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position to turn, 3 wide from 450M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take 3rd, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 450M, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, 2 wide from 600M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly, weakened close home.
Jumped well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at tail, well back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, 3 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Made contact shortly after start, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Crowded shortly after start, raced 2 wide, just behind the lead, peaked on turn, lost position after passing 400M, emptied and eased early in straight.
