Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, wider turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, kept on well, just unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well without threatening.
Away well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, challenged turning in, headed early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, wider turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same position to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, one paced in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, very wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, 2 wide, closed off strongly 400M, led 200M, overhauled 50M.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield, 2 wide, made steady ground 350M, run ended 100M.
Eased at start, took cover, 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased back, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, hung on until 200M weakened.
Box seat, lack room 4-2, no progress when clear.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 3-4 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 350M.
Never competitive at rear.
Never better than midfield.
Settled towards rear, asked for effort passing 400M, quickened passing 200M to score.
Raced midfield, 3 wide with cover, asked for effort passing 450M, responded solidly in the straight.
Raced towards rear, placed pressure passing 450M, made up some nice late ground.
Taken back at start, raced midfield, 4 wide and without cover for majority of race, passing 400M was inconvenienced, responded nicely in the straight.

Began awkwardly, in the early stages lost its left hind plate, travelled keenly in middle stages, in the straight held up until 300M, near 150M bumped with a runner and became unbalanced, finished well.
Raced in front of midfield, passing 400M had some difficulty obtaining clear running, worked home nicely.
Taken back at start, asked for effort near 400M, gained some ground in the straight.
Began well, raced in box seat, responded well in the early part of straight, finished one-paced.
Pushed along to take lead, fought hard in the straight, gave ground passing 100M, rider questioned tactic.
Moderate start, raced behind midfield on rail, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced at tail on rail, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Urged along to race outside the lead, came under pressure passing 500M, weakened passing 200M.
Taken back at start, raced greenly in the straight, no response.
Urged along but left racing wide and without cover near 800M, emptied in the straight.

Didn't begin fast and hard ridden to position just worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Moved the widest on straightening before closing strongly in final 300m to move to lead passing the 75m. Strong win.

Steadied away from heels after start & consequently settled worse than midfield away from rail. Shifted wider passing the 350m before finishing very strongly in the final furlong to charge to second in the closing stages.
Mustered good speed after the start to lead. Raced over 2L clear nearing the 250m before being passed by winner at the 75m. Only beaten just over a length on line in encouraging debut.

Shifted across from wide gate to race midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Moved closer to lead approaching corner when continuing wide with cover before finishing well to be only a length behind on line.

Drifted back after the start before settling third last on rail after first furlong. Shifted wider entering the straight, over 6L from lead before finishing well to halve margin on line. Never likely from rear but ran ok.
Raced in first 4 after start before drifting further back to midfield between runners. Continued between runners on cornering when 3.5L from lead but could only maintain margin in dash to line.

Drifted back after start to just worse than midfield away from rail. Entered last section 4.5L from lead, shifted wider at the 350m & made up a length or so in dash to line but was never a likely threat.
Held rail position in midfield throughout. Hard ridden straightening & never featured.
Began well before racing on leaders back. Continued to follow leader on straightening before peaking on run soon after entering last section & weakening thereafter.

Ridden forward after start but left wide & without cover throughout. Improved position closer to lead nearing 600m when continuing wide passage. Peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakening out after tough run.
Steadied from wide gate & taken back to last away from rail. Moved the widest runner when second last on straightening & never featured in dash to line.
Obtained good position behind leading trio away from rail. Only 2.5L from lead entering last section but offered nothing in the straight & weakened out poorly.
Showed speed after start to improve & race outside leader. Hard ridden on cornering to maintain contact with leader before dropping out poorly in last section to be beaten big margin.
Steadied after start & shifted across from wide barrier to race second last on rail. Relegated to a clear last approaching corner & failed to improve to be a long last.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, closer on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well to the line.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, just stayed on for 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned right behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, no clear run until 200M, closed off well, just missed 2nd.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, no clear running early in straight, showed limited response when clear thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, passed 2 tired runners in straight.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled keenly in the early stages, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M. (Abnormal respiratory noise.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Slow to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
In midfield, at centre-track, closing off nicely and ran on to the line.
Crowded start and raced in front of midfield, on centre-track, battled on nicely to the line.
Sent forward to lead, on stand-side, kept on nicely but headed passing the 200M.
Began only fairly, raced at the rear centre-track, made ground and closed off okay.
Ridden to be prominent, on stand-side after 700M, flattened passing 200M.
Began fairly and sat in front of midfield, centre-track, ran on nicely to the line.
Raced at the rear on stand-side, made some ground and closed off okay.
Crowded start, sat behind midfield on centre-track, did not improve.
Raced in front of midfield, on centre-track, did not run on.
Midfield, on stand-side, made no impression.
Began only fairly, at rear and on centre-track, never a factor.
Raced in midfield, on centre-track, raced tight passing 300M and gave ground from 200M.
Sat towards the rear, on stand-side, found nothing.
Raced at the rear, on centre track, finished off one-paced.
Broke well travelling in first few on stands rails, quickened to join the leader 300 metres out and led inside the 200 metres, held on under pressure.
Ridden to narrow lead, joined by eventual winner shortly before headed inside the 200 metres, unable to peg him back under pressure throughout closing stages.
Settled in midfield some 3L off the pace, ran on steadily under pressure inside the 400 metres, nearest at finish.
Broke well in first few, failed to quicken under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Settled towards the rear near the centre of the track, gained closer under pressure inside the 400 metres, fought on steadily without threatening inside the final 200 metres.
Settled in 5th just over 2L back in pace, gained 4th under pressure over 200 metres out, made no further impression in closing stages.
Lacked early pace travelling well behind, produced good late impression inside the final 300 metres.
Began awkwardly losing ground, travelled in last few, fought on under pressure inside the final 300 metres down the centre of the track.
Settled in forward of midfield on stands rails just over 2L off the pace, found nothing under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, travelled in rear of midfield, faded under pressure inside the final 250 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped awkwardly losing some ground, settled 1L back in 4th, weakened under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Soon dropped well back, never seen with a chance.
Settled in midfield after beginning from a low draw, kept on under pressure before weakening out of contention 200 metres out. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled in rear near the centre of the track, found nothing.
Not far off leader but 3-wide no cover for majority of the race, responded generously from 250M, led inside 150M, won decisively.
Settled down 3-wide towards the rear, closed off well over final 350M to go 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Began awkwardly lost ground, settled towards the rear along the inside, 4Ls to make up 400M, ran on well to claim 3rd before line.
Chased leader 2-wide, challenged strongly for the lead mid-straight, no match for winner 150M, no extra late, edged out to 4th close home.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled 5Ls back at the rear, pushed wide 750M, stayed on mildly final 300M, not reached leaders.
Raced keenly behind the leader, had his chance turning home but held ground only, flat final 100M.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, responded fairly on straightening, always held by leaders.
Reserved behind midfield, raced keenly 750M, ran on fairly final 400M, no threat to leaders.
Quickly into stride, led at decent tempo, kept on well first half of straight, weakened final 150M, swamped by rivals inside 100M.
Steadied in the early stages to obtain cover, held up in rear 5Ls off the good pace, gave limited response on straightening, never dangerous.
From draw 1 settled behind midfield along the rails, couldn't go on passing 200M, weakened to last 100M out.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, finished off very strongly to score narrowly.

Began only fairly, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, still last turning in, taken wide very early in straight, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no daylight early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, made some progress to make frame.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, led narrowly early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.

Moderately away, raced slightly better than midfield on the outside, found cover after passing 800M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, no extra thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, had no clear run for most part of the straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, checked off heels near 900M, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Fast into stride, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, only showed limited response in straight.

Began well, showed limited early speed, trapped wide in midfield early, moved closer after passing 1000M, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened 200M, eased final 100M. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Clean jump, raced very wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 3 lengths or so back, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began only fairly, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, led narrowly on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, travelled well to turn, taken wide early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Quickly into stride, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, very wide turning in, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 13 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, improved after passing 500M, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Began well, raced in midfield on the inside, easy run to turn, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide at rear, 12 lengths back, a bit closer in the middle stages, but still last turning in, finished off well without threatening.

Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, slightly held back passing 1050M to sit behind the leader, improved 500M, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Slow to begin, raced at rear, 12 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced better than midfield, easy run in the middle stages, wider after passing 600M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead and set a strong early tempo, headed after turning in, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide at rear, there to turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Began awkwardly, positioned towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, half length back on turn, weakened and eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Began well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, hard ridden 300M, showed very good response, took the lead near 100M, kept on well to the line, won by 2 lengths.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, no extra thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 10, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, no cover throughout, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Began well from a wide draw, trapped very wide early, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, bumped near 600M, awkwardly placed 400M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Bumped start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, travelled well to turn, angled out after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced towards rear, bumped near 600M, very wide turning in, passed some tired horses in straight.
Crowded start, showed no early speed, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, passed some tired horses in straight.
Away with them, raced prominently but 3 wide, slightly taken back after passing 700M, 2 lengths or so back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Slow to begin, raced 4 lengths behind on the inside, made contact near 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide, 3/4L behind, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Took rail and lead easily, clocked slow sectionals, drifted away 300M, hung on well to score.
Hard ridden early, in front midfield along the fence, ran on well for 2nd.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Slow away, behind midfield along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, made ground around the field in 4 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
At back, took rail, harmed by the slow tempo, never improved.
At back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased at start, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive at rear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, soon emptied 400M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 350M, quickened near 100M, finished strongly to score.
Took lead with nice early speed, travelled well in the lead, responded nicely in the straight, missed by 3/4L.
Raced in box seat, placed pressure passing 400M, close to the finishing line was awkwardly placed, responded well in the straight.
Settled behind the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, fought well in the straight.
Ridden along after start, settled behind midfield, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Raced at rear, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, made some ground in the straight.
Always niggled, throughout the race travelled wide and without cover in handy position, one-paced in the straight.
Travelled midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Niggled along but no early speed, raced behind midfield on rail, worked home one-paced.
Raced towards rear, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly and then was crowded for room, raced detached in early and middle stages, no response.

Showed good speed to lead in early stages before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 800m. Moved over heels on straightening, dashed up to take lead passing 250m before continuing on to win easily.
Began well before drifting back approaching first bend & settling midfield on rail. Continued on inside approaching bend before finishing off steadily to move to second passing the 150m.
Obtained good position in midfield away from rail. Ridden along entering last section when just under 3L from lead before finishing well in the straight to move to third inside last 100m.

Crowded after the start & consequently lost ground & raced near the rear. Continued along the rail entering last section when 5L from the lead before making good late ground into non-threatening 4th in concluding stages.

Hard ridden & improved after start to assume lead after first furlong before crossing to rail in lead near 800m. Raced over a length clear on straightening before being headed by winner near 250m & weakening sharply late.

Had limited early speed & raced tight with other runners consequently racing near the rear throughout. Continued well back on straightening before making steady late ground to pass a number of runners when finishing midfield.

Didn't have the early speed of others & was hard ridden to hold position in midfield between runners. Drifted further back in middle stages, 4.5L from lead entering last section before only holding position in midfield late.

Steadied & shifted back from outside barrier to settle worse than midfield 3 wide with cover throughout. Continued in second half, 4.5L behind entering the last section before failing to improve in straight. No threat.

Crowded & steadied after start before improving after first bend to race in midfield away from rail. Moved 4 wide passing the 800m & steadily improved before cornering extremely wide & yielding ground in concluding stages.

Hard ridden after start to improve position around first bend when racing wide. Continued to improve until moving to second near the 850m. Came under pressure on cornering & weakened badly in last section.

Ridden forward to be prominent before drifting back to midfield after first bend. Continued wide & without cover throughout. Cornered second widest before emptying out on straightening & weakening sharply thereafter.
Was racing wide approaching first bend before hanging out across heels & being severely checked & losing ground. Continued a long last after incident & never improved.
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Out in line, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 750M, similar position in the middle stages, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 50M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 350M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground throughout, finished off well without threatening.

Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, same position on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 200M, angled out thereafter and made minor progress.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide towards rear, awkwardly placed near 1000M, 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, headed and weakened final 50M.
Steadied off heels shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress early in straight, not enough room after passing 100M.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the outside, a bit closer on turn, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide turning in, showed limited response in straight.

Jumped with them, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross after passing 800M, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, showed limited response early in straight, eased final 50M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Sent forward to take the rail, led all the way to score by 2L.
Settled in one-off one-back position, kept going and ran on nicely for 2nd.
Jumped well, then rolled forward to sit behind the lead, kept on going to the line.
Sent forward, 2 wide, stayed on one paced to the line.
Crowded start and raced in worse than midfield initially, at rear after 1200M, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off fairly.
At rear initially, roll forward after 700M, finished off only fairly in the straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, stayed on one paced to the line.
At rear, along the rail, did not improve in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, did not threaten in the Straight.
Slow to begin and raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, never a factor.
Sluggish at start despite ridden along, travelled in 5th within 3L of pace, responded well under pressure to lead just inside the 200 metres, pushed out.
Crowded at start dropping to last few, remained in similar rails position to home straight, ran on well under pressure without threatening.
Settled in rear of midfield in 7th some 4L off the pace, in similar position when wide into straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Settled in rear from the widest gate, remained well back turning for home, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Inconvenienced in midfield and dropped to last few 1000 metres out, remained in rear and widest turning into home straight, made up good ground down the centre of the track.
Slowly away, tailed-off most of the way despite ridden along, ran on well late to be nearest at finish.
Moderate start, settled in midfield in 6th on the rail some 3L off the pace, saved ground turning in but baulked for a run inside the 200 metres, fought on to the line.

Restrained wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide-ish gate, sent forward down back straight to join the leader coming onto home bend, hit the front briefly turning in but soon weakened.
Began well, settled just over 1L off the pace mainly in 4th on the rail, came under pressure upon straightening but faded under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well from a wide-ish gate, settled just off the speed 2-wide and mostly in 3rd, came under pressure rounding home bend, kept on before fading inside the final 150 metres. (Lame)
Pressed forward after moderate start from a wide gate, travelled keenly in lead approaching the 1000 metre bend, led the field until headed over 400 metres out, folded up quickly after straightening.
Reserved in mid-division 4-5Ls away, picked up gradually on straightening, kept coming final stages, wore down leader 50M to score on his 1st start at the Valley.
Settled down midfield, wide no cover from 700M, responded well to pressure final 300M, went 2nd just before line.
From a wide draw left racing wide without cover early stages, improved to take lead near 600M, kept on well under pressure in straight until headed final 50M.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, ran home well to take 4th just before line.
Chased leaders on settling, kept on well in straight, still in contention for a minor placing when gap closed passing 100M, awkwardly placed 50M.
Lost ground on jumping, settled near last, swung widest home, stayed on moderately down outside.
Failed to muster early speed, soon ended up in last detached, 8Ls to make up 400M, made some late progress, laid in under pressure and proved difficult to ride.
Up with early pace, hung in badly from 900M, lost ground and shuffled back to ahead of midfield, lacked further response on straightening, ran home one paced.
Positively ridden, crossed to the lead near 800M, relinquished lead 650M, kept on one paced turning home, swamped by rivals mid-straight.
Unbalanced when bumped at the start, held up in mid-division along the fence, couldn't pick up on straightening, never involved.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden, raced further back than intended 5-6Ls from leader, couldn't finish off in the straight (Jockey : never travelled and made abnormal breathing noise throughout.)
Jumped on terms, moved forward to be tracking leaders along the fence, held ground in straight, weakened final 150M. (Distressed post race.)

Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced prominently, found rail near 700M, travelled well on turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, similar position to turn, angled out 400M, made good progress in straight to take a place.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, angled out near 500M, one paced in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, 2 wide, peaked and headed after turning in, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive. (Blood in trachea.)
Eased back, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Eased to rear for cover, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Pushed forward, not suited by the fast pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M whilst hanging out
Hard ridden to battle for the lead at very fast pace, hung on very well until 150M emptied.
Midfield, on the fence, held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to battle for the lead at very fast sectionals, sat off leaders after 1000M, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden to battle for the lead at very fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no dash.
Eased back, took rail, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Slow away, never a factor.
Pushed forward, 2 wide emptied 400M.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Niggled forward to race outside the lead, responded strongly in the straight, scored unchallenged.
Settled behind leaders, niggled passing 700M, worked home solidly, Close to the line was awkwardly placed.
Settled behind midfield, improved into tight running passing 700M, made some late ground in the straight.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, fought hard and made home one-paced.
Urged along but failed to muster speed, raced at rear, lay out passing 600M, limited response in the straight.
Raced towards rear on rail, placed pressure but no response, weakened passing 200M.
Ridden to take lead, placed pressure but faded out in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced midfield on rail, no response in the straight.
Raced midfield, near 700M was left racing wide and without cover, then lay out passing 700M, came under pressure near 600M, emptied near 300M.
Didn't begin fast but improved to race midfield between runners. Shifted into clear running entering last section before sprinting up to take lead at the 50m & continue on strongly late to win.
Pushed forward to race second before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 800m. Dashed up to take lead near the 350m before being caught by winner near the 50m. Held second.
Strode forward after start before shifting down to rail when racing 4th near the 1000m. Continued along the inside in final section when making continual steady ground to be close behind in third.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail throughout. Stayed hard on the rail on straightening before shifting into clear running at the 200m & closing strongly late to beaten only a length.

Shifted across from wide gate to settle near rear. Shifted the widest runners on straightening when a clear last, 6L from lead before finishing strongly in closing stages to be beaten less than 2L on line.

Began only fairly before improving after start to race in midfield three wide. Drifted further back after first 600m before getting cover passing the 800m. Made up a length or two in last section & was beaten only 2 lengths.
Raced in good position in midfield away from rail throughout. Made no headway in last section & held non-threatening midfield position.
Steadied from wide gate & shifted back near the rear. Steadied when disappointed for a run nearing the 300m before finishing off evenly in last furlong to midfield.
Showed speed after start to stride to lead. Raced 2L clear nearing the 700m. Headed passing the 350m & weakened out thereafter.

Showed no speed after start & raced worse than midfield 4 wide without cover early before improving position when 3 wide from the 900m. Only 2.5L from lead entering last section before weakening after wide passage throughout.

Drifted back after the start & raced 3 wide with cover in second half. Cornered the second widest runner, 4.5L from lead entering last section before weakening further to be well beaten. (Must trial – unacceptable perf.)
Drifted back after the start to settle second last away from rail. Cornered the widest runner when still near the tail before failing to make any headway in last section. Well beaten.
Began awkwardly before settling worse than midfield between runners. Second from last entering last section before weakened out to be beaten 8L. Rider question regarding poor performance. See report.
Strode forward from outside gate to race prominent before settling third away from rail. Peaked approaching the 200m & weakened sharply to long last. (Bled).
Began well, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 450M, showed good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, no extra thereafter.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail better than midfield, easy run to turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off evenly.
Stood flat-footed and missed the start, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 600M, taken wide in straight and made some progress.

Commenced well, trapped 3 wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1350M, took the lead 1150M, led by 3/4L on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, hard ridden after passing 450M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Crowded start, trapped 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.
At rear initially, along the rail, saved ground and ran on strongly to score by 3/4L.
Sent forward, along the rail after 800M, stayed on and only headed in the last 50M.
At rear, wide but with cover after 500M, lay in passing 300M, saved ground and ran on well. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward, along the rail, stayed on one-paced to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, 300M crowded for room and bumped passing 200M, saved minor ground.
Rolled forward, 2 wide, worked home one-paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn of foot. (Roarer)
Raced in midfield, along the rail, limited response in the straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 4 wide no cover, emptied passing 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, did not improve in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced detached initially, saved minor ground only, never a factor.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not feature.
Sent forward, 2 wide after 650M, lost ground in the Straight (Heart Irregularity)
Niggled along before settling in 6th about 3L off the speed, angled out for a run entering straight, responded well inside the final 300 metres to take charge about 100 metres out.
Began well to share the pace, gained narrow advantage with rails run coming onto home bend, outsprinted by the winner inside the final 100 metres.
Met minor interferences at start and soon dropped well behind, made significant progress in straight despite inconvenience about 200 metres out.
Travelled some 2L back in 4th just off the rail, kept on same pace without quickening in the straight.
Ridden to hold place among the leaders, settled one back in 3rd on the rail coming onto home bend, switched out for a run entering the straight, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Slightly slow out, settled on the rail in last few of the small field, came within 3L of the pace turning in, unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Amongst leaders 3-wide early stages, became 2-wide still sharing the pace coming onto home bend, kept on before fading under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in midfield about 3L off the pace, 5th rounding home bend and slightly wider when hampered turning in, never recovered. Jockey reported the horse hung out throughout.
Never better than midfield despite ridden along dropping to tail-end coming onto home bend, detached after straightening.
Not hurried after the start, settled behind midfield only 3Ls away, not clearest run from 350M, picked up strongly once into clear, mowed down long term leaders inside 100M, won going away.
Jumped well to be sharing the lead on outside, driven out near 300M and continued to dispute for lead until winner stormed past inside 100M.
Went forward as expected under 10lb claimer, shared lead on inside in a steadily run race, stuck to his task well in straight but no match with the classy winner late.
Never far off the pace, chased leaders 2-wide home turn, kept on without serious threat in the straight.
Crowded for room at the start, restrained in midfield along the fence, kept on fairly final 400M, not going the pace to challenge.
Went forward after the start but unable to slot in, caught 4-wide no cover making home turn, ran home mildly after tough trip.
From wide draw eased back to race in last 5-6Ls off leader, stayed on past beaten horses final 400M, not reached leaders.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, failed to quicken on straightening, never dangerous.
From draw 4 ended up in a 3-wide spot in midfield, wider from 500M, couldn't finish off turning home.
Chased leaders keenly, came under pressure 500M, kept on same pace early straight, weakened badly final 200M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Clean jump, raced nearer to the middle of the track, 1-3/4L behind, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed very good response, took the lead 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 14, raced prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, closed off well to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in the middle of the track, 2 lengths behind the leader, hard ridden from near 400M, finished off well to take a place, just beaten by a neck.
Moderately away, raced 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, made good progress final 400M to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Began only fairly, raced in the middle of the track, 3 lengths or so back, made some progress final 400M.
Away well, raced prominently on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead in the middle of the track, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the stands' rail, 3 lengths back, passed a few tired horses final 400M.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the stands' side, 4 lengths or so back, made some progress final 400M, never dangerous.

Bumped shortly after start, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden approaching 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Roarer.)
Fast into stride, positioned 2 lengths or so back, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Fast into stride, bumped shortly after start, raced prominently, nearer to the middle track, hard ridden after passing 500M, showed limited response, weakened final 300M.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, outpaced 400M, weakened final furlong.
Commenced well, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 700M, very wide turning in, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, showed limited response in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, one paced in straight. (Lost right front plate in the early stages.)
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, 2 lengths or so back, bumped 1100M, similar position on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back, bumped near 1100M, travelled keenly for a short distance thereafter, no cover on turn, weakened gradually in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.

Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, angled out after passing 350M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out after passing 450M, closed off well to take a place.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at rear on the inside, last turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, made some headway in straight.
Away well, trapped 3 wide behind midfield early, found a 2 wide spot near 1100M, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the outside, hard ridden after passing 500M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead 400M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, headed 400M, eased early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, pace good, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to take rail and lead, pace good, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Midfield, 2 wide, pace good, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Hard ridden early but not muster, at back, 2 wide, pace good, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, pace good, ran on ok.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, pace good, out of fuel 150M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, pace good, emptied 200M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Eased at start, raced greenly throughout, never competitive.
Urged to take lead, fought well in the straight, finished strongly to score.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, widest on straightening, worked home solidly, missed by Neck.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled midfield on rail, made up some nice late ground in the straight.
Settled outside the lead with nice early speed, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure passing 450M, worked home well.
Jumped well, raced in front of midfield, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, commenced to improve passing 400M, gained some ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, had difficulty to obtain clear running over concluding stages.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield, one-paced in the straight when placed under pressure.
At the start was hampered, detached in early stages, no response in the straight.
Wide and without cover throughout in handy position, gave ground in the straight.

Raced on-speed before being crossed & racing on leaders back. Shuffled further back when pace quickened at 650m, moved away from rail passing 500m before closing strongly in last furlong to strike lead 150m & draw away late.

Raced worse than midfield on the rail after start. Moved away from rail near 800m before shifting wider when improving passing the 500m. Cornered extremely wide before finishing strongly to move to second in closing stages.

Strode to midfield before racing keenly & stumbling near 900m. Shifted 3 wide soon after & improved around field to strike lead passing 650m. Raced over a length clear in lead on straightening until caught inside 150m.

Obtained good position in midfield away from rail throughout early stages. Shifted three wide with cover at the 700m & improved position to second near the 550m. Straightened 1.5L from lead before finishing evenly late.

Not bustled after start & drifted back to race in final quartet away from the rail. Moved three wide & improved position to midfield passing the 650m. Cornered second widest before finishing off evenly to not be beaten far.
Strode forward from gate 10 to cross to lead. Headed in the lead by improving horse past the 650m, entered last section just over 2L behind before weakening out late to be well beaten.

Improved after start to race outside the leader in early stages. Relegated back to 5th when pace quickened passing the 600m. Began yielding ground passing the 500m & failed to make any headway in straight.

Ridden forward after start to be prominent until getting good position 1,1 after first section. Lost position badly in third section when pace slowed & also steadied for clear run near 550m. Never improved in last section.
Bumped & start before drifting back to third last on rail. Continued along the inside, 7L from lead entering last section before failing to make any noteworthy headway in straight.

Fractious in gates & consequently began only fairly before settling at tail of field. Continued near the rear on cornering, before shifting wider in straight but failing to improve in dash to line. Well beaten.

Began fast before being crossed & racing two pairs back on rail. Drifted further back passing 600m when others improved before weakening out further in last section to be a well beaten second last. (Lame next day).
Steadied after start & shifted back to rear when racing wide. Continued wide & at the back before beginning to yield ground from the 500m. Long last.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Away well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off well without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 lengths back, no cover throughout, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, wider after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 450M, showed limited response in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped start, raced at rear, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed good kick approaching 200M, continued on to score by 2-3/4L.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly to the line for 2nd.
At rear, failed to muster speed initially and 2 wide, saved ground and ran on well to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, raced tight at 300M, only show some dash in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide, saved some ground but emptied passing 50M.
Rolled forward and shared lead, along the rail after 700M, stayed on but headed passing 200M.
At rear, along the rail, raced tight passing the 300M, pretty one paced.
Slow to begin, at rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening, only one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, saved no ground in the straight.
Sent forward, 2 wide, emptied after 150M and lost ground.
Rolled forward, along the rail, nothing in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, gave ground after 350M and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Moderate start, ridden early before settling one-out-one-back in 4th, came under pressure to challenge upon straightening, ran on well to prevail narrowly in final strides.
Soon took up running 2-wide, obtained rails run about 800 metres out setting a sedate pace, held slender advantage under pressure in home straight until pipped at post.

Jumped best from the one draw, gradually settled just behind the leader in 3rd on the rail, held every chance despite tight run inside the final 200 metres but unable to peg back the race leader throughout.
Travelled in last few, improved steadily to midfield going up the Rock, saved ground turning in, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Settled in rear of midfield, slightly worse when hampered 550 metres out, produced good late progress from 9th inside the final 200 metres.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield in back straight, fought on steadily under pressure in the run to the line but never threatening.
Moderated start, improved steadily to race just outside the leader about 800 metres out, in similar position into home straight but soon weakened.
Travelled in last few, saved ground turning in, inconvenienced 200 metres out, fought on under pressure.
Settled wide in last few after beginning from a wide draw, remained similar into home straight, produced good late impression final stages.
Settled in midfield on the rail, gained slightly closer to 5th at the Rock, kept on until finding no extra inside the final 200 metres.
Refused to settle and raced erratically in midfield causing interferences in back straight, gained slightly closer rounding home bend but ran home one-paced.
Restrained to rear from the widest gate, trailed the field throughout.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield, drifted out under pressure when ridden out in straight, closed off strongly final 150M to score.
Pushed along after the start to hold a position just ahead of midfield, responded well in straight under top weight, not pace of winner final stages.
Chased leader in a race run at decent tempo, moved up well on straightening to challenge for the lead, outpaced by first 2 final stages, held on for 3rd just.
Slightly slow away, held up in midfield along the fence, travelled well into 150M when gap closed, raced tight 100M, lost out on 3rd in photo.
Began only fairly, settled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the decent pace, bustled along 500M, stayed on well to the line, just missed 3rd in a 3-way photo.
Chased the pace 2-wide, battled on early straight, faded final 100M.
From draw 10 driven forward as expected, crossed to lead 650M setting decent tempo, joined by rival passing 200M, no extra and weakened final 100M.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, kept on evenly on straightening, steadied 150M, no impression after.
Driven forward from widest gate but not fast enough to cross, caught wide no cover throughout, battled on at same pace turning home, weakened final 200M.
Slow to muster speed despite ridden, kept wide by rivals and unable to slot in, failed to run on from the rear over final 300M.
Crowded for room at the start, caught wide and shuffled back to last turning for home, couldn't go on in the straight.

Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on very well in straight, easily scored.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off strongly to take 2nd on line.
Quickly into stride, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider after passing 450M, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, same position to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, showed no response in straight.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, hard ridden turning in, showed no response, finished last.
Took rail and led at fast sectionals, drifted away 400M to score.
Very slow away, at rear, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Midfield along the fence, held ground for 3rd.
At back, 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Pressed forward, 2-3 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, weakened 200M.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the fast pace, faded 700M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Bumped start, never competitive, tailed out.
Raced inside the lead, asked for effort near 400M, responded strongly to score.
Raced in lead on outside rail with nice early speed, responded well when asked for effort, missed by 1/2L.
Settled behind leaders, placed pressure passing 400M, worked home well.
Travelled behind leaders on outside rail, gained some ground when placed pressure.
Began awkwardly, raced in middle of track, travelled towards rear, made some ground passing 300M.
Raced midfield, placed pressure passing 500M, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear on outside rail, limited response.
Began only fairly, raced at back, no response when placed pressure.
Raced in front of midfield, gave ground near 300M.
Settled behind midfield, no response when placed pressure.
Settled midfield, came under pressure near 600M, finished tailed-out.

Steadied after start & settled near the rear. Travelled strongly approaching turn, entered last section 3.5L from lead, dashed quickly between runners at 300m, assumed lead at 125m & continued strongly to line for cozy win.

Shifted behind runners, raced third last on rail before improving to midfield near 1000m. Under 3L behind entering last section, held up before shifted ground to get clear running, dashed between runners late to snare second.

Raced in midfield on rail in early stages before improving onto leaders back approaching the 800m. Moved to second soon after straightening, continued close before battling on well late. Not far behind.

Steadied after start, shifted back to race worse than midfield. Shuffled back to second last passing half-way. Moved the widest on cornering, over 4L from lead entering last section, before making late ground in final stages.
Began well & assumed lead. Travelled comfortably in middle stages when uncontested. Asked for full effort at 300m, raced nearly 2L clear before being joined by winner at 125m & weakening late.

Failed to muster speed & consequently raced wide without cover in midfield after start. Hard ridden after first section when improving around field to third, 1.5L from lead on cornering. Weakened final 300m after tough trip.

Raced prominently after start before being crossed & getting good position 1,1. Travelled well into corner, entered last section 2.5L from lead before peaking on short lived effort inside final furlong & weakening out late.
Ridden forward from outside barrier to race outside the leader. Hard ridden on straightening when leader raced clear before empting out at the 350m & yielding ground in the final 250m. Well beaten.
Slow to begin & settled at rear. Lost a length when crowded near the 1000m when continuing at tail. Hard ridden when 6L from lead entering last section before weakening out further in straight.
Obtained good position in midfield between runners. Eased wider passing 600m, entered last section less than 4L from lead before weakening out poorly in straight to be long last.
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned 1 out 1 back, angled out after passing 550M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well, raced prominently, took the lead and found rail near 800M, challenged turning in, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, a bit closer on turn, showed good response early in straight, blocked near 300M, cleared 200M, ran on well to take a place.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 250M, closed off well to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Away with them, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 250M, made little progress thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 10, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 3 wide from 800M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bounded in the air on jumping, then bumped, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Made contact at start and unbalanced, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Away well, raced prominently but wide, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide towards rear, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, trapped very wide, slightly better than midfield, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, crowded approaching 350M, worked home nicely to score by a neck.
Awkward start and raced in worse than midfield, along the rail after 800M, closed off fairly for 2nd.
Bumped start and raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, caught late and missed 2nd.
Taken back and raced at the rear, along the rail after 700M, saved ground and closed off fairly.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, saved some ground but one paced after passing 50M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, after 800M lay out, brushed passing 150M and closed off okay.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, showed some dash in the Straight and closed off fairly. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, only one paced.
At rear, along the rail, saved minor ground in the Straight only.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide after 800M, pretty one paced.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, in the Straight lost ground.
At rear, 2 wide, showed nothing in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, did not threaten.
Sent forward and shared lead, 2 wide, in the Straight lost ground.

Began fairly, soon came to share the pace travelling keenly on the rail, gained slender advantage rounding home bend and 1L clear turning in, kicked further away over 200 metres out and flattered, hung on to the line.
Close up early stages travelling just over 2L back in 5th rounding home bend, ran on under pressure to reach 2nd over 200 metres out but never troubling the winner.
Began fairly from the one draw settling one back on the rail, came under pressure upon straightening, never nearer.
Crowded at the start, travelled keenly forward to 3L 7th coming onto home bend, ran on without threatening in the straight.
Broke well from a wide draw but taken back to close-up 7th, remained wide but gained slightly closer to 6th coming onto home bend, ran on well inside the final 200 metres.
Settled wide in just worse than midfield, came under pressure entering home straight, kept on before making good late impression in closing stages.
Taken back for rails run at the start, made swift progress before settling worse than midfield in 11th, remained similar into home straight, ran on down the centre of the track without threatening.
Began well from a wide-ish gate, travelled keenly in prominent position 3-wide without cover most of the way, found no extra after straightening.
Slowly away, soon recovered to midfield along the rail, travelling some 4L back in 9th or 10th, kept on steadily under pressure in straight.
Niggled at in better than midfield, dropped slightly backward to 8th coming onto home bend, ran home one-paced.
Pressed forward to share the pace early, restrained to close-up 2nd coming onto home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Soon taken well back, trailed the field before gaining slightly closer coming onto home bend, made no impression in the straight.
Gradually dropped to last few, trailed the field into home straight and given reminders, never a factor.
Soon taken back from the widest gate racing ungenerously at times in back straight, never a danger.
Sent forward tracking leader, pace strong from home turn, driven out to lead near 150M, no extra late but managed to hold on from fast finishing rivals.
Given a waiting ride as usual, 7-8Ls off the good pace turning in, switched widest and charged home strongly, just missed.
Settled just ahead of midfield, responded generously when asked in straight, made good headway final 150M to be nearest at the line.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, reserved towards the rear 6Ls off the good pace, closed off well in straight to finish close 4th, nearest line.
Chased leaders in 3rd, stayed on modestly under top weight, not beaten far.
Led at good pace, hung on well to 200M, headed near 150M, no extra late losing several places near line.
From draw 11 ridden forward early, steadied after 1300M for cover, 3-wide behind midfield home turn, stayed on fairly without threat.
Began fairly, held up behind midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, kept on one paced when asked, no impression on leaders.
Settled in mid-division, 3-wide no cover from 1000M, ran home one paced, never a threat to leaders.
From wide draw taken back early stages, settled near last 7Ls off, checked 350M, stayed on fairly over final 250M, not reached leaders.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race in midfield, no extra passing 250M, weakened to last.
Began awkwardly, raced prominently, 2 wide, half-length back on turn, hard ridden 400M, showed very good response, hit the front 300M, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared near 250M, finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position to turn, very wide into straight, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Out in line, raced at tail, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, same position on turn, made some headway in straight.

Moderately away, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, travelled keenly in the middle stages, angled out after passing 600M, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lost left front plate near 600M.)
Slowly away, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider after passing 600M, made no impression in the run home.

Bumped start, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after passing 1000M, bumped 900M, challenged the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)

Shifted out at start and bumped, unable to slot in, trapped very wide in midfield, moved a bit closer after passing 1000M, bumped 900M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll.

Began well from gate 14, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, showed very good response in straight, took the lead 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, always held.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running until approaching 100M, made some progress thereafter.
Bumped on jumping, taken back to race at rear, 5 to 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 200M, cleared 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Clean jump, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 1000M, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed and weakened final furlong.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Away well, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, awkwardly placed near 900M, wider after passing 550M, no clear running in straight, eased final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped on jumping, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1000M, 2 wide turning, half-length back, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
