Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on strongly to the line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide into straight, closed off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 500M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight to take a place.
Commenced well, positioned on rail slight better than midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, hard ridden after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, showed little response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked early in straight, headed and weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, hard ridden 400M, weakened early in straight.
Stood flat-footed and missed the start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to the line.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, blocked most straight, closed off strongly when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, led 250m, overhauled 50M
Checked start, at back, along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, however blocked most straight, ran on well.
Eased back, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden to keep up in box seat, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, benefited by the fast tempo, however blocked most straight, ran on well.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Eased to rear, raced 3 wide, made steady ground 300M.
Failed to muster, trapped 3 wide, moved forward briefly 700M, faded 300M.
In front of midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 400M.
Settled midfield on rail, quickened near 100M, finished strongly to score.
Raced behind leaders, near 650M was taken wider and left wide and without cover, gained some nice ground in the straight.
Ridden forward to race outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, finished well.
Hard ridden from widest gate to take lead, fought well in the straight.
Settled midfield, placed pressure passing 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Slow out, raced at rear, commenced to improve passing 300M, gained some ground passing 50M.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure near 350M, held up for running passing 150M, not fully tested
Settled towards rear, wide on straightening, gained some late ground.
Raced behind midfield, worked home one-paced.
Raced behind midfield on rail, fought hard but only limited response in the straight.
Very slow out, raced detached in early stages, one-paced in the straight, stalls test.

Raced rearward early before improving around field with cover, getting to midfield near 1100m before third at 900m. Continued less than 2L from lead entering last section before powering to lead at 200m & drawing away late.

Raced in midfield on rail in early stages before moving to the outside of runners near half-way. Moved wider on cornering before finishing strongly in the straight to move to second near the 125m behind easy winner.

Had nice position 1,1 in early stages before drifting slightly further back as others improved mid-race. Entered last sect just under 4L from lead before making continual steady ground to move to third in final 100m.
Began awkwardly & consequently raced near the rear after start. Moved away from the inside passing the 500m before finishing strongly between runners in final 250m to not be beaten far on line.

Pushed forward after start, checked away from heels when racing behind leader near 1300m. Shuffled further back to midfield on rail in middle stages. Finished of steadily between runners in late stages & wasn't beaten far.

Steadied across to race in midfield away from rail after start. Shuffled back to third last passing half-way. Shifted the second widest on straightening before making good late ground to be close behind in midfield.

Raced worse than midfield away from rail after the start before being relegated to second last after first section. Continued near the back, along rail on cornering before making up a few lengths late without threatening.
Slow to begin & consequently raced at the tail. Moved 4 wide to improve position approaching 500m, widest in straight before making up a few lengths without threatening.

Raced wide in midfield early before improving around field to take lead near 1100m. Raced away from rail in middle stages before crossing near the 600m. Passed by winner at 200m before weakening a few lengths closing stages.

Showed speed to assume lead before crossing to rail passing winning post. Headed in the lead near the 1100m & raced just behind leading duo thereafter. Weakened out poorly in straight & was well beaten. (Lame next day).

Pushed forward to race outside leader after start before racing keenly when headed on the outside near the 1100m. Held leaders back in middle stages before weakening out significantly from the 400m. Long last, must trial.
Jumped well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, 2 wide after passing 500M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, ran on well to the line.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Slightly slow out and crowded, raced at rear on the inside, improved along the rail on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed limited response after turning in, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, hard ridden after passing 700M, but only showed limited response, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, bumped 1350M, carried wider after passing 800M, no cover thereafter, very wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, bumped near 1350M, 2 wide after passing 800M, wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1200M, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, sent forward to race prominently but trapped wide, took the lead near 1200M, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide on turn, weakened early in straight.
Made contact at start, raced at rear on the outside, weakened on turn, eased final furlong.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, battled on nicely to score by 1-1/4L.
Sent forward, along the rail, battled on nicely but headed in the last 50M to took 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, saved ground and continued on well for 3rd
At rear, 2 wide, saved ground and ran on strongly.
At rear, along the rail, saved some ground in the Straight and ran on fairly.
Sat in midfield and 3 wide with cover initially, sent forward after passing 800M, pretty one paced.
Raced in front of midfield initially, 2 wide, in worse than midfield after 500M and closed off fairly in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover after 600M, one paced only.
Raced in worse than midfield initially, improved passing 800M and wide no cover, weakened passing 200M.
Sent forward and took lead, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide after 650M and finished tailed out. Must trial.
Began fairly, settled over 3L back in 5th, responded well inside the final 200 metres to take charge close to home.
Soon took up running, kicked over 1L clear inside the 200 metres and soon flattered, swamped close to home.
Settled about 2L off the pace on the rail, fought on under pressure after straightening but unable to sustain effort close stages.
Niggled along in 9th towards the rear, made up good ground in straight to be nearest at finish.
Began well from the widest gate but soon taken back, remained in last few to straight, ran on well under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Pressed forward from a wide gate settling in 1L 2nd one off the rail, found nothing under pressure after straightening. Jockey reported horse making an abnormal breathing noise. (Lame next day)
Began well but soon dropped to midfield on the rail over 4L back, found nothing under pressure in home straight.
Moderate start from a wide gate, travelled mostly wide at the back swinging widest turning in, made up good ground down the centre of home straight.
Settled wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, came under pressure when dropped slightly further back on home bend, kept on well in the run to the line.
Inconvenienced at the start settling in rear of midfield, wide entering home straight, kept on to the line. (Mucus in trachea)
Ridden forward before settling one-out-one-back, 3-wide some 2L back in 4th coming onto home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Never a factor.
From wide draw settled behind leaders, 3Ls back making the turn, swung wide into straight, quickened up well to lead 200M, drew clear final 100M, comfortably.
Chased leader 2-wide, kept responding to pressure on straightening but safely held by winner final 200M.
Settled in the 6th spot 4-5Ls off leader, ran on steadily to the line but couldn't get closer to the winner.
Driven forward, crossed to the lead 800M, led at good pace, headed mid-straight, faded final stages.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, reserved near last, 8Ls off the pace 400M, made some progress in straight without troubling first 3.
Held up in mid-division in a fast run race, couldn't sprint with leaders turning home, never in contention.
Checked near 1000M shuffled back to a position behind midfield, kept on same pace in straight, not reached leaders.
Began awkwardly, settled towards the rear in a fast run race, couldn't go on in the straight, never threatened.
Away with them, soon shuffled back to a position towards the rear, 7Ls to make up 400M, failed to make any progress.
Quickly into stride, chased leader on settling, no extra passing 250M, soon out of contention.
Jumped on terms from widest draw but soon detached from the field despite being ridden along throughout the middle stages, never in the picture.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield in a race run at good tempo, didn't respond to riding turning home.

Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, closer to the middle track, no clear run near 400M, found daylight after passing 300M, finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the stands' side, took the lead 400M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival after passing 500M, headed 400M, ran on evenly to the line.
Lifted front feet on jumping then crowded, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader, 3 to 4 away from the stands' rail, no clear running after passing 400M, cleared 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Shifted out at start, positioned half length behind the leader, hard ridden 400M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to race prominently in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong.
Away with them, raced prominently, 3 away from the stands' rail, peaked 400M, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned a length behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden 400M, showed limited response, weakened final 200M.
Moderately away, raced prominently on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed little response, weakened gradually final furlong.
Jumped well from gate 13, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, outpaced in the middle stages, showed nothing thereafter.
Bumped start, race prominently, closer to the middle track, weakened after passing 400M, eased final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently, nearer to the middle track, peaked 400M, weakened 300M, eased thereafter.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, drifted away 300M to score with ease.
Eased to rear for cover, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 350M for 2nd
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Behind midfield, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed forward to share the lead at fast pace, ran on well until 200M weakened.
Slow away, at back, 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made some ground 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to rear, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M.
In front of midfield, not suited by the fast sectionals, emptied 250M.
Eased back, trapped 3-5 wide, suited by the fast pace, no progress.
Trapped wide in midfield, emptied in straight.
Pushed forward, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 400M.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast pace, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 400M.
Slow away, never competitive.
Raced behind midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear, widest on straightening, responded solidly in the straight, missed by Neck.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled towards rear on rail, held up in the early part of straight, gained some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve on straightening, worked home nicely.
Raced behind midfield on rail, held up from on straightening until concluding stages, made some ground close to the line.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort on straightening, finished well in the straight.
Ridden forward, raced behind the lead, fought hard in the straight, finished OK.
Settled midfield on rail, near 1100M was checked and lost running, limited response when placed pressure, blood in trachea.
Raced at tail, placed pressure passing 500M, finished one-paced.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled at rear, limited response in the straight.
Jumped well then ridden along to take lead, no response when asked for effort, emptied near 200M.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout early & middle stages. Eased the second widest on cornering, entered last section 4L from lead before finishing powerfully, dashing to lead near 100m & continuing strongly late.

Raced third on rail after start before shifting away from inside & getting nice run 1,1 from near half-way. Entered last section 2L from lead before closing well in final 250m to snare narrow second on line.

Slow to begin, mustered speed after start to race midfield on rail. Moved away from inside near 800m, shifted wider on cornering, dashed to share lead momentarily near 150m, over-run late, and only beaten half length.

Raced wide without cover in midfield after start before improving position to race outside the leader by 700m. Continued close, holding narrow second by the 200m before being over-run by fast finishers in closing stages.

Raced third in early stages before getting good position in midfield away from rail in middle stages. Eased wider on cornering, entered last section over 3L from lead before making up some ground to be beaten less than 2L.

Shifted behind runners after start to race near rear. Continued in second half, had some difficulty getting clear running on straightening when 4.5L from lead before shifting out at 200m & finishing well to midfield. (Bled).

Steadied after start when attempting to get cover before drifting back to second last near the 800m. Continued with only one behind on straightening, 5L from lead before making steady late ground to midfield.
Began very fast & came across from outside barrier to lead. Continued to hold narrow lead at the 200m mark before peaking & tiring quickly in late stages.

Drifted back, just worse than midfield between runners after start. Taken wider near 850m before racing 3 wide with cover thereafter. Cornered widest, 5.5L from lead before only maintaining position in run to line. No threat.

Crowded on jumping & consequently raced rearward in early stages before improving position along rail to midfield, 4.5L from lead nearing half-way. Offered little in last section & weakened out to be well beaten.
Improved quickly after the start to shift across before getting on leaders back from the 1000m. (Mucus in trachea post-race).
Slow to begin, had no speed & was hard ridden at the tail throughout. Did nothing in the straight & tailed out to long last. (Mucus in trachea post-race).
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on well to hold off the challengers late.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, wider turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Crowded start, positioned towards rear on the inside, angled out after turning in, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, closed off well to take a place.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, unable to obtain clear run early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to make frame.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, similar position on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced very wide towards rear, no cover throughout, 7 lengths back turning in, had no clear run for most part of the straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide after passing 700M, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 10, raced 2 wide better than midfield, moved closer on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened final 100M.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 3 wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, positioned right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed no response in straight (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
Sent forward and took lead after 600M, kept on going and win impressively by 4-3/4L.
Sent forward and sat outside the lead, stayed on well to the finish to take 2nd.
At rear, wide no cover, improved in the straight and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Raced in behind the leader, along the rail, ran on fairly and headed near 250M.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, made ground, ran on well to the line.
Sat in midfield, along the rail, continued on fairly to the line.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on until flattened in final 150M.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, flattened passing 200M.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, weakened passing 250M.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, lost ground and was eased down in the Straight. Unacceptable performance. Must trial. (See Incident Report)
At rear, wide but with cover, did not feature. Finished tailed out. Must trial.

Ridden positively from a wide gate to briefly lead when 4-wide coming onto home bend, shared the pace turning in before gaining 1L advantage inside the 200 metres, just held on to the line while hanging out.
Always well there, one back in 3rd turning in, fought on well under pressure to miss by the narrowest of margins.

Lost ground at the start settling in 10th, commenced move out wide rounding home bend to come within 3L of the pace turning in, ran on under pressure to hold every chance only to be denied in a three-way finish.

Began from a wide gate, with leaders early before taken some 3L back 4-wide cover after the first 150 metres, 2-back 3-wide rounding home bend, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres
Close up, improved to share the pace rounding home bend, headed about 200 metres out and soon weakened.
Travelled in 8th on the rail some 3L off the pace, became 6th in similar position rounding home bend, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran home one-paced.

Lost ground shortly after the start and dropped to just worse than midfield, hampered coming out of back straight and dropped further back into home straight, fought on steadily. (Blood in trachea) (Lame next day)
Soon taken back from the widest gate dropping to last after the first 250 metres, came under pressure rounding home bend and went wide into the straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Amongst the leaders early, remained 4-wide without cover despite shifted one back to 5th rounding home bend, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Broke well, settled within 3L of pace in early stages, gave ground from rounding home bend. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Slowly away, trailed the field for the first 250 metres, saved ground on the rail turning in but never a danger.
Took up running on the rail shortly after the start, headed narrowly coming out of back straight, folded up quickly in home straight.
Crowded start, reserved behind midfield 4Ls back, wide from 550M, quickened up smartly to lead near 200M, drew clear for impressive win.
Tracked leader along the fence, couldn't match winner's acceleration passing 400M, stayed on under top weight to share 2nd.
Raced keenly behind leaders on settling, forward move 650M along the 3 path, led nearing 400M but no match with winner 200M, fought on to hold DH 2nd.
Chased leaders 2-wide, responded mildly early straight, held by first 3 final 200M.
Prominent, pressed leader from home turn, fought on early straight, outsprinted final 250M.
Bumped at start then steadied to find cover, raced 3-wide at the back, ran on fairly final 350M, no threat to leaders.
Reserved near the rear, driven along 500M, awkwardly placed 200M, made limited progress to the line.
Near the rear early stages, improved to midfield before home turn, failed to pick up pace in straight, never able to challenge.
From draw 11 raced wide no cover in midfield from 800M, taken wider 600M, couldn't finish off turning home.
Strolled forward to lead as expected, pressed by rivals 700M, failed to finish off in straight. (Jockey : came under pressure when challenged by rivals home turn.)
Settled at the rear 6Ls off the pace, failed to pick up in the straight, never involved.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, angled out early in straight, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took brief lead 800M, shared lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first few late.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned on rail better than midfield, moved a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear running until 100M, finished off evenly.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the early lead, briefly headed after passing 800M, shared lead on turn, kept on well to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover towards rear, 7 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, same position on turn, kept on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, 8 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, 9 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 11, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, very wide into straight, showed limited response in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, failed to make close off in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, showed no response early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Out in line, positioned 1 out 1 back, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, kept on well in straight to take a place.
Away with them, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, showed good response after turning in, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed near 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 450M, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Reared start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, made some progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L behind turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Ordinary jump, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, trapped very wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, showed some response after turning in, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, showed no response early in straight, eased final furlong.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail throughout. (Bled.)

Average to begin, raced 2 wide, slightly better than midfield, angled out after passing 450M, hard ridden 300M, showed very good response, hit the front 100M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the rail, allowed rival to cross near 550M, angled out after passing 450M, closed off well to take 2nd. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 550M, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, headed 100M, stayed on for 3rd.
Shifted out at start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Began fairly, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced prominently but trapped wide, 2 wide from 550M, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace along the fence, lack room 400M, closed off strongly to score.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 500M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, not suited by the fast pace, hung on well until 200M overhauled.
Midfield, 2 wide, held up 5-3, made good ground when clear.
Slow away, at rear, 2-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Very slow away, at rear, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, soon emptied 400M.
Fast out, travelled keenly in the lead, fought strongly in the straight to score.
Raced behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, made some nice ground passing 150M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort on straightening, fought nicely in the straight.
Jumped well, raced behind the lead, asked for effort passing 450M, finished well.
After 1200M was left racing 3 wide and without cover in front of midfield, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 50M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Settled behind midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 600M, finished one-paced.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure passing 500M, gave ground passing 200M.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, raced at tail, no response in the straight.

Obtained good position in midfield between runners. Under 2L from lead entering last section, held up between runners, unbalanced & bumped when getting clear before rocketing home final 100m to snare lead final strides.

Ridden forward, assumed lead after 100m before crossing to rail soon after. Travelled well when enjoying slow sections in middle stages. Continued to hold narrow lead until being caught by winner in final two strides.
Got good run on leaders back throughout early & middle stages. Obtained running along the rail inside the leader & continued to finish off steadily in late stages to hold narrowly beaten third.
Began well, before racing second outside the leader. Continued only a neck from the lead passing the 300m before peaking approaching the 100m & giving a length or two late. Not beaten far.
Not fast away before settling in midfield, two pairs back on rail. Entered last section 2.5L from lead, shifted away from inside near the 300m before finishing only fairly to midfield in late stages.

Caught wide without cover in midfield before improving position nearing 800m. Continued to cover additional, 1.5L from lead on turn, raced tight, bumped & unbalanced near 300m when peaking on run before tiring thereafter.
Shifted back after the start & raced at the tail. Second last entering last section, passed a few tiring runners but made no relative ground & was well held.

No early speed & settled third last between runners. Keen passing the 800m when 3.5L from lead. Moved into clear running on straightening before weakening in final 300m to be well beaten. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Ridden along on cornering, entered last section under 3L from lead before weakening out to second last over 9L behind.
Began only fairly, crowded & lost ground consequently racing at tail. Failed to improve in straight & weakened out to be beaten nearly 10L last.

Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on very well to score with plenty gas in tank.
Bumped shortly after start, took the early lead, headed near 850M, 2nd on turn, retook the lead early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Away well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 2 to 3 lengths back, wider turning in, one-paced in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, sent forward to race prominently, took the lead 850M, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside with no cover, moved closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, ran on nicely and held off challenge to score.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, made ground and closed off strongly to the line to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, lay out rounding the Home Turn and made some ground in the Straight for 3rd.
Settled to race in about midfield, 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
At rear, along the rail, saved ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and took lead, stayed on but headed passing 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, made some ground until flattened in final 100M.
Sent forward and raced behind the lead, pretty one paced.
At rear, 2 wide after 600M, one paced only.
Eased and settled at rear, along the rail, did not improved in the Straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, weakened passing 100M. (See Incident Report)
Raced in midfield, 3 wide, did not feature.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, lost ground in the Straight.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, nothing in the Straight.
Began well from the widest gate sharing early pace, kicked 1L clear half-way out and drew further away passing the 300 metres, won easily.
Settled about 2L off the pace towards the end of the small field, commenced move inside the final 400 metres, ran on to reach 2nd just inside the 200 metres but never threatening.
Settled just over 1L off the pace behind the leaders, came under pressure when about 2L back in 4th over 400 metres out, never able to quicken to threaten.

Restrained up 1L off the pace without cover near the centre of the track, became 2nd in a similar position coming onto the course proper, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Badly crowded at the start losing ground, shifted out onto stands rails at the back 700 metres out and improved to be just off the pace, found no extra under pressure inside the final 400 metres.
Badly crowded at the start but soon recovered to share the pace far off the stands rails, dropped out from over 400 metres out.
Crowded after a moderate start before settling close up in 3rd, weakened under pressure inside the final 400 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Blood in trachea)
Settled behind leaders in 5th spot, never far off, picked up strongly early straight, vied for lead over final 200M, gained upper hand late.
Chased the pace, in 3rd place making home turn, improved to the lead 300M, joined by rival passing 200M, fought and went down by a head at the finish.
Held up behind midfield, raced keenly from 900M, shifted away from fence 500M, stayed on steadily to the line but safely held by first 2.
Began fairly, soon bustled along, settled near the rear 5Ls back, ran on mildly to go 4th near line, no threat to first 2.
Jumped well, chased leaders in 4th, raced tight and hampered 300M, kept on same pace to line, no impression on leaders.
Caught wide no cover early, improved to race outside the lead 800M, checked 300M lost ground, kept on same pace and no threat after.
Crowded for room at start, held up in the rear 5Ls behind leader, ran past beaten horses in the straight only, never in contention.
Failed to show sufficient early speed, raced further back than intended, wide no cover from 800M, couldn't go on in the straight.
From wide draw dropped back to race at the tail of the field, caught wide home turn, failed to finish off in straight.
Driven out early, led from 1200M, headed near 300M, soon no extra, weakened.
Settled down behind midfield, didn't respond to riding from top of straight, never involved.
Bumped on jumping, raced behind midfield on the inside, there to turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began awkwardly, raced towards rear on the inside, commenced move 450M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.

Made contact at start, raced prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide after passing 900M, 2nd on turn, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, ran on well but unable to hold off the first two final 100M.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, showed good response early in straight, peaked 200M, stayed on for 4th.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, still well back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, commenced move 450M, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, checked early in straight, awkwardly placed 300M, made no progress thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened thereafter.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, got cover after passing 900M, found rail near 650M, 3 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, trapped wide with no cover, 2 lengths or so back, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.

Commenced well from gate 13, raced prominently on the outside, half-length back on turn, hard ridden after passing 450M, showed very good response, hit the front 250M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced 3 wide towards rear, 5 lengths or so back turning in, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, easy run to turn, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began very awkwardly and unbalanced, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, moved closer along the rail on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Out in line, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, checked near 1350M, there to turn, made minor progress despite not getting a clear path in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in midfield, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths back turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, peaked turning in, weakened early in straight.

Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out near 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, found a 2 wide spot near 800M, same margin back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, found rail near 800M, 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Commenced well, positioned on rail behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made good progress to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Shifted in at start, travelled keenly early, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, wider on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Moderately away from a wide draw, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, hampered and dropped to midfield near 900M, 4 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 100M.

Slightly inconvenienced at start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival near 800M, led by a length turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, travelled keenly after passing 1100M, no cover on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, dropped position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Slowly away, raced towards rear on the outside, travelled keenly after passing 1250M, bumped and unbalanced shortly thereafter, moved forward 1000M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M. (Lost right hind plate.)
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, 2 wide on turn, weakened after passing 300M.
Took tail and led easily at slow sectionals, hung on well to score just by a narrow margin.
Settled in front, 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Slow away, took tail at back, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, progressed well 400M, however run ended 150M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
Slow away, at rear, trapped 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, soon weakened 300M.
Slow away, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Slow away, never a factor.
Hard ridden along to race behind the lead, commenced to improve near 500M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Settled midfield on rail, after 400M was held up for clear running, made up some nice late ground.
Travelled midfield, asked for effort passing 600M, gained some nice ground passing 200M.
Niggled to take lead, led by 2L, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, near 300M was checked and lost running, gained some ground passing 100M.
Jumped well, raced in front of midfield, placed pressure on straightening, worked home one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, in the straight placed pressure but only one-paced.
Began only fairly and was crowded for room, then taken back, raced at tail on rail, placed pressure passing 600M, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced in box seat, niggled after 600M, no response in the straight.
Settled at rear, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, gave ground in the straight.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout early & middle stages. Eased wider on cornering, entered last section only 2L from lead, dashed up to take lead approaching the 200m before continuing on late to hold challenger.

Mustered speed to race just behind the leading trio on rail. Held up near 400m when less than 2L from lead, shifted out at 225m when improving to second before closing late to be narrowly beaten. (Rider suspended).

Shifted across behind runners to race at the tail. Awkwardly placed behind heels near 500m when third last on rail. Made steady headway early in straight before shifting wider near the 250m & closing strongly in late stages.

Shifted behind runners after start & raced third last away from rail. Continued near the back, 5.5L from lead entering last section, moved the second widest before making steady late ground to snare forth in late stages.
Raced in midfield on rail in early & middle stages. Moved away from rail on cornering when 3L from lead, shifted out to get clear running near the 300m before finishing off steadily thereafter.

Pushed forward from wide gate but left racing wide & without cover in midfield from the 800m. Continued wide on bend, entered last section around 2L from lead before peaking on effort near 250m & weakening a few lengths late.

Drifted back after start & shifted across to race at the tail. Continued a clear last on cornering, over 6L from lead entering last section before making up a few lengths when running on to midfield finish from last.

Raced just worse than midfield away from rail in early & middle stages. Moved into clear running when 4L from lead on cornering, before making no real headway in straight. (Not comfortable in action-rider).
Began awkwardly before settling worse than midfield on rail. Moved away from inside on cornering, entered last section just under 5L from lead but failed to make any noteworthy ground in straight.

Showed early speed to share lead but was held away from rail by inside runner. Continued to hold slender lead on cornering before emptying out approaching 200m & weakened sharply thereafter. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Strode forward from wide gate, raced three wide outside leader before steadying & racing third with cover from the 800m. Only 1L from lead entering last section before emptying at 250m & weakening sharply in final furlong.

Raced in midfield, three wide with cover throughout. Hung outwards & lost ground around the bend consequently relegated back to last entering last section. Weakened further in straight to be beaten over 10L.

Raced in midfield between runners in early & middle stages. Continued between runners only 2L from lead on straightening before being badly crowded & losing ground near the 200m & played no part thereafter. Had excuse.

Mustered speed after start & held leader away from the inside when racing second along rail. Improved to share lead on cornering before emptying out at the 400m & weakening very poorly in straight to be a long last.
Quickly into stride, sent forward to take the lead, nearer to the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 350M, kept on very well to the line.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed very good response, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, closed off well to take a place.
Began well, raced 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, made good progress final 400M to make frame, nearest on line.
Crowded on jumping, raced prominently, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, made good progress final 400M to be nearest on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Fast into stride, raced towards rear on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M but only showed limited response, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped with them, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, made no progress final 400M.
Crowded start, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, only showed limited response, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from gate 1, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the middle track, hard ridden 450M, showed no response, weakened final furlong.
Began well from gate 14, raced behind midfield on the stands' rail, showed no response final 400M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden 300M, showed no response, weakened final 200M.
At rear, along the rail initially, 2 wide after 700M, made ground and closed off strongly to score by 1L.
Raced in the box-seat, gave a brave run but couldn't hold off the winner in the final strides.
Sent forward and took lead, stayed on but headed passing 100M.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, kept on going to the line.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, in the Straight hung in and ran on only fairly to the line.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, made some ground in the Straight and closed off okay.
Slow to begin, worse than midfield and along the rail, pretty one paced.
Crowded start and at rear, only one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, wide but with cover, did not improved in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced outside the leader, weakened passing 200M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve. Finished tailed out. Must trial.
At rear, wide no cover, did not feature. Finished tailed out. Must trial. (See Incident Report)
Niggled at early stages settling in midfield on the rail, gained closer to within 2L of pace rounding home bend, responded well inside the final 200 metres to take command over 100 metres out.
Restrained mainly 2L off the pace in 5th 2-wide, in similar position turning in when jockey dropped his rein briefly, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled better than midfield about 3L off the pace on the rail, gained closer to 4th coming onto home bend, ran on steadily in straight to narrowly miss 2nd.

Ridden positively from the widest gate to the front before ceding advantage for 2nd spot on the rail turning into back straight, switched out for a run rounding home bend and led into straight, swamped over 100 metres out.
Settled in rear of midfield, inconvenienced and lost position about 800 metres out, made up good late ground to be nearest at finish. (Tactic questioned)

Ridden positively from a wide gate to take up running at the 1200 metres, obtained rails run shortly after turning into back straight, led until narrowly headed home turn, weakened under pressure inside the 200 metres.
Jumped well, gradually settled in forward of midfield in back straight, slightly closer when pace slackened on home bend, one-paced in the run to the line.
Began moderately from a wide gate and soon taken back to the rear, trailed the field most of the way to the straight, ran on past well-beaten runners.
Settled well back, made short-lived impression early in home straight.
Taken back from a wide gate travelling wide without cover towards the rear, made short-lived effort around home bend, gradually weakened after straightening.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Travelling wide without cover throughout, made steady headway to reach within 1L of pace in 3rd in back straight, dropped out of contention from approaching home turn. (Injury to right front foot)
Slowly away, recovered quickly to last few on the rail, gained closer to midfield half-way out, came under pressure rounding home bend, weakened out of contention upon straightening. (Lame next day)

Placing: PU
Comment: Travelled in forward of midfield in 7th, dropped away quickly 900 metres out.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, loomed 300M, responded well to pressure, surged late to nail the long time leader just before line.
Emerged as leader from 1200M, kept on well on straightening, dug deep when pressed by rival late stages, caught near line.
Urged along to take up a spot in midfield, shifted out a number of horses to obtain run 300M, continued on well to the line, nearest finish.
Slotted into a midfield spot, shifted widest nearing 500M, quickened up well to be challenging for the lead 150M, one paced close home.
Chased leaders 2-wide, shifted out nearing 600M, moved up early straight to challenge for the lead, couldn't sustain run passing 150M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, settled on outside of rear pair 9Ls off the pace, closed off final 400M fastest making good headway to the line.
Raced along the fence in a position just ahead of midfield, kept on same pace in straight, well held by leaders.
Taken back from draw 12, restrained to race towards the rear, responded only fairly on straightening, not able to challenge.
From wide draw dropped back to the rear as expected, didn't show his usual finish on straightening. Never involved. (Jockey unable to explain for the disappointing run.)
Settled down 2-wide in midfield, hung under pressure in straight and proved difficult ride, didn't quicken, no impression leaders.
Away awkwardly, ended up towards the rear, couldn't pick up turning in, never reached contention.
From draw 11 caught wide no cover chasing leaders, struggled from 500M, soon no extra and left behind.
Chased leader, came under serious pressure 550M, dropped away rapidly turning home.
Clean jump, positioned 3/4L behind the leader in the middle of the track, showed very good response in the final 400M, won by 1/2L.
Away well, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off well to take 2nd on line.

Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, ran on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Jumped with them, raced prominently on the middle track, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed near 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 lengths or so back in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 350M, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Shifted in at start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, nearer to the far side, peaked and headed 300M, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths or so back, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off evenly.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced towards rear in the middle of the track, 2 to 3 lengths back, showed limited response final 400M.
Jumped well, raced prominently in the middle of the track, peaked 500M, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day.)
Away with them, raced towards rear on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed no response, weakened and eased thereafter.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced at rear on the stands' rail, showed nothing final 400M.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, showed no response, weakened and eased final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move 500M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, ran on very well to the line.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, wider turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Taken back to race 2 wide at rear, moved closer turning in, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, very wide into straight, closed off well to make frame.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well without threatening.
Jumped well, sat right behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked near 150M, headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back turning in, taken very wide in straight and made some progress.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.

Jumped well from gate 12, unable to slot in, trapped very wide behind midfield, sent forward after passing 1350M, settled in 2nd in the middle stages, 2 wide, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Away well, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, severely checked 300M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 900M, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Fast into stride, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 150M, kept on very well to the line, easily scored.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, finished off very strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, angled out 400M, made little progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Average to begin, raced prominently but very wide, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, one-paced in straight.
Away well, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, one paced in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, one paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at fast sectionals, hung on well to win.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made good ground when clear.
Eased back, along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed early, sat in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, on heels 400M, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden early, in front of midfield, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast tempo, weakened 300M.
Slow away, trapped 3-4 wide throughout behind midfield, emptied 400M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Moderate start and no early speed, settled towards rear, commenced to improve passing 400M, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, finished strongly to score.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, mid-race moved to take lead near 600M, fought solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Niggled forward, raced midfield on rail, commenced to improve near 400M, battled nicely in the straight.
Urged along to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, worked home well.
Settled in box seat, placed pressure at 450M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at rear on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield, tried to improve passing 500M, limited response in the straight.
Began awkwardly, after 1200M was left racing wide and without cover behind midfield, widest on straightening, no response in the straight, restricted in all limbs next day, must OVE.
Settled in front of midfield, came under pressure passing 500M and gave ground in the straight, must trial.
Raced behind the lead, came off bridle passing 700M, then gave ground prior Home Turn and failed to finish, must trial.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, won by 1/2L.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back, 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, wider on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover after passing 800M, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently on the outside, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Fast into stride, sat 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Moderately away, positioned on rail behind midfield, 4-1/2L back, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Shifted in abruptly at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, carried wider after passing 400M, no clear running in straight, eased final 75M.
Commenced well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, commenced move after passing 400M, hit the front 200M, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, very good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back to race behind midfield on the inside, angled out 450M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out 400M, finished off evenly.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 100M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, trapped very wide early, positioned outside to the leader after passing 1100M, shared lead to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Away well, trapped 3 wide, a length or so back, found a 2 wide spot near 1100M, hard ridden after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, shared the lead with rival after passing 1100M, peaked and headed 400M, weakened early in straight.
Began very awkwardly and at rear, along the rail, made significant ground and closed off impressively to score by 3/4L.
Sent forward, 2 wide, stayed on but only headed passing 50M.
Bumped start and at rear, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, kept on going to the line.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, ran on only fairly to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, made some ground in the Straight only. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward and raced along the rail, flattened after passing 100M.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on Straightening, only one paced.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, did not feature.
Sent forward and took lead, weakened passing 200M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight and finished tailed out. Must trial. (Heart Irregularity)
Began well settling some 3L back in 5th, slightly further off the pace entering home straight, ran on well to get up near the line.
Sluggish at start, trailed the field to home straight, briefly baulked and switched inward over 250 metres out, finished off the race well between runners to snatch 2nd late.
Soon dropped to last few, finished well down the centre of home straight.
Began well from the widest gate, soon came to dispute the lead over 800 metres out, hit the front under pressure upon straightening only to be collared close to home.
Jumped awkwardly, settled in rear of midfield on the rail, came under pressure over half-way out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, ridden forward to be wide in joint 3rd one-out-one-back in back straight, in similar position entering home straight, kept on steadily until pipped for a placing final strides.
Taken back from a wide gate travelling in 9th about 6L off the pace, switched out for a run entering home straight, ran on and never nearer. (Distressed)
Broke well, niggled at one back on the rail, kept on until finding no extra close to home.
Settled in midfield, kept on same pace without quickening, tightened near the line.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th just over 3L off the pace, made no impression in home straight.
Began well from a wide draw, soon took up running on the rail over 1000 metres out, led the field until joined on home bend, folded up quickly inside the final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground and soon dropped to one from last, remained well behind to home straight and widest turning in, found nil.
Driven forward, wide no cover for most of the trip, opened up 2L lead early straight, continued on well final 200M holding off rivals comfortably.
Began well, drifted back to race in midfield, ran on steadily from top of straight but was readily held by winner over final 150M.
Prominent chasing leader, fought on well final 300M for 3rd but not able to challenge winner.
Away with them, settled just ahead of midfield, swung wide home, stayed on steadily to only just miss a minor placing.
Led early stages, tracked leader from the turn, kept on to hold 2nd until 100M, lost several places close home.
Restrained on jumping from draw 9, settled towards the rear, awkwardly placed behind a rival home turn, closed off well over final 300M.
Unable to slot in from draw 12, caught very wide throughout the race, made minor progress down the outside on straightening.
Began fairly, caught 4-wide towards the rear, made the home turn awkwardly, gave limited response turning in, not reached leaders.
Jumped on terms on draw 1, chased leaders, kept on same pace in straight, no extra final stages. (Blood in trachea.)
Shifted across behind runners, raced in last 7-8Ls off the pace, responded only fairly on straightening, never a threat.
Jumped fairly, raced near the rear along the fence, didn't respond when driven 400M, never reached contention.
Chased leaders early stages, shuffled back to midfield nearing home turn, couldn't go on in the straight.
