Began fairly, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, no daylight early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning, finished off well to take 2nd.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take a place.
Commenced well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress thereafter to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Crowded start, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 3 wide, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Settled in front of midfield, closed off strongly 400M to score.
Slow away, at rear, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M.
Pushed to take rail and led at fast sectionals, overhauled 300M, hung on for 3rd.
Failed to muster, behind midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Slow away, at back, took rail, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, made ground when clear.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, bumped 400M, made steady ground 300M.
Pushed forward, one out one back, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, emptied 300M.
Bumped a runner and became unbalanced at start, the ridden along to take lead, responded strongly in the straight, scored by 3L.
At the start was bumped and became unbalanced, than taken back, asked for effort near 500M, made up some nice late ground.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve near 500M widest on straightening, gained ground passing 150M.
Taken back at start, commenced to improved rounding the Home Turn, made some ground in the straight.
Raced in box seat, placed pressure passing 500M, in the straight lay in, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield, worked home one-paced.
Urged along to race outside the lead, faded out passing 250M.
Niggled throughout, weakened passing 200M.
Ridden forward, raced in handy position, placed pressure passing 500M, faded out near 200M.
Raced in midfield on rail. Shifted away from rail near the 500m, bumped when forcing a wider passage on cornering before dashing to lead at the 200m and drawing away nicely in closing stages.

Allowed to find feet & drifted back to race worse than midfield. Continued well back on cornering, shifted wider, entered last section 4L from lead before making strong late ground to move to second in late stages.
Strode forward, good position 1,1 before racing keenly in middle stages. Dashed up to share lead near 250m before battling on well to hold third on line.
Began only fairly & raced worse than midfield on rail. Continued in second half, nearly 4L from lead entering last section before making steady late headway between runners to be 2L behind on line.

Raced ungenerously in midfield after start before travelling keenly near the 1000m before improving around field to position outside leading pair near the 750m. Moved up to share lead at 250m before peaking soon after.

Obtained nice position on leaders back in early & middle stages. Moved away from rail on straightening, dashed between runners to share lead at 250m before peaking at the 200m & yielding a few lengths late.

Drifted back after the start & settled third last away from rail. Continued well back, over 5L from lead entering last section before passing a few tiring runners when running on to non-threatening midfield position.
Shifted behind runners after start to settle second last on rail. Stayed along rail on cornering, 5.5L from lead entering last section before maintaining margin in dash to line. No threat.
Strode forward from widest gate to race outside leader. Assumed narrow lead entering last section before emptying out at 300m & weakening sharply thereafter. (Restricted action day after racing).
Obtained good position in midfield away from rail. Bumped at forced wider on the track by winner on cornering before offering little in the last section. Well beaten.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield on rail. Shifted away from inside entering last section when 2.5L from lead before weakening out meekly in straight to be well beaten.
Began very fast, crossed from wide gate to lead. Headed in lead near the 400m before weakening sharply in last section.
Had no speed & drifted back to tail of field. Continued a clear last on cornering when hard ridden before failing to improve & was well beaten second last.

Raced just better than midfield away from rail after start. Raced keenly near heels passing the 1000m. Entered last section less than 2L from lead before peaking soon after & weakening sharply to be a long last.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made very good progress in the run home to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame, nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, angled out after passing 500M, very wide turning in, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 900M, travelled well on turn, hard ridden early in straight, peaked and headed near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took toll. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, ran on gamely to the line and scored by 3/4L.
Settled in worse than midfield, 2 wide, crowded for room near 600M, saved ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, kept going until weakened inside final 100M.
Settled to race in front of midfield, 2 wide, kept on going to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail initially, after 850M shifted out and 2 wide, ran on only fairly to the line.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, in the Straight unable to improve and obtain clear running. (See Incident Report)
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, one paced only. (Lame left front)
At rear, 2 wide, only made minor ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide no cover, closed off only fairly.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, did not feature.
Taken back and at rear, along the rail, crowded for room near 600M and then gave ground. Finished tailed out. Must trial.
Broke well, taken back to within 3L of pace in 5th 2-wide, commenced move entering straight and hit the front over 350 metres out, held on well under pressure.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning in, ran on well under pressure to just fail to get up on line.
Began well from the middle gate, travelled in the middle of the leading trio, came under pressure to challenge after straightening but unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled just better than midfield in 6th, switched out for a run entering home straight, ran on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Travelled keenly up to 4th just over 2L back, made the turn awkwardly at about the 900 metres, obtained a clear run shortly passing the 400 metres, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Moderate start, settled in midfield in 7th on the rail, angled out for a run entering straight, ran home one-paced without quickening.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled keenly when wide without cover, remained well behind into home straight, produced good impression running on down the centre of the track.
Taken back to just worse than midfield, remained similar turning in, one-paced under pressure in straight. (Tactic questioned)
Began well from the 2-draw to hold narrow lead on the rail, led until finding no extra inside the final 400 metres.

Slightly slow out, improved steadily from the widest gate to share the lead 3-wide without cover coming onto home bend, remained similar turning in, unable to sustain effort inside the final 400 metres.
Soon dropped well behind and never seen with a chance.
Chased leaders along the fence, into clear 400M, quickened up smoothly to challenge leader 150M, gained upper hand final 100M for a convincing debut win.
Led at decent pace under 10lb claimer, going well into 300M, tackled by winner from 150M, gave way late. Clear from remainders.
Jumped well from draw 1, settled midfield, worked home steadily and improved to 3rd 150M, well held by first 2.
Briefly ridden forward from wide draw but unable to cross, steadied to near the rear for cover, kept on mildly in straight, no threat to first 2.
Dropped back from wide draw, reserved near the rear, made some progress on inner final 400M but not reached contention.
Up with early pace before falling back to midfield, stayed on without threat final 400M.
Jumped on terms, held up 2-wide in midfield, shuffled further back home turn, raced tight 200M, closed off mildly after.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, raced at the rear 6Ls back, responded fairly on straightening, never threatened.
Unbalanced at the start, ridden forward to be racing outside the leader, didn't quicken when pressured passing 400M, soon gave ground.
Crowded at the start, travelled in midfield 3-wide, battled on same pace in the straight, no threat from 200M.
Urged along to take up a prominent position, came under pressure 600M, weak in the finish.
Crowded at the start, bustled along but unable to cross, chased leaders 3-wide without cover, weakened badly passing 350M.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same position on turn, finished off very strongly, easily scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, angled out 450M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Shifted in at start and bumped, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, closed off well to make frame.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently on the outside, 3/4L back on turn, showed some response early in straight, took the lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with no cover, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, showed limited response in straight.
Moderately away from gate 12, taken back to race 3 wide with cover towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off one pace.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, took the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, hard ridden 300M, showed limited response, peaked and headed 200M, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Badly crowded at start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Away well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, travelled well to turn, hit the front 300M, kept on very well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to take a place.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well to make frame, just missed 3rd on line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, angled out 450M, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned on rail behind midfield, same position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider after passing 450M, finished off well without threatening.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 200M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, showed limited response in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.

Began smartly, took the early lead, 2 wide, allowed rival to take the lead near 800M, 3/4L back on turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on strongly to the line and scored.
Made contact at start, raced prominently but 3 wide, found a 2 wide spot near 800M, 2 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd without threatening the winner.
Bumped start, positioned on rail in midfield, hampered near 900M, 3 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, severely checked near 850M, angled out after passing 400M, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, trapped 3 wide and without cover, 2 to 3 lengths back, found a 2 wide spot near 700M, commenced move after passing 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, inconvenienced near 850M, same margin back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Clean jump, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 800M, led by 3/4L turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 to 3 wide, 4 lengths back, no cover after passing 600M, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, taken back to race at rear on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, severely checked near 900M, wider after passing 400M, weakened early in straight.
Pushed early, in front of midfield, 2-3 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Eased at start, took rail behind the field, dashed strongly 250M for 3rd.
At back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, hung on well until 150M emptied.
Pushed forward, 2-3 wide, ran on strongly until 150M weakened.
Slow away, midfield along the fence, no progress.
Eased to rear for cover, 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Eased to rear, took rail, little dash 200M.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, emptied 250M.
Eased at start, sat 2 wide at rear, ran on ok in straight.
Ridden forward, settled in box seat, placed pressure passing 400M, quickened passing 100M to score.
Urged to race behind the lead, asked for effort passing 350M, fought solidly in the straight, missed by 1/2L.
Settled behind midfield on rail, commenced to improve on straightening, gained ground passing 150M.
Settled in one-back-one-off position with nice early speed, responded well in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, made up some good late ground.
Raced midfield, niggled near 400M, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages, wide on straightening, finished one-paced, lame right hind after race.
Raced behind midfield, passing 800M was left racing wide and without cover, commenced to improve near 500M, finished one-paced.
Ridden along but no early speed, settled towards rear, limited response in the straight.
Raced at rear on rail, placed pressure passing 400M but only limited response.
Taken back at start, no response in the straight.
Hard ridden along for some distance to take lead, faded out passing 200M.

Ridden forward to be prominent from outside gate before assuming lead near 600m & crossing to rail soon after. Raced 2L clear on cornering & continued on well in straight to hold 1L advantage on line.

Had good run in midfield away from rail throughout. Eased wider passing the 400m when 3.5L from lead before making continual late ground to move to second near the 100m mark & get within a length on line.

Outpaced after the start & drifted back to second last on rail. Shifted into clear running on cornering when 6.5L from lead before making strong late ground to move to fast finishing third in closing stages.

Began awkwardly before racing in midfield on rail. Moved away from the inside approaching the 400m when over 5L from lead before shifting back inwards when making late ground in closing stages. Not beaten far.
Began fast & held early lead before being headed & crossed after the 600m. Cornered a clear second behind winner before battling on fairly to midfield to be beaten 2L.

Showed good speed to share early lead before getting nice position behind leading trio. Bumped & unbalanced near the 400m when just over 2L from lead. Made no impression in straight when only battling to midfield.

Steadied after start & raced just worse than midfield, 3 wide, before being left without cover near the 600m. Cornered the widest runner before making up a few lengths in last section but was never a threat.
Obtained midfield position away from rail in early & middle stages. Eased wider entering last section when 5L from lead before making no noteworthy headway in straight. Never featured.

Had no speed after the start & settled at the tail. Continued a clear last on cornering, over 8L from lead before halving margin in straight when passing a few tiring runners. Needs further & was never a threat here.
Drifted back after start & raced third from last in middle stages. Continued near the rear, over 6L from lead on cornering & failed to run on.
Raced in midfield along rail in early & middle stages. Continued hard along rail on straightening when 4.5L from lead before weakening out poorly in straight to be second last.

Hard ridden after start to hold rail when a neck behind lead before being crowded when crossed passing the 600m. Lost further ground when bumped nearing the 450m before weakening sharply in straight to be a long last.
Began awkwardly, sent forward to race prominently but trapped 3 wide, took the lead near 800M, found rail near 550M, travelled well on turn, kept on strongly in straight to hold off the challengers.
Jumped with them, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader after passing 400M, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, always held.
Crowded on jumping, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the inside, 2 wide turning, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, same position on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening the first few.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.) (Found to have continuous epiglottic entrapment.)
Away well, raced 2 to 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, made little progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 8, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, made little progress in straight.

Made contact at start, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 800M, allowed rival to cross near 600M, positioned right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide, a length or so back, 3 wide with no cover on turn, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, raced in restricted room near 600M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, made ground in the last 100M and closed off strongly to score.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground and closed off well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly for 3rd.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, continued on nicely in the straight but headed in the last 100M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, closed off only fairly to the line.
Sent forward, wide no cover, pretty one paced.
Bumped start and settled outside the lead, 2 wide, flattened after passing 150M.
Bumped start, raced in midfield, 2 wide after 700M, only one paced.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, closed off fairly only.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover until 400M, lost ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest in the Straight, saved no ground.
At rear, along the rail, did not feature.
Improved steadily from a wide gate before restrained alongside the leader around stables bend, gained upper hand about 200 metres out and held on to the line.

Jumped awkwardly but quickly from the middle draw, obtained rails run in front coming onto first bend, held narrow lead in an even pace until headed into home straight, unable to peg back the winner under pressure.

Ridden early, settled within striking distance just some 2L back in 4th, became 5th in similar position passing the 600 metres, came under pressure rounding home bend, ran on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide draw, remained in rear to home straight, saved ground on the inside turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield mainly 2-wide in 7th, in similar position turning into home straight, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Settled well back, briefly baulked and switched out for a run entering home straight, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.

Broke well from a wide gate and soon taken well back, trailed the field from early in back straight, commenced move over 400 metres out and the widest runner turning in, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards the rear on the rail, awkwardly placed on heels on the rail early in back straight, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled wide behind midfield in 8th after beginning from the widest gate, commenced move rounding home bend and came under strong pressure entering the straight, ran home one-paced.
Travelled just off the pace in 3rd on the rail after beginning from a low gate, became 4th as pace quickened on home bend, faded shortly after straightening. (Tactic questioned)
Travelled in midfield and keenly around 1000-metre bend on the rail, saved ground turning in, made no impression in home straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance – lame next day)
Moderate start, settled 3 wide without cover in forward of midfield in 5th, made short-lived effort around the 600 metres, folded up quickly inside the final 400 metres.
Went forward and set modest pace under 10lb claimer, overtaken at 700M, responded generously from 250M, back to the lead near 50M, hung on.
From draw 11 caught wide no cover until 900M then ridden forward to lead nearing 700M, stuck on well in straight, collared by winner 50M, held on for 2nd just.
Dropped back to race in the rear, 7-8Ls off the pace in middle stages, pushed along 450M, closed off fastest, just missed.
Held up behind mid-division in a modestly run race, wide into straight and 5Ls to make up, ran on well to be nearest at the line.
Unbalanced at the start, raced 3-wide in midfield until 600M, tried hard but held by leaders in straight.
Moved forward to be tracking the leader in a 2-wide spot, kept battling under pressure in straight, run ended 100M, weakened towards the line.
Obtained the rail near 1400M and tracked leaders, not able to quicken in straight, never threatened.
Towards the rear, overraced passing 1000M due to modest tempo, improved to midfield 3-wide back straight, not able to finish off. (Jockey : circumstances of the race note suited. / Blood in trachea)
Held up towards the rear as they settled, 3-wide rounding the final turn, ran past beaten horses in the straight only, no impression on leaders.
Taken back from draw 12, settled near the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, failed to pick up turning home.
Chased leaders early before taking up a midfield position, flat-footed when pace increased 700M, failed to go on in straight.
From draw 1 settled down midfield along the fence, severely checked top of straight and lost momentum, not recovered, eased 250M. (Mucus)

Out in line, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths or so back, moved a bit closer after passing 1100M, very wide into straight, finished off very strongly to score.

Began well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, closer on turn, showed very good response early in straight, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide after passing 900M, 3 to 4 lengths back turning in, closed off well to take a place without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths back, 3 wide after passing 950M, closer on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths back, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.

Away well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail in the middle stages, angled out near 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced at tail, 8 lengths back, moved closer on turn but still the last, made minor progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, hard ridden after passing 500M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Commenced well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened final furlong.
Slow away, at rear, 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, unleashed strong finishing efforts to score.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 200M, just missed by narrow margin in last 2 strides.
Hard ridden to take rail and led at slow sectionals, overhauled 200M, hung on for 3rd.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, on heels 800M, blocked most straight, dashed well.
Hard ridden early, trapped 3 wide in front of midfield, just held ground in straight.
Eased back start, trapped 3-4 wide at back, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
At back, on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Eased to sit outside the leaders, raced very keenly, emptied 150M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 1 out 1 back, benefited by the slow tempo, weakened 200M.
Slow away, took rail at back, harmed by the slow pace, held up and checked in straight, not fully tested.
In front of midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
At back, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Slow away, at back, raced 4-5 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
At back, trapped 3 wide, hampered badly 800M, dropped off 400M.
Raced towards rear on rail, asked for effort passing 450M, quickened passing 200M, finished strongly to score.
Jumped sharply then niggled to take lead, responded solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Checked on jumping and raced at tail, always niggled, made up some nice late ground.
Hard ridden but failed to muster speed, settled midfield, battled well in the straight.
Ridden forward, raced in box seat, had difficulty obtaining clear running in the early part of straight, worked home well.
Settled midfield on rail, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Raced behind the lead, placed pressure but no response in the straight, blood in trachea.

Had good position in midfield between runners throughout early & middle stages. Eased wider into clear running on cornering before dashing to lead approaching the 300m & drawing away for easy win in concluding stages.

Steadied after start & shifted back to race second last away from rail. Shifted the widest in the straight when 5.5L from lead before closing very strongly to charge to fast finishing second inside last 100m.

Not bustled after start before getting good position in midfield between runners. Drifted slightly further back in second section when racing over 6L from lead at 800m. Made steady ground to well beaten third in late stages.

Drifted back after start to race third last on rail. Continued along inside, 7L from lead passing 800m. Improved along rail nearing corner, 3L from lead entering last section before make some gradual headway in late stages.

Improved steadily after start to race midfield on rail. Continued economical run when 5L from lead at 800m. Shifted away from inside on cornering, shifted out further at 300m before finishing steadily in late stages.

Ridden with whip after start to race prominently before being left three wide without cover, 2L from lead from the 1000m mark. Hard ridden when forced wider by winner on bend, before battling away to hold midfield position.

Began well before being crossed & getting good run on leaders back throughout. Moved wider on cornering, entered last section a length from lead before offering no more in final 150m & yielding a length or two thereafter.

Began well before being steadied & racing in midfield, three wide with cover before being left without cover from 800m. Shifted the widest runner when hard ridden on cornering before finishing only moderately to midfield.

Shifted behind runners from widest barrier & raced worse than midfield, wide but with cover. Ridden along on turn, second widest entering last section when 5L from lead. Steadied near 250m but was never a genuine threat.

Enjoyed economical run in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Improved closer to lead along rail nearing bend, entered last section only 1.5L from lead before weakening out in last 300m to be over 6L behind.

Ridden forward after start to race prominently before shifting in to race outside the leader by the 1000m. Hard ridden on straightening before emptying out at the 300m mark & weakening meekly thereafter.
Shifted back behind runners after start to race at the tail. Continued at the back, 9L from lead passing the 800m. Stayed close to the inside in straight but made no real headway & was well beaten.

Bumped & unbalanced at start before mustering speed to race midfield between runners. Continued in midfield approaching turn before offering little in last section & weakening poorly in concluding stages to be second last.

Bumped & unbalanced at start before mustering speed quickly to dahs to lead after 100m. Held lead until being joined by the winner approaching the 300m before weakening badly in concluding stages to be long last.
Clean jump, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, awkwardly placed near 600M, no clear running early in straight, cleared 300M, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began smartly from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner close home.
Moderately away, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.

Average to begin, raced towards rear, unbalanced near 900M, saved ground on turn, made very good progress early in straight, blocked near 100M, not able to be ridden out near the finish. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths or so back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 900M, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, still 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, checked and lost position near 900M, 5 lengths back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear throughout, never a factor. (See Racing Incidents.)
Rolled forward and sat in one-out one-back, finished off impressively to score by 1-3/4L.
At rear, 2 wide, saved ground and closed off well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide no cover, improved and dashed home nicely for 3rd.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, showed some dash only in the Straight.
Raced behind the leader, along the rail, closed off only fairly to the line.
At rear, wide but with cover, made some ground in the Straight only.
Raced in behind midfield, lay out throughout the race when wide no cover, only one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Sent forward and led, along the rail, flattened passing 150M.
Sent forward and raced 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. (Roarer)
At rear, along the rail, did not feature. (See Incident Report)
Raced in midfield, along the rail, no turn of foot and emptied late.
Restrained in 5th just over 2L off the sedate pace, commenced move upon straightening and hit the front passing the 200 metres, won readily.
Broke well to lead, went over 1L clear on straightening, swamped by the winner 200 metres out.
Travelled 3-wide without cover in 4th within 2L of the pace, in similar position turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Raced keenly on heels of the leader in the sedate pace in back straight and around home bend, did not find much room early in straight, unable to quicken to threaten.
Settled in rear of midfield in 8th, ran on quite well in straight to be nearest at finish.
Ridden to close up position early, failed to quicken to threaten inside the final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)

Slowly away and then crowded, quickly recovered along the rail to midfield in 6th just over 3L back taking advantage of the sedate early pace, in similar position turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, saved ground turning for home, ran on quite well without threatening.
Taken back towards the rear in 9th from the widest gate, the widest runner turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.

Slowly away, gradually recovered to rear of the field on the rail taking advantage of the sedate early pace, travelled keenly in 9th approaching home bend, failed to quicken under pressure in the straight.
Taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field 3-wide with cover to home straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Never better than midfield, dropped out in straight.
From wide draw steadied in early stages, settled down behind midfield, quickened well when gap opened up 300M, got up close home.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, swung wide into straight, closed well, not pace of winner final 100M.
Chased leaders along the fence, into clear 400M, fought on, outpaced by first 2 late stages.
Settled in midfield, travelled well into straight, loomed mid-straight before going one paced final 150M.
Driven forward, led along the 2-path, kept on steadily turning in, led to near 100M, lost several places near line.
Began awkwardly, held up near last, over 6Ls to make up 400M, stayed on well without threatening leaders.
Caught 3-wide from draw 10, 3Ls back in midfield making the home turn, kept on one paced in straight, no threat to leaders from 200M.
Driven forward from wide draw, obtained a trailing spot behind leaders, lacked further response in the straight, faded 200M.
Towards the rear, pushed along 550M, gave limited response, never in the picture.
From draw 1 strode forward to be vying for the lead, weakened rapidly passing 200M. (Jockey unable to explain for the disappointing run.)
In mid-division along the fence, bumped the rail 700M and unbalanced, weak in the finish, soon out of contention.
Dropped back to last, detached from 600M, struggled home, eased when no chance.
Commenced well, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, kept on very well after turning in, always held by the winner.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide after passing 600M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved closer along the rail on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared after passing 200M, made some headway thereafter to make frame.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, easy run on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened final 50M.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Moderately away, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, moved closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made little progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield early, checked off heels near 850M, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 3 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight
Made contact on jumping, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, awkwardly placed near 900M, 4 wide on turn, showed no response early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out and bumped, trapped very wide, 2 to 3 lengths back, checked near 900M, very wide turning in, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider after passing 650M, finished off very strongly to score.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take 2nd.

Jumped with them, trapped very wide, a length or so back, moved closer after passing 1200M, 2 wide from 1000M, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 400M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, angled out early in straight, closed off well to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, still 8 lengths back turning in, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Out in line, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away from a middle draw, unable to slot in, trapped 4 wide with no cover in midfield, similar position on turn, one paced in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, very wide turning in, showed limited response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight, eased final 50M.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight, finished last.

Began well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Slightly slow out, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner. (Lost right front plate.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half-length back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 4 lengths or so back on turn, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home without threatening.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off one-paced.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Just behind midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early, took box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, on heels 150M, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 300M, overhauled 150M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, badly hampered 150M, just held ground in straight.
Midfield along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Eased at start, 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, harmed by the slow pace, held up most straight, not properly tested.
At back, 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield throughout, dropped off 400M.
Hard ridden to take tail and led at very slow sectionals, however soon emptied 300M.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, finished strongly to score.
Taken back at start, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, worked home nicely.
Ridden along to take forward position, then steadied to obtain cover near 1600M, raced towards rear, improved passing 500M, widest on straightening, worked home well.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve passing 700M, gained some late ground in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, then slowly improved to handy position passing 700M, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight, rider questioned tactic.
Ridden forward, raced in box seat, placed pressure on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, no response when placed pressure in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, no response when asked for effort.
Wide and without cover throughout in handy position, came under pressure passing 450M, gave ground passing 150M.
Niggled to take lead, came under pressure passing 400M, emptied in the straight.
Hard ridden to stride to lead from outside gate before crossing to rail near 700m. Raced clear on straightening before continuing strongly in charge to line to win by cozy margin.

Showed good speed after start before being crossed & racing on leaders back from 700m. Improved to second soon after straightening before finishing off well to hold that position. No match for winner but clear of third.

Didn't have the early speed of others & drifted back to race worse than midfield away from rail. Entered last section over 4L from lead before making good late ground between runners to move to third at the 100m.

Slow to begin before hard ridden & mustering speed to race midfield on rail. Entered last section 5.5L from lead before making up a few lengths when running on to non-threatening fourth in on-speed dominated race.

Drifted back after the start & raced just worse than midfield early before improving position to be 4L from lead at 800m. Continued to improve between runners nearing corner before only holding position in straight.

Unbalanced at start before striding to midfield when three wide. Bumped & forced wider near the 650m before cornering the widest runner when 3.5L from lead. Held margin in the straight but was never a genuine threat.

Hard ridden to race prominently but couldn't hold out leader/winner before eventually settling second, 1L from lead. Couldn't stay with the winner on straightening before yielding over 3L in dash to line.

Steadied & shifted across to race second last after start. Entered last section nearly 6L from lead before making up a length in late stages to midfield in race that may be short of best. Never likely.

Obtained position in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Continued on inside, just over 4L from lead entering last section before offering little in the straight & weakening further to be well beaten.

Raced behind leading trio after start before keen, bumped & shifted out near 650m & consequently racing three wide, 2L from lead thereafter. Lost some ground when cornering wider before weakening out meekly in straight.
Shifted across behind runners to race third last after start. Forced wider approaching corner, continued 6L from lead entering last section but failed to improve & was well beaten.
Niggled along to hold position at rear before becoming detached approaching the 700m. Weakened badly in second half of race & was a very long last. (Must trial).
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 650M, 3 wide turning, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.

Taken back from gate 11, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 lengths back, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to be nearest on line, just narrowly beaten.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.

Lifted front feet on jumping and away tardily, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, one-paced in the run home.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, found rail near 550M, 5 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
At rear, 2 wide, swung wide on Straightening, made ground impressively to score by a short head.
Sent forward, 2 wide, keep on going for 2nd.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, swung wide on Straightening, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, continued on fairly for 4th.
At rear, 2 wide, saved some ground but emptied passing 50M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
At rear, along the rail, made ground but only ran on fairly.
Sent forward and sat in one-out one-back, only one paced.
Bumped start then sent forward, along the rail, flattened after 100M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail after 600M, emptied after 150M and lost ground.
At rear, wide no cover, nothing in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, crowded for room after 600M and then did not quicken in the Straight.
Broke well from the one draw, settled one back in 3rd on the rail, angled out for a run entering home straight and hit the front over 150 metres out, held on under pressure.
Settled just over 2L back in 4th, commenced move rounding home bend, fought on under pressure from 2L 3rd into straight, unable to peg back the winner throughout.
Took up running coming onto first bend setting a standard pace, held 1L advantage into home straight, unable to sustain effort and swamped inside the final 150 metres.
Settled 2-wide in 8th in midfield mainly over 5L off the pace, came under pressure turning into home straight, finished off the race nicely despite hanging in near the line.
Settled in 5th over 3L off the pace on the rail, gained steadily closer rounding home bend and saved ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began awkwardly, settled in midfield mainly in 7th on the rail, saved ground turning for home, ran on steadily under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled in last few on the rail, in similar position turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began awkwardly, settled 2-wide in 6th over 3L off the pace, commenced move entering home straight, kept on one pace under pressure.
Settled in rear, produced good late impression inside the final 200 metres.
Taken well back from the widest gate, trailed the field most of the way, never seen with a chance.
Travelled towards the rear in 9th, hung in and a difficult ride in the home straight.
Broke well from a middle gate, travelled 4-wide onto first bend before settling one back in 2nd, gave ground from approaching home turn.
Chased leader 2-wide, moved up well to take the lead mid-straight, kept on final stages to hold off fast finishing 2nd.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, picked up well from 300M and closing on winner with every stride, nearest finish.
Tracked leaders, chased hard on straightening, drifted out under pressure final 200M, got up for 3rd near line.
Soon led, pushed out 400M, headed mid-straight, fought on to the line, edged out to 4th in photo.
Settled down midfield, responded fairly turning home, couldn't get closer to leaders in the run home.
Held up behind mid-division, wide into straight, kept on fairly, not going the pace to challenge leaders.
Settled down just ahead of midfield, reluctant to maintain position 600M, couldn't finish off. (Jockey : did not appreciate racing at Happy Valley for the first time.)
Held up in rear pair, 8Ls off the pace 400M, stayed on past beaten horses only, not reached leaders.
Chased leaders in 4th, came under pressure nearing 400M, dropped away turning in. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)
Held up towards the rear, driven out 350M but failed to respond to riding.
Taken back from widest barrier, settled last, failed to finish off on straightening.
Towards the rear, couldn't go on final 400M, very weak in the finish.

Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.

Commenced well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out after passing 450M, made contact early in straight, took the lead 250M, ran on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide at rear, slightly improved on turn, angled out after passing 450M, made contact 300M, made very good progress thereafter to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made contact early in straight, ran on well until peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made minor progress thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide on turn, very wide into straight, made contact 300M, closed off well without threatening.
Away well, raced prominently on the outside, a length or so back, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began only fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Bumped start and unbalanced, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, challenged turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no impression in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover after passing 1000M, wider turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never competitive.
Pushed to share lead, made all.
Bumped start, at rear, progressed steadily 250M.
At back, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit just off the leaders, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed to share the lead, ran on until 100M weakened.
Pushed forward, out of fuel 150M.
Pushed early, midfield, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Eased to sit in midfield, just held ground.
Bumped start, at rear, made steady ground 200M.
At back, weakened 200M.
Pressed forward, emptied 200M.
Slow away, never improved.
Never competitive.
Never a factor.
Settled towards rear on rail, crowded for room passing 400M, quickened passing 200M to score.
Raced midfield, in the early part of straight was held up until near 200M, finished solidly.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, raced midfield on rail, finished nicely.
Settled behind midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, made up some nice late ground.
Jumped well then ridden forward, settled in box seat, had difficulty obtaining clear running in the early part of straight, worked home well.
Raced in front of midfield, tried to improve near 500M, finished one-paced.
Niggled along to take lead, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced at rear, commenced to improve passing 600M, widest on straightening, worked home one-paced.
Settled midfield, steadied away from heels near 300M, worked home one-paced.
Raced in one-back-one-off position, placed pressure but gave ground near 200M.
On jumping was bumped and became unbalanced, hard ridden forward to race outside the lead, weakened near 200M.
Slow to begin, raced at tail, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
After 900M was left racing wide and without cover, checked near 300M, faded out passing 300M.
Raced towards rear on rail, came under pressure near 800M, finished tailed out, must trial.
Showed good speed after start to lead. Held 1.5L advantage in lead entering last section before soon sprinting clear to win by very big margin in what was an auspicious debut performance.

Enjoyed good run on leaders back in early & middle stages. Continued on leaders/winners back entering last section before holding second in dash to line. No match for easy winner but finished clear of third.
Had nice position 1,1 when racing 2L from lead passing the 800m. Held up in early part of straight before getting clear & finishing off steadily to well beaten third. Clear of 4th.

Shifted behind runners before settling third last away from rail. Continued near the tail, over 5L from lead entering last section before making good late ground to forth, but well behind big margin winner.

Steadied after start & shifted back to race second last on rail. Relegated back to last passing the 700m, held up on straightening when 6L from lead before passing a few tiring runners when running on to well beaten fifth.

Raced in midfield on rail, just under 4L from lead passing the 800m. Continued along rail on straightening, 2.75L from lead entering last section before battling away to hold well beaten midfield finish. (Bled).

Was the fastest to begin but failed to muster & was caught in midfield, three wide without cover throughout. Continued less than 2L from lead on cornering before peaking on run at the 300m & yielding ground thereafter.
Strode forward from outside barrier before racing keenly when being steadied to race in midfield. Eased wider on cornering before failing to improve in straight. Well beaten.
Hard ridden after start & improved to race outside the leader. Dropped off leader on straightening before weakening sharply in last 300m to be well beaten.

Shifted ground after start, steadied to get cover before racing keenly when racing just worse than midfield. Just over 4L from lead entering last section but offered little & weakened out to be beaten a big margin.

Had no early speed & drifted back to worse than midfield on rail. Continued along inside on cornering, just over 4L from lead entering last section before offering nothing in straight & weakening to long second last.
Began awkwardly & crowded before shifting back to the tail. Moved wider passing the 800m, improved position slightly approaching corner before weakening badly in straight to be long last.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths back, commenced move 600M, made contact 450M, hit the front early in straight, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Moderately away, raced in midfield, found rail near 1250M, angled out after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Shifted in at start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off well to take 3rd.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 300M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, moved closer in the middle stages, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1-1/2L back, same position on turn, made contact and unbalanced near 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 12, raced at rear on the outside, slightly improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began well, positioned 6 lengths behind the leader on rail, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.) (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Away well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Average to begin, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
Taken back and at rear, along the rail after 850M, saved ground and closed off strongly and scored by a neck.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground and ran on well to take 2nd.
At rear initially, along the rail, ran on well for 3rd.
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on straightening and closed off strongly.
Taken back, 3 wide but with cover, made ground, ran on well to the line.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, continued on but headed in the last 200M.
Settled in one-out one-back, pretty one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
Sent forward and took lead, flattened in the last 150M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, one paced only. (See Incident Report)
At rear, 2 wide, was hampered passing 250M and one paced thereafter.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not feature.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, passing 1000M lay out when travelling keenly, nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced next to leaders after 1000M, 3 wide no cover, never a factor. (See Incident Report)
Travelled mainly in midfield on the rail, commenced move upon straightening, ran on well to hit the front over 150 metres out, held on well.

Ridden forward to 6th just over 2L off the pace, became 5th rounding home bend, quickened under pressure to hit the front briefly inside the 200 metres while hanging in, kept on well to maintain 2nd placing.
Broke well before taken back to just worse than midfield, widest runner turning in, ran on well under pressure down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, settled mainly in midfield, made short-lived effort under pressure early in straight, unable to sustain run inside the final 50 metres.
Settled in last few, one of the back-markers entering straight, ran home strongly down the centre of the track inside the final 200 metres. (Tactic questioned)
Settled well behind after beginning from a wide gate, finished off the race well inside the final 200 metres.

Close up, taken one back coming onto home bend, came under pressure 500 metres out holding some chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Settled about 2L off the pace on the rail in 5th, drifted slightly backward to 6th rounding home bend, did not find much room behind runners after straightening, ran home one-paced.

Close up and wide after beginning from a wide gate, improved to share the lead from 800 metres out, gained narrow advantage under pressure entering straight, but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.

Stumbled badly at start losing ground, recovered steadily along the rail to reach rear of midfield in joint 9th at the 1000 metres, saved ground turning in, ran on under pressure to come within 2L of pace 200 metres out, no extra.

Pressed forward to lead from the widest gate, obtained rails run coming onto first bend but soon joined on the bend, headed narrowly turning for home and folded up quickly under pressure inside the final 300 metres.
Always in last few, never seen with a chance.
Began well from a wide gate, gradually drifted back for cover towards the rear in 11th, given reminders from approaching home turn, found nothing.
Travelled mainly one-out-one-back to straight, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Lame next day)
Driven forward under 10lb claimer, led from 800M, ridden out 350M, held on well from pursuers.
Began very awkwardly, recovered to be close up behind leader, responded well final 400M but couldn't reel in winner.
Close up behind leader, driven near 350M, kept on but held by winner to the line.
Lifted its front feet off the ground and slow to begin, moved up to chase the pace, went 2nd 150M, no extra closing stages.
Held up in mid-division, crowded for room 200M, kept on reasonably well to line before hampered near line.
Raced behind midfield towards the outside of group, stayed on mildly final 400M, ran respectably on comeback.
Chased the pace, kept on steadily passing 400M, always held by leaders.
Raced towards the outside of field, never far off the pace, held ground over final 400M, faded final stages.
Slow to begin, settled last, hard driven 500M, badly held up from 150M when starting to pick up, shifted to outside of field for clear run final 50M.
Began fairly, held up midfield, 3Ls to make up 400M, kept on same pace under pressure, checked close home.
Settled midfield towards the stand's side, kept on same pace final 400M, never near to challenge.
Raced in mid-pack, came under pressure 600M, failed to respond to riding.
Tracked leader along the stand's rail, inclined to lay in for majority of the race, weak in the finish. (Jockey : did not travel comfortably at any stage.)
Raced along the stand's rail from draw 14, struggled to hold its position midway, never threatened.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled well to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced prominently on the outside, travelled well to turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to take a place.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, commenced move 550M, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Away well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, made little progress when clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, very wide turning in, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Slightly slow out, unable to slot in, trapped wide with no cover in midfield, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Average to begin, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, wider from 600M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 150M, weakened rapidly thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.

Jumped well from gate 10, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 500M, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 250M, kept on strongly to hold off the challengers.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd.
Clean jump, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared near 250M, finished off well to take a place.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, angled out 450M, closed off well to make frame, always held.

Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide towards rear of midfield, bumped and unbalanced near 700M, angled out early in straight, made very good progress thereafter to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.

Jumped well from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, took the lead 1100M, found rail 900M, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly and hampered, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, angled out 450M, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, checked off heels near 700M, still 7 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Hampered at start, raced at rear on the inside, difficult to settle and bumped near 700M, 5 to 6 lengths back turning in, kept to inside after straightening and made little progress.
Began smartly, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide behind midfield, no cover throughout, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Bumped start, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross near 900M, sat right behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
