Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on strongly to the line, easily scored.
Fast into stride, raced prominently, 2 wide, 1-1/2L behind the leader on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced in 3rd, trapped 3 wide with no cover throughout, 2 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 3 lengths back on turn, made contact near 350M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, made contact near 350M, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, passed some tired rivals in straight.
Began fairly, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, blocked near 250M, cleared 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, 6 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Hard ridden to secure box seat, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to take rail and lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield along the fence, ran on ok.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, lack turn of foot.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, ran on ok.
At back, 2 wide, no dash.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Eased back, 2 wide, never competitive.
Bumped start, never a factor.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide throughout, dropped off 600M.
Raced midfield on rail, made the Home Turn awkwardly, quickened passing 150M to score.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, fought solidly in the straight.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 350M, gained nice ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, made up some nice late ground.
Settled behind midfield on rail, gained some ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, raced at rear on rail, one-paced in the straight.
Raced in box seat, held up from 250M until 150M, worked home one-paced.
Ridden along in early stages but left wide and without cover, then continued to ridden along to race outside the lead passing 700M, weakened near 100M.
Slow to begin, raced at tail, placed pressure but no response.
Ridden along for some distance to obtain lead, came under pressure near 200M and then gave ground.
Raced midfield, passing 700M was left racing wide and without cover, widest on straightening, emptied passing 150M.
Taken back at start, 3 wide with cover, never in it.

Ridden forward before improving position after first bend to race outside leader from the 900m. Took over lead approaching the 200m & dug deep under hard riding in closing stages to hold off challengers.
Obtained good position 1,1 when racing between runners. Closed off strongly in final furlong to get within a head on the line.

First into stride before steadying & racing in midfield on rail. Three lengths from lead entering last section, moved into clear running on corner before finishing strongly between runners. Raced tight near line.

Mustered speed after start & improved to second before getting leaders back from the 800m. Stayed on the inside rail on straightening before offering no more in final furlong before holding non-threatening forth.
Steadied & shifted back to last after start. Moved wider & improved around field from the 600m, very wide on corner before closing off well in last section to not be beaten far. Improved performance.

Drifted back after first bend & raced worse than midfield, wide but with cover. Improved position passing the 800m to be 3L from lead. Eased wider on bend before finishing evenly in straight. (Blood in trachea post-race).

Steadied after the start & shifted back to race rearward. Continued near tail, 4.5L from lead entering last section, shifted to be the widest runner passing 250m before closing well in late stages. (Rider questioned).
Began only fairly before racing just worse than midfield on rail. Shuffled back to 4th last passing the 800m. Made up a length or so along the inside in final section but was never a factor.
Showed good speed after start to lead before crossing to rail near 800m. Headed by winner approaching the 200m before yielding a few lengths in final furlong.
Obtained good position in midfield between runners. Entered last section 3.5L from lead but offered little in straight & weakened a further few lengths.

Hard ridden to race prominently but was crossed at first bend & was left racing wide in midfield. Left without cover from the 700m, continued wide around bend, peaked soon after straightening before weakening thereafter.

Began awkwardly, steadied approaching first bend & raced third last. Raced ungenerously for considerable distance before being relegated to last near 700m. Raced a clear last on corner before making no headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 500M, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, 2 wide after passing 500M, closed off well to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.

Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover throughout, showed good response after turning in, peaked on run 100M, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced 2 wide towards rear, hard ridden after passing 500M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, there to turn, showed some response early in straight, raced tight near 200M, peaked 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, a bit closer on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear on the inside early, 2 wide after entering the back straight, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, raced tight near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made no impression in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final 150M.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made ground steadily to score by a short head.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, stayed on but just unable to hold off the winner late.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, ran on well for 3rd.
At rear, along the rail, swung widest on straightening and closed off strongly for 4th.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, saved ground and closed off fairly to the line.
Raced in behind midfield initially, at rear after 950M, along the rail, only one paced.
Sent forward initially, settled behind the leader after 1100M, along the rail, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
Niggled but failed to muster speed, midfield, 2 wide, failed to improve in the Straight. (Roarer)
Raced next to the leader, 2 wide, flattened in the last 200M.
At rear initially, midfield after 800M, wide no cover, did not feature.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, lost ground in the Straight.

Travelled wide in midifield from the widest gate, improved steadily to over 2L back in 4th without cover leaving the Rock, went wider rounding home bend and into straight, ran on gamely to hit the front over 150 metres out.
With leaders early, taken one back to 3rd at the Rock, fought on under pressure but found winner too good.
Moderate start, settled in midfield on the rail, gained slightly closer along the rail rounding home bend, fought on under pressure despite a tight run 200 metres out.
Very slowly away and slow to muster, well back and switched wide into home straight, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Travelled mostly in better than midfield in 5th, fought on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from a low draw to lead along the rail, held narrow advantage most of way until home turn, found no extra under pressure.
Jumped fairly from a wide gate, gradually taken back to settle wide in last few, widest runner turning for home, ran on under pressure down the centre of the straight.
Settled behind midfield, in similar position into home straight, kept on well under pressure.
Settled just worse than midfield, slightly worse into home straight, produced good late impression closing stages.
Jumped well from a wide gate, improved to dispute lead from approaching home bend, shared the pace turning in before folding up quickly. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped very awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field onto home bend, found nothing in the straight.
Travelled 3-wide mainly in rear of midfield, dropped out of contention from the 400 metres.
Strode forward, soon crossed to the lead under 10lb claimer, kicked further clear on straightening, in total control final 200M.
Jumped on terms, in 4th spot never far off leaders, driven to go 2nd near 150M, tried hard but unable to close the gap on winner.
Pushed along early, unable to cross and ended up in midfield, no cover from 900M, wide move 500M, stayed on to take 3rd near line.
Reserved in midfield, had a ground saving trip, kept on steadily over final 300M, just missed 3rd, no threat to winner though.
Began well, restrained to race in midfield, stayed on mildly towards the finish without serious threat.
Jumped well from draw 1, settled ahead of midfield, lacked a strong finish final 300M, held by leaders.
Reigned back after jumping from gate 10, settled near last, plenty to do top of straight, got going final 200M making progress late.
Settled down behind midfield, responded only fairly in straight, never going the pace to challenge.
Driven forward from draw 12, settled one out one back, fought on same pace early straight, held 2nd to near 150M, no extra weakened rapidly.
Dropped back to last 8-9Ls off the pace, ran past a couple of beaten horses in the straight, never threatened.
Began fairly, held up towards the rear, failed to finish off in the straight.
Pushed along to be tracking leaders, came under serious pressure 500M, weakened rapidly on straightening. (Lame RF leg / Blood in trachea.)
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to score.
Began smartly from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, travelled well on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back, closer on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Out in line, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, wider on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths or so back, closer on turn but still the last into straight, passed a few tired runners in the run home.

Bumped start, positioned 1 out 1 back, difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, commenced move 500M, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame right front leg.)
Away well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 700M, 4 wide on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out 550M, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.

Shifted in at start and bumped, trapped 3 wide with no cover in midfield early, moved closer on the first turn, positioned 2 wide in 2nd after entering the back straight, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Away well, took the early lead, headed 1550M, allowed rival to cross after entering the back straight, easy run in the middle stages, showed good response after turning in, hit the front 250M, ran on well to the line and scored.
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear on the outside, 3 to 4 lengths back, improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take 2nd.

Began well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader early, 2 to 3 lengths back in the middle stages, saved ground on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, just stayed on for 3rd.
Average to begin, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame, nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, no extra thereafter.

Began only fairly, difficult to settle early, took the lead near 1550M, found rail after entering the back straight, led by a length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover for the majority for the race, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (Roarer.)
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, made steady ground 400M to score.
Slow away, at back, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Bumped start, midfield on the fence, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased back, took rail, lack room 4-2, made good ground.
Hard ridden to park outside the lead, weakened 200M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, weakened 250M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Trapped 4-5 wide throughout, no dash.
Slow away, 2-3 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, out of fuel 350M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, emptied 400M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Slow away, never a factor.
Settled midfield on rail, improved passing 500M, responded strongly in the straight.
Raced midfield, fought solidly in the straight, missed by SH.
Raced outside the lead, asked for effort on straightening, battled well in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, made some late ground in the straight.
Took lead with nice early speed, asked for effort on straightening, gave some ground passing 50M.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced.
Settled towards rear, fought hard but only one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, passing 700M was checked away from heels, one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield, made the Home Turn awkwardly then lost ground, finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, made the Home Turn awkwardly, limited response in the straight.
Niggled to race in box seat, placed pressure and gave ground passing 100M.

Ridden to be prominent after start before getting good position 1,1 throughout. Entered last section just over a length from lead before making continual steady ground to snare lead in final stride to win by narrowest margin.
Showed good speed after start to lead. Continued to hold narrow lead until caught in final stride by winner. Beaten by narrowest of margins but held second in blanket finish.
Strode forward from outside gate before settling outside the leader. Continued close to lead right the way to line before finishing third but only a short head behind in blanket finish.

Hampered on jumping before drifting back to race just worse than midfield after start. Moved away from rail near 600m, obtained clear running on straightening before closing well to be narrowly beaten on line.

Raced in midfield away from rail, 4.5L from lead passing the 800m. Shuffled further back but closer to lead as pace slowed in third section. Raced tight between runners in straight before closing well to be narrowly beaten.

Drifted back to race in midfield after start, but left wide & without cover from the 1000m. Improved position at half-way as pace slowed, before cornered 3L from lead. Made strong headway in straight to be beaten only a neck.

Didn't begin fast but mustered speed to race on leaders back. Continued to track leader on cornering before having difficulty obtaining clear running entire length of straight. Beaten under 2L but had obvious excuse.

Began moderately before shifting to rail & settling worse than midfield. Raced keenly & checked away from heels near 750m. Moved away from rail on turn, 4L from lead, before getting no clear run & not being tested in straight.

Shifted behind runners after start & raced a clear last along rail. Checked away from heels near 750m. Continued at rear on cornering, over 5L from lead before passing a few when making some ground to midfield in late stages.
Obtained good position in midfield away from rail throughout. Eased wider approaching corner, raced tight near the 300m before failing to improve & finishing in second half. Failed to challenge.

Shifted behind runners after start & raced second last, wide but with cover. Forced very wide when pace slowed near 750m. Cornered the widest runner, just over 3L from lead but failed to improve in straight & was no threat.
Raced in midfield along the rail throughout. Entered last section just over 3L from lead before failing to improve position & weakened out to beat only two runners home.
Raced just worse than midfield between runners in early & middle stages. Awkwardly placed behind heels at the 750m before shifting wider nearing corner. Made no headway in straight & was second last.

Began awkwardly & then had no speed, consequently racing near the tail throughout. Shifted away from heels passing the 750m before cornering very wide. Weakened further in straight to be last. (Blood in trachea post-race).
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out 600M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front near 100M, kept on strongly to the line, good debut win.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently on the outside, challenged the leader turning in, took the lead 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 100M, stayed on for 2nd.
Began well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off well to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, steadied off heels near 850M, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly. (Lost left hind plate.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Bumped start and unbalanced, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, no cover throughout, hard ridden after turning in, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, 6 lengths or so back, closer on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Began fairly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final 150M.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 700M, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle in the middle stages, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began well, showed no early speed, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Shifted in abruptly at start and bumped, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed no response early in straight, eased after passing 300M.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest on Straightening, made ground noticeably and scored by 1-3/4L.
At rear, wide but with cover, made ground and closed off strongly to the line.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail after 800M, kept going until weakened inside final 50M.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground steadily to the line.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground in the Straight only.
Sent forward and raced behind the leader, along the rail, flattened in the last 100M.
Sent forward, 2 wide, stayed on but headed in the last 150M.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, show some dash in the Straight but flattened in the last 100M.
Raced in midfield, wide no cover after 900M, weakened in the last 150M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, only one paced. (Roarer)
Slow to begin and at rear, along the rail, did not feature.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, showed no turn on foot.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. Finished tailed out, must trial (Lame left front)
Settled just over 2L off the pace, quickened well under pressure 200 metres out to assert authority over 50 metres out.
Soon took up running from a low draw and crossed the track for the stands rails, led the field until finding no extra over 50 metres out, hung on for 2nd
Settled just over 2L off the pace without cover near the centre of track, came to challenge under pressure 300 metres out but unable to sustain effort closing stages.
Missed the break, recovered steadily towards rear of midfield about 4L off the speed, commenced run inside the final 300 metres, fought on well.
Never far off, fought on steadily without threatening.
Moderate start after leaning on the gate, commenced move coming onto course proper but tightened over 200 metres out, sustained progress in closing stages to do best work late.
Moderate start, travelled not far off the pace, kept on same pace without quickening inside the final 300 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Broke well from the stands side gate settling just off the pace in 4th some 2L back, faded steadily inside the final 400 metres.
Soon dropped to last few travelling near the centre of the track, came under pressure coming onto course proper, made up some late ground.
Settled in midfield some 4L off the pace, kept on at the one pace to finish. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon dropped well behind, produced good late impression in the final 50 metres.
Soon improved to about 1L off the pace near the centre of the track, weakened under pressure from over 300 metres out.
Niggled along in midfield after crowding at the start, dropped towards the rear from over half-way out.
Broke well, settled in forward of midfield near stands rails, gave ground steadily from approaching course proper.
Began only fairly, settled towards the rear 5Ls back, into clear 400M, responded strongly to lead 150M, kept on final stages.
Chased leaders 2-wide, moved up well when asked early straight, not pace of winner final 200M but fought on under top weight to secure 2nd.
Dropped back to race in the rear, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, moved out to challenge 400M, finished off strongly, just missed 2nd.
Crossed to the lead 1100M, slowed down the pace middle stages, driven out 350M, headed 150M, faded towards the line.
Reserved at the rear, saved ground on inside, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
Settled down midfield along the 2-path, ran on steadily from 400M without threatening first 3.
Raced along the fence in a position behind midfield, responded mildly from 400M, not reached top 3.
Retrained after the start, settled down 3-wide at the back, widest into straight, ran on moderately, flattened final 100M.
Tracked leaders along the fence, ran on at same pace from 400M, out of contention 150M.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners early stages, 3-wide no cover behind mid-division from 1000M, closed off only fairly on straightening, never a threat.
Held up midfield, lacked a finishing response on straightening, soon gave way.
Made a lot of use in early stages to clear runners to his inside, settled outside the leader, came under pressure 750M, gave ground noticeably early straight.

Jumped well, showed good speed to take the early lead, headed 950M, allowed rival to cross 750M, sat right behind the leader on turn, hit the front 250M, kept on strongly to hold off the challengers late.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, moved a bit closer after passing 900M, raced 2 wide in 2nd on turn, kept on well in straight to take a place, always held.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight, not clear closed home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off well without threatening.
Taken back from gate 7, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, found rail near 750M, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened gradually final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened and eased final 100M.
Average to begin, positioned behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 2 wide, 2 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the outside, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths back, no cover throughout, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 150M, no extra thereafter.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned right behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, taken back to race behind midfield on the outside, 5 lengths back on turn, weakened early in straight.

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, challenged from 400M, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Crowded start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Moderately away, raced prominently on the outside, challenged the leader from 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 150M, weakened close home.
Began well, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 700M, hard ridden turning in, kept on evenly in straight.
Stumbled badly at start, raced behind midfield on the outside, hard ridden after passing 500M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out 400M, one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made little progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 750M, angled out 400M, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Began well from gate 10, raced 3 wide in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, showed no early speed, raced at tail throughout, never a factor.
Just behind midfield along the fence, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, made steady ground 300M.
Bumped start, hard ridden to keep up with the field, 3 wide, progressed steadily 400M.
Hard ridden early, 3 wide in front of midfield, held ground in straight.
Pushed early, at back, 2-3 wide, checked 400M, made steady ground 250M.
Checked at start and lost ground, at rear, worked around the field in 4 wide, made ground 400M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, out of fuel 200M.
At rear, took rail, ran on ok.
Eased back, took rail, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, emptied 350M.
Never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, faded rapidly 500M.
In front of midfield, dropped off 500M.
Never better than midfield.
Travelled keenly in the early stages, settled in box seat, improved near 300M and responded strongly, finished unchallenged.
Took lead with nice early speed, asked for effort near 400M, worked home nicely.
Settled behind midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, gained some late ground.
Ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled midfield, commenced to improve passing 600M, fought hard in the straight but only one-paced.
Settled in front of midfield, placed pressure near 600M, worked home one-paced.
Ridden some distance to obtain forward position, raced outside the lead, tried to improve passing 700M, gave some ground passing 100M.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, wide on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, settled towards rear, came under pressure passing 700M, gave ground near 200M.
Settled midfield on rail, in the straight lay in and proved difficult to ride, faded out passing 200M.
Raced at rear, placed pressure passing 700M, wide rounding the Home Turn, finished tailed-out, must trial.
Showed early speed to lead before crossing to rail in lead near 900m. Raced clear on cornering before dashing away in straight to win by big margin.

Didn't begin fast but improved after first furlong to race in midfield, three wide with cover. Eased wider on cornering when around 6L from lead before making good late headway to move to second in final 50m.

Ridden forward from outside barrier before improving to race 3 wide outside the leader from near the 800m. Improved within a neck of the lead near the 500m before being dropped by winner in straight. Held third but 5L behind.
Raced in midfield on rail before improving near the 600m to race on leaders back. Dropped off the leader on cornering before battling away to hold distant 4th on line.

Showed some speed to race prominently early before being crossed & racing in midfield. Niggled along from the 500m, entered last section 4L from lead before emptying out at the 250m & weakening thereafter.

Raced prominently after start, holding second place between runners before getting 1,1 from half-way. Entered last section only 2.5L from lead but peaked soon after cornering & weakened to midfield to be 7.5L behind on line.
Raced in midfield between runners after start before drifting slightly further when laying in near half-way. Entered last section 4.5L from lead before weakening in straight to be well beaten.

Raced in second half after the start before becoming unbalanced & being relegated back to last passing the 800m. Continued a long way from lead entering last section & despite passing a few was never likely from rear.
Had no early speed & raced at rear soon after start. Moved slightly along the rail passing half-way before offering nothing in the straight & weakening to be beaten nearly 10L.

Slow to begin, consequently raced at rear early before settling second last. Raced greenly & continued wide without cover when awkward around bend. Cornered extremely wide & cost itself all chance. Long way behind.

Limited early speed & raced worse than midfield on rail early. Improved slightly along the rail to race under 4L from lead at the 800m. Offered nothing in the straight & weakened out to long second last.

Fractious in barriers, awkwardly placed & lost position after first 100m, consequently racing worse than midfield. Began yielding further ground from the 700m, soon last before tailing. (Irregular heart rhythm post-race).
Away with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back, there to turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Began very awkwardly and bumped, raced towards rear on the outside, 7 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place, nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, challenged the leader after turning in, took brief lead after passing 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first few late.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out after passing 400M, made some progress early in straight, no extra final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 550M, peaked and headed near 300M, kept on evenly to 50M, weakened thereafter.
Began smartly from a wide draw, raced prominently but 3 wide, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Inconvenienced at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, 9 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, peaked on turn, weakened final 200M.
Settled in midfield, along the rail, made ground and closed off strongly to the line.
Raced in behind the leader, along the rail, stayed on but only headed in the last 50M.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, continued on well for 3rd.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, swung wide on straightening and ran on strongly.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made minor ground only in the Straight.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, only one paced.
At rear, along the rail, did not improve in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, one paced only
At rear, 2 wide, did not feature in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, not competitive.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Travelled mainly 3-wide slightly worse than midfield, came under pressure turning in, quickened well inside the final 200 metres to snatch victory near the line.

Taken back just off the pace 3-wide in 5th from a wide gate, edged slightly closer making home turn, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out, looked a winner but only to be collared final strides.
Shared early pace, taken one back one out after the first quarter, did not find much room in similar position after turning in, made up some late ground inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden forward from a wide gate to take up running, obtained rails run approaching home bend holding narrow advantage into the straight, swamped under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Broke well before settling in rear of midfield on the rail, shaken up entering home straight, switched out for a run 200 metres out but made no impression. (Lame next day)
Travelled wide without cover in midfield after beginning from a wide gate, commenced move rounding home bend coming within 2L of pace turning in, faded under pressure inside the final 200 metres.
Ridden positively from the widest gate to share early pace, restrained outside the leader rounding home bend, came under pressure to hold place turning in, weakened inside the final 200 metres.
Slowly away from a wide draw, improved from last to 10th along the rail coming onto home bend, in similar position turning into straight, made up some late ground.
Soon dropped to the rear despite niggling along, became last coming onto home bend, ran on quite well past well-beaten horses down the centre of the straight.
Travelling in just worse than midfield when badly blundered and lost considerable ground at the 900 metres, kept on steadily without making any impression in home straight.
Began well, settled just off the pace on the rail, chased the leader into home straight, dropped out under pressure.
Travelled just worse than midfield after a moderate start, given reminders rounding home bend, found nothing.
Quickly into stride, had uncontested lead, kicked on well passing 400M, opened up big lead mid-straight, galloped on strongly for dominant win.
Began awkwardly, held up midfield, ran on to take 2nd 200M, no threat to the runaway winner.
From wide draw got into a 2-wide position in midfield, went wide 600M, kept on evenly over final 400M, no chance with the runaway winner.
In 4th place always in touch, pushed along 600M, battled on at same pace to the finish.
Held up behind midfield 5Ls off the slow pace, responded fairly on straightening, made limited progress only.
Jumped well, tracked leader in a slowly run race, pushed out 400M, lost 2nd mid-straight, battled on to line, faded towards the line.
Chased leaders in a slowly run race, battled on same pace early straight, weakened 200M.
Dropped back to race towards the rear of the field, moved closer to be 5Ls off the pace 400M, ran home same paced. Never threatened.
Reserved near the rear, wide no cover from 1100M, wide into straight, responded fairly, never reached leaders.
Settled behind midfield, bustled along 500M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Settled towards the rear 8Ls away, never involved. (Lame RF leg.)
Dropped back to last, came under pressure 600M and didn't respond to riding, never in the picture.

Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 600M, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, took the lead 400M, kept on very well after turning in, just couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, 3 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear, hard ridden after passing 400M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Away well, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run in the middle stages, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Crowded start, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at tail, 8 to 9 lengths back, closer on turn, made no progress in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped on jumping, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length, peaked and headed 400M, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Eased back, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 350M to score.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 600M.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, held ground in straight.
Eased back, on the fence, lack room 300M, made ground when clear.
Hard ridden early, at back, progressed steadily 200M.
Eased at start, took rail, lack room 4-2, made steady ground.
Eased back, trapped 2-4 wide, made ground 200M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield along the fence, bumped 250M, weakened.
Took rail and lead, emptied 200M.
Eased back, 2 wide, held up and checked 250M, no progress.
Raced midfield, asked for effort near 400M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Raced at tail, badly held up from 350M to 75M, made up some nice late ground, missed by Head.
Began only fairly, settled behind midfield on rail, wide on straightening, gained some nice ground in the straight.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, asked for effort on straightening, finished well.
Travelled in box seat, improved passing 400M, responded well in the straight.
Jumped well, ridden along but failed to muster speed, wide and without cover outside leaders throughout, responded nicely in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Taken back at start, always niggled throughout, made some ground in the straight.
Jumped nicely, settled outside the lead, placed pressure near 500M, limited response in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on rail, commenced to improve passing 400M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, passing 800M was checked when travelling keenly, near 150M was crowded for room, failed to make impression.
Hard ridden along to take lead, came under pressure near 400M, weakened passing 200M.
Raced in the clear in midfield throughout early & middle stages. Moved wider on cornering before finishing strongly to dash to lead at the 50m & ran through line strongly to win.
Raced prominently before being caught 3 wide without cover, around a length from the lead after first section. Continued wide around bend before finishing well to move to second in final few strides.

Showed speed, led early before being joined & sharing lead near 700m. Continued on to re-assume lead passing 600m. Raced over a length clear on cornering, continued to hold lead until being joined at the 50m. Held third.
Shifted back to race second last away from rail. Moved the widest runner on cornering when near 5L from lead, before finishing strongly in late stage to be beaten only a length on line.

Had limited speed after start & was niggled along to maintain position at the rear of field. Continued a clear last entering last section when 7.5L from lead before making good late from hopeless position. Needs further.
Enjoyed nice run 1,1 early before being left without cover from the 450m. Continued just over a length form lead at the furlong before weakening a few lengths in late stages.
Improved after start to race on leaders back after first furlong before being shuffled a pair further back near half-way. Failed to improve in straight & was no threat.
Raced second on rail before improving to share lead near 700m. Was then re-headed & raced on leaders back from the 500m. Peaked at furlong & weakened out thereafter. (Rider questioned).
Steadied after start & shifted back to race third last on rail. Entered last section 5L from lead along rail, crowded & lost ground near 150m but probably wasn't a threat at that point. Last.

Moderately away, raced towards rear on the outside, moved closer on the 1st turn, positioned 3W in midfield after entering the back straight, commenced move 700M, took the lead 450M, kept on well in straight to hold off the rivals.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.

Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, closed off well without threatening.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out 400M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, allowed rival to cross near 950M, angled out 450M, showed limited response early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide behind midfield, carried wider after passing 700M, no cover thereafter, one-paced in the run home.

Began well from gate 12, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, 2 wide from 950M, challenged the leader 500M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened final 100M. (Intermittent displacement of the soft palate.)
Out with rest, raced 3 wide at rear, very wide turning in, finished off one pace.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, 3 wide from 700M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 100M.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, peaked and headed 500M, weakened early in straight.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide after 500M, made ground and closed off strongly to the line.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, had difficulty to obtain a run at 200M and closed of well to the line.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, continued on well but headed in the last 100M.
Raced next to the leader, ran on well to the line for 4th.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, made some ground only in the Straight.
Taken back, 2 wide, made minor ground only.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail after 600M, only one paced.
At rear, along the rail, swung wide and lay in on Straightening, made minor ground late.
At rear, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, did not feature in the Straight.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, lost ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, wide no cover, never a factor. (Roarer)
Settled in forward of midfield in 7th on the rail, saved ground turning in, responded well to hit the front passing the 100 metres, held on to the line.
Settled in rear and waited with, commenced move out wide rounding home bend, swung widest into straight, finished off the race well but never threatening.
Taken back just behind midfield for cover, commenced move out wide on top of home bend racing wide into straight, ran on until finding no extra near the line.
Attempted to make all, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Jumped fairly, pressed forward to join the leader, settled just off the pace in 2nd turning into back straight, came to challenge entering home straight but ran home one-paced.
Settled 3-wide in midfield after beginning from the middle gate, gained slightly closer to 6th about 3L off on the far side but remained 3-wide without cover, made no impression in home straight.
Broke well settling just off the pace in 4th on the rail, came under pressure to hold position rounding home bend, one-paced under pressure in the run to the line.
Began well from a middle draw settling just off the pace 2-wide in 5th, remained similar turning in and switched out to challenge upon straightening, found nothing.

Race prominently and wide without cover early stages after beginning from the widest gate, improved steadily to 3rd without cover entering back straight, weakened under pressure shortly after straightening.
Settled in rear of midfield, kept on steadily without quickening in home straight.
Ridden but slow to muster early, remained in last few to home straight, saved ground turning in, one-paced (Blood in trachea)
Always well behind and never seen with a chance.
From draw 1 led as expected, set even pace, responded well to pressure from 300M, held rivals at bay.
Sat outside leader in a race run at even tempo, driven 350M, drifted out under pressure in straight, always held by winner.
Chased leaders along the 2-path, tried hard on straightening but unable to reel in winner.
Away well enough, chased leaders on inside, battled on under pressure final 300M, held by leaders.
Began slowly, raced at the back until passing 600M,7Ls to make up 400M, finished off well, awkwardly placed close home and not ridden out.
Began awkwardly, bustled along to take up a position in midfield, made home turn awkwardly, closed off fairly final 300M.
Rushed forward from draw 12, caught wide no cover outside leaders, no extra to challenge on straightening.
Badly crowded for room at start, settled towards the rear 5Ls back, ran on only fairly final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Jumped fairly, caught in a 3-wide spot towards the rear, lacked response when asked, made no real progress in the straight.
Badly crowded for room at start, raced behind midfield, over 5Ls to make up 400M, couldn't go on.
Jumped well but soon outpaced and fell back to the rear passing 600M, already beaten turning for home. Poor debut effort.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, same position on turn, finished off very strongly to score by a neck.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off well to take 2nd.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, commenced move after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide better than midfield early, moved closer after entering the back straight, 2 wide from 800M, 2nd on turn, kept on well early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Began smartly, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 800M, a length back on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, very wide into straight, closed off well without threatening.
Moderately away from the widest draw, showed no early speed, raced behind midfield on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some headway in the run home.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, made little progress thereafter.

Average to begin, trapped very wide in midfield early, sent forward after entering the back straight, raced 3 wide, a length back in the middle stages, no cover throughout, kept on evenly to 100M, no extra thereafter.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, weakened early in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin.

Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide at rear, checked off heels near 550M, wider turning in, finished off strongly to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run after passing 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear on the inside, 4 lengths or so back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, led by half-length on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, wider from 450M, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact at start, raced very wide towards rear, no cover throughout, hung out on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 11, raced prominently but trapped very wide, no cover throughout, a length back on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, half-length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Clean jump, raced 3 wide better than midfield, 2 wide from 550M, 1-1/2L back on turn, finished off strongly to score by a nose.

Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, easy run on turn, showed very good response after turning in, took the lead 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner on line.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, awkwardly placed near 550M, 2 wide on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to make frame.
Hampered at start, raced towards rear on the inside, slightly improved after passing 500M, 2 wide on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at tail, 7 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.

Began smartly from the widest draw, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide after passing 600M, shared lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, found rail after passing 600M, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover on turn, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 550M, weakened early in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the pace, 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to secure box seat, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased at start, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 600M, run ended 100M.
Eased at start, 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 400M.
Hard ridden early, midfield on the fence, made steady ground 300M.
Slow away, at rear along the fence, lack room 300M, made ground when clear.
At back, trapped 3 wide throughout, moved forward 600M, emptied 200M.
At back, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, emptied 300M.
Never better than midfield.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, faded 500M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, dropped off quickly 600M.
On jumping was bumped and rider lost his left stirrup iron, took box seat with nice early speed, lay in in the early part of straight, quickened passing 150M, scored by 2-1/2L.
Began awkwardly, then ridden along but failed to muster speed, settled midfield on rail, responded nicely in the straight, blood in trachea.
Travelled behind midfield, improved near 400M, gained nice ground passing 100M.
Began only fairly and lost ground, raced behind midfield on rail, asked for effort passing 400M, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, wide on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure in the straight but finished one-paced.
Taken back at start, raced at tail, commenced to improve in the straight, worked home one-paced.
At start was crowded then taken back, wide on straightening, one-paced in the straight.
Hard ridden along to take lead passing 1000M, led by 3L, weakened near 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, travelled keenly in middle stages, placed pressure but gave ground near 150M.
Taken back at start, came under pressure near 700M, no response in the straight.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover in midfield, passing 700M was taken wider, faded out in the straight.

Began fast before being steadied & getting good position two pairs back on rail for majority. Improved to third on rail entering last section before making continual ground last furlong to snatch narrow lead in late stages.

Steadied from outside gate & shifted behind runners to race midfield on rail. Travelled well entering last section, stayed on inside on cornering before making strong late ground to charge to narrowly beaten second on line.

Raced wide leaving straight first time before crossing to rail when leading near the 1200m. Raced 2L clear approaching corner, continued to hold over 3L margin at 200m before tiring in late stages & being over-run late.

Shifted behind runners & raced third last. Moved wider near the 500m, continued near the tail when a long way from lead on cornering before making strong late ground down the outside to be beaten less than two lengths.

Had a good position 1,1 for majority. Moved three wide around a tiring runner near the 500m, entered last section just under 4L from lead before finishing off steadily in straight to be beaten less than two lengths.
Raced in midfield away from rail throughout. Came under hard riding when pace quickened near the 450m, cornered just over 5L from lead before finishing off one paced in straight to be 3.5L behind.

Strode to prominent position after start before racing just behind easy leader away from rail. Niggled along from the 600m before beginning to lose ground from the 500m before weakening a further few lengths in straight.
Raced close to lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back form the 1200m. Continued in second but nearly 2L behind leader who raced clear on cornering before weakening out in final 250m.

Got head down prior to the start & consequently lost significant ground before joining onto back of the field after 300m. Continued last, 9L from lead entering last section before playing no part late. Had excuse at start.

Raced just worse than midfield away from rail for majority. Niggled along passing the 600m, entered last section 7L from lead before making no impression & weakening out to second last in straight. Well beaten.
Began slowly losing a length or two before racing second last on the rail. Continued reward approaching corner when over 7L from lead before weakening out meekly in straight to be last.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on very well in straight, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced towards rear on the inside, badly hampered near 550M, 10 lengths on turn, made some progress in straight.
Commenced well, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide, peaked on turn, ran on evenly early in straight, weakened final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced behind midfield on the outside, 9 to 10 lengths back on turn, showed some response in straight.
Crowded on jumping, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length behind the leader on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually thereafter. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, badly hampered near 550M, well back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear, badly hampered by the faller near 550M, well back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Slightly slow out, showed no speed, raced at tail throughout, hampered near 500M, soon tailed off. (Unacceptable performance.)

Placing: UR
Comment: Bumped start, raced in midfield on the inside, badly unbalanced and fell near 550M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, closed off strongly and scored by a head.
Settled in one-out one-back, battled on to the line to take 2nd.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, stayed on but headed in the last 150M.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, raced tight passing 300M, saved some ground and ran on for 4th.
Taken back, along the rail, raced tight passing 300M, made ground and ran on well to the line.
Taken back, 3 wide but with cover, saved ground and ran on fairly.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, pretty one paced.
Midfield, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide, got its head up around 1000M, one paced only. (See Incident Report)
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve in the Straight.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, lost ground after 400M.
Sent forward, 2 wide, flattened after 250M and lost ground in the Straight.
Moderate start, settled just better than midfield in 5th on the rail over 4L off the speed, saved ground entering straight, hit the front under pressure over 100 metres out.

Jumped fairly from the one draw settling some 3L back in 3rd behind the leading pair, switched 3-wide for a run entering straight, quickened under pressure to hold every chance over 150 metres out but outsprinted late.
Travelled wide without cover in midfield in 6th over 5L off the speed, commenced move approaching home turn and ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Ridden positively from a wide gate to soon take up running on the rail at the 1000 metres, had no more to give and swamped just inside the final 100 metres.
Inconvenienced at start, settled in last few some 7L off the pace, made significant progress in straight with an impressive late run despite hanging under pressure.
Ridden in the front briefly before drifting back to just better than midfield in 5th some 3L off the speed, renewed pressure after straightening, kept on same pace without quickening.
Soon dropped to worse than midfield in 8th despite ridden early, inconvenienced at the 750 metres, made up some late ground down the centre of the track, never nearer.
Moderate start, settled in midfield, snuck up on rails rounding home turn, unable to quicken under pressure.

Pressed forward after moderate start from the widest gate settling just outside the leader turning into back straight, remained same to home turn but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.
Began awkwardly losing ground, trailed the field to the 500 metres, kept on same pace in straight.
Sluggish at start, always in rear on the rail, inconvenienced approaching home bend and was last into straight, made good late impression closing stages.
Inconvenienced at start, taken back from a wide gate and remained wide in last few without cover while travelling keenly at times in back straight, found nothing in home straight. (Lame next day)
Settled down midfield, travelled strongly into straight, quickened up swiftly when clear 250M, soon opened up sizable lead, won easily.
Held up in mid-division, ran on steadily over final 300M, got up for 2nd in blanket finish for minor placings.
Chased leaders 2-wide, not pace to challenge winner final 250M but fought on to hold 3rd in a blanket finish for minor placings.
Tracked pace along the fence, not pace of winner passing 300M, kept on evenly to line, just missed a place in photo finish.
Steadied early stages to find cover, held up behind midfield 3-wide, swung widest home, ran on steadily to line, just missed a place but no threat to runaway winner.
Began only fairly, settled down towards the rear, ran on evenly from 300M down the inside, restricted room 150M, lost out in a photo finish for 2nd to 6th placing.
Driven forward from wide draw, led to near 250M, battled on one paced to line.
Sent forward to race outside leader from wide draw, hung in during race, jockey unable to property test the horse in the straight, lost several places close home.
In midfield early stages, shuffled back to near the rear home turn, ran on same pace in straight, never threatened.
Reserved at the rear, not quickened final 300M, no impression.
Began only fairly, held up near the rear 6Ls off the pace, never near to challenge.
Vigorously ridden after the start but unable to cross, caught wide no cover throughout the race, weakened badly turning home.
