Average to begin, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, a bit closer in the middle stages, angled out after passing 500M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked and headed near 150M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Away well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, easy run to turn, angled out 500M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground to turn, angled out 450M, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, angled out 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, 3 to 4 lengths back, very wide turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, closer on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back, similar position on turn, showed nothing in straight. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped start, eased back, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Took lead, hung on well until 100M overhauled.
Prominent, held ground for 3rd.
Midfield, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield, bumped early, dashed well 200M.
Bumped start, at back, made steady ground 250M.
Eased to rear, made ground 300M.
Pushed forward, emptied 200M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, no dash.
Eased to rear, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, on heels 250M, weakened.
Eased back, never improved.
Hard ridden forward, weakened 300M.
Raced towards rear, placed pressure near 450M, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score
Settled midfield on rail, asked for effort near 400M, responded solidly in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, improved near 450M, worked home nicely.
Settled midfield, asked for effort near 450M, responded nicely in the straight.
Settled in handy position, commenced to improve near 500M, fought hard but only one-paced.
Ridden along but no early speed, raced behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, finished one-paced.
Ridden along for some distance to race outside the lead, travelled keenly in middle stages, came under pressure passing 300M and lay in, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced at back, tried to improve passing 500M, one-paced in the straight.
Raced at rear on rail, placed pressure but no response in the straight.
Urged along to take lead, placed pressure passing 450M, weakened passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, passing 850M was left racing wide and without cover, weakened in the straight.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, widest on straightening, never in it.
Began well, held lead momentarily before being crossed & racing on leaders back. Moved away from rail passing the 800m. Dashed to the lead at the 250m before drawing away for easy win.

Began only fairly before improving after the start to race in midfield. Moved away from rail on cornering when 3.5L from lead, held up from 400m to 300m before shifting wider & closing strongly to snare second in late stages.

Began awkwardly & stumbled before being caught 3 wide without cover in midfield throughout. Continued wide around bend, cornered the widest runner to make good late ground before being caught for second on line.

Began awkwardly & bumped before shifting behind runners to race near the tail. Staye3d close to the rail on cornering when over 4L from lead before making steady late ground between runners to close to 4th on line.

Showed good early speed before steadying & racing midfield away from rail. Eased 3 wide nearing the 600m, entered last section only 2L from lead before finishing off evenly in last section. Not beaten far.

Bumped at start before being shifted back from outside gate to race at tail. Continued last, nearly 10L from lead passing the 800m. Shifted out at 350m before making good ground between runners in late stages, only 3L behind.

Showed speed after the start to stride to lead after 100m before crossing to rail near the 900m. Continued in lead until being joined by winner near the 250m before weakening a few lengths in last furlong.

Had no speed after the start & raced worse than midfield between runners. Continued in second half, entered last section 5L from lead, continued to make steady ground, held up near 200m before finishing ok under quite riding.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Shifted wider entering last section when around 4L from lead before holding margin in dash to line.
Steadied after start & shifted back to race worse than midfield when 3 wide with cover. Continued wide around bend when 7L from lead. Made no real headway in straight & was never a threat.

Strode forward after start before improving position after first section to race second, 1L behind leader after the 900m. Peaked on run passing the 300m before weakening out in last 250m to be well beaten. (See report).
Raced in midfield on rail in early stages. Moved away from rail passing the 600m, entered last section only 2.5L from lead before emptying out at the 300m & weakening thereafter. Well beaten.

Steadied after the start & shifted back to race third last away from rail. Relegated to second last after 350m. Moved wider with cover passing 800m, cornered wide before making no headway in last section & was second last.

Improved after start to race second after 100m. Inconvenienced near the 1000m when crossed by leader before racing on leaders back thereafter. Entered last section 2L from lead before weakening badly to last.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, kept on strongly to the line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide slightly behind midfield, 2 wide from 800M, moved a bit closer on turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, found rail near 800M, angled out after passing 500M, no daylight early in straight, then hampered near 150M, ran on well to take a place.
Taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 700M, very wide turning in, made very good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 3 to 4 lengths turning in, unable to obtain clear running until final 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, positioned on rail behind midfield, angled out after passing 500M, finished off evenly.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail better than midfield, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths back turning in, showed some response early in straight, blocked near 100M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, raced prominently on the inside, inconvenienced near 850M, crossed by rival 750M, 2 wide turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M. (Lame right front leg.)
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross 900M, challenged the leader turning in, peaked on run 300M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 13, raced behind midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide in midfield, 2 wide from 850M, commenced move after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Away with them, sent forward to race prominently but very wide, took the lead 1000M, found rail near 750M, challenged by rivals turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
At rear, along the rail, swung widest on Straightening, made significant ground to score by a neck.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, stayed on and only caught by the leader in the last 30M.
At rear, along the rail, saved ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide no cover, made some ground and ran on fairly for 4th.
Raced in midfield, wide no cover, made minor ground only.
At rear, 2 wide after 1200M, flattened in the last 150M.
Sent forward and raced behind the leader, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Bumped start and raced in midfield, 2 wide and checked at 1100M, only one paced in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide, one paced only.
Raced in worse than midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not improve in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, one paced in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, no clear run from 300M to 200M, did not feature.
Settled in one-out one-back, lost ground in the Straight. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, lost ground after 200M.

Held narrow lead 3-wide in early stages, obtained rails run approaching the first turn, maintained 1L advantage rounding home bend at a comfortable pace, kicked over 1L clear after straightening and kept on well to the line.
Settled about 4L back in 7th on the rail after a moderate start, not much room between runners early in straight, responded well inside the 300 metres and did best work late.
Began well from a wide gate settling over 2L back 2-wide in 4th, fought on steadily under pressure inside the final 300 metres without threatening.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled keenly at the rear of the field to straight, made up good ground under pressure near the centre of track.
Broke well, shifted back for 3rd just off the pace, became 2nd in similar position coming onto home bend, kept on under pressure but swamped close to home.
Soon taken back for rails run from the widest gate, trailed the field to home straight, went past beaten horses along the rail without making any serious impression.
Moderate start, settled just worse than midfield in 6th over 3L off the pace, travelled keenly at times rounding home bend, failed to quicken to challenge.
Began fairly sharing early pace on the rail, refused to settle when taken back when leader came across, faded steadily inside the final 200 metres.
Niggled along in midfield 5th, weakened steadily after straightening.
Settled towards the rear, made good progress from 400M, got up to beat the odds on favorite close home.
Always prominent, driven out 400M and vied for lead with rival, established narrow lead 100M out, caught by fast finishing winner late.
Up with leaders down the center of track, driven 400M and vied for lead until no extra 100M.
Chased leaders, fought on evenly to claim modest 4th
Always prominent, tried hard final 300M, in contention until 100M, faded late.
Held up midfield, 3-4L to make up on leaders passing 400M, kept on without threat.
Lost ground at the start, soon in last detached, made limited progress final 400M, never reached leaders.
Settled midfield, kept on same pace final 400M, no threat to leaders
Ridden along early stages to take up a forward position, came under pressure prior to 500M, soon weakened . (Jockey : didn't travel well at any stage / Blood in trachea.)
Chased leaders in midfield, ran on same pace to line, never dangerous.
Raced in mid-pack towards the outside of group, weak in the finish, dropped away final 200M. (Bled 3rd time)
Towards the rear, failed to respond over final 400M. Made no impression on debut.
Raced along the stand's rail, under pressure halfway, soon struggled, eased final 200M.
Began smartly from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challengers.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Began well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with no cover, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to make frame, always held.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide towards rear, wider on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide in midfield early, found rail near 1000M, angled out 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Out in line, raced 3 wide in midfield early, 2 wide from 1000M, commenced move 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, kept on evenly to the line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear, 9 lengths or so back, still well back on turn, made some progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, same position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide behind midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back, saved ground on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Inconvenienced at start, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, took the lead 1000M, travelled comfortably on turn, kept on very well in straight to hold off the challenger late.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned right behind the leader on rail, there to turn, finished off well to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, finished off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Began awkwardly, raced in midfield on the outside, there to turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Began well, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear running early in straight, made little progress thereafter.
Away well, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, a length behind the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide and without cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 8 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, made minor progress in the run home.
Crowded on jumping, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 4 wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Slowly away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.

Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, ran on well to hold off the challenger late. (Bled.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well to take a place.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Slightly slow out, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited early in straight, blocked near 250M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently but 3 wide, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight when hard run took effect.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 9 lengths back, same margin back on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, never competitive.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, dominated from 600M, overhauled 100M.
At back, 2-3 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M
Eased back, sat 2 wide, made early move 800M into the lead, ran on until 200M emptied.
Eased to sit behind the leaders, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, checked and hampered during early and middle stages on 3 occasions, not properly tested.
Eased at start, 2 wide, little dash 200M.
Slow away, at back on the fence, held up and carried back further 6-4, dashed well 200M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Box seat, weakened 600M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, dropped off quickly 600M.
Niggled to race in box seat, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 100M, scored by 2L.
Settled in front of midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, fought well in the straight.
Settled midfield, placed pressure passing 500M, made some nice late ground.
Wide and without cover in handy position until passing 600M, asked for effort near 400M, responded well in the straight.
Taken back at start, settled midfield, 3 wide with cover, worked home nicely.
Raced outside the lead, travelled keenly in early stages, limited response in the straight.
Slow to begin, raced behind midfield on rail, held up for clear running from approaching 200M until passing 150M, finished one-paced.
Began awkwardly, settled midfield on rail, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Ridden along to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, gave ground passing 150M.
Slow to begin, raced at rear, widest on straightening, limited response in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, passing 600M was left racing wide and without cover, wide on straightening, weakened passing 150M.
Taken back at start, raced detached in early and middle stages, weakened in the straight.

Raced behind leading trio leaving straight before steadying near 1000m & racing just worse than midfield. Moved 4 wide passing 450m, cornered second widest, dashed to second near 200m before kicking back in final 50m to win.

Checked when crowded after start & consequently racing second from last. Moved wider & improved quickly passing the 450m, cornered very wide, sprinted quickly to assume lead at 200m before being headed by winner in last 50m.

Steadied after start before shifting to rail when racing near the rear. Moved away from rail entering last section when 4.5L from lead, held up on cornering before finishing strongly to move to third at 100m. Clear of 4th.

Raced wide in midfield leading the straight first time before shifting in to get nice run 1,1 from the 1000m. Hard ridden near the 600m, moved wider approaching corner before fighting on ok in straight.

Shared early lead before being headed near the 1200m & racing on leaders back from 1000m. Moved over the heels of leader on cornering, dashed to get within half-length of lead at 200m before weakening thereafter.

Ridden forward and raced prominently before continuing on to take lead passing the 1200m. Continued to hold narrow lead until being joined & passed nearing the 200m before giving a few lengths thereafter.

Had no speed after the start & shifted behind runners to race at the tail. Continued at the rear, 5.5L from lead entering last section, shifted wider on straightening but only held margin in dash to line. Well beaten.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout early & middle stages. Continued along inside on cornering when 3L from lead before offering little in last 250m & weakening to be beaten nearly 6L.

Steadied passing winning post first time before drifting back to race worse than midfield. Momentarily racing 3 wide near the 900m before being relegated to share last place near 400m. Failed to make any headway in straight
Shared lead approaching the 1200m before racing second, away from rail, 1L from lead near half-way. Hard ridden from the 600m mark before weakening significantly in last section to be very long last.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kicked clear early in straight, kept on very well to the line and scored.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced prominently on the inside, allowed rival to cross 600M, sat right behind the leader on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced in midfield on the outside, 4 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began only fairly, raced at rear on the inside, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield on the outside, laid out near 550M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced prominently but 3 wide, 2 wide from 600M, a length back on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from gate 8, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, closed off strongly and battled on to the line by 1/2L.
At rear, 2 wide after 550M, swung widest on Straightening, made significant ground and ran on gamely to the line for 2nd.
At rear, along the rail, made ground and closed off strongly for 3rd.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, ran on fairly only for 4th.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, closed off only fairly in the Straight.
Midfield, 2 wide, only one paced.
At rear, along the rail, saved some ground but run ended in the last 50M.
Raced in worse than midfield, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
Raced in worse than midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, in the Straight lost ground.
Sent forward and raced behind the leader, no extra passing 100M. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward and took lead, never a factor.
Settled in midfield in 7th some 5L off the pace, angled off the rail for a run entering home straight, quickened well inside the final 200 metres to snatch victory closing stages.

Began well settling one back in joint 4th 2-wide, became two back passing the 700 metres, went wide into straight and hit the front under pressure briefly over 150 metres out, drifting out when outsprinted close to home.
Jumped fairly, settled 2-back in joint 4th on the rail, switched in for a run upon straightening, ran on steadily under pressure near the rail but never threatening.
Settled in midfield in joint 6th 2-wide, commenced move rounding home bend and wide into straight, ran on steadily down the centre of the track without threatening.
Pressed forward from a wide gate, raced wide with the leaders before obtaining rails run in front 700 metres out, led until swamped under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Ridden along up with the leaders, settled for one back position 2-wide without cover over 600 metres out, raced alongside leader into straight when inconvenienced, ran home one-paced.
Shared pace on the rail early, quitted speed battle to settle one back 700 metres out, kept on in straight until fading inside final 100 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Inconvenienced at start, settled behind midfield in 8th, came under pressure 4-wide rounding home bend and went wider into straight, fought on steadily but without quickening.
Crowded at start, trailed the field to the 400 metres, saved ground on inside making home turn, kept on at the one pace.
Soon dropped to the rear, never seen with a chance.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped to last few, in similar position on the rail turning in, made no further impression in straight.
Broke well from the widest gate but failed to muster pace and dropped backward, travelling wide without cover throughout, never seen with a chance. (Blood in trachea)
Slow to begin, settled behind midfield 5-6Ls back, swung wide home, gave good response, vied for lead final 150M before gaining upper hand late.
Guided to a 2-wide spot in mid-division, moved closer to leaders from 600M, finished off well when switched to outside in straight, joined by winner from 150M, just denied.
From draw 1 settled down midfield, responded moderately when driven out in straight, not finishing pace of first 2 final 200M.
Taken across from wide draw, reserved in the rear in a fast run race, over 6Ls to make up 400M, closed off well and just missed 3rd.
Always prominent in a fast run race, challenged for lead early straight, flat final 150M.
Taken across from wide draw, held up towards the race in a fast run race, saved ground on inside, kept on steadily to the line, held by leaders.
Taken across from wide draw, settled down at the rear 8Ls off leader in a fast run race, ran past beaten horses in straight, no threat to leaders.
Steadied for cover early stages, held up towards the rear 7Ls off the good pace, stayed on fairly final 300M.
Took lead entering first turn, quickened up pace from 1200M, hard driven 400M, fought on until 150M, swamped by rivals.
Tracked leaders in 4th spot, lay in from 300M, stayed on fairly before hampered 100M and lost running.
Went forward tracking the leader who set a good pace from 1200M, swung to center of track on straightening, kept on same pace until weakened 200M.
Began only fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide from 500M, finished off strongly to score.
Began well, raced better than midfield, 2 lengths or so back, 3 wide turning in, finished off very well, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Away with them, raced 3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail, 9 lengths back, closer on turn but still 6 lengths behind, made some progress in straight.
Clean jump, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, saddle shifted rounding the home turn, not able to test properly in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kicked clear early in straight, ran on strongly to the line and scored.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Taken back from gate 8, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide on turn, not clear run near 400M, made good progress final 200M to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the outside, commenced move after passing 600M, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 6 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, passed some tired runners in straight.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, there to turn, angled out after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide in midfield early, 3 wide from 1000M, wider turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Commenced well, raced 3 wide in midfield, carried wider after passing 1000M, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced prominently but trapped 3 wide early, 2 wide after passing 1300M, peaked on turn, weakened final 300M.
Began well from gate 13, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover after passing 1300M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross after entering the back straight, peaked on turn, emptied early in straight, eased final 300M.
Took rail and lead easily, made all.
Pushed forward, ran on well for 2nd.
Pressed forward, took rail, held ground for 3rd.
Midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 350M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, blocked most straight, progressed steadily.
Eased at start, took cover, 3 wide, blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, lack room in straight, ran on ok.
At back, trapped 4 wide, ran on fairly.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, out of fuel 250M.
At back, never improved.
Midfield, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never competitive.
Never a factor.
Settled behind midfield, improved passing 400M, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged.
Niggled forward to take lead, asked for effort passing 400M, responded nicely in the straight, finished well.
Settled outside the lead with nice early speed, commenced to improve passing 450M, worked home nicely.
Raced midfield, placed pressure passing 500M, responded well in the straight.
Taken back, near 1400M was left racing wide and without cover, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Very slow to begin, raced at rear on rail, tried to improve passing 450M, finished one-paced, must stall test.
Raced at back, placed pressure on straightening, limited response in the straight.

No early speed before improving to midfield on rail after start. Cornered over 3L behind, held up at 300m, shifted inwards for clear running before making continual headway despite shifting ground to strike lead final stride.

Began awkwardly & was slow to begin before racing near tail. Shifted out when making ground near 300m, continued to make strong late ground before directed away from heels at 150m & then closing hard to be narrowly beaten.

Raced prominently before being crowded & losing ground after 200m & continuing in midfield between runners. Sprinted quickly to lead passing 300m, shifted out under pressure at 150m before being caught in final few strides.

Began only fairly before being shifted back to race at tail. Cornered widest before entering last section 4L from lead. Dashed well to move to second near the 150m before being less than a length behind on line.

Raced in midfield between runners. Crowded near the 1000m before drifting further soon after. Held up from the 350m before getting clear at 250m & closing strongly to be beaten less than 2L despite being hampered late.

Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Shifted away from rail on straightening, held up soon after, dashed well between runners 200m before closing strongly & finishing close behind despite racing in restricted room late.

Strode forward to race prominently after the start before being bumped at 1100m, shifted ground before ultimate settling 1,1 near the 850m. Improved to share lead momentarily near 300m before tiring a few lengths late.

Steadied after start & shifted back to third last. Hard ridden passing 700m & relegated to last. Clear last, 5L form lead entering last section before making some ground when running on to midfield finish. (Lame next-day).
Raced just worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Eased wider into clear running on straightening before making no real headway in straight.

Improved after the start to race in midfield before improving further to race on leaders back from the 800m. Continued a length form the lead before being checked near the 300m before playing no part thereafter.

Strode forward & raced second in early stages before being caught 3 wide without cover in midfield throughout. Entered last section just over a length form lead before emptying at the 250m & weakening out thereafter.
Caught 4 wide without cover in midfield throughout. Cornered wide, entered last section under 3L from lead before weakening significantly in last section after wide passage throughout.

Improved after start before ultimately racing second away from the rail in middle stages. Cornered awkwardly before improving to lead momentarily passing the 400m before weakening sharply in last section.
Showed early speed to when racing away from rail. Continued on & crossed to rail near the 800m. Emptied out at the 350m & weakened badly to long last thereafter.
Jumped well, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, ran on evenly to take 2nd.
Slowly away, raced at tail, 7 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, crowded near 900M, 2 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began well, raced prominently, 2 wide, allowed rival to cross near 900M, a length back on turn, angled out 450M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from gate 9, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight.
Away with them, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began smartly, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, 2 lengths or so back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 550M, failed to make any progress in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
Away well, raced prominently on the outside, took the lead 1000M, 2 wide on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
At rear, 2 wide, swung wide on Straightening, made ground and ran on gamely to score by 3/4L.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly but only headed in the last 75M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, improved steadily to the line for 3rd.
Settled to race in behind midfield, along the rail, saved ground but crowded at 200M, ran on fairly only.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide no cover, only one paced in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, swung widest on Straightening, made ground steadily to the line.
Raced in behind the leader, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Sent forward and took lead, flattened in the last 100M.
At rear, along the rail, made some ground only in the last 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, did not improved in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, crowded passing 300M and then lost ground thereafter.
Raced next to the leader, 2 wide, lost ground in the Straight.
Settled over 2L back in 3rd on the rail, commenced move entering home straight, quickened well to take charge 200 metres out, won confidently.

Pressed forward from a wide draw before settling 1L back in 2nd off the rail, remained in a similar position into straight when came under pressure, outstayed by fast-finishing winner inside the final 200 metres.
Settled at the back and waited with, shaken up 600 metres out and saved ground turning for home, switched out for a run 300 metres out, finished off the race well under pressure.
Crowded at start, settled in 5th in midfield some 4L off the pace, crowded entering straight, kept on steadily without threatening.
Settled towards the rear in 7th some 6L off the pace on the rail, angled out for a run entering home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Settled in last few, last into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses.
Settled over 3L back 2-wide in 4th, came under pressure rounding home bend, minor bump entering the straight and gave ground steadily.
Settled in 6th just worse than midfield some 5L off the speed, came under pressure rounding home bend, made no impression in the run to the line.
Set a sound pace, kicked over 2L clear on straightening but unable to sustain effort and overhauled inside the final 250 metres. (Mucus)
Chased the pace, moved up to challenge leader 300M, went neck to neck all the way to the finish, just prevailed.
From draw 11 ridden to take the lead, pressed by rivals home turn, vied for lead with eventual winner from 300M, refused to give in, went down narrowly.
Moved forward from widest draw to be 3-wide outside leader on settling, tried hard turning home but safely held by first 2 over final 300M.
Jumped fast, soon restrained to be tracking the pace, held up for clear running early straight, battled on final 300M but always held by first 3.
Reserved towards the rear, took time to get going on straightening, did best work final 250M.
From draw 1 settled down midfield along the fence, gave only mild response under top weight, never looked like getting to leaders.
Held up towards the rear on inside, 4Ls to make up 400M, ran home one paced.
Settled down 2-wide in mid-division, lacked a finishing kick, remained one pace final 300M, no threat to leaders.
Unable to slot in, raced in midfield, left 4-wide without cover from 900M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled down 3-wide at the rear, over 5Ls off the pace 400M, closed off fairly.
Held up behind midfield, raced 3-wide throughout, ran on fairly, never threatened.
Steadied early stages to find cover, settled down at the rear 6Ls back, failed to run on in the straight.
From draw 12 slotted into a 3-wide spot in midfield, came under pressure 500M, weak in the finish.
Shuffled back to the rear before the bend, lay out making home turn awkwardly, soon left behind on straightening.
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the inside, commenced move after passing 500M, finished off very strongly to score.

Commenced well, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide early, sent forward after passing 1050M, took the lead 900M, 2 wide turning, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 100M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths or so back, no cover on turn, finished off well to take a place without threatening.
Began well, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out 600M, made some progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, wider turning in, hampered near 400M, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly.
Reared in stalls, missed break and lost a significant amount of ground, detached from the main group early, got back to it near 600M, 6 to 7 lengths back turning in, made some progress in straight.
Inconvenienced shortly after start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, carried wider 600M, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, one-paced in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, headed briefly 900M, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Average to begin, raced slightly behind midfield on the outside, peaked on turn, eased final 450M.

Moderately away, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, angled out after passing 600M, 3 wide turning in, hard ridden from 400M, showed very good response, hit the front 100M, ran on strongly to the line.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, improved along the rail on turn, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Jumped well, raced prominently on the inside, travelled well to turn, took the lead 450M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, 2 wide after passing 550M, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 700M, headed 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Hampered on jumping, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide, 5 to 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some progress early in straight, blocked near 100M, one-paced thereafter.
Average to begin, raced in midfield on the outside, 3 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped with them, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, dropped to midfield on turn, awkwardly placed early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced at rear on the outside, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently but wide, allowed rival to cross near 700M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 400M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.

Shifted in at start and made contact, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made some progress to make frame.
Hampered start, raced in 2nd, half-length back, took the lead 400M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, commenced move after passing 550M, very wide turning in, made some headway in straight.

Made contact at start, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Midfield, on the fence, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Dipped start, at back along the fence, lack room 4-2, unleashed strong finishing efforts when clear.
Box seat, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, ran on well until 100M weakened.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, dashed well 250M.
Midfield, 2 wide, ran on fairly in straight.
Slow away, at rear, dashed well 200M.
At back, 2-3 wide, little dash 250M.
Checked at start, took rail at rear, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, emptied 250M.
Sat behind leaders, asked for effort near 400M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Settled midfield, improved passing 400M, made up some nice late ground, missed by SH.
Slow to begin, raced midfield on rail, responded nicely in the straight.
Ridden along to race in front of midfield, gained some nice ground passing 100M.
Taken back at start, raced at tail on rail, in the straight made up some nice late ground.
Began only fairly and taken back, raced at rear on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn to save ground, responded well in the straight.
Taken back at start, widest on straightening, fought nicely in the straight.
Ridden along for some distance to take lead, placed pressure in the straight, gave ground passing 100M, lame left front leg.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, tried to improve passing 400M, close to finishing line was checked when crowded for room.
Settled behind the lead, placed pressure passing 400M, gave ground passing 150M.
Near 1050M was checked, clipped heels and stumbled, raced behind midfield, limited response in the straight, mucus in trachea and epiglottic entrapment.
At start was steadied away from heels and lost ground, raced towards rear, no response in the straight.

Began well before steadying at first bend & drifting back to midfield on rail. Moved away from rail entering last section when 4L from lead before dashing quickly between runners to strike lead near 100m & winning strongly.
Had soft run in midfield between runners throughout. Eased wider entering last section, cornered the widest before dashing well to share lead near 100m before overpowered by winner late. Held second.

Lost ground after start before settling last. Continued at rear, 7L from lead entering last section before making strong late ground to charge to fast finishing third along inside in closing stages. (Rider questioned).
Showed good speed after the start to lead before crossing to rail near the 1000m. Held lead until being joined near the 100m before yielding a length or two late to hold 4th on line.

Drifted back soon after start before racing third last away from rail. Continued near rear, over 6L from lead entering last section before making some late headway when running on to non-threatening midfield finish.

Began well from inside barrier before being crossed & racing behind the leader from 1000m. Entered last section only 2.5L from lead, improved to be 1.5L behind at 200m before emptying out & giving a few lengths thereafter.

Attempted to be steadied after start before racing keenly after first bend & improving to race in midfield, 3 wide with cover. Continued to improve passing the 500m, cornered 2L from lead before weakening in last furlong.

Raced second outside the lead in middle stages before getting some cover momentarily near the 600m. Entered last section under 2L from lead, peaked on effort soon after straightening & weakened out. (Lame post-race).

Began awkwardly & raced near the rear throughout. Relegated to share last place entering last section 7L from lead, stayed along rail in straight, finishing off evenly before short of room passing the 100m. No threat.

Raced prominently after start but caught 3 wide without cover before working hard to improve & race outside leader from 600m. Continued outside leader on straightening, emptied out soon after & weakened sharply last furlong.
Failed to muster speed after start & raced very wide without cover in middle stages before shifting to 3 wide line near the 650m. Weakened out in the straight & was second last.

Raced in first 3 in early stages but was caught 4 wide no cover throughout. Continued to race keenly when very wide in middle stages before weakening badly from the 500m. Long last. (Rider questioned).
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on very well in straight to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, angled out after passing 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, same position on turn, kept on well in straight without threatening.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, slightly better than midfield, moved closer in the middle stages, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Hampered at start, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, very wide into straight, one-paced in the run home.
Inconvenienced at start, raced towards rear on the inside, 5 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Bled.)
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest on Straightening, ran on impressively to score by 3-1/4L.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, made ground steadily and closed off fairly to the line to take 2nd.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground in the Straight and ran on fairly for 3rd.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover after 700M, made ground and closed off strongly to the line.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, stayed on but headed in the last 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground steadily in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
Raced in behind the leader, along the rail, made minor ground but emptied in the last 150M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Settled in one-out one-back, showed nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward and took lead, lost ground in the Straight.

Shifted back towards the rear from the widest gate, gained closer under pressure turning onto home bend, some 3L back in 8th entering home straight, ran on strongly under pressure to snatch victory final strides.
Sluggish at start, improved steadily under pressure before settling just behind the leader in 4th on the rail, quickened well to hit the front 200 metres out, only to be caught close to home.
Settled in rear, saved ground turning in, behind heels of horses inside the 200 metres, finished off the race well under pressure.
Persevered 5-wide without cover amongst the leaders, taken back swiftly for rails run in 2L 6th before making home bend, gained 4th entering home straight and fought on steadily without threatening.
Inconvenienced at start, settled towards the rear on the rail, snuck up on the rail turning for home, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Niggled along from a wide gate settling just worse than midfield in 8th, in similar position turning in, produced good late finish inside the final 150 metres.
Ridden along amongst the leaders, travelled alongside the leader rounding home bend, faded steadily after straightening.

Ridden along 4-wide amongst the leaders after beginning from a wide gate, taken 2-back 4-wide without cover in 5th coming onto home bend, lost position when the widest runner turning in, ran home one-paced.
Began fairly from the one draw, took up running passing the 800 metres and led until headed 200 metres out, folded up quickly. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon dropped to tail-end, never seen with a chance.
3-wide amongst the leaders early, hung out and remained wide without cover in 3rd some 1L off the pace rounding home bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Held up in mid-division, travelled strongly into contention 400M, quickened up well to lead 150M, held on from fast finishing 2nd late.
Taken back, settled near the rear, 5Ls to make up 400M, closed off well to claim 2nd last stride, nearest finish.
Failed to muster, wide no cover 1000M, made forward move 900M along the 3-path, challenged for the lead mid-straight, not pace of first 2 late.
Crossed to the lead 1200M, led at good pace, headed near 150M, battled on to hold 4th.
Restrained to race in midfield, 6th at halfway point, wide into straight, stayed on well to the line.
Dropped back to race at the rear, 7Ls off the good pace middle stages, made progress final 400M, not reached leaders.
Driven forward, chased leaders in 3rd, in contention until 200M, faded towards the line.
Taken across behind runners, settled towards the rear 6Ls back, off bridle 500M, wide into straight, ran on fairly. (Jockey: travelled well until 500M, did not quicken)
Chased leaders in a fast run race, pushed along 550M, battled on same pace, run ended 150M.
Restrained behind midfield, settled 4Ls back along the fence, failed to pick up in straight, never threatened.
From draw 12 caught wide first 600M, tracked leader on settling, came under pressure 500M, soon weakened turning home.
Settled behind midfield in a fast run race, shifted out to 3-wide 800M, struggled passing 500M. (Jockey : travelled well but did not respond after 500M.)

Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled comfortably in the middle stages, ridden after passing 250M, showed very good response, easily scored, impressive debut.
Began well from gate 14, positioned a length behind the leader, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off well without threatening the winner.
Began smartly from gate 1, raced in midfield on the middle track, kept on well final 400M to take a place.
Bumped on jumping, raced towards rear, 3 lengths or so back, made some headway final 400M to make frame.
Moderately away, raced towards rear on the stands' rail, kept on evenly final 400M.
Slowly away, raced at rear in the middle of the track, hampered 400M, hard ridden 350M, made some progress before inconvenienced 150M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced in the middle of the track, 1 to 2 lengths back, peaked 300M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear in the middle of the track, made no progress final 400M.
Bumped start, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on the stands' side, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Away with them, raced in midfield, 2 away from the stands' rail, weakened gradually final 400M.
Jumped with them, raced 1 to 2 lengths back, nearer to the middle track, weakened final 400M.
Made contact at start, raced 1 to 2 lengths back, nearer to the stands' side, weakened final 400M.
Average to begin, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, weakened final 450M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Slightly slow out and made contact, raced towards rear, nearer to the middle track, stumbled and unseated rider near 400M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, closed off strongly to score.
Pushed to obtain box seat, ran on well for 2nd.
Slow away, at back on the rails, blocked most straight, made steady ground.
Hard ridden early but failed to cross in front, then eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield along the fence, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, out of fuel 250M.
At back, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2 wide, ran on ok.
Eased back, 2 wide, made ground 250M, lack room 150M.
Slow away, took rail at rear, made ground 200M.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide, faded 400M.
Raced midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, responded strongly in the straight to score.
Settled midfield on rail, placed pressure near 400M, gained some nice ground in the straight.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, fought nicely in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield, tried to improve passing 450M, responded well in the straight.
Raced towards rear, widest on straightening, made up some late ground in the straight.
Settled in forward position, wide and without cover throughout, one-paced in the straight.
Began awkwardly and then was crowded for room, raced at rear, made some ground in the straight.
Raced at tail, placed pressure and only one-paced in the straight.
Raced in box seat, badly held up from on straightening until passing 200M, then near 50M was awkwardly placed.
Slow to begin, raced at back on rail, no response when placed pressure.
Ridden along to take lead, placed pressure but weakened passing 200M.
Raced outside the lead, came off bridle near 800M and under heavy pressure rounding the Home Turn, faded out in the straight, must trial.

Began well, shared lead early before settling just behind the speed when racing 3 wide without cover. Cornered less than 1L behind, sprinted quickly to assume lead passing 250m before running away to score big margin win.

Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Shifted into clear running on straightening when 3L from the lead before making continual steady ground to snare second on line. Well behind big margin winner

Raced very wide without cover in midfield in early stages, improved position near 850m before shifting to race outside leader from 550m. Continued close to lead until passed by winner at 250m before fighting on to hold 3rd.

Raced wide in midfield after start before being checked & losing ground near 700m. Continued wide & without cover when hanging around bend, entered last section a length behind before finishing off well to just miss a place.
Shared lead after start before continuing on & crossing to the rail when leading near the 750m. Headed & passed by winner at 250m before weakening to be just behind place-getters.

Didn't have the early speed of others but mustered speed to race in midfield on rail. Moved away from the rail passing the 500m before finishing off steadily between runners to be not far behind second.

Crowded at start before shifting behind runners to race wide with cover in second half. Checked near 650m before being hampered & forced very wide near 600m. Cornered widest, 3L from lead before finishing fairly to midfield.
Drifted back to race at the rear after start. Continued in second half, 3.5L from lead on straightening before finishing off steadily to midfield.

Raced near the lead after start before being crossed at racing on the leaders back from the 750m. Shifted away from the rail after straightening before tiring out sharply in last furlong. Well beaten.
Crowded & lost ground at start before racing at tail. Improved position between runners mid-race, second widest on cornering before making no ground in straight. Well beaten.
Shared lead in early stages before racing outside leader prior to getting cover momentarily near the 500m. Hard ridden on straightening before weakening out poorly in last section.
Drifted back & raced third last in early stages before being hard ridden but losing further ground to last passing half-way. Weakened further in straight to be very long last.
Began smartly from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on strongly in straight, won by 1-3/4L.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out 500M, finished off evenly.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out and made contact early in straight, made some headway thereafter to make frame.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 100M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, very wide turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Shifted out at start and made contact, raced at rear on the inside, angled out 500M, made some progress early in straight, blocked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 500M, made contact early in straight, steadied near 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide better than midfield, sent forward after passing 1000M, 2 wide from 850M, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.

Crowded start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled keenly in the early and middle stages, angled out 500M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.) (Lame left front leg.)
Jumped with them, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, 4 wide throughout, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly to the line by 3/4L.
Raced behind the lead, along the rail, made ground steadily and only headed in the last 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, swung wide on Straightening, bumped at 300M but still closed off well in the last 100M for 3rd.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground but bumped at 300M, closed off well to the line thereafter.
Settled in one-out one-back, saved some ground only in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail after 900M, saved ground and closed off fairly in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
Began awkwardly and at rear, along the rail, raced tight near 150M, only one paced thereafter.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, pretty one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, flattened in the last 200M.
Sent forward and took lead, lost ground in the Straight.
Sent forward, 2 wide after 800M, emptied in the last 200M.
At rear, 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, did not feature.

Travelled keenly in 3L 4th mainly, gained closer along the rail to one back position 400 metres out, did not find much room after straightening, quickened under pressure inside final 200 metres to snatch victory near the line.
Settled just worse than midfield mainly 3-wide, came under pressure entering home straight, ran on to hold every chance inside the final 200 metres and pipped at post.

Ridden forward to settled just off the pace in 2nd on the rail, tracked the leader before improving to gain slender advantage into straight, kicked 1L clear under pressure 200 metres out only to be swamped close to home.
Stumbled at start losing ground, soon recovered to midfield in 7th on the rail, angled out for a run on straightening, ran on under pressure.
Settled in rear on the rail, improved to 9th just worse than midfield over 1000 metres out, saved ground turning for home, did not find much room until the 200 metres, finished off the race well.
Travelled keenly in forward of midfield, made headway rounding home bend 3-wide to be close up into straight, ran home one-paced.
Began fairly from a wide gate settling just over 2L back in 3rd 2-wide, came under pressure approaching home turn but failed to quicken to challenge. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped awkwardly, quickly taken back to rear of the field, obtained rails run over 1000 metres out, ran on past well-beaten horses in the straight, did best work late.
Travelled wide without cover in last few from a wide gate, gained slightly closer rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Soon dropped to tail-end despite niggling along, trailed the field into home straight, went past well-beaten horses near the centre of the track.
Settled in last few, made no impression in straight.
Soon took up running on the rail, led unchallenged rounding home bend until joined into home straight, faded gradually.
Began well from a wide draw, soon taken back to travel wide without cover in midfield, remained in similar position into home straight, found nothing under pressure.
Went forward from draw 12 and took the lead going into the turn, led them slowly, sprinted well passing 300M, always had enough to hold off rivals.
Tracked leaders, travelled well into straight, loomed 300M, ran on well to line but safely held by winner final stages.
Moved forward tracking leader in a slowly run race, had some difficulty obtaining clear running early straight, fought on evenly to line, unable to gain ground on winner.
Tracked leader 2-wide in a slowly run race, fought on early straight, held 2nd till 200M, faded final stages.
Settled in 5th, never far off the pace, saved ground on the inside, held ground in the run home, not pace to challenge leaders.
Dropped back to near the rear, made the home turn awkwardly, 5Ls to make up 400M, made some progress without reaching leaders.
Settled down 2-wide behind midfield 4Ls off the slow pace, failed to quicken when asked, no threat to leaders.
Crowded for room at the start, steadied to near last for cover, swung wide home, ran on fairly passing beaten horses only.
Taken across to race at the rear inside, no clear run early straight, stayed on well until 100M when crowded for room and not properly tested to line. (Jockey questioned re riding tactics.)
Shifted out abruptly at start, settled down 3-wide in mid-division, wide no cover from 900M, kept on same pace turning home, never in contention.
Crowded for room on jumping, from draw 2 obtained a midfield position along the fence, difficult to settle passing 800M, couldn't go on in the straight.
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, raced keenly and checked 800M, widest into straight, weak in the finish.
Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, easy run on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Clean jump, sent forward to race prominently, allowed rival to cross near 1100M, 3 wide turning in, finished off well to take a place. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently on the inside, took the lead 900M, enjoyed the easy lead on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made some progress in straight, no threat to the first few.
Taken back from gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some headway in straight.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening and made minor progress.
Average to begin, raced prominently on the outside, 2nd on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back to race at tail, 10 lengths back, closer on turn but still the last into straight, made little progress in the run home.
Commenced well from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Inconvenienced at start, raced at rear on the outside, 6 lengths or so back on turn, failed to make any progress in straight. (Mucus in trachea.)
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced towards rear on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, weakened early in straight, eased final furlong.
Bumped start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, squeezed through gap 150M, finished off strongly to score.
Commenced well, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, finished off well to take 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide towards rear, there to turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at tail, 6 lengths or so back on turn, made very good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked on run 100M, headed 50M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, made good progress early in straight, peaked 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running in straight.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, finished off evenly.
Began well from gate 1, raced better than midfield on rail, angled out after passing 550M, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, there to turn, showed limited response in straight.
Shifted in at start and bumped, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover, 4 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, carried wider 500M, peaked early in straight, crowded 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, trapped very wide with no cover in midfield early, found cover near 900M, 3 wide on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.

Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide into straight, finished off well to take 2nd, always held.
Moderately away from gate 9, taken back to race at tail, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Clean jump, positioned 2 to 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, similar position on turn, angled out 350M, finished off evenly.

Taken back to race towards rear on the inside, angled out after entering the back straight, commenced move 750M, 3 lengths or so back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 wide from 800M, slightly hampered and dropped towards rear 600M, peaked on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Average to begin, trapped wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer 1700M, 2 wide from 1500M, gradually dropped towards rear after passing 800M, emptied and eased early in straight.

Taken back to race 2 wide towards rear, sent forward after entering the back straight, took the lead 750M, peaked and headed 600M, weakened from 500M, emptied and eased early in straight. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Pressed forward, 2-3 wide, closed off strongly to score.
Box seat, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, made steady ground 300M.

Slow away, at back, progressed steadily 350M, run ended 150M.

At back, 2-4 wide, progressed steadily 200M.
Eased to rear, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, out of fuel 300M.
