Raced in box seat, commenced to improve passing 600M, quickened passing 150M to score.
Settled midfield on rail, improved near 300M, made up some nice late ground, missed by SH.
Raced at rear, wide on straightening, gained some nice ground passing 100M.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, niggled from near 550M, responded well in the straight.
On jumping was bumped and became unbalanced, raced in front of midfield, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced behind midfield, placed pressure at 300M, made some ground passing 100M.
Urged along to race outside the lead, placed pressure in the straight but finished only one-paced.
Hard ridden to take lead, asked for effort on straightening, gave ground passing 150M, lame left front after race.
Travelled at back, widest on straightening, no response when asked for effort.
Settled midfield, near 600M was left racing wide and without cover, gave ground passing 200M.
Shortly after the start was crowded for room and lost ground, detached in early and middle stages, no response in the straight.

Held early lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 900m. Shifted over the heels of the leading pair on straightening, dashed to lead passing 150m before cruising to line to win strongly.

Raced worse than midfield away from rail. Raced close to heels in middle stages when improving to midfield between runners. Cornered the widest runner when over 4L from lead before finishing strongly to second on line.
Began awkwardly before being shifted back to race at tail. Eased the widest runner on straightening before closing strongly in late stages to snare fast finishing third.
Crowded on jumping & consequently raced third last on rail. Continued rearward, 5L from lead entering last section before making continual late headway between runners to less than 2L behind.

Raced wide in early stages before improving position to eventually race outside leader from the 650m. Assumed lead momentarily near the 200m before emptying out soon after & giving a few lengths late.
Showed speed to dash to lead after first 100m before crossing to rail passing the 900m. Held narrow lead approaching the 200m before weakening out to midfield in late stages.

Improved after start to race midfield between runners. Raced keenly & near heels before losing ground behind tiring runner passing the 500m. Held up on straightening before shifting out & finishing evenly. (See report).
Steadied after the start & raced at the tail throughout. Continued a clear last on cornering before passing a few tiring runners in late stages without threatening.
Raced the widest runner in early stages before shifting across to midfield before being left 3 wide without cover from 650m. Entered last section a length from lead before emptying out soon after.
Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Hard ridden to hold position passing half-way. Weakened out in last section & was well beaten.

Pushed forward before shifting in to race one horse off rail near the 850m. Continued between runners 1.5L from lead before losing ground when reluctant near the 450m. Was hard ridden on straightening before weakening poorly.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Continued wide around bend before weakening out poorly in the final 350m. Last.
Began well from gate 1, raced slightly better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 800M, commenced move after passing 400M, hit the front 150M, kept on well to the line and scored.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 400M, made very good progress in straight to take 2nd.
Taken back from gate 11, raced at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, improved from 400M, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer on turn, made some progress early in straight, peaked 150M, no extra thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader turning in, took brief lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped shortly after start, raced towards rear on the outside, awkwardly placed near 800M, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, passed some tired rivals in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, slightly hampered 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, inconvenienced near 550M, checked off heels 400M, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, awkwardly placed shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled greenly in the middle stages, 3 wide after passing 800M, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Made contact at start, trapped very wide in midfield, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Made contact shortly after start, raced better than midfield on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened gradually in straight, eased final 150M.
Began well, raced behind midfield on the inside, badly unbalanced near 550M, dropped to last turning in, showed no response in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Raced in midfield, 3 wide no cover initially, along the rail after 400M, passing 250M bumped, made ground and ran on gamely to the line and score.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, stayed on but only headed in the last 30M.
Settled in one-out one-back, bumped at 250M but still ran on well for 3rd.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, stayed on but ran on only fairly to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly only in the last 50M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide after 600M, ran on only fairly in the Straight.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, only one paced.
Bumped start and at rear, along the rail, pretty one paced. (See Incident Report)
Sent forward and raced behind the leader, along the rail, flattened in the last 150M.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, did not feature.
At rear, 2 wide, nothing in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, emptied in the last 200M.
Slightly slow out, settled towards rear in 10th on the rail, commenced move passing the 600 metres and angled out for a run entering straight, ran on well to snatch victory final strides.

Niggled at early stages, settled in midfield in 6th most of back straight, gained slightly closer over 600 metres out, sustained progress from 2L 4th into straight to hit the front 150 metres out, pipped at post.
Taken well back for rails run from the widest gate, trailed the field to home bend, saved ground on the inner turning in, ran on well under pressure to be nearest at finish.

Began well from a wide gate, pressed forward to lead 3-wide 1400 metres out before obtaining rails run shortly afterwards, steadied pace in the front in back straight and led until headed under pressure 150 metres out.
Settled in rear of midfield early stages, gradually dropped to last few in back straight, saved ground on the inside turning for home, ran on to do best work late.

Travelled wide in midfield after sluggish start, circled the field around first bend before settling outside the leader in back straight, drew level early in straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200 metres.

Settled well back from a wide gate, 3-wide rounding home bend when came under pressure, went very wide dropping to last turning in before producing good late impression down the centre of home straight.
Began well from the one draw, settled just off the pace behind the leader to straight, tightened on the rail over 200 metres out, made no further impression.
Broke well to be close up early, drifted back steadily towards the rear 800 metres out, found nothing under pressure in home straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Broke well from a wide gate, soon taken back towards the rear travelling 3-wide without cover, went very wide and dropped to second last into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began well from a middle gate, settled in one-out-one-back position coming onto first bend, remained in similar position when came under pressure approaching home straight but soon weakened.
Bumped and unbalanced early, pulled keenly towards first few rounding first bend, shifted back to midfield in back straight, weakened under pressure on straightening.
Began awkwardly, reserved in mid-division along the 2-path, picked up strongly final 250M, wore down the race leader near line.
Positively ridden to clear runners on its inside, emerged as leader 950M, kept on well turning home, caught near line.
Chased leaders in 4th, kept responding to pressure on straightening, got up for 3rd 50M.
Held up midfield, 5Ls to make up 400M, into clear 200M, closed off well to the line, just missed 3rd.
From draw 1 strode forward to be tracking leader, lay in early straight, battled on same pace and no threat over final 200M
Dropped back on jumping from wide draw, held up near last, made some progress along the fence final 300M, not reached leaders.
Up with early pace, eased back to sit ahead of midfield, kept on one paced in the straight, no impression final 200M.
Moved up gradually to be chasing the pace on outside, fought on same pace turning home, faded late stages.
Settled down 2-wide behind midfield, driven out 450M, stayed on to the line without threatening.
Taken back to the rear after the start, 7-8Ls off the pace on settling, driven out top of straight, made limited progress over final 300M.
Jumped awkwardly, shifted across behind runners, in last spot turning in, failed to run on.
Began fairly, held up towards the rear, failed to finish off in the straight, never a factor.

Jumped with them, raced in midfield on the outside early, moved a bit closer on the first turn, 1-1/2L back in the middle stages but still 3 wide, showed good response after turning in, hit the from 200M, ran on very well to the line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, closed off well to take 2nd on line.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, 2 wide in the middle stages, finished off well to take a place, always held.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, wider on turn, closed off well to make frame.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, raced in 2nd, challenged the leader turning in, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 200M. (Lost right hind plate in the early stages.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Began only fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the outside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Pushed to share the lead, drifted away 300M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
At back, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, held ground in straight.
At rear, 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, behind midfield, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, emptied 300M.
Eased back, no progress.
Hard ridden to share the lead, dropped off 400M.
Never better than midfield, hung out badly.
Never a factor.

Placing: PU
Comment: Shortly after entering the Straight was eased down.
Ridden along to take box seat, fought strongly in the straight to score.
Urged along to take lead, battled hard in the straight, missed by Neck.
Raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, quickened near 200M, finished nicely.
Niggled along to race in front of midfield, placed pressure but only one-paced in the straight.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 400M, finished one-paced.
Raced behind midfield, always off the bridle, limited response in the straight, failed to make impression.
Began only fairly, raced towards rear, placed pressure near 500M, wide on straightening, limited response.
Began awkwardly, then ridden along but failed to muster speed, no response in the straight.
Stumbled at the start, raced behind midfield on rail, came under pressure rounding the Home Turn, faded out in the straight.
Raced in front of midfield on rail, weakened passing 300M, blood in trachea.
Taken back at start, no response when placed pressure.
Settled in handy position, faded out passing 300M.
Enjoyed nice position 1,1 throughout. Entered last section 2.5L from lead, dashed quickly in straight to assume lead near the 150m before drawing away in late stages for easy win
Began well before pushing forward & racing outside the leader. Hard ridden on cornering before battling on well in late stages to hold second but well behind easy winner.

Steadied from wide gate before shifting back to tail. Moved closer to lead when making some ground along rail passing 450m before closing off strongly between runners in late stages to just miss second.

Didn't begin fast & shifted rearwards. Improved position along the rail to race in midfield, 4.5L from the lead near half-way. Moved away from the inside on cornering before making good late ground to be beaten only 2L.
Ridden forward after the start to lead. Continued in lead until being passed by winner at the 100m before being caught for minor placing in late stages.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Drifted further back approaching the 700m, cornered third last 6.5L from lead before making some late headway without proving a genuine threat.

Raced just worse than midfield between runners after start. Relegated to third last passing the 900m. Moved very wide to improve passing the 500m, cornered the widest 6.5L from lead before passing a few late.
Caught very wide around first bend before being caught 4 & 5 wide in middle stages. Left without cover form the 700m before battling on fairly to midfield considering wide passage.
Not fast to begin but improved to race midfield between runners. Hard ridden passing the 500m before making no real headway in the straight & never really looked likely to challenge.

Crowded away from heels & lost ground on first bend before racing second last. Relegated to last near half-way. Hard ridden passing 550m, a clear last 8L from lead on cornering, passed a few late but always well back.

Pushed forward to race prominently before being left 3 wide without cover in midfield before getting some cover near 750m when 3L from lead. Lost position prior to straightening before weakening out in straight.
Didn't begin fast before improving position after first furlong to race midfield on rail. Eventually settled on leaders back before being hard ridden from the 500m & weakening out to be well beaten.

Raced three & four wide with cover in midfield throughout. Continued to cover additional ground before entering last section over 6L behind. Second widest on straightening before emptying at 300m & weakening, beaten 9L.

Raced 4 wide without cover for first half before improving slightly to race 3 wide without cover from the 750m. Began yielding ground from the 450m & weakened out to long last after tough passage throughout.

Away with them, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, angled out early in straight, hard ridden after passing 350M, hit the front 150M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide towards rear, very wide turning in, finished off very strongly to take 2nd, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Bumped start and unbalanced, raced at tail, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Commenced well from gate 1, positioned on rail behind midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, closed off well to make frame.
Made contact at start, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, there to turn, took the lead early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from gate 11, raced in midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, there to turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, showed limited response in straight, eased final 50M.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 100M.
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced towards rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival turning in, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide after 1000M, kept on nicely to score by 1L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly to the line for 2nd.
At rear, 3 wide with cover, swung wide on Straightening, made ground and closed off fairly.
Began awkwardly, sent forward and took lead, along the rail, stayed on but headed in the last 250M.
At rear, 2 wide, made ground steadily to the line only.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, found no extra for final 100M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, swung widest on Straightening, was one paced.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide with cover, emptied after 200M.
Raced in behind midfield, wide no cover, pretty one paced.
Sent forward, 3 wide no cover, lost ground after 250M.
At rear, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.
At rear, along the rail, never a factor.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, lost ground in the Straight. Finished at rear, must trial. (See Incident report)
Ridden along from the one draw, took up running about 1100 metres out, gained 1L advantage rounding home bend and 2L clear after straightening, unchallenged.
With leaders after beginning from a wide gate, settled for 2L 3rd coming onto home bend, gained 2nd under pressure about 300 metres out but never threatened the winner.
Niggled along wide in rear of midfield, circled the field rounding home bend, 5th over 3L back 4-wide turning in, fought on steadily for distant 3rd.
Settled towards the rear, hampered and lost ground 800 metres out, last of all turning for home, baulked for a run upon straightening, produced some late impression closing stages.
Steadied at start, soon recovered to rear of field, remained in rear into home straight, ran on past well-beaten horses down the centre of the track.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, commenced move rounding home bend and the widest runner into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly in midfield on the rail, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced.
Settled wide in last few from a wide gate, gained slightly closer between runners rounding home bend, baulked and switched out for a run 300 metres out, kept on same pace without quickening.
Began fairly, settled towards the rear, baulked for a run on the rail until the 300 metres and again between 250 and 150 metres, not properly tested.
Just better than midfield early stages, drifted back to rear of midfield rounding home bend, ran home one-paced.
Began well from the widest gate, remained wide in first few throughout back straight, gained one back position coming onto home bend, weakened gradually after straightening.

Inconvenienced at start, travelled wide in forward of midfield and keenly, hampered coming onto home bend and remained wide without cover, gained closer to be 3L 4th into straight, gradually weakened.
Prominent and wide from a poor gate, shuffled back to midfield rounding home bend, dropped further back into straight.
Ridden along from a middle gate to be amongst the leaders, drifted back to 4th some 3L back coming onto home bend, yielded further ground after straightening.
Settled behind midfield towards the outside of group, pushed along halfway, did best work final 200M, quickened well to get up near line.
Reserved in midfield along the stands' rail, ran on well final 250M, just held.
Began awkwardly, chased leaders in 5th, fought its way to the lead 100M, no match for winner final 50M, lost 2nd near line.
Led passing 850M, joined by rivals 600M, inclined to lay in, stuck to task well, in contention until no extra final 80M.
Moved up to be tracking the pace along the stands' rail, battled on from 400M, held by leaders.
Held up behind mid-division 5Ls off the pace, made modest progress final 400M, not reaching top 3.
Began awkwardly, recovered to join leaders from 650M, raced greenly passing 450M, vied for lead until run ended 100M and weakened away.
In the 6th spot never far off the pace, kept on moderately to the finish, no threat to leaders though.
Began fairly, settled 2nd last, 7Ls to make up 400M, finished off mildly but never going the pace to challenge leaders.
Outpaced early stages, ended up near last, made some headway final 250M without troubling leaders.
Began well and joined leader near 600M, came under heavy pressure 400M, gave ground over final 200M. (Jockey and Trainer unable to explain the disappointing run. / Unacceptable Performance.)
Obtained a spot in midfield, 9th at midway and 5Ls off the pace, fought on same speed, weakened final 200M.
Head up on jumping and away awkwardly, raced in mid-division, no extra and dropped away from 300M.
Outpaced from the start, ended up in detached last, failed to run on.
Clean jump, raced 2 wide behind midfield, found rail near 800M, moved a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to take 2nd.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned right behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well to take a place.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the inside, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced better than midfield on the inside, 2 wide from 650M, commenced move after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 2 wide from near 800M, improved on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Stumbled on jumping, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, 3/4L there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from near 650M, dropped to rear on turn, showed nothing in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, weakened early in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L on turn, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened quickly thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced better than midfield but trapped very wide, weakened on turn, eased early in straight.
Began only fairly and crowded, raced 3 wide with no cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, a bit closer on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently, 2 wide, travelled well on turn, hit the front early in straight, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Average to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made some progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from the widest draw, 7 to 8 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, peaked early in straight, weakened gradually final 150M.
Shifted out at start and bumped, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, made some progress early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Bumped start, raced at rear, 7 lengths or so back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Made contact at start, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Slightly slow out, sent forward to take the lead, led by half length on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, gradually dropped position on turn, weakened final 250M.

Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 100M, kept on well to hold off the rivals late.
Commenced well from gate 1, raced in midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.
Jumped well from the widest draw, positioned a length behind the leader on the inside early, 3 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to take a place.

Moderately away, raced slightly behind midfield on rail, 2 wide from 800M, 5 lengths back on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide after passing 800M, commenced move 400M, very wide into straight, finished off well without threatening.

Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, sent forward after passing 800M, took the lead 600M, led by 2 lengths on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide from 700M, 4 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, no extra final 100M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, 2 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take race prominently on the inside, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Eased to obtain box seat, ran on well in straight.
Hard ridden early, midfield 2-3 wide, closed off strongly 200M.
Slow away, took rail at rear, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden early, midfield, 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
In front of midfield along the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Slow away, at back, 2 wide, progressed steadily 200M.
Slow away, at rear, 2-3 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 2-3 wide, made ground 300M, run ended 150M.
Slow away, at back along the fence, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, 2 wide, weakened 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, hung on until 200M emptied.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Settled behind midfield on rail, asked for effort near 300M, finished strongly to score, lame left hind leg after racing.
Raced towards rear, improved passing 550M, responded solidly in the straight.
Travelled midfield, improved passing 400M, worked home nicely.
Settled midfield on rail, fought nicely when asked for effort in the straight.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, raced at rear, commenced to improve passing 400M, responded well in the straight.

Near 1300M was eased away from heels, then after 1300M was severely checked and left racing wide and without cover near 1100M, near 800M improved to outside the lead, placed pressure near 400M, gave ground passing 50M.
Settled at tail, widest on straightening, worked home one-paced.
Taken back at start, was left racing wide and without cover near 800M, wide on straightening, no response in the straight.
Hard ridden along after start, took lead passing 1200M, weakened passing 150M.
After 1300M was checked and lost ground, raced on front of midfield, taken back near 500M and passing 400M was checked away from heels, no response in the straight.
Settled in box seat, came under pressure near 500M, faded out passing 150M.
Raced in handy position, came under pressure near 500M, gave ground passing 400M, never in it.
Shared early lead before continuing on & crossing to rail when leading near the 700m. Kicked over a length clear on cornering before continuing strongly & holding similar advantage on line.

Pushed forward after the start but was caught 3 wide without cover a length from lead. Continued wide around bend before digging deep in concluding stages to hold second after wide passage throughout.
Enjoyed soft run in midfield along the rail throughout. Stayed close to the inside on cornering before making continual ground along the rail in concluding stages to just miss second.

Shifted across to midfield after start when racing 3 wide with cover in middle stages. Moved closer to lead approaching the 500m, cornered only 3L from lead before closing well in late stages to just miss a placing.

Drifted back after start & raced just worse than midfield away from rail. Moved closer to lead passing half-way, cornered 4L from lead, moved the widest runner on straightening before finishing well to be under 2L behind.
Shared early lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back from near the 700m. Emptied out passing the 200m & gave a length or two in concluding stages.
Steadied & shifted across after start to race third last away from rail. Shifted wider in the straight before making some late ground in closing stages from rearward position.

Pushed forward before settling third away from rail without cover. Cornered a length from lead, raced tight between runners near the 100m, emptied out soon after before being crowded in concluding stages. No threat.
Slow to begin & consequently raced second last throughout. Made up some ground in the concluding stages but was never a threat.
Slow to begin before mustering speed to improve to midfield on rail. Raced keenly in middle stages & lost a length near the 550m. Made no improvement in straight & was no threat.
Shifted back from wide gate & raced at the tail. Continued a clear last on cornering & made no real improvement. Second last.
Raced in midfield between runners after start before travelling keenly near the 800m. Awkwardly placed close to heels near the 550m, cornered 3L from lead before weakening poorly in last furlong.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to score.

Began well from gate 1, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M, finished 2nd.
Crowded start, raced at tail, still 8 lengths back on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Made contact shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider turning in, no daylight early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off well to make frame without threatening.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move 350M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Clean jump, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to take the lead, led by 3/4L turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 150M, weakened final 100M.
Made contact at start, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 7 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, very wide into straight, made little progress in the run home.

Made contact at start, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, found a 2 wide spot near 800M, 2 lengths back on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded start, raced at rear on the inside, 6 lengths back on turn, one-paced in straight.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, 3/4L back on turn, weakened early in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm.)
At rear, 2 wide, swung widest on Straightening, battled on to the line and scored by only a Neck.
Settled in one-out one-back, raced tight near 800M, ran on gamely, only to miss by a Neck.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground and closed off strongly in the last 100M.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground steadily and closed off well to the line.
Raced in behind midfield, wide no cover, swung wide on Straightening, closed off strongly to the line in the last 50M.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, weakened passing 100M.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, remain one paced to the line.
At rear, along the rail, saved minor ground in the straight.
At rear, 2 wide, emptied in the last 100M.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail after 700M, lost ground in the Straight. (See incident report)
Sent forward, did not improved passing 150M and lost ground thereafter. (See incident report)
Settled 2L back in 4th 2-wide, came to challenge under pressure over 400 metres out, hit the front at the 200 metres from wide into straight, hung on well.
Led early, ceded lead for one back position 1200 metres out, tracked leader in 3rd to home straight, held every chance until unable to sustain effort inside the final 150 metres.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, came to challenge under pressure entering home straight, ran on well inside final 200 metres.
Settled wide towards the rear in 9th, obtained run under pressure 200 metres out, finished off the race well.

Settled in rear from a wide gate, commenced run coming onto home bend and saved ground on the inside improving to within 3L of pace entering straight, unable to match pace of first few inside final 200 metres.
Began well from the one draw settling 2 back on the rail in 5th, came under pressure rounding home bend and saved ground on the inside turning in, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Settled in last few on the rail, saved ground turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Settled just worse than midfield on the rail, snuck up on the inside turning for home, soon weakened after straightening.
Pressed forward from the widest gate, obtained lead on the rail passing the 1200 metres setting a sound pace to the straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
Ridden early stages, travelled wide without cover in midfield until faded into straight. (Blood in trachea)
Ridden forward from a middle gate, settled in 2nd outside the leader, came under pressure to challenge rounding home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Reared and lost considerable ground at start, remained well behind and never seen with a chance.
Chased leader 2-wide, asserted 250M, held on well under pressure.
Tracked leader along the fence, moved up to challenge for lead early straight, held by winner over final 200M.
Taken back to last from wide draw in a fast run race, finished off soundly final 300M to share the 3rd spot.
Soon led, battled on, headed 250M, faded final stages but held on for dead heat 3rd.
Settled towards rear, brought wide into straight, made steady progress to be nearest at the finish.
Never far off from pace, not able to quicken final 300M, held ground towards the finish. (Bled.)
Settled 2-wide midfield, stayed on same pace to the line, never seriously threatened.
Reserved in mid-division, not pace to challenge in straight, never a threat.
Slow to muster, ended up towards the rear along the inside, made no real progress in straight.
Held up 3-wide in mid-division, gave limited response turning home, no impression on leaders.
Caught wide no cover chasing leaders from draw 11, no extra mid-straight, weakened rapidly.
Restrained to race at the rear of the field, couldn't go on in the straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score by a narrow margin.

Commenced well from gate 1, positioned 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 150M, ran on very well, just unable to hold off the winner on line.
Began only fairly, positioned 4 to 5 lengths behind the leader on rail, 2 wide on turn, finished off strongly to take a place, nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, commenced move after passing 400M, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, 2 wide, half-length back on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, showed good response early in straight, took brief lead 200M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened gradually final 50M.
Made contact at start, raced 2 wide towards rear, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, made little progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, finished off evenly. (See Racing Incidents.)
Crowded on jumping, raced towards rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced at tail, 6 to 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear on the outside, peaked on turn, one-paced in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)

Made contact shortly after start, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, angled out after passing 450M, finished off very strongly to score.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 4 to 5 lengths back, there to turn, finished off strongly to take 2nd. (See Racing Incidents.)

Moderately away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground throughout, showed good response early in straight, took the lead 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the first two late.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide, 1 to 2 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover slightly behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length or so back, 2 wide from 600M, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened gradually thereafter.

Stumbled at start and inconvenienced, raced 2 wide towards rear early, found rail near 650M, saved ground on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 200M, made little progress thereafter.
Clean jump, positioned 3 wide with cover, 3 lengths or so back, similar position on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, finished off one pace.
Jumped well from the widest draw, trapped 4 wide, a length or so back, 3 wide form 600M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Began well from gate 12, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Began fairly, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Eased back along the fence, on heels early, lack room 400M, unleashed strong finishing efforts 250M.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped very wide, progressed forward to sit outside the leader, led 350M, overhauled 100M.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2 wide, dashed well 300M.
Midfield, 2-3 wide, dashed well 300M.
Pushed to secure box seat, ran on well until 150M emptied.
Pushed to sit in midfield, little dash 300M.
Eased at start, 3-4 wide, dashed well 300, run ended 100M.
Eased back, took rail, lack room 400M, no dash.
Eased at start, 2 wide at rear, little dash 200M.
Pushed forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Midfield, trapped 3-5 wide, never improved.
Pushed to take rail and lead, dropped off 350M.
Checked start, race ungenerously, never competitive.
Never a factor.
Travelled behind midfield, held up for clear running in the early part of the Straight, quickened passing 100M to score.
Raced midfield, 3 wide with cover, widest on straightening, gained some ground passing 100M, finished strongly.
Raced at tail, was held up for clear running in the early part of the Straight, finished solidly.
Settled in one-back-one-off position, commenced to improve near 500M, fought well in the straight.
Raced towards rear, approaching and passing 200M had difficulty obtaining clear running until passing 100M, gained some ground after obtaining clear running.
Taken back at start, fought hard in the straight, gradually gained ground passing 200M.
Raced outside the lead with nice early speed, passing the 200M rider's whip was knocked off, gave some ground passing 100M.
Niggled to race in box seat, in the early part of straight held up for clear running, worked home well.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield on rail, held up from passing the 400M to near 200M, finished well.
Ridden along to take lead, responded well in the early part of straight, gave ground passing 150M.
Settled behind midfield, placed pressure in the straight, limited response.
Crowded at start, settled midfield on rail, raced in restricted room near 200M and was not fully tested.
Near 1500M was left racing wide and without cover in forward position, gave ground in the straight, blood in trachea.
Near 1400M was left racing 4 wide and without cover in handy position, faded out passing 400M.

Raced worse than midfield after start before racing 1,1 in midfield throughout. Eased 3 wide on cornering, dashed quickly to share lead at the 300m before continuing on strongly to draw away for easy 3L win.
Strode forward to lead. Continued in lead until being joined by the winner at the 300m before battling in to hold distant second.

Drifted back to second last after start. Continued with only one runner behind when just over 4L from the lead at the 800m. Eased wider on straightening before making continual steady ground to third, neck behind second.

Raced in midfield on rail throughout. Shuffled back to third last, just under 4L from lead at the 800m. Moved away from the rail approaching corner, finished off ok to 4th but well behind easy winner.
Steadied after start & taken back to last. Continued a clear last on cornering, 5L from lead entering last section before making no improvement in straight.
Strode forward early before steadying & racing on leaders back passing winning post first time. Ridden along passing the 500m, straightened 2L behind lead before weakening out to be beaten over 8L.

Raced in midfield early before improving position passing the 1700m to race second away from rail. Hard ridden passing the 600m, cornered only a length from the lead before weakening in final 300m. Last, 10L behind.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 2 wide in midfield, wider from 600M, hard ridden after turning in, showed very good response, hit the front 150M, kept on strongly to the line.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, there to turn, crowded early in straight, made very good progress thereafter to take 2nd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide towards rear, similar position on turn, closed off strongly to take a place.
Taken back from gate 9, raced at tail, 7 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, finished off very strongly to make frame, nearest on line.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, wider turning in, made good progress in straight.
Made contact at start, raced better than midfield on the outside, similar position on turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked 150M, no extra thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, travelled well to turn, showed good response early in straight, peaked on run 150M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with no cover, a length back, moved a bit closer on turn, took the lead 300M, peaked and headed 150M, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight near 200M but failed to make any progress thereafter.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on the rail, saved ground on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.

Began fairly, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 500M, no clear running early in straight, failed to make any progress thereafter. (Lame right front leg.) (See Racing Incidents.)
Began awkwardly and bumped, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, took the lead 450M, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.
Average to begin, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, peaked and headed 450M, weakened early in straight, eased final 200M. (Bled.) (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Rolled forward, along the rail, stayed on and closed off strongly in the last 200M to score.
Settled to race in midfield, along the rail, ran on strongly in the straight.
Sent forward and took lead, 2 wide, stayed on but headed in the last 100M.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, ran on well to line for 4th.
Rolled forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide after 700M, stayed on but emptied only in the last 50M.
At rear, 2 wide, improved well to the line.
Bumped start and raced in behind midfield, along the rail, only one paced.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, swung wide on Straightening, made marginal ground only.
Raced in midfield, 3 wide but with cover, raced greenly in the Straight and remain one paced to the line.
Raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, pretty one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, emptied in the last 150M. Poor performance, must trial. (See incident report)
At rear, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, checked near 200M and then lost ground thereafter.
At rear, 2 wide, found nothing in the Straight.
Settled in last few, commenced move on top of home bend switching wide for a run into straight, showed a great turn of foot on straightening to take command passing the 200M.
Settled towards the rear, ran on under pressure in straight to snatch 2nd late.

Pressed forward from the widest gate to travel just outside race leader, raced keenly from the 1300M and drew level over 600M out, hit the front briefly after straightening and headed inside the 200M.

Began fairly, settled within 4L of pace in 5th 2-wide, gained slightly closer rounding home bend and switched out for a run entering straight, quickened to hold some chance over 200M, outsprinted by winner and lost 2nd late.

Began fairly, ridden along before settling some 2L back in 4th 2-wide, gained slightly closer to 3rd rounding home bend, quickened to hold some chance early in straight but unable to sustain effort and swamped inside final 250M.
Soon picked up to one back position in 3rd on the rail after a moderate start, came under pressure to challenge after straightening but faded inside the final 200M.
Moderate start, quickly recovered to midfield in 6th over 4L back, improved slightly closer under pressure early in home straight but unable to sustain effort inside the final 200M.
Soon took up running, obtained rails run shortly passing the 1400M, travelled keenly in front before joined rounding home bend, folded up shortly after straightening.
Settled well back from a wide gate, came under pressure in straight but never seen with a chance.
Very slowly away losing considerable ground, remained well back throughout and never seen with a chance.
Settled towards the rear, responded generously to pressure on straightening, led from 100M held on well close home.
In 4th spot always close up behind leaders, fought on well passing 400M, outgunned by winner final stages.
Held up towards the rear 4Ls behind leaders, progressed steadily over final 400M, just missed 2nd.
Tracked leader, travelled well into straight, took over 400M, all out, unable to hold off first 3 final 100M.
Tracked leader on inside, well placed to strike turning home, had his chance, faded final 100M.
Settled 2-wide at the rear, tried hard in straight, stayed on without threatening much higher rated rivals.
Slow out, held up at the rear, never going the pace to challenge. (Blood in trachea.)
Soon led, quickened up tempo from 1200M, came under pressure 500M, headed top of straight, weakened to last.

Average to begin, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, hard ridden early in straight, showed very good response, hit the front near 125M, kept on strongly to the line.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 125M.
Jumped with them, raced 4 wide in midfield, no cover in the middle stages, bumped near 500M, hard ridden after passing 350M, finished off strongly to take a place.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at tail, 5 lengths or so back, very wide turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, bumped 500M, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 to 3 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, wider turning in, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, made little progress in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Away with them, raced better than midfield on the outside, no cover on turn, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to 100M, weakened thereafter.
Crowded on jumping, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Crowded shortly after start, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened inside final furlong. (Lame right front leg next day morning.)
Began well from a wide draw, raced prominently but trapped very wide early, 2 wide from 700M, a length back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Made contact at start, raced 3 lengths behind the leader on rail, same margin back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Quickly into stride, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 2 to 3 lengths back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, carried wider on turn, bumped and unbalanced early in straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Jumped well from the widest draw, taken back to race towards rear on the outside, no cover on turn, weakened early in straight. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 2 wide after passing 700M, a bit closer turning in, finished off strongly to score by a neck.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, commenced move after passing 650M, 3 wide turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner final 50M.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, hard ridden after passing 550M, made good progress in straight to take a place without threatening.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, hard ridden 300M, showed some response, peaked on run 100M, no extra thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, travelled keenly near 800M, wider on turn, made good progress early in straight, peaked 200M, ran on evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, 2 wide from 700M, challenged the leader turning in, kept on well early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide at rear, angled out after passing 500M, raced tight 300M, finished off evenly.
Began well from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, gradually moved closer on turn, very wide into straight, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Commenced well, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rivals turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, headed near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover towards rear, very wide turning in, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced at rear on the outside, a bit closer in the middle stages, very wide turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced better than midfield on the outside, peaked turning in, ran on evenly early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Taken back from gate 10, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover for the majority of the race, very wide turning in, raced tight 300M, weakened final furlong.
Bounded in the air at the start and landed awkwardly, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong. (Lame right front leg.)

Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, took the lead 200M, kept on well, just won by a nose.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the outside, moved a bit closer after passing 700M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly, just missed by a narrow margin.
Began well, positioned on rail better than midfield, 2 wide turning in, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, similar position on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back form gate 9, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made some progress in the run home.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, moved closer on turn, 3 wide into straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at rear on the inside, saved ground on turn, made little progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 450M, finished off evenly.
Began fairly from gate 1, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, one-paced in straight.
Began well, raced in 2nd, 2 lengths behind the leader, pushed along after passing 600M, took the lead 400M, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened final 100M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to take the lead, led by 2 lengths, peaked and headed 400M, weakened early in straight.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, led 350M, overhauled 150M.
At rear, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
At back, 2 wide, made steady ground 250M.
Eased back, raced keenly, took rail, blocked 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Midfield along the rails, ran on ok in straight.
Hard ridden early but failed to muster, trapped 3 wide, held ground in straight.
Eased back, took rail, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Behind midfield, trapped 3 wide, lack room 4-2, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, dropped off quickly 500M, hampered 200M.
Settled behind midfield, wide on straightening, quickened passing 150M, scored unchallenged.
Raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, improved passing 400M, wide on straightening, gained ground passing 200M, finished solidly.
Raced at rear, widest on straightening, commenced to improve passing 600M, made up some nice late ground, right front tendon injured next day.
Settled in box seat, asked for effort passing 500M, fought well in the straight.
Throughout the race travelled wide and without cover in handy position, gained some ground in the straight.
Settled midfield on rail, responded well in the early part of straight, gave some ground passing 50M.
Settled midfield, lost its left front plate rounding the Home Turn, near 100M was hampered, worked home one-paced.
Settled in front of midfield, placed pressure passing 600M, no response in the straight.
Raced outside the lead with nice early speed, came under pressure near 500M, gave ground passing 200M, near 100M was hampered.
Ridden along to take lead, came under pressure approaching Home Turn, weakened in the straight, rider questioned tactic.
Buffeted for a short distance after start, raced at tail on rail, placed pressure but no response.
Settled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, faded out in the straight.
Raced close to lead before being crossed & racing on leaders back from the 850m. Stayed on rail on straightening, dashed through to take lead at 200m before drawing away in late stages for cozy win.
Steadied near the 950m before settling in midfield between runners. Continued 3.5L from lead entering last section before closing off well in final 100m to snare second on line.

Steadied after start & shifted back to clear second last. Moved wider to improve entering last section when 5.5L from lead, cornered the widest runner before finishing strongly in late stages to just miss second on line.
Mustered speed after the start before striding to lead at the 900m. Continued in lead until being joined & passed by winner near 200m before caught for minor placing in final stride.

Caught 3 wide without cover in midfield throughout. Continued wide around bend, entered last section just under 3L from lead before fighting on well in dying stages to finish in a bunch, around 2L behind.
Steadied away from heels after start before improving position to ultimately settled 1,1 from the 900m. Battled on ok in the straight to be beaten only around 2L in a bunch behind cozy winner.

Shifted across & raced just worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover throughout. Continued wide, 4.5L from lead entering last section, eased wider on straightening before closing off steadily to midfield.

Steadied & shifted back to tail. Became detached from field in middle stages, racing over 8L from lead near half-way. Continued at tail entering last section, passed a few along the inside late but was never likely.
Raced in midfield on the rail throughout. Niggled along approaching 450m before weakening out in straight to be well beaten.
Fastest to begin, held early lead before ultimately racing outside the leader form the 900m. Emptied out soon after straightening & weakened out sharply in final 250m. Well beaten.
Had no early speed & drifted back to third last on rail. Cornered around 5L from lead before yielding further ground in straight to be beaten 8L.
Drifted back after the start & raced worse than midfield between runners. Hard ridden entering last section when 5L from lead before weakening out in straight to be well beaten last.
Made contact at start and unbalanced, raced 2 wide better than midfield, 1 to 2 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly to score.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, wider turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, nearest on line.

Shifted out at start and made contact, raced 2 wide towards rear early, 3 wide from 1000M, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, 3 lengths back on turn, closed off well to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed near 1100M, challenged the leader on turn, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter, missed 3rd on line.
Clean jump, raced prominently but trapped wide early, took the lead 1100M, led by a length in the middle stages, challenged by rivals on turn, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Commenced well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide behind midfield early, gradually moved forward after passing 1200M but still 3 wide, 3/4L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, similar position on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, failed to make any progress in the run home.
Raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began awkwardly and at rear, along the rail, swung widest on Straightening, made ground and closed off strongly to score by 3/4L.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, battled on gamely but couldn't hold off the winner, settled for 2nd.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, swung wide on Straightening and made some ground in the Straight.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, made ground steadily to the line.
Taken back, 2 wide, ran on only fairly to the line.
Raced in front of midfield initially, continued to roll forward and raced next to the leader after 850M, 2 wide, found no extra for final 150M.
Raced behind the leader, along the rail, did not make ground in the Straight. (See incident report)
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, only one paced in the Straight.
Sent forward and settled in one-out one-back, flattened in the last 150M.
At rear, 2 wide, checked near 250M and lost ground thereafter.
Sent forward and took lead, along the rail, near the 250M lost ground. (Lame left hind, blood in trachea and roarer)
Raced in midfield, along the rail, saved ground but severely checked near 250M and did not feature thereafter.
With the leaders on the rail, settled for one back position in 3rd coming onto home bend, hit the front under pressure over 50 metres out, won readily.
Crowded at start settling in rear, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off the race strongly inside the final 130 metres.
Jumped well from the one draw, close up early before drifting back to forward of midfield in 6th just over 3L back, saved ground on the inside turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

Persevered from the widest gate to be up with the pace, travelled just outside the leader rounding home bend, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside the final 50 metres after a hard run.

Close up early, gradually settled in 7th in midfield, met minor inconvenience coming onto home bend, became 6th into straight, minor interference 250 metres out, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Settled wide in rear from a wide gate travelling wide throughout, widest runner turn for home, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.

Jumped fairly, ridden to gain narrow advantage 3-wide among a line of 6 horses, obtained rails run in the front coming onto home bend, led until headed upon straightening, folded up quickly inside the final 150 metres.
Jumped fairly gradually settling at the back, trailed the field most of the way to straight, saved ground turning for home, ran on in straight to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along to keep with the leaders, drifted back to 4th some 2L back coming onto home bend, weakened steadily after straightening.

Travelled wide amongst the leaders early from a wide gate, taken back to rear of midfield passing the 800 metres but remained wide rounding home bend, kept on steadily despite buffeted 200 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Moderate start, improved steadily along the rail to 9th in rear of midfield while niggling along, saved ground turning in and ran home one-paced.

Jumped awkwardly, ridden to share early pace, gradually taken back to 5th passing the 800 metres but remained wide and further back rounding home bend, one-paced when hampered 200 metres out, never recovered.
Tracked leader on outside, quickened to lead mid-straight, kept on well to score.
Jumped well, tracked leader on inside, responded well passing 300M but always held by winner to the line.
Restrained in midfield along the fence, ran on steadily passing 300M, held by first 2.
Crowded for room at start, dropped back to the rear, brought widest for home, closed fastest to be nearest at the line.
Began well from draw 12, heavily restrained to race towards the rear, wide no cover throughout, made some progress final 300M. (Jockey and Trainer questioned re riding tactics.)
Held up 3-wide behind midfield, driven out near 400M, kept on mildly, not reach leaders.
Crowded for room at start, raced towards the rear, keenly 700M, responded fairly on straightening, no threat to leaders.
Never far off from the pace, 5th turning in, kept on same pace under pressure.
Settled just ahead of midfield, wide no cover from 900M, not quickened turning home, fought on same pace to line.
Moved up to the lead 1000M, headed nearing 200M, weakened towards the line. (Lame next day.)
Held up towards the rear 5Ls behind leader, not going the pace to challenge final 300M, never involved.
Settled down behind midfield, driven out nearing 400M, weak in the finish.
