Moderately away, raced at rear on the stands' side, 2 lengths or so back, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off very strongly to score.
Made contact at start, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader in the middle of the track, hard ridden after passing 300M, closed off well to take 2nd.
Bumped start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader in the middle of the track, commenced move after passing 450M, hit the front 300M, peaked and headed 100M, ran on evenly to the line.
Began well from gate 14, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 300M, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced on the stands' side, a length back, hard ridden from 400M, only showed limited response, weakened final 100M.
Shifted in at start, sent forward to take the lead, peaked 400M, headed 300M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, peaked 300M, weakened final furlong.
Began well, positioned a length or so back, 2 away from the stands' rail, peaked 400M, crowded 350M, one-paced thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 3/4L behind the leader, nearer to the stands' side, peaked 450M, weakened final 300M.
Commenced well, raced in midfield, 3 away from the stands' rail, made no progress final 400M. (Bled.)
Shifted out at start and bumped, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader in the middle of the track, crowded 300M, made no progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced prominently in the middle of the track, hard ridden 350M, showed limited response, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Moderately away from gate 1, raced prominently on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, showed limited response, weakened final 250M.
Began only fairly, raced prominently in the middle of the track, peaked on run 400M, weakened gradually thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Hard ridden to keep up with the front runners, closed off well 350M to score.
Eased back, took rails, dashed well 300M.
Slow away, at rear, 2-4 wide, unleashed strong finishing efforts 300M.
Pushed to take rail and lead, hung on well until 100M weakened.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, little dash 200M.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 2 wide, lack room most straight, dashed well.
Eased to sit in midfield but trapped wide, allowed to move forward 900M, ran on until 150M emptied.
Behind midfield, trapped 4 wide, moved forward 800M, ran on fairly in straight.
Hard ridden early, at back, little dash 200M.
Shared the lead early in 2 wide, weakened 400M.
At rear, 2 wide, ran on fairly in straight.
Box seat, out fuel 500M.
Eased to sit in midfield, raced keenly, allowed to move forward 800M into the lead, emptied 250M.
Slow away, never better than midfield, on heels 100M.
Raced behind midfield on rail, quickened passing 100M, finished strongly to score.
Niggled forward, raced behind leaders on rail, placed pressure passing 400M, worked home solidly.
Raced midfield, responded nicely when asked for effort, finished well.
Raced behind midfield, commenced to improve near 400M, responded well when placed under pressure.
Raced at rear, asked for effort near 400M, made some nice ground passing 200M.
Settled midfield, asked for effort passing 450M, finished one-paced.
Raced towards rear, worked home one-paced.
Ridden along to take lead, tried to improve but gave ground near 200M.
Raced at tail, placed pressure near 500M, limited response.
Settled midfield, limited response when asked for effort, gave ground passing 100M.
Raced towards rear in central of track, no response when placed pressure.
Raced behind the lead, came under pressure near 400M, weakened passing 400M.
Travelled towards rear, placed pressure but no response, never in it.
Showed nice early speed, raced midfield in central of track, action deteriorated noticeably over the latter stages, must trial.

Showed good speed after start to assume lead before crossing to rail when leading after first 300m. Kicked away from immediate challenger passing the 300m before drawing away in last 250m to win easily.

Raced 4 wide in early stages before drifting further back & racing 3 wide with cover when 4.5L from the lead approaching the 800m. Moved wider approaching corner, dashed to second at 250m before holding that place on line.

Shifted behind runners to race 4th last on rail. Continued rearward & on rail on straightening, entered last section 4.5L from lead, closed off strongly in final furlong to just miss second. (Lame right foreleg post-race).
Enjoyed good run on leaders back throughout. Continued to follow leader/winner entering last section when 2L behind before battling on ok to hold 4th.
Slow to begin & consequently raced at the tail. Eased wider on straightening, entered last section 4L form lead before passing a few in the dash to line without threatening.
Ridden forward after the start before improving to race outside the leader from the 1100m. Emptied out passing the 300m mark before weakening in last furlong.
Ridden forward after start but was caught 3 wide without cover throughout. Hard ridden on straightening before weakening a few lengths in final 300m after wide passage throughout.

Crowded & badly unbalanced at start, losing ground before mustering speed & improving position to midfield on rail. Stayed along rail on straightening before offering no challenge & weakening to midfield.

Raced in midfield between runners early before drifting slightly further back to be 4.5L from the lead at half-way. Eased wider approaching corner, forced the widest entering last section before failing to improve thereafter.

Allowed to find feet after the start before ultimately drifting back to third last after first section. Relegated to last place passing half-way, entered last section 5.5L from lead & never challenged in straight.
Raced in midfield between runners throughout. Awkwardly placed behind runners entering last section when 4L from lead before weakening out meekly in final 250m.
Began awkwardly before striding to midfield but racing three wide with cover throughout. Continued wide around bend before offering nothing in last section & weakening poorly to be well beaten.

Not bustled after the start & drifted back to race second last away from the inside for the majority. Continued near the tail on cornering before weakening out poorly in straight to be very long second last.
Crowded at start before mustering speed quickly to race 1,1 throughout. Weakened out sharply in final section to be very long last.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced towards rear on the outside, a bit closer on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to score.
Made contact at start, raced prominently but trapped very wide, shared lead on turn, hard ridden after passing 300M, kept on very well, just unable to hold off the winner late.
Commenced well from gate 1, sat right behind the leader on rail, angled out after turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening the first two.

Taken back from the widest draw, raced behind midfield on the outside early, moved closer after passing 950M, found rail near 700M, 2 lengths back on turn, angled out 400M, closed off well to make frame without threatening.
Began well, raced in midfield on the outside, very wide turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked on run 200M, ran on evenly to the line.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, peaked early in straight, kept on evenly to the line.
Made contact at start, raced prominently, 2 wide, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Shifted out at start and made contact, sent forward to race prominently, found rail 600M, shared lead on turn, peaked and headed early in straight, weakened gradually final furlong.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, made no progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Crowded on jumping, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Made contact at start, raced 3 wide better than midfield, peaked on turn, ran on evenly to 200M, weakened and eased thereafter.
Settled behind the leader, along the rail, ran on strongly to line.
Settled in midfield, along the rail, made ground steadily to the line.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, made ground and ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Sent forward and took lead, stayed on but headed in the last 200M.
Crowded start, raced in behind midfield, 2 wide after 800M, made some ground only in the Straight.
At rear, along the rail, made ground and closed off okay in the Straight.
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, only one paced.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, showed no turn on foot.
Sent forward, 2 wide after 850M, flattened in the last 150M.
Missed the start, raced in behind midfield, nothing in the Straight.
At rear, 2 wide, never a factor.
At rear, 2 wide, did not feature.
Raced in front of midfield, near the 900M steadied, 3 wide no cover after 850M, lost ground in the Straight.

Ridden along after moderate start from a wide gate, shared pace 4-wide before obtaining position just outside race leader coming onto home bend, hit the front on straightening and held on well under pressure.

Soon dropped behind midfield mainly 3-wide despite ridden along, made headway to joint 6th some 3L back rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure inside final 200 metres to snatch 2nd late.
Crowded at start from a wide gate settling wide in rear, made headway out wide around home bend, sustained good progress from 4L 8th into straight, nearest at finish.
Ridden to the front early before shifting one back to 3rd just behind the leaders, given reminders approaching home turn, fought on steadily to reach 2nd briefly over 100 metres out.
Travelled wide in prominent position in early stages, pushed forward 3-wide without cover to 3rd about 1L back rounding home bend, faded gradually inside final 200 metres.
Ridden to be up with the pace after moderate start, shared the lead until narrowly headed on straightening, faded gradually under pressure.
Ridden early to obtain rails run, drifted 2L back to 5th passing the 800 metres, just behind the leaders entering home straight and baulked early on, one-paced inside final 200 metres.
Moderate start, niggled along in forward of midfield, some 4L back in joint 6th rounding home bend and into straight, dropped out tamely.
Began fairly settling in rear of midfield on the rail, shuffled back towards the rear 800 metres out, switched wide for a run entering home straight, found nothing.
Sluggish trailing the field most of the way despite ridden along, never seen with a chance.
Sluggish at start and soon dropped well behind, yielded further ground on straightening. (Mucus)
Moderate start and ridden along, improved steadily to 3-wide in midfield, gave ground noticeably on home bend. (Lame next day and soft palate intermittent displacement)
From draw 12 steadied and shifted across behind runners early stages, moved up to race behind midfield home turn, gave generous response final 250M, led passing 100M.
Unable to cross from draw 11, raced 3-wide in a midfield position, picked up well to challenge for the lead mid-straight, out-battled by winner final 150M.
Crowded for room at start, restrained in a rearward position, held up for a while early straight, responded well final 300M to claim 3rd just in time.
Always prominent, wide no cover chasing leaders, vied for lead from 400M, led briefly mid-straight, outpaced final stages.
Slow to begin, recovered to be chasing leaders along the fence, fought on steadily final 350M, held by leaders.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled 3-wide behind midfield, wide into straight, stayed on without threatening over final 400M.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, gave limited response on straightening, well held by leaders final 200M.
Chased leaders, unable to quicken under pressure turning in, ran home same pace.
Positive ridden, shared lead on inside, battled on early straight, gave ground over final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Dropped back from wide draw, settled at the rear 5Ls off the pace, failed to finish off, never in the picture.
Driven forward to be racing outside leader, weakened passing 350M, dropped away rapidly.
Outpaced, dropped back to race in last, didn't respond on straightening. Poor effort.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back, a bit closer on turn, angled out early in straight, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 250M, closed off well to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, wider turning in, finished off well to take a place without threatening.

Slightly slow out, raced towards rear on the inside, angled out after passing 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, no clear running early in straight, finished off strongly thereafter to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 6 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, found daylight 300M, made some progress thereafter.
Began smartly, raced 2 wide better than midfield, similar position on turn, angled out after passing 500M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at tail on rail, commenced move after passing 600M, still 6 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, challenged by rival from 650M, kept on well early in straight, peaked and headed 200M, weakened final 100M.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced in 2nd, 2 wide, challenged the leader from 650M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, commenced move after passing 600M, 4 to 5 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back, a bit closer on turn, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Began fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from gate 1, raced better than midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final 250M.

Began fairly from a tricky gate, trapped very wide in midfield early, moved a bit closer after passing 1200M, but still 3 wide with no cover, hard ridden from 500M, only showed limited response, weakened early in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, similar position on turn, took the lead 300M, headed narrowly near 150M, rallied and regained lead close home.

Clean jump, raced 2 wide in midfield, a bit closer on turn, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 300M, showed very good response, took brief lead near 150M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner close home.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, there to turn, made some headway in straight to take a place, no threat to the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, improved on turn, very wide into straight, finished off well to make frame.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide slightly better than midfield, no cover throughout, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced 2 wide at rear, difficult to settle in the early stages, 4 lengths or so back turning in, no clear running early in straight, cleared 250M, made little progress thereafter.
Began only fairly, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, cleared 200M, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 5 to 6 lengths back on turn, angled out early in straight, made good progress final 200M.
Jumped well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, saved ground on turn, no clear run early in straight, cleared 150M, finished off evenly.
Made contact shortly after start, raced in midfield on the inside, 2 wide on turn, showed limited response in straight, weakened final 50M.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the early lead, headed 1000M, sat right behind the leader on turn, showed some response early in straight, peaked 200M, weakened thereafter.
Shifted in at start and made contact, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3 wide from 500M, failed to make any progress in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently but wide, took the lead 1000M, found rail near 800M, led by a length on turn, peaked and headed 300M, weakened final furlong.

Made contact at start, raced slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back, found rail near 1050M, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 50M, kept on well to hold off the challenger late.
Away with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground on turn, finished off very strongly, just beaten by a narrow margin. (See Racing Incidents.)
Began smartly, sent forward to take the lead, found rail 1050M, easy lead on turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the first two final 50M.
Moderately away form a wide draw, raced behind midfield on the outside, inconvenienced near 1300M, commenced move after passing 450M, made some headway in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the home run without threatening.
Shifted out at start and made contact, positioned on rail in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off evenly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail, 8 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield on the inside, angled out after passing 450M, very wide turning in, made little progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Crowded start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, weakened final 150M.
Crowded start, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, there to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong. (See Racing Incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position on turn, weakened early in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield along the rails, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Pushed to take rail and lead, hung on well until 150M overhauled.
Slow away, at back, along the fence, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed to obtain box seat, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 2 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased back, 2 wide, never improved.
Pressed forward, sat 2 wide, raced keenly, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, moved forward 800M, weakened 200M.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield, no progress.
Never competitive.
Pushed early to keep up in front of midfield, trapped 3 wide, emptied 500M.
Settled outside the lead, asked for effort passing 400M, quickened near 50M to score.
Niggled along to take lead, placed pressure passing 300M, responded solidly in the straight.
Took box seat with nice early speed, worked home solidly when placed pressure.
Raced in front of midfield, niggled from passing 700M, worked home well.
Slow out, raced towards rear on rail, asked for effort passing 450M, made up some nice late ground.
Settled midfield on rail, lay in in the straight, worked home well.
Near 1100M was bumped and became unbalanced, then was checked when crowded for room, raced behind midfield, widest on straightening, finished one-paced.
Travelled behind midfield on rail, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, gave ground passing 50M.
Raced keenly when being steadied in early stages, settled midfield, limited response in the straight.
Taken back at start, raced at rear, no response when asked for effort.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, weakened in the straight.
Began awkwardly and taken back, raced ungenerously in early and middle stages, never in it.
Enjoyed a good run 1,1 throughout. Cornered just over a length form lead before closing hard in final 100m to strike lead in final stride.
Showed speed after start to assume lead after first 100m. Continued in lead on straightening, continued a length clear at the 150m before caught by winner in final stride.
Began fastest before racing on leaders back. Cornered only a length behind before finishing well to hold third, only half length behind on line.

Steadied & shifted back after start before settling second last on rail. Continued in second half, moved away from rail on cornering before finishing strongly between runners in final furlong to be beaten just over a length.

Raced in midfield but left wide & without cover from the 800m. Moved closer to lead approaching half-way when continuing wide before peaking on effort at the 150m. Not beaten far & was ok considering wide passage throughout.

Ridden forward from outside gate before coming across to race outside the leader from the 800m. Continued second but dropped off leader who raced clear before emptying out at the 100m. Steadied late & wasn't beaten far.

Began awkwardly & lost ground before hard ridden to improve to midfield. Raced keenly & steadied when close to heels in middle stages. Angled back to the inside on straightening before finishing fairly in late stages.
Began well but drifted back to midfield when racing 3 wide with cover throughout. Entered last section over 4L from lead before finishing evenly in straight to hold midfield position on line.

Had no speed early but held position in midfield position on rail throughout. Entered last section 3.5L from lead, unbalanced & lost some ground on cornering when continuing on inside before making no improvement thereafter.

Raced very wide without cover in first half before steadying & shifting back to second last passing the 600m. Continued three wide with cover entering last section, 5.5L from lead before being unable to improve in straight.

Slightly slow to begin before racing third last after start. Continued in second half, between runners, 5L from lead entering last section before failing to make any headway in straight & finishing second last.
Shifted back behind runners after start & raced at tail. Continued a clear last, 6.5L from lead entering last section, before failing to pass any rivals in dash to line.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide slightly better than midfield, 3 lengths or so back on turn, finished off strongly to score. (Rider dropped whip 200M.)

Made contact at start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, showed very good response in straight, hit the front 100M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late. (Lame right front leg.)
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, saved ground on turn, made very good progress in straight to take a place.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced towards rear, 6 lengths or so back, same margin back on turn, finished off strongly to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Made contact at start, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length on turn, kept on well early in straight, peaked 150M, headed 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, raced at rear, 7 lengths back, same margin back on turn, made some headway in straight.
Jumped well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in midfield, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide better than midfield, wider turning in, showed some response early in straight, peaked 150M, weakened thereafter.
Out in line, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, there to turn, one-paced in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail, still well back on turn, showed limited response in straight.
Away with them, raced 2 wide slightly behind midfield, there to turn, failed to make any progress in straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently but 3 wide early, 2 wide from 750M, peaked on turn, weakened early in straight, checked off heels 200M, eased thereafter. (Blood in trachea.)
Sent forward, along the rail initially, 2 wide after 500M, kept on going to the line and score.
Settled to race in front of midfield, along the rail, ran on well in the straight to take 2nd.
Settled in midfield, along the rail, kept going and ran on nicely for 3rd, finished 2-3/4L behind.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, checked near 150M and ran on only fairly thereafter.
Raced in midfield, 2 wide, continued on steadily to the line.
Slow to begin, at rear, along the rail, improved steadily to the line. (See Incident Report)
Raced in front of midfield, 2 wide, pretty one paced.
Raced in behind midfield, along the rail, found nothing after 200M.
At rear, along the rail, was one pace.
Sat one-out one-back, in the Straight lost ground.
Sent forward and took lead, found nothing in the Straight (Lame both hind, see incident report)
At rear and detached, along the rail, did not improve in the straight.

Driven from the widest gate to soon take up running, set steady pace after obtaining rails run passing the 1100 metres, went over 1L clear under pressure early in straight, just defied late challenges close to home.

Moderate start, showed natural speed to obtain prominent position on the rail, steadied and lost position when pace slackened early in back straight, switched off rails for a run upon straightening, ran on quite well to just fail.

Ridden forward from a poor draw to travel wide in 2L 3rd, closer when pace slackened early in back straight, obtained cover one-out-one-back over 650 metres out, came under pressure wide into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.

Blundered at start, soon taken across in rear for rails run, shifted 3-wide when 8th in the slow pace passing the 900 metres, swung the widest turning for home, finished off the race well down the centre of the track.

Broke well from the middle gate, settled just behind race leader travelling keenly when pace slackened early in back straight, regained momentum for 3rd rounding home bend, fought on steadily under pressure in straight.
Settled in midfield on the rail, gradually drifted backward to last by 800 metres, commenced move and saved ground making home turn, switched out for a run over 200 metres out, nearest at finish

Began from a low draw, wide in midfield when shifted back for cover on first turn, headway to reach 4th briefly 800 metres out, drifted back to midfield on home bend and wide into straight, make late impression closing stages.

Travelled wide without cover in last few from a wide gate, came forward from the 1000 metres to join race leader 800 metres out, came under pressure to hold place rounding home bend, faded steadily after straightening.
Awkward and lost position shortly after start but soon recovered to midfield, remained similar into home straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in last few, trailed the field into home straight, never nearer. (Continuous displacement of soft palate)
Held up in midfield along the fence, soon into clear on straightening, quickened to take lead near 150M, continued on well final stages.
Dropped back from wide draw, settled down near last 5Ls off the pace, closed off fastest in straight but readily held by winner.
Jumped on terms, reserved behind midfield, ran on well final 300M to take 3rd.
Settled behind mid-division, into clear top of straight, stayed on moderately, got up for 4th near line.
Strode forward, crossed to the lead near 800M, stuck to task well early straight, caught near 100M, lost several places near the line.
From draw 1 ridden along to track leader, fought on same pace in straight, no impression final 200M.
Chased leaders, in 4th spot home turn, responded fairly on straightening, no threat final 150M.
Always prominent, moved up to 2nd spot passing 800M, held ground early straight before fading final 200M.
From draw 11 unable to get closer than 3-wide, behind mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace home turn, fought on same pace to the line. No threat to leaders.
Taken back from draw 12, settled last 6Ls off the pace, taken widest on straightening, responded fairly, never dangerous.
Raced in mid-division along the 3-path, no cover from 800M, lacked a finishing response entering straight, weakened final 200M.
Held up behind midfield early stages, checked 700M and shuffled back to last, failed to run on in straight, eased when no chance.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, a length or so back, there to turn, finished off strongly to score.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in midfield, hard ridden after passing 400M, 3 wide turning in, finished off strongly to take 2nd, just narrowly beaten.
Began well from gate 1, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight, just unable to hold off the first two late.
Jumped with them, positioned 4 lengths behind the leader on rail, shifted out off heels near 450M, made good progress in straight to make frame, no threat to the first few.
Commenced well, positioned 1-1/2L behind the leader on rail, crowded and badly unbalanced near 450M, showed some response early in straight, peaked 100M, no clear run close home.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back on turn, made good progress in straight without threatening.
Shifted in at start and made contact, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back turning in, made some headway in straight.
Crowded out start, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths back on turn, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths back on turn, finished off evenly.

Jumped well from gate 11, raced in midfield on the outside, slightly taken back after entering the back straight, found a 2 wide spot near 750M, commenced move 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned on rail in midfield, severely checked near 450M, peaked early in straight, weakened thereafter.
Moderately away, raced behind midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, very wide turning in, weakened gradually in straight.

Began well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 500M, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, bumped early in straight, finished off very strongly thereafter to take 2nd, always held.
Began well from gate 1, positioned on rail in midfield, moved a bit closer along the rail on turn, angled out 500M, hit the front 200M, peaked and headed 100M, stayed on to take a place.
Bumped start, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, hard ridden after passing 500M, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Taken back to race at rear on the inside, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, made some headway in straight.

Began well, took the early lead, headed 1300M, a length behind the leader in the middle stages, moved closer after passing 700M, hit the front 500M, peaked early in straight, headed 200M, weakened final 150M.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide better than midfield, carried wider after passing 500M, peaked early in straight, weakened final 300M.
Crowded at start, raced behind midfield on the inside, saved ground to turn, peaked early in straight, weakened inside final furlong.
Bumped start, raced prominently, 2 wide, took the lead after passing 1300M, led by a length in the middle stages, peaked and headed near 500M, weakened final furlong.
Hard ridden early, midfield along the fence, made steady ground 300M to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to rear, blocked most straight, made good ground.
Eased back, 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail and lead, emptied 150M.
In front of midfield, 2 wide, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, behind midfield, made ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, weakened 200M.
Slow away, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on fairly.
Eased back, on the fence, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, out of fuel 300M.
Eased back, 2 wide, on heels 300M, no progress.
Pushed early, bumped 300M, then emptied.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Settled in handy position, quickened passing 200M, scored unchallenged by 4-3/4L.
Taken back at start, raced towards rear, asked for effort near 400M, gained some nice ground passing 200M.
Taken back at start, raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, improved passing 450M, wide on straightening, made up some nice late ground.
Led with nice early speed, placed pressure on straightening, in the straight hung out and difficult to ride, finished well.
Settled in front of midfield on rail, placed pressure passing 700M, kept on rail rounding the Home Turn, finished one-paced.
Slow out, raced at back, widest on straightening, gained some ground in the straight.
Raced behind the lead, placed pressure near 450M, worked home one-paced.
Travelled midfield, tried to improve passing 450M, finished one-paced.
After start lost ground when buffeted between runners, settled midfield on rail, near 300M rider dropped his left rein, limited response when asked for effort.
Taken back at start, raced at tail on rail, limited response in the straight.
Settled midfield, wide and without cover for the majority of the race, weakened passing 200M.
Travelled midfield, wide and without cover for the majority of the race, faded out passing 250M.
In the early stages lost its right front plate, raced behind midfield, weakened passing 200M.
Taken back at start, placed pressure but no response.

Ridden forward after the start before steadying & being caught 3 wide with cover in midfield. Moved 4 wide to improve from the 600m, sprinted to lead at 250m, drew away under no riding before being eased late. Impressive win.
Stride forward before getting good run 1,1 throughout. Dashed to second at the 150m before closing off well late behind impressive winner. Clear of third.
Raced in midfield on the rail throughout. Continued on the inside on straightening when 3L form lead before working home steadily in late stages to snare third on the line.
Shifted behind runners & settled third last away from rail. Ridden along on straightening when 6L from lead before shifting wider & making some late ground when running on to snare forth on line.

Checked & lost ground after start & consequently raced 4th last on rail. Continued in second half when 4L behind entering last section, held up until passing the 250m before closing off steadily in late stages.
Began well before being steadied & racing on leaders back throughout. Entered last section 2L from lead before weakening a few lengths in straight to midfield.
Slow to begin before being steadied away from heels before improving after start to race in midfield on rail. Passed a few in the straight when finishing off steadily in late stages to midfield.
Showed good speed to lead after the start. Headed by winner at the 250m before weakening in last furlong.

Inconvenienced after the start before improving to midfield but racing 3 wide with cover for the majority. Shifted to be the widest runner on straightening when just over 4L from lead before making no headway in straight.
Had good position in midfield between runners throughout. Eased wider on cornering before weakening in last 250m. (Bled).
Not bustled after the start & was allowed to drift back to second last after the start. Failed to run on in the straight & was well beaten.
Steadied & shifted back to the tail after the start. Continued at the tail on straightening when over 7L from the lead before making no headway in the run home.
Hard ridden after the start before racing outside the leader. Hard ridden on straightening before weakening badly in the final 300m.
Ridden forward after the start before improving to race 3 wide without cover outside the leading pair. Began yielding ground from the 600m & tailed out to be distant last. (Must trial).
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, moved a bit closer in the middle stages, showed very good response after turning in, hit the front 200M, kept on very strongly to the line.
Out in line, raced 3 wide better than midfield, no cover throughout, moved closer on turn, took the lead 250M, peaked and headed 200M, weakened close home, finished 2nd.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 2 wide towards rear, commenced move after passing 900M, 4 to 5 lengths back on turn, very wide into straight, made good progress in the run home to take a place.
Began well from gate 1, raced at rear on the inside, 7 lengths or so back, same margin back in the middle stages, very wide turning in, finished off strongly to make frame without threatening.
Commenced well, raced 2 wide better than midfield, found rail 450M, 2 lengths back turning in, peaked early in straight, ran on evenly to the line.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, commenced move after passing 450M, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail early, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 6 lengths or so back on turn, very wide into straight, finished off evenly.
Bumped shortly after start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning in, showed limited response early in straight, no extra final furlong. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well, positioned on rail in midfield, angled out after passing 400M, showed limited response early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Began well, positioned 2 wide, a length or so back, moved closer after passing 800M, took the lead 650M, peaked early in straight, headed 250M, weakened thereafter. (See Racing Incidents.)
Average to begin, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, 8 lengths back turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, positioned 1 to 2 lengths behind the leader on the inside, angled out 500M, peaked turning in, kept on evenly early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Moderately away, sent forward to take the lead, led by a length, peaked and headed 650M, weakened thereafter, eased early in straight.
At rear, along the rail, swung wide on Straightening, made significant ground and score.
At rear, 3 wide but with cover, improved and battled on to the line, just caught in the last 20M.
Raced in behind midfield, 3 wide but with cover, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Rolled forward and raced in front of midfield, 3 wide no cover, ran on strongly in the Straight and only flattened in the last 30M.
Raced in behind midfield, 2 wide, improved ground steadily to the line.
Sent forward and raced next to the leader, 2 wide, stayed on but headed in the last 100M.
At rear, 2 wide, improved ground steadily to the line.
At rear, 2 wide, only one paced to the line.
Raced in midfield, along the rail, pretty one paced.
Settled in midfield, 2 wide, weakened in the last 150M.
At rear, wide no cover, nothing in the Straight.
Sent forward, 2 wide initially, along the rail after 550M, lost ground in the Straight.
Raced in front of midfield, along the rail, did not feature.
Sent forward and took lead initially, in the Straight lost ground abruptly. Finished tailed out, must trial. (Blood in trachea.)

Broke well settling within 3L of pace in 5th, became slightly further back rounding home bend, commenced move to be closer up and 4-wide into straight, quickened well to assert authority over 200 metres out, won cosily.

Ridden forward for one back position, became 3rd over 1000 metres out and remained 2 wide home bend, in similar position entering straight, held some chance under pressure until outsprinted by the winner over 200 metres out.

Soon obtained rails run after moderate start, pulled his way forward to within 3L of steadying pace in 6th 1000 metres out, remained keen home bend and on heels after straightening, found daylight 200 metres out and ran on.
Slightly slow out from a wide gate settling towards the rear on the rail, angled out for a run on straightening obtaining clear run 350 metres out, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began well before taken back to midfield 3-wide without cover, went wider entering home straight, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.

Settled in midfield in 7th or 8th, travelling keenly when checked from heels and lost about a length over 1000 metres out, went wide for a run entering straight, fought on steadily for a nice impression closing stages.

Settled wide towards the rear from the widest gate, drifted further back approaching home bend travelling wide, baulked for a run after straightening and did not find much room until too late in closing stages, not fully tested.

Settled behind midfield mainly in 10th, steadied from heels and lost some 2L passing the 1000 metres, renewed effort approaching home straight and went very wide on the turn, fought on steadily without threatening.
Taken well back from a wide gate, trailed the field most of the way to home straight, saved ground on the inside turning in, did not find much room until too late after the 150 metres.

Broke well from a wide draw, soon taken back to 3rd but remained wide without cover, allowed to make rapid progress from the 1100 metres to lead coming onto home bend, led until overhauled inside final 250 metres.

Allowed to drift backward early and soon obtained rails run, improved to rear of midfield in 9th over 1000 metres out, snuck up on rails to within 3L of pace upon straightening, found no extra inside final 300 metres.
Taken back to the rear from a wide gate, commenced move and went widest rounding home bend, unable to quicken down the centre of home straight.

Began fairly, soon picked up to 4th within striking distance along the rails, awkwardly placed on heels over 1000 metres out, in similar position turning into home straight, weakened under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Driven hard to lead and crossed for rails run over 1200 metres out, headed approaching the 1000 metres travelling some 2L back in 2nd around home bend, soon weakened after straightening.
Reserved near the rear, 6Ls off the pace middle stages, came home widest, stayed on strongly to lead near 50M. Won going away.
Never far off from leaders, in 5th spot halfway, responded well on straightening and came through to lead briefly near 100M, not pace of winner late stages.
Took up early running, set slow pace until taken on by rival passing 1300M, fought on well early straight, headed near 100M, held on for 3rd from pursuing rivals.
Lost ground at the start, reserved at the rear 7-8Ls behind leader, stayed on moderately final 400M for non-threatening 4th.
Chased leaders along the fence, took time to muster speed on straightening, progressed steadily over final 150M.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, made his move near 600M, quickened well early straight to be challenging for the lead, one paced final 150M.
Taken across behind runners, settled near last 6Ls off leader back straight, moved out to commence his run near 600M, stayed on mildly for 7th but not far behind the placegetters.
Travelled in midfield, responded mildly in straight, always held by leaders.
Positively ridden, tracked leader 2-wide, commenced to race keenly back-straight and would not relax, chased hard early straight, no extra 200M. (Vet : made breathing noise on returning / Mucus.)
Blundered at the start, caught 3-wde no cover midfield, rolled forward 1500M to obtain a position closer to rail, battled on same pace turning in, faded from 250M.
Moderately away, raced in midfield on the outside, no cover throughout, 4 lengths back on turn, finished off very strongly to score.
Bumped start, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Taken back from gate 10, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position on turn, made good progress in straight to take a place. (Lame left front leg next day morning.)
Average to begin, raced 2 wide towards rear, found rail near 600M, 7 lengths back turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame without threatening.
Began well, positioned on rail slightly better than midfield, 4 lengths or so back, commenced move after passing 500M, made minor progress in straight.
Taken back from gate 13, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 to 8 lengths back, very wide turning in, made some progress in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground on turn, hard ridden after passing 450M, only showed limited response, ran on evenly to the line.
Bumped start, raced better than midfield on the outside, moved a bit closer after entering the back straight, 2-1/2L back on turn, peaked early in straight, weakened final furlong.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, there to turn, weakened gradually in straight.
Began fairly, raced at rear throughout, never a threat.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide behind midfield, wider turning in, failed to make any progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Began smartly from gate 1, positioned on rail slightly behind midfield, saved ground on turn, weakened early in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 away from the stands' rail, 3/4L back, hit the front 400M, kept on very strongly to the line, won by 2-1/4L.
Began well, positioned 2 away from the stands' rail, 2 lengths or so back, made good progress final 300M to take 2nd, no threat to the winner.
Bumped start, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on the middle track, raced tight near 350M, finished off strongly to take a place, just missed 2nd on line.
Commenced well from gate 14, raced in midfield on the stands' rail, made some progress final 400M to make frame.
Began fairly, sent forward to race prominently, 3 away from the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 350M, only showed limited response, weakened gradually final 100M.
Began awkwardly and made contact, raced prominently on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 450M, showed limited response, weakened final 100M.
Bumped start, raced towards rear on the middle track, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Slowly away, raced at rear on the stands' side, hard ridden after passing 400M, finished off evenly.
Began only fairly, raced in midfield, nearer to the middle track, raced tight near 350M, weakened gradually final furlong.
Commenced well, raced in midfield on the middle track, checked near 500M, failed to make any progress final 400M.
Away with them, raced at rear on the stands' rail, hard ridden after passing 450M, but only showed limited response, one-paced to the line.
Made contact at start, raced prominently on the stands' side, ridden from 450M, showed limited response, blocked 350M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, peaked and headed 400M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Average to begin, raced at rear in the middle of the track, weakened final 400M.

Raced worse than midfield on rail, over 6L from the lead passing the 800m. Made continual headway in straight, moved away from rail at 300m before squeezing between runners in late stages to snare narrow lead on line.

Raced prominently before getting good position 1,1 from the 850m. Eased 3 wide on corner, entered last section 3L from lead before making continual ground to share lead at the 50m mark before being caught by winner on wire.

Shared lead momentarily after start before being crossed & racing on leaders back for majority. Moved over leaders heals on straightening, dashed up to take lead at 150m mark before being over-run late. Not ridden out late.

Began well before being allowed to drift back before shifting across to midfield. Shifted into clear running entering last section when 4.5L from lead before closing strongly in last 250m to be beaten under a length on line.

Shifted across to midfield but was left 3 wide without cover from the 900m. Improved position around field when pace slowed in middle stages, forced the widest runner on turn before making steady late ground, close behind.

Improved after the start before striding to lead near the 1200m & crossing to rail near the 900m. Raced nearly 2L clear in front entering last section before being joined at the 150m. Hampered late & wasn't beaten far.

Obtained good position in midfield on the rail, only 2.5L form the lead approaching the 800m. Continued along the rail on straightening when 3L from the lead before weakening out poorly in final 250m.

Steadied after start before shifting across to race just worse than midfield. Ridden along to improve passing 500m, cornered the widest runner when 5L behind before passing a few when running on fairly to midfield.
Hard ridden after the start to hold position at the rear. Continued near the tail when 7L from the lead on straightening before passing only one or two tiring runners in late stages. Beaten over 5L.

Drifted back after the start before settling rearward. Relegated to last near the 800m when shifting out. Continued a clear last, over 8L from lead on straightening, passed a few tiring runners late, never likely.

Raced in midfield on rail throughout, around 4L from lead passing the 800m. Attempted to move away from rail on straightening before being checked & losing ground before making no headway thereafter. Well beaten.
Shifted out at the start before drifting back & racing third last, 7.5L from the lead at the 800m. Continued well back entering the straight before making no headway & being well beaten.

Showed speed to share early lead when racing wide before steadying & drifting back to midfield. Eased 3 wide passing the 500m, continued within 3L before peaking at 300m & weakening sharply in last furlong. (Bled).

Improved position when racing wide after the start before eventually getting outside the leader near the 800m. Hard ridden prior to straightening before weakening significantly to long last. (Lame, must trial).
